name: Aarin
meetText: Meet Aarin! Did you know that she's helping her friends publish their very own cookbook? Boyer cooks the food, Aarin writes the captions, and her BFF Selly is the food photographer! The best part? They get to test all the yummy recipes after! Grab a fork! They'd love to share!

name: Abbitt
meetText: Abbitt is a marine biologist helping regrow coral reefs in his area. He's the perfect scientist for the job since he can hold his breath underwater for several minutes! Abbitt knows the health of all coral reefs is important for 'Mallows everywhere, and hopes you'll join his team on the next reef dive!

name: Abby
meetText: Meet Abby. This water enthusiast takes her passion to the next level as the Head Lifeguard at a waterpark! Monitoring slides and ensuring Squishmallows' safety is kind of Abby's thing. At closing time, Abby lets loose and slips down her favorite slide: The Sea Creature Funnel!

name: Abdul
meetText: Abdul just got back from a five month archaeological dig in the dessert! This paleontologist was researching a newly discovered bone thought to be an ancient dinosaur. Back in the classroom, Abdul teaches his students everything he learned. Want to see his slideshow presentation?

name: Abe
meetText: Say hello to Abe. He’s the top student in his class and is studying hard to become a teacher! His favorite subjects are English and History, but he also loves to do science experiments in his spare time! Want to try out a new experiment with Abe?

name: Abel
meetText: Abel wrote a short story! It's the story of a young manatee taking bass lessons and performing in spring recitals. His own fond memories of these parties make the story so real. Abel just submitted his story to a music magazine—he'll mail you a copy when it prints!

name: Abena
meetText: While her friends Oz and Afiyah love to be in the spotlight, Abena is quite shy. She prefers giving direction from the sidelines and making sure everything is ready behind the curtains. Abena is very organized and keeps her friends on schedule wherever they go.

name: Abilene
meetText: Abilene is a creative director who loves to have fun. She picks a new game for her team to play each month to get their creative juices flowing. her dream is to work for a game company and play games all day! What game should she try next?

name: Ace
meetText: Version 1: Lights, camera, action! Need someone to make you laugh? Get to know Ace! He is ready to be your next big thing. Ace is the actor- extraordinaire born on January 4th. Where is his favorite place to be? The stage of course! He isn’t shy if you couldn’t tell. Ace wants to one day write and direct his own film.

name: Adabelle
meetText: Meet Adabelle. She loves dogs, yoga, and meeting new people! She wants to open a dog-friendly yoga studio called Downward Dog! Will you join her pup-tastic yoga class?

name: Addison
meetText: Addison seeks travel wherever she goes. She is constantly learning new languages, so that she can make friends across the globe! Where will your next adventure be with Addison?

name: Adela
meetText: Got a toothache? Have no fear--Adela the dentist has arrived to the rescue! She helps remove tooth decay, fills cavities, and repair fractured tooth. Adela even double checks your enamel strength. Go home feeling well cared for, and with minty fresh breath, too!

name: Adelaide
meetText: Meet Adelaide. This is one sassy 'Mallow who LOVES all things fashion. She is known for having a great sense of style and speaking her mind, she's got enough sass for all eight tentacles! If you need a second opinion, give her a call!

name: Adelle
meetText: Meet Adelle. This far out ‘Mallow loves her film camera, shopping for vintage thrifted clothing and listening to rock! She loves doing groovy photo shoots with her friends and putting them on her fashion blog! Want to join? She’d love to style you!

name: Adila
meetText: Adila is a bit nervous around new people, but she's trying to be brave and speak in front of others by joining the debate team. Adila's secret advantage is that she is a great writer so words come to her naturally. Would you help her practice for her first big debate?

name: Adin
meetText: Meet Adin. He loves black and white movies, thrift shopping and even owns his own video store. Are you ready to go back in time with Adin?

name: Adrian
meetText: Meet Adrian. He wants to be a radio DJ when he grows up. He loves eclectic music from all around the world! There’s nothing he loves more than discovering a new song he’s never heard before and then sharing it with his friends. Got a song you love? Share it with Adrian!

name: Adrie
meetText: Say hey to Adrie! Adrie tours all over the globe with her flute! Since she's often on the move, Adrie writes postcards to all her closest 'Mallows friends. She always makes sure to write them with pretty colors and adds lots of stickers! Want to be pen pals with Adrie?

name: Afiyah
meetText: Meet Afiyah. She loves to sing and dance along with Oz; they make a great dancing duo. Afiyah has been dancing most of her life and says that dancing is like the air she needs to breathe. Between her talent and her determination, she is one show-stopping succulent.

name: Aicha
meetText: Meet Aicha. She is the strongest swimmer in the ocean and the prettiest shell on the beach. When she’s not soaking in the sun, she’s diving into the water to save lives. Whenever Aicha is around, you can guarantee a smile and a fun day in the sun.

name: Aiden
meetText: Whos' ready to change the world? Aiden, this thoughtful mallow tries to think about everyone around them and how to be fair. Even though he's not quite perfect, he hopes he can make a difference.

name: Aika
meetText: Aika is a runner who loves the outdoors. She loves to race along the beach or try a new trail in the mountains. She is fast and loves healthy competition. When it's time for a break, she loves to curl up in the sand and soak up some sun. Do you want to race?

name: Aimee
meetText: This chick has got quite the resume! From clubs to competitions to shows and more, Aimee is a busy bee both on and off the floor. In her spare time she plans events that she isn't even a part of and hopes to be in charge of red carpet events someday.

name: Aina
meetText: Aina is the queen of DIY and loves to create! She especially enjoys baking and shares her delicious confections with the people she loves most. When she grows up, she wants to have a cooking show but also show off her cool DIY designs. Do you want to create with Aina?

name: Ainhoca
meetText: Do you hear a whistle? That's Ainhoca stopping traffic to let little 'Mallows cross the street to on their way to school. Ainhoca is a crossing guard at her local elementary school and uses her powerful tail to block cars, or move students to the other side of the road!

name: Aja
meetText: Step into the tiny world of Aja, she is one crafty alicorn! Aja’s love for crafts has inspired her to build a tiny world. She makes furniture and loves to show them to her friends. Do you want to see the world she’s building?

name: Akina
meetText: Green and blue are Akina's favorite colors and she loves to show them off with brightly colored shoes. Because she loves shoes so much, Akina has a shoe collection like no other. From vintage treasures to one-of-a-kind creations, she has a story for almost every pair!

name: Aksel
meetText: Aksel just started his empanada business. He's using a family recipe with added spicy sauce. Aksel takes orders over phone and cooks everything from scratch in his kitchen- he'll even deliver it to you personally! What kind of empanada can Aksel make for you?

name: Alan
meetText: Alan is a talented woodworker, and loves coming up with unique gifts that he crafts by hand for all his family and friends. We're excited to see what he comes up with for this Valentine's Day!

name: Alandy
meetText: Polka dots and cars are two of Alandy's favorite things. Alandy loves going to car shows and packs a polka dot picnic for lunch. When it comes to music, the classics are what Alandy loves the most. Maybe one day you can ride in Alandy's polka dot cruiser!

name: Alba
meetText: Alba believes that simple things in life are best. Like peanut butter sandwiches with crusty bread--that's it! Nothing more, nothing less. Alba packs all her school lunches herself and makes sure to always use reusable containers or recyclable packaging.

name: Albinia
meetText: Meet Albinia. She has vitiligo and loves that her body is beautiful, marble canvas. She is obsessed with the ocean! Albinia loves going to the beach to hear the waves crash and watch the stars at night, Would you like to join her?

name: Aldea
meetText: Meet Aldea. This earthy mama is a holistic healer. She’s a certified Reiki massage therapist and she loves how much it heals. Aldea also knows all about plants and their healing property. Have a headache? She has the perfect essential oil for you!

name: Alder
meetText: Alder thinks there's nothing like the great outdoors. That's why she goes camping as often as she can - even in her backyard! Alder always brings extra pillows to make her tent super comfy. Roll out your sleeping bag and get ready to go glamping with Alder!

name: Aldous
meetText: Aldous quotes his favorite cowboy movies every chance he gets. He hopes you will catch the reference! Aldous dreams of owning his own ranch one day, so he can make and star in cowboy movies of his own. He's got his camera ready and reckons you'd make a great co-star.

name: Aldron
meetText: Meet Aldron. He gets a bad rap. He looks a little scary, but he's a total sweetheart. When he's not working at his coffee shop making extra sweet pumpkin spice lattes, he volunteers with his friend Benti at an animal shelter and bottle feeds the baby kittens!

name: Ale
meetText: Ale likes to celebrate Valentine's day with her friends, being pampered with manis and pedis. When they're done, they get to have a tea party followed by a photo shoot!

name: Alec
meetText: Alec buries a little treasure box time capsule for himself every five years! He gathers special knick knacks, notes to his future self, and even snacks! The snacks don't usually survive - but the memories do! Want to make a time capsule with Alec?

name: Alejandra
meetText: Alejandra loves to play games and go to the beach. If you can't find her winning at card games or reading a book at the beach you might need to check again! She's always ready to try a new game with her friends.

name: Aleka
meetText: Meet Aleka. She started making her own candles, and once her friends got a whiff of the scents, they needed to have them too! Now Aleka spends all day making candles, and she loves to create new scents for her friends. Be sure to catch her next candle release!

name: Alessi
meetText: Alessi is a sleepy fox, she loves to nap because her bed is as soft as a cloud! When she's not napping, you can find her sipping on iced coffee and getting ready for her next class. She teaches gym and also goes to night school to become a nurse.

name: Alex
meetText: Alex practices karate moves every day in his backyard. He's getting ready to be a stunt-dog in superhero movies! First, he copies what he sees in action scenes, then adds his own flair. Once his friend Bambz introduces him to her film pals, he can prepare a demo tape!

name: Xandra
meetText: There's no Squishmallow more well traveled than Xandra! She used to be a professional scuba diver and traveled to over 50 countries before she hung up her snorkel to work in the city. Unlike her hermit neighbors, Xandra is an outgoing and friendly crab who loves to party with her friend Carlos.

name: Alexie
meetText: Meet Alexie. He's anything but a morning 'Mallow. He loves lazy mornings and sleeping in but he makes exceptions! Have an early morning project you need help with? He'll be the first to lend a helping hand. He just needs a hot cup of coffee and a warm pastry first!

name: Alfred
meetText: Meet Alfred. He stays up to date on the latest health food trends. Right now, Alfred is all about eating leafy greens! He adds them to everything from lunches to smoothies. Alfred has also discovered that roasting Brussels sprouts leads to delicious results! Want to join Alfred's health kick?

name: Aligail
meetText: Aligail helps 'Mallows with all their vacation needs! She's a longtime travel agent who loves to personalize every trip, and even prepares a special booklet of important info every 'Mallow needs while traveling. Be sure to stop by Aligail's office around a holiday - she dresses up for the occasion all week!

name: Alice
meetText: Strawberry smoothies and pineapple pizza are two of Alice's favorite things. Even though she has wings - Alice is afraid of heights! She prefers to keep both her feet on the ground, but maybe one day she will soar the skies.

name: Alita
meetText: Say hi to Alita! Want to challenge Alita to an underwater race? Alita is a super fast swimmer, and can hold her breath for five laps - she's counted! Put on your goggles and swimsuit, and hit the pool with Alita!

name: Alizeh
meetText: Meet Alizeh. This sly fox loves practical jokes and giving her friends a fright. Some of Alizeh's practical jokes involve costumes, fake bugs and silly string. She always gets permission when she records a good scare. Do you want to watch one of her compilation videos?

name: Allina
meetText: Meet Allina! She's a lifelong optimist. No matter how dark the storm clouds get, she always focuses on the bits of light peeking out from behind them! She's taking a woodworking class to learn how to make her own rocking chair so she can sit and listen to the rain from her porch.

name: Ally
meetText: Meet Ally the Axolotl! She's a total sweetheart who LOVES coffee, shopping, and being with family. There's nothing she loves more than a good clothing haul... except a perfectly planned vacation! When she's not with family, you can find her dreaming about her future job as a fashion buyer.

name: Alonzo
meetText: Alonzo is renting a party bus for his birthday weekend! He wants to spread party vibes all over town with his squad. The bus has two coolers for snacks and sodas, and every rider gets a balloon and goodie bags that Alonzo put together himself. Snap some glow sticks and jump on the bus!

name: Alten
meetText: Think you know milk? Think again! Alten is a carrot farmer with a special secret—he loves to carol! Along with his movie star sister, Arlene, Alten spends every Christmas morning regaling his neighbors with yuletide cheer and toe-tapping melodies.

name: Althea
meetText: Excuse Althea if she seems a little sleepy. She has insomnia which keeps her up at night when she would much rather be sleeping! She's tried everything, exercise, herbal tea, even counting sheep! But she makes up for it in the daytime with cat naps and lots of coffee!

name: Altman
meetText: Eight arms, you're in! Altman is an invaluable outfielder for his company's after-work baseball team. With suction cups for catching and slippery ink for sliding, it's no wonder this gigantically talented squid is a seven-time MVP.

name: Alva
meetText: Alva stumbles into wacky situations everywhere she goes. Some memorable experiences include the time she found the end of a rainbow, the summer she discovered a secret treasure map, and when she saw a ghost in her bathtub on Halloween! Alva can’t explain the moments — she’s just a ‘Mallow with good timing.

name: Alyssa
meetText: Alyssa is a coffee shop barista who loves bringing smiles to customers faces by whipping up delicious coffee creations. She's an animal lover and wants to become a vet tech one day. Make sure you try her special mallow mocha!

name: Amal
meetText: Tonight Amal debuts her latest fall fashion collection! Be prepared to see lots of fun prints and fluffy fabrics, as this 'Mallow is known for blending comfort and style in all her designs. Want to come to the runaway show? Amal saved you a front row seat!

name: Amala
meetText: Meet Amala. She is a social butterfly and loves being a host. She is obsessed with balloons so there is a special balloon bouquet at all her events. Amala's favorite place to window shop is her local party supply store, she could spend hours planning the perfect balloon displays.

name: Amalie
meetText: Meet Amalie. She loves slithering through the jungle with her iced coffee before she starts her day. Amalie is a vegetarian chef and works hard to keep her menu tasty and intriguing, her latest menu features jackfruit with a variety of beans. Do you want to try the nacho tower?

name: Amanda
meetText: Amanda is a head baker for the Easter bunny! She makes sure all the eggs are decorated properly and any other basket goodies are ready to go.

name: Amandine
meetText: Amandine has a super exciting goal for the new year— to help at least one 'Mallow a day! Whether counseling a friend in need or volunteering at the local food bank, Amandine can't wait to lend a helping hand. After all, a little kindness goes a long way!

name: Amara
meetText: Have you met Amara? She's an expert at building snow forts and snowmen, but one of her special skills is making delicious candy! One day she wants to open up a candy shop, her first big treat might be peppermint snowballs or even peppermint and chocolate lollipops.

name: Amaro
meetText: Amaro comes from a big family. They love to laugh, talk, and make dinner together! This fall, Amaro made the brave decision to try something new and attend a college outside of town. He's going to miss his family a lot, but knows they love and support him no matter what!

name: Amelie
meetText: Meet Amelie. She loves baking and painting. First, she bakes an assortment of delicious blueberry muffins, oatmeal cookies, and chocolate cakes, then she sets them up and paints a still life! Afterward, she invites all her friends over and they eat them with tea!

name: Amiah
meetText: Are you ready for the show? It's Amiah's time to shine. She's been practicing all year for the talent show and she's ready to unveil her talent: magic! She has a special deck of cards and knows quite a few tricks. Will you pick the right card?

name: Amideus
meetText: Meet Amideus. He has Type I Diabetes and used to be very scared of finger pricks. At first, his parents took care of his blood sugar but now he does it all by himself! On weeknights, after homework, he loves playing soccer, helping cook dinner, and talking with friends.

name: Amil
meetText: Looking for a sparring partner? Amil is the mallow for you! He works at a boxing gym and helps many mallows perfect their form. When he's not correcting technique or cleaning up the locker room, he loves to sing oldies jams at the top of his lungs.

name: Amina
meetText: Meet Amina. This spunky squirrel loves to read, she almost has enough books to open her own library! Amina's favorite books are about adventures in far-away places, and some type of quest. One day she wants to go on a quest of her own!

name: Amleth
meetText: Amleth isn't shy about claiming his own space and asking for alone time. This 'Mallow doesn't have siblings and never got the hang of sharing, but with a little patience, Amleth will open up and maybe even let you sit at his lunch table. Wanna to trade juice boxes?

name: Amor
meetText: Amor means love, and that is exactly what this unicorn is all about. Though she doesn't always know how to explain her feelings, she knows no matter what you are, you deserve to be loved.

name: Analea
meetText: Volcanos and earthquakes are scary to some, but Analea has been fascinated with them since her very first earthquake! She is going to school to become a geologist and can't wait to learn more!

name: Anara
meetText: Anara invented an app for her favorite hobby-karaoke! With her app, karaoke can be sung anytime, anywhere, which is exactly why Anara came up with an idea. You never know when you might have some spare time, so why not spend it singing your favorite song!

name: Anastasia
meetText: If you need some help starting a project, Anastasia is the axolotl for you! Anastasia is a planner and likes to be prepared for everything, she keeps track of her ideas by writing lists. What can she help you with?

name: Anca
meetText: Safety first! Anca is a crossing guard and helps with the morning busses at school. Anca gets up so early, sometimes it's still dark out! Anca wears a bright green reflective vest and has matching gloves in case they need to direct any cars. Maybe one day, they can help you cross the street!

name: Andreina
meetText: Meet Andreina. She is a nurse who books her time from sun-up to sun-down. She works out almost every morning and spends a few minutes in her garden for clarity. In her free time, Andreina loves to sunbathe and entertain. She loves spending time in her beautiful rooftop garden.

name: Andres
meetText: Andres is a very silly Squishmallow, he loves practical jokes and hearing people laugh. He wants to be a comedian when he grows up, do you know any good jokes he can tell?

name: Andrew
meetText: Meet Andrew. He enjoys listening to music and going to concerts. You can often find him streaming music or waiting for news on his favorite band's tour. If you need a concert buddy, Andrew is the jackalope for you!

name: Androu
meetText: Meet Androu. Androu is a really crafty 'Mallow - he loves to whittle all kinds of different shapes and designs out of the wood! One of his favorite designs is a tiny collection of stars in the shape of his favorite constellation. Can you guess which one it is?

name: Aneira
meetText: Meet Aneira. She loves painting, working at her cafe. and singing along with her friend Henley. Aneira and Henley do almost everything together. She is working on a painting as a surprise for her friend, would you like to see it?

name: Anessa
meetText: Anessa can sew a flower crown with her eyes closed. She credits her mother and grandmother for her unique sense of fashion, and is inspired by their flowy, colorful dresses. Anessa embroiders her own dresses by hand, and tops off her ensembles with a flower crown to give it her signature look.

name: Aneta
meetText: Aneta is thrifty gal who's great at pinching pennies. Aneta's hobby is couponing and finding bargains wherever she can, so you can always ask her how to get the best deal! Want to go shopping with Aneta?

name: Angelie
meetText: Ready, set go - Angelie is on the move! She and her best friend Xenia practically live at the skate park. Angelie wants to be the first unicorn pro-skater, do you want to see some of her moves?

name: Angie
meetText: Angie loves a good fiesta, she loves going to parties and events as much as she enjoys hosting. When she hosts, she makes special themed food and drinks for her friends. Want to know some of her favorite things to make? Guacamole, peanut butter brownies, and samosas!

name: Angusan
meetText: Meet Angusan. They love late-night movie marathons with their friends. They load up on blankets, pillows and snacks! Popcorn and red licorice are two of Angusan’s favorites! When they grow up, they want to be a cinematographer and create their own movie magic!

name: Anica
meetText: Although Anica is a unicorn, she sleeps like a bear! In fact, Anica sleeps almost 16 hours a day; she sleeps more than she's actually awake! When Anica finally wakes up from her deep sleep, she's always very well-rested, energized, and ready to play with her pals.

name: Aniela
meetText: Can you feel the burn? Aniela can! This peppy pilates instructor loves helping her students find their inner— and outer— strength. With her emphasis on crunches and planks, they're bound to!

name: Anjara
meetText: Anjara runs tech for the morning news of her local TV station. She's responsible for the lights, teleprompter, and announcing when they're back on air from commercial. Anjara sure has a lot of responsibility, but this burrito is up for the challenge!

name: Anna
meetText: Anna spends a lot of time with her family and loves to read. You can almost always find her curled up with a good book and some freshly made chocolate chip cookies.

name: Anneli
meetText: Anneli is the carpool queen who plays the best tunes! She is the oldest of five siblings, so she's been zooming her friends and family around from the moment she got her driver's license. Anneli is on her way to scoop you up now!

name: Anouk
meetText: Anouk is quite the beauty queen. She has a closet filled with shoes, makeup, and accessories for almost every occasion. Her motto is 'dress for success' and she loves a bold look that stands out, especially with makeup. Her signature lip color is a berrylicious pink!

name: Anthony
meetText: Anthony is the oldest of his brothers and does his best to keep them in line. He helps them with homework, bullies, and teaches them to be smart, fun, and kind.

name: Antonella
meetText: Antonella is a baker; she makes delicious bread in the shape of a 'Mallow! She has to get up very early to bake enough for the farmers market, but sometimes she still runs out. Her latest creation is a four-cheese crust, would you like a taste?

name: Antoni
meetText: This is one creative sea turtle. Antoni loves to build things: puzzles, block towers, and model cars. He even builds things with his breakfast! Once he made a scrambled egg tower with salsa for lava and a toast drawbridge. What should he build next?

name: Anu
meetText: Anu meditates every day in their own special way — on a pool floaty! Anu loves floating on their back, feeling weightless, and just being present in the moment. They're thinking of finally sticking to the daily meditation! Grab a floaty and join Anu in their serenity pool.

name: Anya
meetText: Meet Anya! This curious Squishmallow loves swimming to the depths of the sea with her mer-gals where they go on all sorts of adventures. When she’s not on an underwater adventure, you can find her studying to become a real-life explorer, she wants to be an archaeologist.

name: Aqua
meetText: Aqua may be a sloth but he loves to be the life of the party! He absolutely loves tacos and trying to enjoy snow cones before they melt. Look for him in the DJ booth!

name: Aquitaine
meetText: Meet Aquitaine. Her studies in science and research have inspired her to create her own cosmetics line! Her skincare products are all vegan and cruelty-free, and she hopes one day all products will do the same. Will you help Aquitaine save the animals and skincare?

name: Arabella
meetText: Arabella is a very talented violinist, she can play almost any song just by hearing it! While she loves to play the violin and practices every day, she'd rather play outside. When it's nice out she sits on her porch and takes a break to play catch with her friends.

name: Araminta
meetText: This caticorn is quick on her toes, can lead, follow, and teach all at the same time, and has a room full of costumes! Grab your dancing shoes, are you ready to take a class with Araminta?

name: Archer
meetText: Archer dreams of being a black belt but there's just one problem, he isn't very athletic! He tries his best and hopes that he will get better, just like his Sensei says. Until then, would you mind practicing with him?

name: Archie
meetText: Original: Have you met Archie? This shy 'Mallow has a special talent – he talks with his hands! Archie loves to play soccer and even started a club for 'Mallows to play and learn Sign. Someday you might see him play in the 'Mallows Cup!

name: Arco
meetText: Arco plays percussion on anything he can his claws on. His collection of instruments is growing steadily, and Arco's current pride and joy is his xylophone. This 'Mallow is getting a group together for weekend percussion jams—you're invited!

name: Argie
meetText: Argie never thought math could be fun because she always had a difficult time learning it. But now, Argie is taking a statistics class and having the best time ever! Statistics makes so much sense to her, and she loves solving the word problems, What's your favorite school subject?

name: Ari
meetText: Ari dreams of being a DJ. He loves electronic music, but plays other tunes because he enjoys making his friends smile. Ari hopes to headline a massive show, one day, at the Squishmallows Music Festival! What do you want to hear Ari play?

name: Aria
meetText: Meet Aria, your next party guru. When she's not planning her next event, you can find her and her Uni-gals exploring. How does she unwind? By being silly with her family and friends.

name: Ariana
meetText: Ariana plays the organ!  Right now, she's practicing a creepy new song for her town's Halloween festival. Ariana thinks the organ makes the prettiest sounds, but she can also make it sound dark and scary by playing the lower keys. Want to hear the song Ariana is working on?

name: Arlene
meetText: Movie actress Arlene is known by 'Mallows far and wide as the 'Queen of Holiday Romcoms'. Despite her busy filming schedule, Arlene makes sure to celebrate every Christmas with her brother Alten. Together, they go caroling!

name: Arlie
meetText: Meet Arlie, he wants to become a geologist! Arlie loves all thing sci-fi, especially movies about alien planets. He hopes he can uncover the next living planet, can he tell you about his latest theory?

name: Armie
meetText: Meet Armie. Ever since he was a little 'Mallow he's been a train fanatic. He even has a model track that travels throughout his bedroom! Armie loves create videos showing off his favorite trains driving through the station. All aboard!

name: Arnel
meetText: Arnel is a movie buff! You name it, he's probably seen it. He especially loves the deep cuts and black and white french films. Want to join? He'd love a movie buddy! But he's memorized all his favorite scenes by heart so don't be surprised if he talks through the whole thing.

name: Aron
meetText: Meet Aaron, a young stock investor who loves to cook. His hands are strong like diamonds; he can whip up the best crème brûlée! His favorite foods are pasta, sushi, and cheese! Murphy can whip up a delicious treat, or make a smart stock recommendation!

name: Arona
meetText: Arona flutters with holiday spirit. This 'Mallow knows there's no better way to celebrate than with a parade! Arona is planning the first Valentine's Day parade in her town with live music, floral arrangements, and lots of heart-shaped goodies. Want to join her parade committee?

name: Arthur
meetText: Arthur is quite the artsy dude. He spends all day painting large murals for local businesses or putting the finishing touches on a brand-new sculpture. At night he loves to go dancing with his friends, often times still covered in splatters of paint.

name: Arturo
meetText: Dancing, family, and tamales are some of Arturo's favorite things. He has a large family and whenever they get together there is a lot of noise, dancing, and laughter. His favorite thing about family visits is the yummy tamales that his aunt makes.

name: Ash
meetText: Ash is a true morning 'Mallow! He can't wait to get up and start creating new beats on his keyboard. A donut helps him start his day and get the music flowing! Sometimes, sprinkles get stuck on the keys, but Ash doesn't mind. Want to make music with Ash?

name: Asher
meetText: Are you ready for an adventure? Asher will take you there—through his photos! This narwhal is a photographer who travels the globe taking photos for magazines and newspapers. How can you capture his attention? His favorite dish is shrimp ceviche!

name: Ashley
meetText: Ashley loves table tennis, one day she wants to be part of the world’s best table tennis team! For now, she practices with her friends and hosts backyard tournaments. You can help her keep score!

name: Ashlyn
meetText: Close your eyes, sprinkle a dash of glitter, and make a wish; Ashlyn is here to be your fairy godmother! Though she’s still a fairy in training, Ashlyn can’t wait to make Squishmallow dreams come true. What’s her biggest wish? This week it’s world peace and gooey triple chocolate chip cookies.

name: Astra
meetText: Astra loves coffee, cupcakes, and bubble-gum ice cream. She is a nurse who works in the hospital with mini mallows. She loves to have fun with her patients and tries to tell a new joke every day. Do you have a good joke for her to share?

name: Astrid
meetText: Original: Do you believe in fate? Astrid does! She is a dreamer and loves learning how about how the stars align. Her birthday is December 21st, the longest night of the year! Isn’t that perfect for Astrid? Her most prized possession is her telescope, and she is rarely ever without it.

name: Astrud
meetText: Anytime is a good time for a hike! Astrud and her bestie, Evita, meet up for hikes no matter the weather—these tough 'Mallows are prepared for anything. Astrud's favorite part is grabbing a hot peppermint latte at the little cafe near the trailhead. It keeps her perfectly warm and energized.

name: Atlas
meetText: Need some help for surviving life 101? Though she is still a student herself, from pasta to paying taxes, Atlas is a great teacher. She shares all the tips and tricks she comes across on her vlog. Go ahead and give her a follow!

name: Atoosa
meetText: Have you ever imagined what life would be like in space? Atoosa has! She’s an aerospace engineer and designed a space cruise ship to vacation among the stars! There’s an ice cream sundae bar, a galaxy arcade, and portholes to stargaze through. Next stop, new planets!

name: Aubrey
meetText: Aubrey loves movies about horses, camping, and singing in the rain. For her birthday this year, she even had a karaoke camp out. A few of her friends camped out in her backyard and they sang songs by the fire. What song would you like to sing?

name: August
meetText: Give August a call next time you need fashion advice. This alpaca knows all the latest trends and prides himself in dressing his 'Mallow friends based on their individual style. August is waiting to hear back from the fashion school he applied to. Think he'll get accepted?

name: Aurora
meetText: Aurora is from a mystical planet near the Milky Way. This magical unicorn loves learning about her galaxy and aspires to be an astronomer. When she's not learning about the magical world around her, she enjoys skiing down the slippery slopes of Mt. Jupiter.

name: Austin
meetText: Austin loves drawing aliens and dreams of one day living in space! He loves pretending that he lives on the moon or is climbing rock mountains on Mars. Austin became obsessed with outer space in school after reading a book about aliens, will you help Austin plan his next space adventure?

name: Autumn
meetText: You could say that Autumn is not a morning person. Her adventure-seeking personality comes out as the darkness fills the skies. Autumn is one with nature, and travels all over the world from one Halloween to the next.

name: Autumn the Fox
meetText: Autumn loves listening to music and playing the piano. Her friends love her playful personality.

name: Ava the Avocado
meetText: Ava loves to travel! Her favorite place to visit is Mexico. When Ava travels, she enjoys trying new foods and experiencing other cultures.

name: Ava
meetText: Ava is one cool chick who has an eye for design. She is one to always put things together. Ava's dream is to create a big dollhouse with her favourite Squishmallows!

name: Avana
meetText: Meet Avana. This axolotl loves a good cry. She enjoys watching tearjerkers and sob stories any day of the week. She can't pinpoint exactly why if you ask her, but she'll share her top 10 movie list if you'd like!

name: Avery
meetText: Original: Don't let his size fool you, Avery is a skilled left wingman for the Squishmallows rugby team and one day wants to be a coach! His whole family comes to watch and they bring popsicles to celebrate once the game is over.

name: Avrill
meetText: Meet Avrill. He loves to tinker and find out how everything around him works. Curiosity rules his world! In his free time, he likes to design airplanes and hopes to be an airplane engineer someday. He wants to make flying the best way to move, do you want to see his latest design?

name: Axel
meetText: Axel poses for all the most well-known designers. Axel was discovered at a shopping mall when he was a young beetle, and even though he always knew he was unique looking, he never imagined it would take him to the cover of magazines. Have you seen Axel's latest photo shoot?

name: Aziza
meetText: Aziza is a little alternative and loves to push buttons. Sarcasm, sleeping in, and being silly are just a few of her favorite things. If you need a second opinion or a new topic to debate, Aziza is the mallow for you!

name: Azizi
meetText: If you're looking for a sense of purpose or direction, Azizi is the dragon for you! This dragon was once all over the place and now helps other Mallows find their happy place. Azizi has studied traditions old and new to understand being organized, calm, and collected.

name: Babs
meetText: Meet Babs. She loves super heroes, sci-fi, and created her own superhero, Captain Blueberry! Captain Blueberry is a regular bird by day and solves crime by night. Now Babs just needs to create a sidekick, what should she call them?

name: Baiden
meetText: Original: Baiden has an after-school job at a farm, he helps with the planting and harvesting. It can be very hard work but Baiden loves to learn all about taking care of the soil and doing what he can for the best harvest possible.

name: Bailey
meetText: Bailey is the bubblegum blowing champion in her town, she's set many records for blowing the biggest bubble, chewing her gum the longest, and even creating some of the yummiest bubblegum flavors! Do you think you can blow bigger bubbles than Bailey?

name: Balia
meetText: Meet Balia. This sweet and lovable social butterfly is always here to make sure you're having fun! She may be cuddly, but Balia is one tough 'Mallow who works for what she wants. When you're with Balia, you are sure to have a fun time and meet new people!

name: Ballis
meetText: Ballis can come off as very quiet and serious, but it's only because he's a little shy. He really likes people and loves making new friends. It takes him a while to open up, but he's totally worth the wait. He has the funniest dry sense of humor and gives the best advice!

name: Balni
meetText: Meet Balni. She's super-friendly and open-minded and never shies away from new experiences! She finds joy in the little things, like a sunny beach day, a silly dance, or making her friends laugh. Balni always includes everyone, so come along she'd love to meet you!

name: Bambalina
meetText: Meet Bambalina. This cuddly cat loves crunchy peanut butter cookies, sleeping in, and making music. One day she wants to be a DJ; she'll play in between naps and her favorite sweet treats. Do you want to play some music with Bambalina?

name: Bambz
meetText: Bambz is a little Pomchi with a big personality. She loves making new friends and watching films with her family. Bambz is going to be a movie producer when she's older and start a production company with her besties Rheya, Fitch, and Monty. What kind of films do you think they should make?

name: Banks
meetText: Banks recently started his own optometry practice. He examines and treats eyes for all 'Mallows and can even prescribe glasses. Banks keeps the office energy levels up and positive by hosting gatherings throughout the week. This Friday, he's throwing a bagel party!

name: Banu
meetText: Meet Banu. Though some mau call him grumpy, he just likes to keep to himself. He's a bit of an introvert who prefers small groups to large ones. Want to know his happy place? A cabin tucked away with his good friend Norman!

name: Bara
meetText: Meet Bara. This biomedical engineer wants to make the world a better place. Bara just finished a big paper for her latest design. Sometimes she works long hours but she loves the value in her work. In her free time, Bara loves to go camping and off-roading in the desert.

name: Baratelli
meetText: The hills are alive with the sound of tap shoes and top hats! Baratelli loves the limelight, just watch him sing and dance! On weekends he enjoys trying as many food trucks as possible. Baratelli might be a rising star, but he's always looking for a dance partner. Is it you?

name: Barb
meetText: Barb says hello! Barb is quite the gymnast and can do all kinds of tricks, from aerials to tricks on the trapeze. If asked nicely, Barb will even put on a show for her friends! While she's a humble 'Mallow, Barb loves to show off her moves.

name: Barika
meetText: Barika can't see colors but that isn't stopping her from living her dream. She wants to be a digital designer, she loves creating digital art. At first, she was too shy to share it but now she's very proud to share her ideas. Would you like to see her work?

name: Barnabus
meetText: Looking for a new hobby? Join Barnabus and make some cool sand art! Barnabus loves how calming and tidy sand art can be, he even has a little sandbox on his desk to play with. Next, he wants to get a big sandbox for his backyard so more can join in the fun!

name: Barnes
meetText: Coloring, card games, and cooking are some of Barnes's favorite things to do. He drew his own snack menu for friends to order from during card games. He gets excited when it's time to put on his chef hat and make yummy snacks.

name: Barnet
meetText: Barnet wakes up bright and early, ready to check off everything on their to-do list! This ambitious ‘Mallow starts their day with a quick yoga flow and vitamin-packed smoothie before even heading to work. Barnet has a big presentation to make next week but they already know it’s going to be a hit!

name: Baron
meetText: Grab your bear necessities because you are going on a camping trip with Baron! Let Baron be your next guide at your favorite national park. He is the king of the mountains and beary social!

name: Barrie
meetText: Congrats to Barrie who just graduated from design school! Barrie draws with pencils, Inks--- even a stylus digital pen. His favorite scenes to draw are magic and fantasy because he can use so many different colors and create make-believe creatures. Want to see Barrie's latest artwork?

name: Tim
meetText: Ever seen Tim before? You might not recognize him now, but you will!  He is one of the greatest leading guitarists of today. Want to join Tim on his next tour bus? He gets to travel all over the world alongside his younger brother, Jim! What’s his favorite kind of music to perform? Alternative rock! He loves celebrating birthdays, which is why his January 1st birthday is always poppin'.

name: Bart
meetText: Bart is an explorer who dreams of becoming an astronaut. At night he uses his wings to fly up into space to discover new stars and planets. He also loves photography and takes a lot of photos while in space, which he shares with his friends and family!

name: Bart
meetText: Bart is on his way to become a certified diver, he dreams of one day leading an underwater expedition to discover Atlantis! If you need a diving buddy, Bart is your guy!

name: Bartie
meetText: Bartie and Fred are almost inseparable, Fred is an extrovert while Bartie is an introvert. Even though he loves to play games in the snow, his favorite past-time is watching movies on repeat. He loves watching holiday classics, do you want to join?

name: Bashira
meetText: Meet Bashira. She's training at a special comedy school to become a magician! Bashira loves interacting with the audience and making people smile. Her dream is to one day travel the world and perform in different cities, can she show you some cool tricks?

name: Basma
meetText: Meet Basma. She lives near the coast with her family and loves taking family trips. They enjoy seeing different landscapes across the globe, but her favorite is their wetland backyard. She hopes that more 'Mallows visit her hometown to know how important the environment truly is.

name: Basmina
meetText: Meet Basmina. She loves writing haikus about nature and spirituality, and takes her notebook and pen with her on long walks to find inspiration! Something about the sound of the sea always gets her creative juices flowing! Would you like to join her?

name: Bastian
meetText: Bastian takes the art of pizza making seriously. He even built his own brick pizza oven! Now he can bake a ton of pies in the blink of an eye—and get crispy crusts, too. Tell Bastian your favorite toppings and he'll put something in the oven just for you!

name: Beata
meetText: Beata speaks from the heart in every speech they give. This latte travels all around giving motivational speeches to any 'Mallow who wants a little boost of positively and encouragement. Now Beata is writing their first book about motivational speaking. They'll give you a signed copy!

name: Beatrice
meetText: Beatrice lives by the bell. She can't wait to hear it chime after class because it means she gets to play outside with her other fluffy friends during her favorite time of year: spring!

name: Bebb
meetText: Meet Bebb. He can barely sit still he has so much energy! This makes him a wonderful running partner! He loves long jogs on his favorite jungle trail and is working on his mile time. Want to give it a try? Don't worry about how fast you go. Just enjoy the journey!

name: Bebe
meetText: You've never seen a blue bird hit a home run like Bebe can! Bebe loves to play and cheer with friends at their school games! Their favorite thing to do is play 'who can whistle the loudest'; Bebe always is the loudest on the team! Join Bebe to root at their next home game!

name: Beck
meetText: Beck fidgets sometimes without realizing. Talking to a trusted friend every week helps him manage the fidgeting and interrupting—oh, sometimes Beck talks out of turn and he gets really enthusiastic. If this happens, just tell Beck to pause because he doesn't mind waiting to share his thoughts, even if it's a funny joke!

name: Becki
meetText: Meet Becki. This talkative ‘Mallow never runs out of things to say. She loves chatting about current events, pop culture, and even a little hot gossip! She’s also a great listener! Have something you need to get off your chest? Becki is the ‘Mallow for you!

name: Beemie
meetText: Beemie might get stern when she's on a sailboat, but that's only because she's thinking about safety. This 'Mallow teaches her students everything she knows about sailing--- and wind! Make sure to take notes on all the different kinds of knots. Beemie ends each class with a quiz

name: Behemoth
meetText: Behemoth is a big party animal who craves chaos, loves airtime, and the colour yellow. Fiercely protective, Behemoth never hesitates to go out and back for those he calls true friends.

name: Belana
meetText: This creative cow loves to paint and has dreams of going to art school. She paints furniture and woodwork designed by her brother Ronnie. After school she wants to open a gallery to share their furniture.

name: Belina
meetText: Need a good book to read? Ask Belina! She loves to read and has a different book club almost every day of the week! Her favorite books are mystery or sci-fi, but she's always up for suggestions!

name: Belinda
meetText: Belinda is a very thoughtful bear, she loves to make handmade gifts! Valentine's Day is one of her favorite days to bake cookies and share them with her friends.

name: Belissa
meetText: Belissa loves trick or treating, she makes a glittery costume every year! One year she was a fairy princess with beautiful glitter wings, and another year she was a witch with a glittery broom and a matching hat. Can you guess what her costume is this year?

name: Bella
meetText: Using Bella's spider sense is easy. She is not only a palm reader, but also a gifted magician. As the darkness creeps in, she goes from a regular Squishmallow to a girl with tricks up her sleeve.

name: Belle
meetText: Belle is adventurous and loves to try new things. Her favorite hobbies are knitting, travelling, cooking, and eating all the sushi rolls she possibly can!

name: Belozi
meetText: Meet Belozi. This dapper dresser loves to stand out, sometimes it's thanks to his looks, and other times it's for his kindness. He lives by two simple rules: putting your best foot forward and treating others with respect.

name: Belton
meetText: Meet Belton. They work at the local bookstore and have a passion for old books and mythical stories. Sometimes when Belton is at the bookstore at night, they say they can hear the books talk! Do you want to dive into the historical, mythical world of the bookstore with Belton?

name: Ben
meetText: Ben is your walking textbook. He is a trivia expert who is quite knowledgeable in every topic from pop culture, history, technology and more. Looking for a partner for your next game night? Ben is your perfect Squishmallows match!

name: Benedict
meetText: Benedict grew up in a small family as an only child, and enjoys his privacy and quiet time. You can usually find Benedict kayaking or fishing alone, but if you aske him, he will welcome your company any time! Grab your floaties and jump in!

name: Benkamin
meetText: Benkamin plays sudoku to help him fall asleep. It's a cozy activity he loves pairing with hibiscus tea and a calming incense. That way, if the puzzle gets too tricky, he still has a relaxing time. Grab a book and snuggle up with Benkamin!

name: Benny
meetText: Benny is a bigfoot and one of the smartest creature in the woods! He loves to run and play with his pals in the forest and beyond. When he is not running around you can often find him taking photographs with woodland friends.

name: Bergit
meetText: Bergit is here and camera ready, behind the camera that is. She's always looking for the perfect shot. Bergit even plans her vacations around snappable places like murals, nature, and architecture. Get ready for your close-up because her favorite subjects are her friends!

name: Berit
meetText: Meet Berit. This moth loves to dream and interpret dreams for others. Yesterday she dreamt that she became a snowflake fairy princess and ruled a magical kingdom. She was about to host a snowball when suddenly she woke up. Do you have any dreams to share with Berit?

name: Berko
meetText: Berko is a park ranger. Ask him all about all the different plant life—it's his specialty! Berko wrote the booklet on all the edible plants and flowers in the park. He even knows all the best spots to watch the sunset. Come visit Berko on your next park adventure!

name: Berna
meetText: Meet Berna. This narwhal is one clever lawyer. She's dedicated and hardworking, she loves thinking creatively to makes things happen. Berna hopes to help change the world, one day at a time.

name: Bernard
meetText: Bernard puts together the most elaborate picnics! He spreads out a big blanket on the lawn of his favorite seaweed forest and arranges homemade snacks, drinks, and utensils all on a little shell table. You're invited to join Bernard on his next picnic!

name: Bernardo
meetText: Are you ready for a spicy surprise? Be sure to catch Bernardo on the baby grand every Friday night. He sings and plays the piano, but with a little twist. He only sings in Spanish, and by the time you leave, you might sing in Spanish too!

name: Bernice
meetText: Blissful, bubbly and bright. Three words to describe the best boba you'll meet! Bernice is sweet, but not too sweet, and always lends a helping hand to her friends.

name: Bernie
meetText: Bernie loves the mountains and helping other people more than anything else in the world. Bernie’s dream is to become an Emergency Medical Technician (EMT) in order to assist in mountain rescues. When he’s not saving lives, you will find Bernie enjoying the snowy weather. He keeps himself entertained by romping, rolling and pulling his friends on sleds!

name: Berry
meetText: Choose your own adventure books are Berry's favorite kind, she loves to have options! Last week she went on a treasure hunt and saved a guppy in distress! What kind of adventure book should she read next?

name: Bertie
meetText: Bertie is one cool 'Mallow. In fact, they might be the coolest 'Mallow around! They like to keep their room super cold all the time, but they have plenty of comfy blankets for guests. Make sure you pack a jacket if you go to visit Bertie!

name: Bertwin
meetText: Meet Bertwin. He loves coffee, reading, and combing his beard. He loves to read books about magic and mystery and is even working on his own novel. Bertwin gets pretty distracted so he needs a study buddy to help him stay focused on his writing; will you help him write?

name: Bessa
meetText: Meet Bessa. Bessa loves activities that others might find frightening! White water rafting, skydiving, or even zip-lining, there is nothing too scary. Bessa's biggest dream is to one day break the land speed record and become the fastest 'Mallow alive! So don't blink or you might miss her!

name: Bessie
meetText: Bessie organizes community events! Whether it's a block party for the grand opening of a new business, or fundraising for a 5K race, she makes sure the whole town is involved. Want to know what Bessie is planning next? It's the yearly toy drive!

name: Bethany
meetText: Bethany's favorite meal is breakfast, especially fresh biscuits and jam! Her mom makes them every Friday for dinner. On the weekends, Bethany helps her mom in the garden, tending to all the yummy berries she uses for jam.

name: Bethuna
meetText: Meet Bethuna. She is a personal trainer with a giant sweet tooth. Bethuna's favorite dessert is a scoop of mint chocolate chip ice cream, and she'll usually enjoy it after a long run outside! And even though she has a sweet tooth, she doesn't let it stop her from hitting the gym every day!

name: Betty
meetText: Betty loves a good thrill! Whether it's rock climbing or skydiving, this daredevil will do anything to satisfy her thirst for adventure! She tries to push people out of their comfort zones, yet respects her friends' decisions to not join her.

name: Beula
meetText: Meet Beula. She loves DIY painting and making everyday things into beautiful art. Beula wants to be an art teacher when she grows up, so she can paint and share how much art means to her.

name: Bevalee
meetText: Have you seen Bevalee? This unicorn is a heart of gold and is always ready for competition. Even if she isn't always number 1, she loves to try! Bevalee loves to thrill of competing whether it's a sport, in class, or even shares at home. Her secret is keeping it fun!

name: Bevin
meetText: Bevin leaves for sleepaway camp tomorrow! She's never been away from home this long and is feeling nervous about being on her own. Bevin memorized the camp song so she can sing along with everyone. Maybe she'll make a friend on the bus ride there!

name: Bex
meetText: Who has a sweet tooth and loves to help others? It's Bex! She is a nurse who works with mini 'Mallows and takes her job very seriously. She tries to brighten their day with the occasional sweet treat and even a song, what can she sing for you?

name: Bexley
meetText: Ready for a math lesson? Make sure to call Bexley for some extra help. Bexley uses some of her favorite candies like jelly beans and marshmallows to help make math fun.

name: Biatrix
meetText: Meet Biatrix. She's an amazing multitasker! Did you know she can play the piano while stirring sugar into her tea and reading her favorite book? She's even been known to knit socks for her friends in her sleep! With Biatrix, you never know what she'll do next!

name: Bibiana
meetText: Welcome Bibiana! Her favorite activity is weekend picnics with her family - her mom makes the best potato salad! Bibiana thinks about studying art history so she can grow up and work at a museum. Would you like to visit her art exhibits?

name: Bijan
meetText: Meet Bijan. He really knows how to go with the flow and improvise. He's a jazz musician! His eight tentacles make him an amazing drummer. His parents own a restaurant on the reef where they have weekly jazz nights and he's been playing there since he was just a little 'Mallow!

name: Bimbi
meetText: Bimbi graduates from clown academy this year! Bimbi is so excited to be a professional clown. They're perfecting a comedy routine, so they can start working right away, Not only does Bimbi have perfect comedic timing, they're also a talented tap dancer!

name: Bindy
meetText: Meet Bindy. He is a very kind and caring walrus. He loves animals and always tries to help those in need. One day Bindy hopes to have his own rescue organisation, so all animals and Mallows can live happy lives!

name: Binxie
meetText: Ready to meet a hero of the night? Say hello to Binxie! Binxie works at a haunted house and uses her sonar skills to help navigate 'Mallows to the scare-free zones. Binxie loves a good scare but when things get too scary she's there to lend a helping hand.

name: Bittie
meetText: Need a new swim cap? Let Bittie design one for you! Bittie is an aspiring swimwear designer, and is working on a new type of material that is both waterproof, and comfortable to wear! What design should Bittie use for your new cap?

name: Blair
meetText: Blair is an outgoing cat who expresses her creativity through makeup. She loves all things beauty and dreams of becoming a cosmetologist. She's the perfect friend to call when you have a big event to attend as she'll help you look your most beautiful!

name: Blake
meetText: Blake loves to dress up! You can find her in all different costumes, especially on playdates with her friend Ava. She is always in character, whether on ship as a pirate, on land as a princess, or at sea as a mermaid.

name: Blake B.
meetText: Grab your bear necessities because you are going on a camping trip with Blake! Let Blake be your next guide at you favorite national park. He is the king of the mountains and beary social!

name: Blanca
meetText: Even though she's a rainbow kangaroo, Blanca's favorite color is black. She loves to draw and paint in black and white and even designs her own artsy Easter baskets for her friends.

name: Blas
meetText: Blas rakes the fallen autumn leaves in front of his home every day. When he's done, it's time to jump in! Blas loves the crunchy sound of leaves as he files into a great big pile. Come join Blas and his 'Mallow pals for some fall fun!

name: Blaze
meetText: Ready for a haunted house extraordinaire? Blaze is the mallow for you! Blaze makes sure every spider web, headless horsemallow, and creepy cauldron are in the right place for the Malloween Mansion.

name: Bliss
meetText: This is one bear you can't wait to meet! Bliss always has a smile on her face, her cheerful grin is contagious! Bliss is a great pal and loves comedy and hearing good news from her friends. If you ever need someone to cheer you up Bliss is the bear for you.

name: Bluby
meetText: You know Bluby is happy when she does her telltale happy dance! If you really want to make Bluby's day, just give her a heads up when sunny weather is in the forecast. Then watch Bluby dance all the way out to her favorite sunny spot!

name: Bly
meetText: Bly might not see the way her 'Mallow friends do, but she can look into your future. This clairvoyant kitty reads palms and paws, using her intuition to inform results of the reading. Got a question for Bly? She's ready to share wisdom.

name: Blyne
meetText: Life as a corporate tax attorney can get pretty stressful. That's why Blyne colors! This chronic workaholic loves winding with a fresh pack of crayons and a good coloring back. She especially enjoys giving animals fun and funky patterns—like polka dots on zebras!

name: Bo
meetText: Bo wanders the world spreading good vibes. She makes new friends, learns about their cultures, and shares stories about her adventures

name: Bo Lynn
meetText: Bo Lynn doesn't just sing about the forest—she sings with the forest! This down-to-earth country singer loves humming with the bees and crooning with the crows. Her next album is dedicated to Mother Nature and she hopes it inspires the world to protect her!

name: Bob
meetText: Bob is an illustrator who lives by the beach! His gears are always turning as he dreams up new drawing. Bob collects one-of-a-kind toys that sometimes inspire his art, and he loves to showcase his work and collectibles in a large window facing the shore. Come check out Bob's artsy window display!

name: Bobbie
meetText: Bobbie is one clever 'Mallow! Bobbie and his BFF Bowie spend hours in the library every weekend drawing sketches for new gadgets, and reading books about famous inventors. Bobbie and Bowie know there's no such thing as a bad idea, so don't be shy - so come join the brainstorm!

name: Bobbix
meetText: You can always find Bobbix at the shaded table in front of the boba tea shop! She scooters there every day after school for a quick snack with her classmates. Sometimes Bobbix even has homework sessions at her favorite table. Have a seat and join Bobbix for a boba tea!

name: Bobby
meetText: Meet Bobby! This bright bunny used to be embarrassed about the tie-dye pattern of their birthmarks but now Bobby knows that is part of what makes them special. Every year Bobby dyes eggs to match and shares them with other Squishmallows.

name: Bobzi
meetText: Meet Bobzi. This pup is one amazing chalk artist. They could spend all afternoon drawing beautiful and brightly colored landscapes on the blacktop. Bobzi doesn't seem to mind when the rain washes away their art. It's a chance to draw something new! Would you like to join them?

name: Bolivar
meetText: Bolivar only watches monster movies! If you ask him about it, he will teach you all about how the movies were made. You'll often find Bolivar playing rock n' roll hits on the jukebox at his local diner--come by and introduce yourself! Bolivar loves making new friends.

name: Bongo
meetText: Bongo is a playful pug who loves to play and cuddle with his mom. His favorite toy is a cute little caterpillar, and Bongo takes the caterpillar with him almost everywhere he goes. It's his favorite toy, so he can't imagine a day without it!

name: Bonnie
meetText: Want to start your own garden? Bonnie is the mallow for you! Bonnie spends her mornings outside in the garden, drinking tea and meditating. This panda princess is a free soul at heart, and loves to be surrounded by mother nature.

name: Bop
meetText: Bop is the queen of nail design. She's so good that she has to paint her sisters' nails, her mom's nails and even her grandma's. She's known for her striped and spotted Easter egg nail design.

name: Boulder
meetText: Grab some quarters and get ready for an intense day, Boulder is trying to beat their high score in pinball! Ever since their first game, Boulder has been obsessed with getting the highest score, ever! Do you ever get the end-of-ball bonus?

name: Bowie
meetText: Bowie is one sleepy hedgehog, but she only likes to sleep because she has such big dreams! Bowie is an entrepreneur and one day plans on bringing fascinating innovations to the whole ‘Mallow world! Just after she wakes up from this nap…

name: Boyd
meetText: Boyd is a professionally trained opera singer; this monkey is the most beautiful baritone. You can recognize his voice from miles away! Boyd's friends beg him to give them singing lessons, and he loves to help them sing. One day he might open his own music school!

name: Boyer
meetText: Meet Boyer! Boyer is creative, charming and cool as a cucumber. Need someone to help you add the finishing touches to a project for school, or work? Boyer's attention to detail will help you make sure that everything looks top notch!

name: Braedon
meetText: Who loves history, grilled cheese, and being organized? Braedon does! This triceratops loves to discover historical fun facts and shares them with his friends. When he's in research mode, he feels invincible with his favorite sandwich by his side. Do you have a favorite sandwich?

name: Brandi
meetText: Have you met Brandi? She's the cheetah queen of the ring! Brandi loves kickboxing and riding her bike on the beach. After a day of teaching classes, she loves to catch the cotton candy sunset on her way home.

name: Braven
meetText: Meet Braven. He's the conductor for the winter parade and he hopes all 'Mallows will join on the fun. Even if they don't celebrate the same holidays, Braven thinks spreading joy, kindness, and compassion is good for everyone. Do you want to join in the parade festivities?

name: Bren
meetText: Storytime is all the time with Bren! This multitasking 'Mallow is always in the middle of a book, even when listening to audiobooks on her daily jogs. Bren is finishing up a book now while setting up for her squad's weekly game night. Get ready for an evening of cards and laughter!

name: Brenda
meetText: Brenda loves to be outside and enjoy the sun! She has a green thumb and sells flowers from her garden at the farmers market every week. Her favorite flowers are marigolds and phlox!

name: Brenden
meetText: Meet Brenden. He's allergic to food dye, likes kale salads, and hates to act his age. Brenden loves to have fun and remains all of his friends that age is just a number. When he's not moonlighting as a motivational speaker you'll find him watching design competition shows.

name: Bri
meetText: Bri loves travelling, tiaras, and having tea parties. Her parents travel a lot and sometimes she gets to go with them! When she gets back from a trip she plans a tea party to share her latest travel adventures with her friends.

name: Brian
meetText: Brian wants to be a graphic designer when he grows up and spends his time editing his friends' pictures and watching black and white movies.

name: Briannika
meetText: This lovable 'Mallow is a true extrovert and can strike up a conversation with anyone. Briannika leads with an open mind and heart and believes everyone brings something valuable to the table. Briannika doesn't judge, so come hang for a bit and talk with her!

name: Bridgie
meetText: Have you ever seen a tulip do a kickflip? Bridgie will show you how. She and her best friend Maui spend weekends at the skate park learning new tricks. When she's not on her board, Bridgie loves to watch scary movies or unsolved mysteries.

name: Brie
meetText: Brie is a brilliant baker known for her the melty cheese brownies she makes every Halloween. When Brie isn't experimenting with brownie recipes, she's racking up a high score in a spooky pinball game! This makes her a little competitive, but she always plays with an upbeat spirit. Come join the game!

name: Brielle
meetText: Brielle and her friend Prince are getting ready to go to space! At least that's what they're telling her mom, they've built a space station out of pillows in the living room! They might have to save the planet before dinner time, do you think they can do it?

name: Brigita
meetText: Brigita loves bagels and ladybugs, she even has a dancing ladybug bathrobe. She makes the same breakfast everyday; a peanut butter bagel with a yummy green smoothie. She loves to dance around in her bathrobe while she makes breakfast, it makes mornings more fun!

name: Brina
meetText: Say hi to Brina the Bigfoot. This confident little creature likes going on new adventures. Brina’s favorite season is winter because her favorite sport is snowboarding. She waits all year to participate in the local snowboarding competition.

name: Brindall
meetText: Meet Brindall. She doesn't like hummus, she loves it! She makes her own from scratch with garbanzo beans and fresh herbs from the garden. She makes the perfect dinner guest because she's guaranteed to bring a jar to share!

name: Brinkley
meetText: Meet Brinkley. She can absolutely shred on her electric guitar. Though she cannot see well, she learned to play by memorizing the strings of the guitar and the sounds they make. Make a request, she can play almost any song you can imagine.

name: Brinya
meetText: Got a birthday or special celebration coming up? Don't forget to invite Brinya! She loves get-togethers with friends and and goes crazy for a good surprise party. She'll even help you decorate! Brinya's always ready for some fun.

name: Brisby
meetText: "Home On The Range" is one of Brisby's favorite songs, he loves spending time on the ranch with his family. If you get the chance you should join him camping in the mountains, whipping up some delicious s'mores.

name: Brissa
meetText: Brissa loves dancing on roller skates and video games. Thanks to gaming, she's made friends around the world! She loves to share videos of cool skating tricks and hopes to visit many of her friends one day. Would you like her to teach you how to skate?

name: Bristle
meetText: You've never met a bear more creative than Bristle! She has a large family and loves to create memories that last a lifetime. Bristle has scrapbooks for birthdays, graduations, holidays, so she always remembers the good times!

name: Britta
meetText: Meet Britta. She's going to school to study physics and astronomy, she loves all things space! She keeps a close-knit group of friends who love to hang out and play games, both IRL and online. If you need a friend to game with, Britta is the owl for you!

name: Brittany
meetText: Reading, photography and crafting are some of Brittany's favorite things to do. She even has a mini-gallery in her hallway and an amazing crafting corner to show off some of her work! Next on Brittany's list: some DIY birthday gifts for her friends, want to help her out?

name: Brixton
meetText: Everyone at the spa knows Brixton! She glides over there weekly for a paw massage and facial. When Brixton really has the time, she spends her whole day lounging in different saunas and drinking barley tea. Want to know Brixton's secret to glowing fur? Ice baths!

name: Brizby
meetText: Meet Brizby. He gets nervous in large crowds, that is until he's on stage! Brizby and his friend Iman are a super cool synth-pop duo! When they're rocking out on stage, all of Brizby's social anxiety melts away and he becomes a super star! Want to come to one of their shows?

name: Brizla
meetText: Meet Brizla. She's always on the go! She is a pro at multitasking and checking things off her to-do list. Nobody knows quite how she does it! On top of it all, she always has a warm smile on her face and a never ending supply of hugs for her friends and family! How cool it that?

name: Brock
meetText: Normal bio: Brock is the quarterback of the football team who has a heart of gold! When he's not making touchdowns on the field, you'll find him volunteering his time at the local hospital. He loves to read to the sick children and wants to become a nurse one day!     Astronaut bio: Grab your helmet and join Brock and his pal Daryl on an intergalactic adventure. They want to see the universe! There's just one problem: Brock is afraid of heights! Can you help him overcome his fear before take-off?

name: Brody
meetText: Brody loves flying and dreams of one day becoming a Pilot! He's a very adventurous guy whose favorite past time is creating new tricks that he can teach his friends and family. When on land you'll find him playing his favorite video games!

name: Bronk
meetText: Bronk is an all-star athlete and loves a good competition. Don’t worry though, he’s a good sport even when he loses. Bronk loves playing games and sports of all kinds, but you’ll be his very best friend if you offer to play a game of catch!

name: Bronte
meetText: Meet Bronte. This chameleon loves to dance and can choreograph something to every type of music. She grew up as a ballet dancer and found love for hip hop and jazz soon after. Bronte even opened her own dance studio! If there is music playing, you know you can find Bronte on the dance floor.

name: Brooke
meetText: Brooke doesn't need to curl up by the fire during the holidays, because her presence is warm enough. Her sweet spirit is best received in the kitchen. She loves to bake yummy treats for her lifetime Squishmallows pals.

name: Bruce
meetText: Want to explore the beauty of Alaska? Bruce is your guy! An active kayaker, Bruce leads travellers on amazing river tours and shows them all if his favourite hidden gems. Get ready for a photo opp!

name: Bryce
meetText: Meet Bryce. This is one funny 'Mallow, even when he's not trying to be. He loves baseball, playing guitar, and riding roller coasters. He usually splits his time between baseball and guitar, but once in a while, he takes a trip to ride new roller coasters. Where should he go next?

name: Bubba
meetText: Who's that playing center on the court? It's Bubba! Even though he's not very tall, Bubba never lets the haters get him down. He is lightning fast and his layup is the team's secret weapon. One day he might even go pro!

name: Bubbles
meetText: It's rumored that Bubbles' father is the Easter Bunny himself, but only close family and friends know for sure. If you can't find her with her large family, Bubbles is most likely at the park jumping rope.

name: Buffy
meetText: Ready to have a fang-tastic time, meet Buffy the bat! Buffy is not your average gal, she enjoys going on adventures into the forest and fruit picking with her pals. When she's not exploring the world around her, she enjoys hanging around with her family and baking fruit pies.

name: Bufinda
meetText: Bufinda is a night-owl and seems to do her best work when everyone else is in bed. She wants to be a writer and is working on her first book! Mystery, suspense, and even a little bit of comedy are all some of the things she writes about. One day you can read it!

name: Buford
meetText: Psst! Remember to call Buford a bear! This method-acting moose is playing a bear in his latest movie and prefers to stay in character. While some might call his acting process extreme, this two-time award winner is going for a third. Wish him luck!

name: Buna
meetText: Buna washes her hands constantly- sometimes out of habit, sometimes to relax, and sometimes because she has garlic stuck to her fingers! Buna only likes her homemade garlic bread and has a tray in the oven right now. Don't forgot to wash up before dinner!

name: Buttons
meetText: Buttons is the king of Easter egg hunts. He always gets the most eggs, but he shares his prizes with his siblings. His favorite Easter treat? Marshmallows!

name: Buzz
meetText: If you give a sloth a donut, he's sure to want more! Especially Buzz, the way to this smooth sloth's heart is through his stomach. And donuts are his favorite. Another thing about Buzz is, he seems to know EVERYTHING! The buzz on Buzz is: he's the best secret keeper in town.

name: Cacey
meetText: Cacey seeks adventure of all kinds, and lately she's been going parasailing at the beach! She loves to feel the wind through her spines. Cacey has so much fun pursuing these exciting hobbies, but she also wants someone to share in the thrills. Could it be you?

name: Cade
meetText: Meet Cade. Cade has a very creative personality and likes to let his imagination run wild. One of Cade's favorite activities is drawing funny pictures of his classmates. Cade uses silly shapes and wacky colors to make everyone look brand new, how should Cade draw you?

name: Caden
meetText: Caden can pitch a tent in a snap! She goes camping every year and knows all the tricks to make it easy and fun. This 'Mallow always has a compass and first aid kit handy, and they never forget to pack marshmallows for nightly s'mores parties. Join Caden on their next big camping trip!

name: Caedia
meetText: Grab your gloves and get ready for a workout, Caedia is your new de-stress coach! She teaches kick-boxing and has a stress-busting routine for everyone. She likes to write her stress on the punching bag for some extra motivation. Would you like to take her class?

name: Caedyn
meetText: Do you like apple pies and movie nights? So does Caedyn! She loves baking pies and watching scary movies, especially for a movie marathon. She loves a monster movie with a side of fresh pie. Would you like to join her?

name: Caeli
meetText: Who's that cat caught in the yarn, it must be Caeli! This crafty cat is a yarn expert but occasionally she gets all tangled up. Caeli loves long and sparkly nails even though they sometimes get stuck while she's knitting.

name: Cailey
meetText: Cailey loves noodles, cooking with her grandmother, and reading up on her favorite stars. Pop culture and being cozy are some of her favorite things, she is an ace with random pop culture facts. Whenever she meets someone new, Cailey shares a factoid to remember their name.

name: Caitroina
meetText: Are you looking for some delicious chocolates for your friends and family? Caitroina is the one for you! Visit Caitroina's chocolate shop where she whips up the best homemade chocolates! She loves to create new and exciting flavors because chocolate is her passion. Want to try?

name: Calais
meetText: Meet Calais. This chameleon can shift into any type of musician you want to hear. Calais grew up as a piano player, and after mastering this instrument, picked up the violin. Now every year, Calais learns to play a new instrument. What do you want to hear Calais play?

name: Cali
meetText: Cali is a tired kitty, she has insomnia but that doesn’t keep this tabby cat down for long! She journals or writes poetry when she can’t sleep and shares her poems with her naptastic friend Paulita. Can you help Cali catch some ZZZs?

name: Calio
meetText: Meet Calio. She and her friend Riba can't wait to load up their pails with candy on Halloween night. They make the perfect duo. Calio loves chocolate, but can't stand sour candy, and Riba loves sour candy, but is allergic to chocolate, so they just trade!

name: Callista
meetText: Callista is a free spirit and goes wherever the wind blows her. She loves to surprise her friends with a visit and always shouts ‘Boo!’. Callista’s favorite spooky treat? Marshmallow treats in the shape of a ghost!

name: Callum
meetText: Callum loves Slime! He makes his own with DIY recipes and always adds lots of glitter. Callum plays with slime while he watches TV, or under his desk in class to help him stay focus and nor fidget. Callum just picked up some googly eyes. Want to help him make fun slime blobs?

name: Calton
meetText: Learn to cook with Calton! He loves food: everything from lasagna to making pot pies. When Calton isn't whipping up delicious food, he's probably taking a quick snooze. What kind of food can Calton show you how to cook?

name: Calynda
meetText: Meet Calynda. Her free spirit makes her the perfect travel buddy. She loves meeting new people and trying new things. She once went to a circus and ended up swinging on the trapeze! Fun and adventure are always in-store when you're rolling with Calynda!

name: Calypsa
meetText: Anxious about the future? Talk to Calypsa! This enchanted dragon is an expert at using her crystal ball to assure nervous 'Mallows that no matter their situation, things can and will get better. Can you believe she has yet to be wrong?

name: Cam
meetText: Original: If you’re looking for a feline friend, Cameron’s your cat. He loves to jump in and out of boxes, build forts with his friends Hoot and Wendy and use his skateboard to get around town. Cam also loves going to the beach to take cat naps with his friends, but is always up for an adventure!

name: Camden
meetText: Camden is a happy chick who loves to smile! He's going to school to become a dental hygienist so he can help others love their smiles too! When he's not studying and cleaning teeth, he loves to go on hikes with his spring squad friends.

name: Camette
