meetText: Meet Camette. She plays the piano for her school choir and loves to have her friends sing along. Every winter she accompanies the choir to bring holiday cheer and the joy of music to others, what can she play for you?

name: Camile
meetText: Say cheese! Camile snaps portraits of all her closest 'Mallow friends with her instant film camera and she's ready to take one of you! She's known for capturing her subjects in the middle of a laugh, making her photos beautiful and funny. Will you go to her next gallery showing?

name: Camilla
meetText: Don't let Camilla's sparkly appearance trick you - this caticorn isn't afraid to get her paws dirty. Camilla works for the Parks Service, and one of her favorite activities is hosting neighborhood cleanups!

name: Camilo
meetText: Meet Camilo. Camilo is a musical theatre major, and their dream is to be onstage. Camilo has been taking voice, dance and acting lessons for years, and knows all the words to the big musicals. Do you want to sing and dance with Camilo?

name: Canda
meetText: Meet Canda. This fish has a passion for FASHION! She loves to stand out and make the world her runaway. In addition to being a style icon, Canda also has a gift of gab. You can ask anyone, she loves some feel-good gossip but she knows when the gossip has gone too far.

name: Candace
meetText: Candace plays the triangle in her school band, she wears her lucky t-shirt the day before they perform. Her lucky t-shirt is from her first year at band camp! Candace also plays soccer and wants to be the best goalie in her league.

name: Candela
meetText: Candela knows she has the best job in the world as a theater usher! She watches all the newest plays, eats candy from concessions, and meets the whole cast and crew of each production. Come catch a show anytime — Candela left two tickets at the box office just for you!

name: Candess
meetText: Meet Candess. She is all about natural and holistic remedies and loves helping others heal emotionally or physically. Candess is in school learning about nutrition and anatomy so she can open her own holistic practice!

name: Candy
meetText: Cotton candy and jelly beans are Candy's favorite, can you guess why? This bright bunny loves springtime for flowers, fun and the annual Squishmallow egg hunt! She holds the record for finding the most candy eggs!

name: Cannon
meetText: Despite his name and appearance, Cannon is a wellness coach who teaches kids how to make healthy meals. However, he can't resist a sweet treat during Halloween, so he makes his famous caramel apples for himself and all the trick-or-treaters!

name: Caparinne
meetText: Meet Caparinne. She keeps freshly picked flowers in almost every room and loves taking a morning stroll through her garden to see the latest flowers. You'll find her rocking her favorite bright blue broad-brimmed hat and matching gardening gloves.

name: Capri
meetText: Capri tackles every task and challenge that comes her way with confidence. She's a 'Mallow with moxie, and a natural born leader. Everything's taken care of when you're hanging with Capri. Would you let her give you a hand?

name: Caprina
meetText: Bright colors, bangles, and ice cream sandwiches are some of Caprina's favorite things. You can usually spot her a mile away in one of her neon ensembles, Caprina loves to stand out. Can you guess her favorite color? Hot pink of course!

name: Carah
meetText: Meet Carah. She's a theater kid at heart. Halloween is her favorite time of year because she gets to dress up and really get into character. She can never decide on just one costume so she gets seven of them and dresses up all week! Want to join her trick or treating?

name: Carin
meetText: Where is that beautiful music coming from? It's Carin playing the French horn! She loves that brassy sound how simple it is to play with just her wings. Carin is planning a big beach trip this weekend with other members of the orchestra, and she's packing her favorite food—burritos!

name: Carina
meetText: Maybe Carina watched too many TV shows about UFOs, because she's on a mission to find one! Carina loves space and astronomy more than any other subject. and dreams of one day seeing a UFO with her own eyes wanna go UFO hunting with Carina?

name: Carl
meetText: This is Carl the cheeseburger. He loves practical jokes and hanging out with his burger bros. When he was just a little mallow patty, he dreamt of one day being the funniest cheeseburger in the pack.

name: Carla
meetText: Meet Carla, a therapy caticorn in training! She visits hospitals and clinics all over her city to help people. Carla is always ready to greet you with a smile and a hug (but only if you want one).

name: Carlee
meetText: Carlee is an amazing poet and her dream is to give a reading at her local bookstore. There's just one problem: public speaking makes her very nervous. Carlee's friend Miley is helping her practice so one day you can hear her poems too!

name: Carlita
meetText: Meet Carlita. This caticorn has one of her best giggles around. Her giggles is contagious and unique, so its not hard to join, If she laughs at your jokes its considered a pretty good compliment. Do you have any jokes for Carlita?

name: Carlito
meetText: Meet Carlito. His favorite type of music is ska—he's a pretty chill frog. Carlito also enjoys the outdoors so if you like to go camping, he's the frog for you! Want to know his hidden talent? Making the best grilled cheese sandwiches.

name: Carlos
meetText: Have you met Carlos? This creative crustacean is a salsa instructor and a world traveler. Carlos is a travel writer and writes about dance and food across the globe! His favorite travel food: tapas in Spain.

name: Carmelita
meetText: Do you like manga? You should check out some of Carmelita's work. She draws black and white manga about school, her life, and adventures with her best friend Cinnamon. Don't worry about spilling any secrets, Carmelita uses code names for any juicy stuff.

name: Carmella
meetText: Meet Carmella. Her personality is as bright as she is! With her distinct laugh and pretty feathers, she truly stands out in the crowd. She loves dashing around in the snow or hanging out in her treehouse eating S'mores and playing cards with her friends! Want to join?

name: Carmen
meetText: Carmen always has a camera strapped to her side. She loves nature and spends all day photographing rocks, trees and beaches. With each picture she takes, Carmen feels more appreciative of our beautiful world.

name: Carol
meetText: Caroling, cocoa, and cookies are some of Carol's favorite things. This festive mallow loves the bright and cheery vibe of the holidays and wishes the world could be that way every day. She sings in an acapella group that visits schools, homes and hospitals to sing festive tunes all year round.

name: Caroleena
meetText: Ready for a laugh? Caroleena is the queen of impressions, even if you're in a bad mood she'll have you laughing in no time. Her impressions are spot on, and she can stay in character for a long time. One time she made her aunt laugh so hard, she broke a table!

name: Carpio
meetText: Congratulations to Carpio! This entrepreneurial scorpion just opened his neighborhood's first vegan taqueria. His signature cactus tacos might be out-of-this-desert delicious, but be warned: they're super spicy! Make sure to pair it with a glass of almond milk horchata!

name: Carson
meetText: Carson loves cars, monster movies, and travelling to new places. He calls Texas his home state, but has been to many other places in the U.S.

name: Carty
meetText: Carty finds it hard to say hello and goodbye. Greetings can be so awkward! Help Carty out by giving her a high five next time you see her out and about. She's a reclusive koala most of the time, but an energizing wave or warm hug is all she needs to start socializing.

name: Caryl
meetText: Meet Caryl. She teaches an aerobic class with her fantastic friend Brock. They celebrate all body types and ability levels, so all are welcome to join! Grab a towel, some weights, or maybe a partner and get moving with Caryl and Brock!

name: Casey
meetText: When you think of a candy corn witch, traffic cop doesn't come to mind but that's exactly what Casey is! Casey helps navigate the busy streets so that every mallow has a safe place to live.

name: Casja
meetText: Meet Casja. She is visually impaired, but that doesn't stop her from playing her favorite video games! Want to try an audio video game?

name: Casmir
meetText: Meet Casmir. His friends say that his name should be "Caring" because he is always taking care of others. By day he is working at the retirement home, and by night he is volunteering... anywhere! If you want to give back to the community, join Casmir on his next outing!

name: Cassie
meetText: Meet Cassie! She is the head nurse at the hospital where she works to help save lives every day. Cassie knows hospitals can be scary so she keeps lollipops and stickers in her pocket for any mini-mallow patients she sees. Don’t be shy, give Cassie a smile or a wave if you see her rushing around!

name: Cataleya
meetText: Cataleya is one bright koala, she's made the school honor roll almost every month this year! She is also very witty; she loves to laugh at puns and bad jokes. Because her favorite subject is science, she created science-punny valentines for her friends. Do you have any good science jokes to share with her?

name: Catarina
meetText: Do you have a favorite time of year? Catarina does - it's spooky season! Every year she starts to decorate on October 1st, with decorations inside and out. Catarina hosts a haunted house party and every year she tries a new spooky theme.

name: Cato
meetText: Meet Cato. He's turned another year older and another year wiser! But no matter how old he gets, he's still young at heart. He loves a silly birthday party with balloons, games, and a pinata filled with extra candy! And the perfect gift? The company of his friends of course!

name: Catrina
meetText: Nobody makes better pan de muerto than Catrina! Her pan de muerto comes out of the oven super soft and sweet every time. Want to help Catrina dust loaves with sugar? She's baking a large batch for Día de los Muertos celebrations and would love to have you as her assistant baker!

name: Caylee
meetText: Caylee is a Gemini and embraces her two sides! Some days she's feeling dark and mysterious, other days, bright and  sunny! Her friends love her and accept her no matter what. They love to hang at the coffee shop, sip super sweet mochas and read their horoscopes!

name: Cazden
meetText: Cazden gets excited and nervous when meeting a new friend because he wants to make a good impression. Will you calm his nerves with a hug?

name: Cazlan
meetText: Did you see that flash of red soaring through the skies? It must be Cazlan! This speedy cardinal loves to zoom about but when she finally lands, it's time to get her nerd on with her best friend Babs. One day she wants to be her sidekick!

name: Ceba
meetText: Meet Ceba. She is stubborn, yet productive, so if she says she will do something, she gets it done. In her free time, she loves to shop 'til she drops. When she's done, she's ready for a nap as nothing gets between Ceba and her sleep!

name: Cece
meetText: Today is a very special day can you guess why? The party hat might give you a clue, today is Cece's birthday! This cuddly cat can't wait to celebrate, will you join her special day?

name: Cecilia
meetText: Dumplings, dancing, and dragons are some of Cecilia's favorite things. She loves mystical movies and tv shows, (especially if it includes dragons), and even has her room decorated like a castle! Would you go on a dragon quest with Cecilia?

name: Cecy
meetText: This beaming bunny lives on the bright side. For anything that doesn't quite go their way, Cecy tries to see the positive side and make the best of things. They're the perfect pal to have when you need some cheering up.

name: Cedrick
meetText: Cedrick wants to be an engineer when he grows up - he loves building forts, clubhouses, and crazy cool mini buildings with his friends. Once they even built a clubhouse from Easter baskets and popsicles sticks!

name: Celenia
meetText: Celenia wishes she could hug everyone but her immune system has to work a little bit harder in order to fight off germs. She sticks to fist bumps and air high-fives to say hello. She's a huge fan of French baking and is striving to perfect her flaky croissant dough. Do you want to help her taste-test?

name: Celeste
meetText: Celeste is the queen of balloon animals! She has an obsession with clowns and making a balloon animal for every occasion! Don’t worry, she won’t put on a red nose or scare you but she will make you the best balloon animal you have ever seen.

name: Celestina
meetText: Celestina loves bubble baths and bathrobes, she has one for every day of the week! When it's time for a bath, she lights candles and adds some of her favorite scents to create the perfect at-home spa experience.

name: Celia
meetText: Roller coasters and beach trips are two things Celia loves to do every summer. She loves to go to the amusement park and scream on all her favorite rides. Her favorite rides are on the boardwalk so she can see the ocean just before the drop, want to tag along next time?

name: Celine
meetText: You might never meet a sweeter Squishmallow than Celine, she wants to help everyone she meets. Her aunt works for a nonprofit that helps Squishmallows in other parts of the world and when Celine grows up, she wants to work there too.

name: Cella
meetText: Meet Cella. She owns a boutique where she sells homemade candles. She experiments with unexpected ingredients to make intriguing scents. Last week, she made a basil, jasmine, and peppercorn candle and it sold out! Swing by her shop, you never know what she'll be lighting up!

name: Chaitra
meetText: Congrats to Chaitra who just moved into her first apartment! Living alone can be tough at the beginning, so Chaitra plans on hosting lots of dinner parties and game nights with all her besties. But first, she has to unpack. Will you come over and give Chaitra a hand?

name: Champ
meetText: Though he's not old enough to race yet, one day Champ hopes to live up to his name and become a champion racehorse. He comes from a family of legacy horses and he can't wait to have them cheer him on for his first big race.

name: Chance
meetText: Chance is fearless, she loves adventure and stepping outside of her comfort zone. From beating her own race times to not being afraid of the dark, she loves to find new ways to challenge herself or get over her fears.

name: Chandler
meetText: Besides show and tell, naps and snacks are two of Chandler's favorite things. He loves to share and learn more about his friends. Next week is his turn and he can't decide if he should bring his favorite blanket or his favorite snack, can you help him choose?

name: Chanel
meetText: Say hi to Chanel the cinnamon roll. She’s sweeter than your average pastry, and she’s a pastry chef who loves giving back! Chanel likes to volunteer with her free time at the local food pantry and teaches cake baking and decorating classes.

name: Channing
meetText: Have you met Channing? Channing has never met someone he doesn't like and would love to be your new bestie. On a snowy day, you'll probably see him making snow angels and building a moat for his snow fort. Do you want to join in the fun?

name: Chantal
meetText: How many snowflakes fall in one day? Are they really all different? Ask your new friend Chantal. Chantal loves to find out random facts and share them with her friends, especially when snow is involved!

name: Chappy
meetText: Chappy draws six-panel comics about a caterpillar named Terpi! He completes a story almost every week, even writing the action and dialogue. Chappy's dream is to expand Terpi the caterpillar's story into a longer form epic! Would you read Chappy's comics?

name: Charaka
meetText: Charaka creates beautiful multimedia sculptures! Her favorite sculpture is a life - sized barrel cactus with blooming flowers made of brown glass. Charaka names every sculpture after someone she loves. Can Charaka name one of her works of art after you?

name: Charisma
meetText: Meet Charisma. She loves chocolate wafers, crunchy peanut butter, and cinnamon toast. Charisma is the queen of video games, she live-streams her favorite video games especially when they go on raids. She loves making friends this way, would you join her on her next boss fight?

name: Charity
meetText: Guess who just learned how to ride a bike? Charity did! She has a blue and purple bike with streamers on the handle bars. She used to be afraid of falling but then she got right back up and tried again. Will you go on bike rides with Charity?

name: Charles
meetText: You will usually find Charles working on a new drawing! He loves to doodle even if he doesn't have a specific idea in mind. Sometimes, drawing reminds Charles of fun memories and his family who live in a faraway land. He can't wait to visit them this year!

name: Charlie
meetText: This little pup is always on the go. Charlie has had the travel bug since he was little. He is spotted at the finest areas in the world. It makes sense since he aspires to break the news as a future reporter someday!

name: Charlize
meetText: Meet Charlize. She is a professional masseuse and thinks everyone could use a little more self-care. This chick is very strong and loves soothing her fellow Squishmallows whenever they need some TLC. What does she do for her own self-care? A nice weekend to herself in a cabin far, far away.

name: Charlon
meetText: Charlon entered his school's pumpkin carving contest. Think he can win? Charlon has carved a few pumpkins before, but that was just for fun. Charlon wants to impress the judges with a space design. He's been drawing little stars all month to practice!

name: Charlotte
meetText: Easter is one of Charlotte’s favorite holidays because it means she can jump in and out of as many Easter baskets as she wants. When she gets tired, she’ll nestle up in side one of the smallest baskets to enjoy a nice nap.

name: Chase
meetText: Chase loves camping, canoes, and capture the flag. Every summer he goes on a trip with his Squishmallow Scouts group and they have a blast, last year it was Chase that found the opposing team’s flag! If you love the outdoors then Chase is the cat for you.

name: Chasmen
meetText: Chasmen shows off his unique personality through flowing dresses and and brightly colored manicures. Every day is a new chance to make a statement and express himself. He embraces himself for exactly who he is and he wants you to, too!

name: Chauncy
meetText: Chauncy lives with his grandmother on a farm and helps her take care of all the animals. His favorite thing to do in the summer is to run through the sprinkler with all his friends. Chauncy wants to be a superhero when he grows up, what could his superpower be?

name: Chelsea
meetText: When Chelsea is not showing off her quick wit and her brilliant endurance, she enjoys relaxing with her friends. Known as "Chill Chelsea", she loves to stay home for a movie night, full of popcorn and laughter. Whenever Chelsea's friends are in need of a comfy cat-nap, they know Chelsea's their girl!

name: Cherie
meetText: Meet Cherie. There's nothing she can't handle, although she is a little afraid of the dark. But, she knows that doesn't mean that she's not brave. She's ready to conquer the world! All she asks is that you leave a light on.

name: Cherish
meetText: Roller skates, picnics, and crunchy peanut butter are some of Cherish's favorite things. This roller skating Squishmallow loves a good picnic by the beach, want to know her favorite sandwich? Peanut butter and banana!

name: Cherry
meetText: Cherry loves to create music. She enjoys playing the flute and wants to learn how to play more instruments every year. This year she wants to play the bass guitar and the tuba, which do you think she should try first?

name: Chester
meetText: Even though he's small, Chester is a strong shrimp. He works as a stage hand and helps set up many 'Mallow shows. Even though it is hard work, Chester loves traveling and exploring the interesting places he visit on tours.

name: Chet
meetText: Bobbleheads and sneakers are two things Chet loves to collect. He has almost 100 figurines and a crazy story for almost every pair of sneakers, just wait until you hear about his latest pair!

name: Cheyenne
meetText: This octocorn has a sweet tooth, can you guess her favorite treat? For her birthday last year, she had a candy-themed party. She had a candy cake, a candy buffet for party favors, and even a piñata!

name: Chienda
meetText: Chienda is a flower artist. She makes extravagant and strange bouquets at her flower shop that will make your eyes pop! She pairs flowers, feathers, shiny jewels, and even live butterflies, to make completely unique creations that look and smell amazing! Swing by and pick one up!

name: Chip
meetText: Chip is a smart guy! He is very kind and likes to help people. When he grows up, Chip wants to be an aircraft designer and fly the jets that he creates!

name: Chloe
meetText: Chloe is a pampered, prize winning show poodle who has an eye for style. She's happiest when she's playing dress-up with her friends. She's the perfect fashionista to accompany you on your next shopping spree!

name: Chloeyana
meetText: Who is always happy to see you with a big smile on her face? It's Chloeyana! She loves to go for an early morning walk and head back to bed until brunch. If she had her way, she could sleep and play all day.

name: Chrissy
meetText: Meet Chrissy. She's proud to be part of the LGBTQ community! This proud 'Mallow may have a coolcat exterior, but she's really just a big goofball! She loves grabbing burgers with her friends and has been known to squirt soda out of her nose from laughing so hard! Want to go?

name: Christian
meetText: Christian writes children's books with his pal, Nova! After Christian writes the story, Nova draws the pictures for it. They are working on a series now about a 'Mallow who goes on underwater adventures! Want to check out their latest story?

name: Chuck
meetText: Don't let his cute appearance fool you... Chuck is a tough chick. Chuck plays guitar, goes on the tallest rides at the far and is not afraid of the dark. Easter is his favorite holiday, since it's all about him!

name: Chuey
meetText: Chuey is a student of the world, he loves to pick up new tips and tricks on the adventures with his twin brother. They aren't old enough to travel on their own just yet, but they have a huge list of places they want to go. Where do you think they should go first?

name: Chuy
meetText: Do you need a racing partner? Or maybe someone to laugh and snuggle with? Chuy is the pup for you! This courageous Cairn Terrier may be small but his heart makes him ginormous. He loves playing with his sister Chloeyana and staying up late on his rooftop patio.

name: Cici
meetText: Cici loves commercials! She can recite almost any jingle at the drop of a hat and loves coming up with creative ideas for her friends and family. Look out world – here comes the next advertising CEO!

name: Cienna
meetText: Cienna is a daydreamer and loves collecting stickers. She especially enjoys listening to the sound of rain and taking pictures of thunderstorms. Her favorite color is rainbow, which might explain why she loves thunderstorms so much.

name: Cillian
meetText: Have you seen Cillian's vlog? He has thousands of followers and now he's turning his successful online series into a TV show! Since Cillian studies photography at his local art collage, he is developing the show at school-even his classmates love the idea! Want to help Cillian on set?

name: Cincy
meetText: Despite her beautiful wings, Cincy has a great fear of heights. With the encouragement of her friends she is gaining more and more confidence in her ability to fly. She now prefers soaring across the skyline downtown instead of walking through the streets. She can't walk a full city block without being asked to pose for selfies!

name: Cinda
meetText: Have you met Cinda the chef? Cinda's love language is food, eating AND preparing it, and she loves to share her food with friends. Cinda delivers meals to shelters and wants to start a nonprofit that feeds 'Mallows in need. Would you like to help?

name: Cindy
meetText: Cindy is a very shy cat but she loves to draw. She has her own comic book where she creates new stories based on things she finds fascinating each week and shares it with her friends. One day she wants to create a cartoon based on her comics to share with everyone!

name: Cinnamon
meetText: Cinnamon and her best friend Carmelita are like two peas in a pod, but sweeter! You can usually find them in the writing lab working on new stories or at the mall, they love to window shop. If you see them out and about, they'll be sure to give you a big hug.

name: Claire
meetText: Picking clover, enjoying the sunrise, and bananas on toast are some of Claire's favorite things. She is up bright and early every morning to help her family do chores.

name: Clara
meetText: Have you ever seen a ‘Mallow deadlift or power clean? It’s time you met Clara! This girl loves to see her friends at the local gym, they call themselves the Sugar Box Gang.

name: Clarice
meetText: Meet Clarice, one of the trendiest Squishmallows! Clarice's favorite activity is dyeing her bangs different colors. This caticorn could not settle on a color this time around, so she decided to dye her hair all of the colors in the rainbow! Do you like her rainbow bangs?

name: Clarissa
meetText: Clarissa loves the color purple and wearing sparkly shoes to school. She loves listening to her parents' records while painting in her attic - the music inspires a lot of her work. Clarissa is a hippie at heart, she loves bright colors, smiling faces and being kind to those around her.

name: Claudella
meetText: Meet Claudella. This handy 'Mallow knows how to build just about anything. Right now, Claudella is building a treehouse with a tire swing and a slide! She loves to soak up all the fun and sun of summer, and can't wait to spend time in her new happy place. Would you like to help?

name: Claudette
meetText: Claudette works as a meteorologist on 'Mallow channel 3. She loves reporting good weather news like rain after a drought, or a sunny day in the winter. Claudette is not only recognized on TV but also in her community! This 'Mallow loves to volunteer for environmental projects, and you can usually find her planting trees.

name: Claudia
meetText: Claudia wakes up with the sunrise! She's a responsible little beet and supports all her friends and family with anything they need – even if it's just for a laugh. Claudia knows that generosity comes in all forms, including goofy ones. And nobody makes a better key lime pie!

name: Clay
meetText: Clay has been participating in the beauty pageant circuit as long as she remember. Last year, Clay was crowned Little Miss County and went on to compete at all-star regionals! Judges can't get enough Clay's folky voice and mellow banjo when she performs for the talent round.

name: Clayton
meetText: Whenever Clayton is feeling anxious, he likes to imagine himself as Clayton the Brave, a comic book superhero. With superpowers of strength and courage. Clayton the Brave is able to vanish his nerves and bring peace to his mind. He even has a sidekick—The Weighted Blanket!

name: Cleary
meetText: Vroom, vroom! Cleary is in town for a big monster truck show and is ready to show off his speed skills, and freestyle crashing tricks. After the show, Cleary wants to take his squad out for a ride in his truck. Don't forget to wear ear protection!

name: Cleo
meetText: Cleo is an aspiring actress whose favorite Holiday is Halloween. She's president of the drama club and loves to get her friends together to dress up and act out scenes from some of their favorite plays.

name: Clover
meetText: Meet Clover! Your cuddly, squishy and udderly adoraBULL friend from Prince Edward Island! Clover loves to watch MOOvies while being warm and COWzy and gives great big hugs before hitting the hay.

name: Clutch
meetText: Meet Clutch. He is Archie’s best friend and teammate; they are almost inseparable. Clutch steps in to be Archie’s ears and advocate when they’re with someone who doesn’t sign. He taught their whole team how to sign for Archie’s birthday, would you like to learn?

name: Cobie
meetText: Say hi to Cobie! Cobie works hard on his family's farm from morning to night, and he loves having such an important job! Cobie's favorite part of the day is watching the colors in the sky change when the sun rises. Want to watch the sun rise with Cobie?

name: Coco
meetText: Meet Coco. Her favorite color is purple and she loves rock candy. Coco lives next door to her friends Florence and Amina, and they ride their bikes to school together every day. Coco's basket is purple with sparkles and her bike horn sounds like a foghorn.

name: Cody
meetText: Cody loves fixing cars and he’s a water polo coach. His hobbies include DIY projects and making beautiful things with any material he comes across. He loves listening to music and his favorite color is brown.

name: Cole
meetText: Ready for some robot rumble fun? Cole is your guy if you like building things and tearing them down, he loves making crazy cool robots and letting them race and dual it out, just don't destroy his best bot!

name: Coleen
meetText: Coleen only considers herself competitive when it comes to climbing in the playground! She can hang upside down longer than her classmates and is the fastest on the wavy bars. Rub your hands in some sand and come join Coleen on the dome climber!

name: Colleen
meetText: Colleen is the type of friend you call on for adventure, for advice, and more. She always seems to have the answer! Colleen has a heart like gold she loves spending time with people or taking care of them to help them feel better.

name: Colette
meetText: Colette sure loves to nap! She often dreams that she is a meow-maid in the water, exploring and collecting her favorite shells!

name: Colleta
meetText: Meet Colleta! She used to be afraid of the dentist then one day she conquered her fear. Now she's going to school to become a dentist so she can help 'Mallows who are afraid like her. Colleta hopes that by sharing her story she'll inspire others to conquer their fears too.

name: Coley
meetText: Coley is one gigglicious dragon and she loves to joke around with friends. It might sound corny, but Coley thinks that laughter can be the best medicine. She is the perfect 'Mallow to keep around when you need to turn your frown upside down.

name: Colin
meetText: Grab your mat and a set of weights, class is about to start! Colin is a barre instructor and teaches one of the most fun classes around. He has backlights and music blasting so his class feels like a party. No matter how tired you are, you'll want to dance it out!

name: Colm
meetText: You’re invited to Colm’s holiday music showcase! He’s been practicing new songs on his saxophone, piano, bongos, and cello. The best part is, he can play them all at the same time! Colm is a one ‘Mallow jazz band, and with his perfect coordination, he’s sure to be a hit at this year’s show.

name: Colton
meetText: Colton loves scary movies and popcorn - as long as there's some hot sauce on top! He has a blog dedicated to all the scary movies ever created. Can you guess his favorite?

name: Connie
meetText: Are you afraid of the dark? So is Connie! That's why this plucky yoga lover moved way far north. Though the days are super long, that's what Connie prefers--the more the sun is in the sky, the more she can salute it!

name: Connor
meetText: Original: Mooove out of the way, Connor is at the finish line waiting for you! Connor is quite the athlete! You can catch him riding his bike everywhere! What's the coolest place he's ever travelled to? Cowlifornia!

name: Conrad
meetText: Have questions about eating better? Conrad is the corn for you! He wants to be a chef one day and loves food science. He knows there is more to food than just taste and wants to share more about the science behind it.

name: Conradina
meetText: Meet Conradina. Conradina is an amazing writer. She sees the world with vivid imagery and emotion. Now she’s working up the courage to share her work. She wants to read in front of a crowd at open mic night, but public speaking makes her nervous. Can she practice reading a poem in front of you?

name: Conway
meetText: Are you looking for Conway? You should try calling his restaurant. Conway is the maître d' at Super Fancy, a new bistro downtown! Lucky for you, Conway always saves reservations for his best pals. Get ready for a glitzy night out and lots of yummy plates. Cheers!

name: Cookie
meetText: Cookie has been fascinated by flora and fauna ever since she’s been able to walk. She aspires to become a botanist some day to teach others all about plants!

name: Cooper
meetText: Cooper likes to think life is what happens in between naps! This 'Mallow always gets his beauty rest, but when it's time to have fun, Cooper is the first one there. Cooper joins his bestie, Sager, every Sunday to snuggle with a cozy blanket for their favorite shows and treats!

name: Cora
meetText: Have you ever met a cat who loves extreme sports? Cora loves doing things for the thrill; cliff diving, parasailing, and hang gliding are just some of the things she loves crossing off her bucket list. What's next? Swimming with sharks or scaling a mountain.

name: Coralie
meetText: Coralie studies biology at her dream school! She specializes in plant life and loves to take little samples on her weekend walks in the woods. Coralie wants to learn everything she can about plants, trees, and flowers so she can help protect them and keep beautiful plants growing forever!

name: Cordelia
meetText: Cordelia is a regular at all the local, small toy shops in her area. She drops by almost every weekend looking for new and unique keepsakes to add to her collection or gift to a close friend. Cordelia's favorite toys are miniatures so she can always hold onto one when she's on the go.

name: Corinna
meetText: Even though she's stuck at home, Corinna is one imaginative cat. She and her best friend Priya go on all kinds of magical adventures together. They love to look up at the clouds and pretend they're slaying dragons or hopping around on the clouds.

name: Cornelia
meetText: Cornelia is one of the funniest 'Mallows around. They have the gift of gab and know laughter is truly the best medicine. That's why they love making others laugh! With silly antics and spot-on impressions, Cornelia dreams of being a late-night talk show host.

name: Cornelias
meetText: Meet Cornelias. He loves to lend a helping hand, but be warned, he's known for his cheesy puns! They're so bad, you won't be able to help but giggle. For Cornelias, there is no task to big or small. And whatever he helps you with, you're guaranteed to have a ton of pun!

name: Cornella
meetText: Cornella is a total plant mom, some might say she likes plants a little more than 'Mallows. She loves plants of all varieties and sizes, ready to guess her current fave? The bonsai has a special place in Cornella's heart. What's your favorite plant?

name: Cortez
meetText: Meet Cortez. This 'Mallow is a true friend. He always has something uplifting and encouraging to say. Cortez is always ready to celebrate your glow-up! Plus he has eight arms, which makes him an amazing hugger!

name: Cosimo
meetText: Not everyone gets Cosimo's sense of humor—but his dedicated readers sure do! This edgy mushroom writes a weekly column in the local paper and never holds back his honest opinions. Sometimes Cosimo even receives responses from fans! Want to read Cosimo's latest article?

name: Cosmina
meetText: Make sure you schedule your checkup with Cosmina, she's the best dentist around! Cosmina loves to make her patients laugh, so if you're afraid to show your smile she'll put on her cheese hat to make you smile.

name: Cressida
meetText: Cressida is a tech wiz and loves everything digital. When she grows up, she wants to be a programmer, so she practices her coding whenever she can! If you're looking for Cressida - she's probably at her computer desk.

name: Cris
meetText: If you like playing with gadgets and fixing your mom's cell phone, then Cris is the Squishmallow for you! He knows all the phone and game hacks and will play any video game!

name: Crisanta
meetText: Meet Crisanta. She loves hot cocoa, ice skating, and going to the movies. She gets so excited when the cozy, winter weather sets in so she sips hot cocoa and bundles up in her favorite super-soft, cashmere scarf! She's amazing on the ice and would love to teach you her moves!

name: Crissle
meetText: Crissle is a true optimist at heart. She has a special talent for always being able to shine a positive light on any situation. She and Sunshine are best friends and even have a secret handshake! They'd love to teach it to you!

name: Cruz
meetText: Mini-golf and guac are two things Cruz can't live without, he would play every day if he could! He likes to have guac on everything, from breakfast foods and sandwiches to his mom's healthy avocado cupcakes!

name: Cyan
meetText: Meet Cyan. He's a great friend and an even greater singer. He and all his friends have formed an underwater traveling band and they swim around to all the different reefs to perform. Their favorite kind of music? You guessed it, the blues!

name: Cyma
meetText: Meet Cyma. She loves off-roading, concerts, and soccer. She especially enjoys cheering on her cousin Reginald, who taught her how to play. Cyma plays in her own league for 'Mallows with low vision. Are you ready to cheer her on in her next game?

name: Cyra
meetText: Meet Cyra. She can't wait to study abroad. She's been studying extra hard to make sure she's ready! She's most excited about the late-night dinners, espresso, and architecture! Do you want to practice your Spanish with her?

name: Cyrena
meetText: Cyrena is a cupcake queen! Every weekend she bakes up a giant batch of cupcakes in the most unique flavors that she can think of. Last week, she made passionfruit meringue cupcakes topped with sour sprinkles. This week, she's going to make a spicy hot chocolate flavored cupcake. Do you have any flavor ideas for Cyrena's next cupcakes?

name: Dabney
meetText: Meet Dabney. She's a composer and knows how to play almost every instrument in the world. Her two favorites are the violin and piano. Her music is known to melt hearts and make you feel all the feels! She's working on a new song, want to listen?

name: Dabria
meetText: Meet Dabria. She is always working hard and trying her best at everything she does. Whether it's selling jewelry at her store or supporting a friend, she always gives 100 percent. Her friends like to say that Dabria shines brighter than any diamond in her store.

name: Dahlia
meetText: Meet Dahlia. She loves all things miniature; little toy houses, little toy cars, and is building a mini mansion for all her little playthings. She loves to take care of her little town, maybe when she grows up, Dahlia will become the mayor of her own town!

name: Daisy the Bunny
meetText: Daisy loves to play and jump rope with her friends. The best thing about Daisy is her sweet personality.

name: Daisy
meetText: Daisy is dangerously creative! If you need someone to spice up your next outfit, Daisy is your go-to Squishmallow. From beadwork to embroidery to hair accessories and more, Daisy is the designer for you!

name: Daja
meetText: Beaches, volleyball and soaking up the sun are three of Daja's favorite things. This Squishmallow is the go-to gal for activities when the squad needs some fun in the sun!

name: Dakota
meetText: Dakota soars the skies searching for the perfect pie - she's a pastry chef in training! Her specialty? Dragon pies, crumbly crust on top and warm and delicious on the inside. One day you might be able to visit her pastry shop.

name: Daksa
meetText: Meet Daksa. Daksa is silly to the max and always seems to have hilarious inside jokes with their friends. They like to try new things even if they might fail. Once, they made pasta that tasted awful but it was so much fun to try so it was all worth it.

name: Dalha
meetText: Meet Dalha. She has loads of energy and she loves to run. Lately, when she runs she's been using her GPS to try and write secret messages with her friends. Last weekend she ran and spelled out 'LOVE!', what should she try to spell next?

name: Dalia
meetText: Dalia is a busy family doctor who sings in a mariachi band in her free time. She even plays the guitar and knows the lyrics by heart! Drop by her home during Día de los Muertos celebrations and be a part of this musical tradition.

name: Dallas
meetText: Don't be fooled by Dallas' cute exterior: she's one tough 'Mallow. She's a professional rugby player and has a black belt in karate! After a long day of being fierce, she loves winding down with hot yoga, hot cocoa, and a hot lavender bubble bath!

name: Dally
meetText: Meet Dally.  This cuddly pug loves to play tag, watch movies, and dress up. You can find Dally dressing up in all sorts of outfits from superheros to his favorite snacks. Do you want to play dress-up with Dally?

name: Dalton
meetText: Dalton adds chocolate milk to his marshmallow cereal and hot sauce on his omelets. He has trouble sharing and he needs you to help him learn how.

name: Damien
meetText: This dino knows how to beat the winter blues – snowboarding, snowboarding, snowboarding! You can catch Damien on the slopes with his friends or editing his latest video. His favorite color is red and for his birthday this year he got a brand-new red board.

name: Dandii
meetText: Meet Dandii. She spends all year looking forward to summer when she gets together with her extended family at their lake house. They have a giant oyster bake and play games like sack racing and tug-o-war. At night they catch lightening bugs in jars and watch them glow!

name: Dane
meetText: Original: Hi from Dane the Dragon! Dane is always ready for some action; he loves amusement parks! His favorite rides are the tallest rollercoaster he can find. When he's not soaring through the sky, he's already looking for the next best ride. Join Dane on his next roaring rollercoaster.

name: Dani
meetText: Dani loves sushi so much, she taught herself how to make it! This 'Mallow achieves anything she sets her mind to- like being the brand director of her favorite plush toy. When Dani's not working toward her goals, you can find her hosting a fun game night and feasting on homemade tuna rolls, with her besties, Jettward and Alfie!

name: Danielito
meetText: Meet Danielito. This cool cat is eager to learn new things and lives his life to the fullest! When he's not working in his family business, he is golfing, traveling, going to baseball games, and more. He loves playing the drums and making music with all of his different bands.

name: Danielle
meetText: Meet Danielle. She loves playing music, video games, and strawberry kiwi smoothies. Danielle plays the piano and is learning how to play the music from her favorite video games for her next recital. What song would you like her to play?

name: Danika
meetText: Danika starts her workout classes right on time — don't be late! This Pilates instructor does not cut corners. She helps every student reach their highest potential! If you're new to the exercise, Danika will train you in all the major poses. Ready to feel the burn?

name: Danilo
meetText: Did you know Danilo has a special power? He can put positive spin on anything! If Danilo runs into bad luck, he decides to take it as a learning experience. Danilo spreads thoughtfulness and optimism just by being around!

name: Danny
meetText: You will always want Danny on your team! Why? He is the king of games! Danny loves strategizing for board games, puzzles, outdoor sports, or scavenger hunts with his buddies.

name: Dante
meetText: Dante is the tour manager for a metal band, his friend Vlad is the lead singer. Dante loves ghost pepper hot wings and hosts a hot wing cookoff every fall. He calls his secret sauce “Dante’s Fire”, would you try his wings?

name: Danya
meetText: Meet Danya. She loves going to school because her class is filled with friends and she loves to learn about history. On the weekends she loves to explore the museums around her, especially the art museum. Do you want to tag along with Danya?

name: Darex
meetText: Have you met Darex? Darex may be a little loud and boisterous, but he gives the best bear hugs. Darex is a great builder and carpenter and he creates beautiful custom furniture. What can Darex build for you?

name: Darla
meetText: Meet Darla. She likes to play in the snow and catch snowflakes on her tongue. She may have rosy cheeks but she aspires to have a red nose. Nothing cheers her up like a hot cup of cocoa, she prefers whipped cream and sprinkles instead of marshmallows.

name: Daryl
meetText: Ready for liftoff? Daryl and Brock are best buds and they're headed to the space station for an adventure. Their mission? To see the universe! Daryl hopes to meet an alien or two, Brock wants to throw a football around the moon, are you ready to go?

name: Daryl The EMT
meetText: Meet Daryl. He's a first responder and is always there when someone needs help. Daryl has always loved helping people and loves his job as an EMT. Daryl has been in some scary situations but knows that staying cool, calm, and collected is very important. When you see the ambulance go by, make sure to wave at Daryl!

name: Dash
meetText: You will have to hurry to meet Dash, the Dragster racer. He is quick as can be and will show you how to screech into the finish line first. Just grab you shoes and your shades and jump into the race. Win or lose, it's always a fun time.

name: Dash
meetText: Meet Dash, the most artistic dumpling you'll find! Dash is inspired by classical works of art and loves to create designs of his own. He dreams of appearing in a museum one day - would you like to see some of his work?

name: David
meetText: Meet David, when he's not twirling his favorite noodle you can find him playing video games with his friends, just don't get mad if he levels up before you do! His favorite class is science and when he grows up he wants to be a research scientist.

name: Davie
meetText: Meet Davie. He loves figuring out how things work. He takes apart clocks and radios just to put them back together again! He's always tinkering with electronics and creating his own inventions. Next on his list? An alarm clock that wakes you up with eggs, bacon, and orange juice!

name: Davina
meetText: Though she's shy at first, Davina is a lot of fun, she does really great impressions and can almost always make you laugh. She wants to be a voiceover artist when she grows up, she has many voices and impressions that she just can't wait to try out.

name: Davitta
meetText: Davitta is a language teacher and this week her class is starting her favorite topic: forgotten languages. Even though they might not be used anymore, Davitta wants her students to know about them and why they no longer exist. Do you know any forgotten languages?

name: Dawn
meetText: Dawn is a tomboy who is always up for a camping adventure. She is fluent in all animal languages and loves to teach her friends all about the different animals who live in the forest. She hopes to be a park ranger one day!

name: Dawna
meetText: Dawna's favourite food is ice cream, can you tell? Dawna wants to become a food scientist to understand how to create treats that are as yummy as they are healthy.

name: Dax
meetText: Dax wants a hug when it's raining out and his feathers are too wet to fly, will you help Dax dry off?

name: Daxxon
meetText: Daxxon has traveled very far to join the Squishmallows Squad. He was exploring a new galaxy and met his best friend Rudy on the way. These best buds love to pretend they are superheroes and love to save the day.

name: Dear
meetText: When Dear was choosing a career for himself, he looked to his name for inspiration. This happy-go-lucky frog is a professional letter writer! Dear loves helping busy 'Mallows keep up with their pen pals. One day, he hopes to write acceptance letters for the local college!

name: Deacon
meetText: Sunday night ice cream sundae parties are at Deacon's house! Any time is a good time for ice cream, and Deacon loves to start off his week with triple scoops of rocky road, rainbow sprinkles, and extra cherries. Want to join Deacon's Sunday sundae party?

name: DeeDee
meetText: Meet DeeDee. She loves dancing, reading, and tending to her garden of sea cucumbers! She is patient, caring, and tries to learn something new every day. One day she wants to be a 1st-grade teacher and a mom. She's also an amazing baker! Want to try her shortbread cookies?

name: Deeto
meetText: Meet Deeto. His ears are as perky as his personality! Deeto loves picking flowers, going shopping, and having dessert before breakfast! He might be a little barky when he first meets you, but give him a belly scratch and he will love you forever.

name: Deezo
meetText: Take a deep-sea dive with Deezo! This 'Mallow wants to be a volcanist when he grows up and study underwater volcanoes! He's working on designing the perfect submarine for deep-sea adventures. Come explore with him!

name: Deidra
meetText: Deidra repairs and sells leather goods in her shop. Come by and check out her new satchels! This 'Mallow loves to work with her hands, and you can always find her behind the counter in the middle of a repair, listening to her favorite records.

name: Deja
meetText: Meet Deja. She loves improv, makeup, and vintage clothes. All of it help her to get into character. She's great at doing impressions and is perfecting all of her different accents. When she grows up, she wants to be a voice actor in animated movies!

name: Delaney
meetText: Meet Delaney. He can get overwhelmed when things are too loud, so if you see him put his headphones on, don't be alarmed. He listens to classical music to calm his nerves. Delaney can play flute, piano, and clarinet, and one day hopes to fulfill his dream of being a composer.

name: Delenne
meetText: Meet Delenne. She loves tea parties with fancy hats, tiny sandwiches, and cakes. Every year for her birthday she and her friends dress up for a birthday tea party. This year she wants to decorate mini-cakes and cookies, would you like to join?

name: Delfina
meetText: Meet Delfina. She loves bright-colored paintings, spicy candy, and telling stories with her friends. Delfina grew up with her aunt and spooky season is very special to them. They wear matching costumes every year and make special sugar skulls to share with their friends.

name: Delie
meetText: Delie is dressing up as her favorite animal — a bat! Last year, she was a flying fox bat. The year before that, a fruit bat. She's obsessed and knows all about them, like how they use echolocation to see where they're going. Watch out, this year she's a vampire bat!

name: Delilah
meetText: Delilah's favorite season is fall; she loves baking anything apple! Apple donuts, apple muffins, and especially caramel apples. Are you ready to become her baking assistant?

name: Delindy
meetText: Delindy loves live music! If you've got an extra ticket, she's guaranteed to want to come along and dance, no matter if the music is fast or slow! So put on a sparkly outfit, or some comfy dancing shoes, and get ready to move!

name: Delita
meetText: Meet Delita! Delita is a morning person who enjoys crosswords puzzles and breakfast. She makes a special granola recipe almost every day. One day Delita wants to have her very own granola shop! What kind of granola mix can Delita make for you?

name: Della
meetText: Meet Della. This ambitious athlete is going for gold as she swims for victory! She is one competitive duck which helps her stay motivated for those early morning swims! Do you have a sport you're training hard for?

name: Delores
meetText: Meet Delores. This clownfish cutie loves to dance! Fun fact about Delores: her love for dance inspired her to learn new languages. Delores is all about growth and trying new things, what inspires you?

name: Delphine
meetText: Meet Delphine. She loves flowers, heart-shaped balloons, and chocolate. She loves to live every moment to the fullest, which is why she always eats a piece of chocolate before her meal. The sugar isn't good for Delphine so she is going to try dark chocolate!

name: Delroy
meetText: Meet Delroy. Besides being a great friend, Delroy has a superpower. Its his stomach! He can eat anything and everything. When you're full, he's going back for seconds. It's no wonder his favorite restaurant is buffet style!

name: Delva
meetText: Devla loves going to the beach, if she could she would live there. She loves the sound of the ocean, the warm sun, and picnics with her friends. Do you want to join?

name: Demi
meetText: Demi appreciates life's simple moments, like the rustling sound of leaves, and the crisp smell of of autumn air. When he's not flying around town, Demi goes apple picking with his squad! This 'Mallow's favorite apples are red and sweet, making them perfect for pies - and he wants your help to bake them!

name: Demir
meetText: Demir loves all kinds of water activities. Whether it's scuba diving, snorkeling, or surfing, you can always find them near the beach. Demir is saving up to buy a boat and learn how to sail, do you want to join?

name: Den
meetText: There goes Den making another touchdown! This speedy 'Mallow knows when to scramble or throw, and is always ready to support his teammates. Off the field, Den chills out with a good book or rides his scooter around town with pals.

name: Denise
meetText: Denise loves donuts, iced coffee, and spending time with her family. She is the go-to mermaid for the latest hair and makeup trends in all the ocean, and still has time to keep up with her friends looking fab! You can recognize her signature nails and matching purple hair.

name: Deniz
meetText: Do you have an alter ego who loves to be the center of attention? So does Deniz! After his first improv class, his alter ego blossomed and this once-shy pelican rules the stage! He loves to practice new roles and push his limits as a performer. One day you can see him perform!

name: Dent
meetText: Dent just moved from the other side of the globe! He's starting to meet new 'Mallows at school, but some of them have a hard time understanding his accent. Dent loves cinema and he can't wait to be a film critic. So if you get to know Dent, he'll be sure to give you a great movie suggestion!

name: Denton
meetText: Meet Denton! Denton is Kent's older sibling and loves supporting Kent's dreams of being on-stage by helping with his makeup. When the stage isn't calling, Denton likes to sit at the park and sketch everything from a new perspective. Do you want to see some of Denton's work?

name: DeRay
meetText: DeRay plays video games all day! He works in the video game industry testing new games and reporting any bugs or glitches. There’s no difficulty level DeRay can’t beat. He can even play an entire game straight through without losing! There’s no doubt this ‘Mallow is the best gamer around.

name: Derek
meetText: Derek is a curious explorer who enjoys taking epic backpacking trips through different cities with his friends! He always comes back from his trips with fascinating tales that inspire others to go out and explore. His dream is to become a National Geographic Explorer. So he can conduct expeditions that shed light on a corner of the world that no one has yet discovered! He's training for a body building competition right now, and after that, a marathon!

name: Desmund
meetText: When it comes to cooking, look no further than Desmund! Not only does Desmund cook with the best spices and flavors, but he also heats up his steak with his burning hot breath. Everyone in his squad loves a special, home-cooked meal made by Desmund!

name: Destiny
meetText: Destiny's favorite place to visit with her family is the aquarium. She loves watching the colorful fish swim around in their large tanks, visiting the shark lagoon, and touching sea jellies. The highlight of Destiny's day is learning all about the incredible creatures that live in the ocean!

name: Dessa
meetText: Dessa loves sports, video games, and dreams of becoming a model. She loves to try on new accessories and showoff on the catwalk for her friends. When she's not busy working on a new look, you can find her engrossed in a game and strategizing the next move with her 'Mallow teammates.

name: Detina
meetText: Meet Detina. She is one cuddly pup who is eager to make new friends and go on adventures! Detina loves to give emotional support, but make sure you give it back because Detina can get anxious, too. When she's not at the park with friends, she is at home cooking up a new adventure.

name: Detra
meetText: Looking for a Halloween costume? Give Detra a call! Detra works at a costume shop and has a costume for everyone! She loves to help find the perfect costume, do you have anything in mind?

name: Devika
meetText: This birthday babe is having a great day! Devika's birthday started off with breakfast in bed; blueberry pancakes and chocolate milk. At school, her friends covered her locker with streamers and balloons. Can you guess what she wants to do next?

name: Devin
meetText: Knock, knock, here is Devin! Devin is an aspiring standup comedian and loves knock-knock jokes! This silly Squishmallow thinks that comedy is the answer to everything and will always have a joke ready if you are having a bad day.

name: Devra
meetText: Are you ready for a style session with Devra? This diva-licious dragon wants to be a stylist and has all her friends glammed up in home-style chic. She loves to go through her virtual closet app and plan red-carpet looks for her friends. What can she style for you?

name: Dexter
meetText: Dexter is a unique individual who loves to fly around town with his friend Brody. His dream is to become a pilot and travel the world, but for now Dexter sticks to soaring the skies around his neighborhood showing off the tricks Brody taught him to their group of fun-loving fly friends!

name: Dezzy
meetText: Unlike her sister Meg, Dezzy does not like the outdoors. Sleepovers with scary stories, makeovers, and of course making s'mores are more her style. To compromise, Meg and Dezzy have sleepovers in their treehouse. Do you want to join them?

name: Diana
meetText: Meet Diana. Whether she's spreading her wings on the dance floor or taking a stroll through the park, this social butterfly is guaranteed to bump into someone she knows. Come meet her! She loves trying new things, making new friends, and always accepts others for who they are!

name: Dianalee
meetText: Dianalee is a world-famous pop star! This musically-gifted 'Mallow loves to sing about practicing positivity, helping others, and doing it all with a smile. Though she's constantly on the road. Dianalee always makes time for her biggest fans of all time—her family!

name: Diane
meetText: Diane recently gradutated college and is taking her new life one day at a time. She submitted a few job resumes this morning before going to rowing practice. Even without a new routine, Diane still has shepherd's pie for dinner at her favorite bistro almost every night! Would you like to join her?

name: Diedre
meetText: If you've got rhythm and can handle some competition, you might be the perfect match for Diedre. She and her friends love to jump rope and are getting ready for a big contest. They're looking for the best jump ropers around, are you ready to jump on in?

name: Diego
meetText: Inspired by his surroundings, Diego uses the jungle as his muse for all of the poems that he writes. He recently had one published in the local paper!

name: Dina
meetText: Dina loves blue-raspberry Danishes and watching the sunrise. She reads books with her friend Tatiana every weekend and wants to travel to all the places she reads about.

name: Dion
meetText: Ready for a delicious snack? Dion is here to make your day! She loves making yummy snacks for her friends; usually cheese, crackers, and something sweet. She's ready to be the host with the most!

name: Dionne
meetText: Here comes Dionne! He's a wiz at tabletop games, but sometimes his wings flap and blow all the pieces down! At least he got his fiery hiccups under control, and he has a squad to help him get the game back on track! Do you have what it takes to play with Dionne?

name: Ditka
meetText: Ditka is currently working on getting her broom license! She's still learning and flies into trees every once in a while but she doesn't mind! She loves trying new things and working at them until she's mastered them! Next, she wants to perfect her cauldron cooking skills!

name: Ditty
meetText: Say hi to Ditty. He wants to be a geologist and has a huge collection of rocks and minerals! Sometimes Ditty goes hunting for quartz and fossils in the mountains with his friends! Would you like to go rock hunting with Ditty?

name: Dixie
meetText: Binge watching sci-fi shows and drawing are two things Dixie is known for, she loves the design inspo! Dixie wants to be an architect and has notebooks full of crazy cool designs. Her latest drawing has 3 garden rooftops and a waterfall.

name: Dobrilla
meetText: Meet Dobrilla. She's a fashion model who lives for the catwalk. Catch her rolling down the runway in her wheelchair, all decked out with jewels and a fringe. When she's not modeling, Dobrilla loves to knit, play video games, and go on scavenger hunts.

name: Dohna
meetText: Meet Dohna. She love fashion and design! Her collection of shoes and purses is so amazing, people have asked her to open her own closet museum! When she is not working as a personal designer, she is hiking and playing pickleball! Do you want to take a look at Dohna's collection?

name: Dolma
meetText: Grab your camera and follow along with Dolma. She's a tour guide who loves to entertain her guests. She loves showing off her city and helping 'Mallows discover new sights to see. Would you like to join her tour?

name: Dominic
meetText: Dominic's favorite place to visit with his family is the aquarium. He loves watching the colorful fish swim around in their large tanks, visiting the shark lagoon, and touching sea jellies. The highlight of Dominic's day is learning all about the incredible creatures that live in the ocean!

name: Dixie
meetText: Binge watching sci-fi shows and drawing are two things Dixie is known for, she loves the design inspo! Dixie wants to be an architect and has notebooks full of crazy cool designs. Her latest drawing has 3 garden rooftops and a waterfall.

name: Dominik
meetText: Meet Dominik. He loves shoes! His closet is full to the brim with fancy footwear! That's because he has to buy extra to fit all of his eight feet! He's currently looking for the perfect pair of leather boots to go with his witch costume! Want to help him shop?

name: Donaver
meetText: If you're afraid of the dark give Donaver a call, he loves things that glow at night. He has a collection of cool lava lamps of all shapes and sizes. He even has streamers and stickers that glow for his bike!

name: Donnan
meetText: Meet Donnan. This super-smart 'Mallow is a doctor and a scientist! And guess what? She found the cure for hiccups! That's right. You never have to worry about drinking your soda too fast again! When she's not in the lab, Donnan loves to rollerblade of tend to her herb garden.

name: Donnelly
meetText: You can usually find Donnelly with their headphones on making music on their keyboard! They love mixing lo-fi beats and even layering in real life dialogue. Donnelly always gives their tracks a personal touch. follow Donnelly's playlist to hear their latest tunes

name: Donnie
meetText: Meet Donnie. He loves board games and movie nights; his family plays a new game every month! When he grows up, Donnie wants to open a game store where people can play board games and watch movies.

name: Doreen
meetText: This cheetah-corn loves a good beat, she plays the drums and wants to start her own band. For practice she puts on a show for all her stuffed animals and occasionally her grandparents, they are her biggest fans.

name: Dorgee
meetText: Meet Dorgee. He loves anything outdoorsy and in nature! He is the activities leader at his summer camp and takes his role seriously. So don't forget your sunscreen and your water bottle, and get ready for fun outdoor exploration with Dorgee!

name: Dorina
meetText: Birthdays are extra-special when Dorina’s around. This ‘Mallow loves to celebrate her friends the whole week! She makes cards, sends them a special birthday treat, and loves to sing them a special birthday song.

name: Dorthea
meetText: Meet Dorthea, she loves biking, climbing mountains, and staying busy. Dorthea hates sitting still for so long so don't expect her schedule to be free at the drop of a hat. She's planning a camping trip very soon, would you like to join her?

name: Dottie
meetText: Dottie goes through many phases. Last month, she only ate french fries and Caesar salads! Now Dottie's obsessed with purple things, like acai bowls, lavender wallpaper, and amethyst crystals. What do you think Dottie's next phase will be?

name: Doug
meetText: Doug is very smart and an athlete. His favorite sports are basketball and volleyball and he likes to write on rainy days. He loves to play in the mud and sometimes chase squirrels around his yard. When he grows up, Doug wants to be a pilot.

name: Dove
meetText: Dove is a flying attendant with a dream: to be the savannah's first crocodile pilot! Though the lions in the cockpit think she's crazy, Dove is determined to prove them wrong—with her sky-high persistence she's bound to!

name: Doxl
meetText: Doxl lives on a farm where he grows organic veggies and herbs. What he doesn't eat, he donates to the local school so the students can have a healthy and organic lunch! When he's not gardening, you can find him playing table tennis with his best friend, Leonori.

name: Drake
meetText: Drake is here to take your blood... for donation. Drake aspires to be a nurse, and help others as much as he can. He wants to treat patients and offer them the best care, even on Halloween night!

name: Dray
meetText: Meet Dray. He is an expert typer by day and a professional cartoon watcher by night. If you couldn't tell, Dray is one busy 'Mallow! In case you're wondering, Dray has hot takes on animation styles that he'd love to discuss. Have you seen any good cartoons lately?

name: Drella
meetText: Drella and her sister Marina are complete opposites. Marina loves to play outside while Drella would rather stay inside and play video games. Drella's favorite thing about spring is the rainy days.

name: Drella
meetText: Meet Drella. She loves playing catch with her friends, sprinkles on her cupcakes, and loves to climb. She loves to hike and see how far she can get. Maybe one day she'll climb to the top of Mallow Mountain!

name: Drew
meetText: Drew is a confident little creature who has a passion for baseball! When he is not playing in the fantasy league, he likes going on magical adventures to new stadiums. Drew's creative mind loves learning new languages and hopes to one day become an airplane engineer so he can travel to all the enchanted stadiums!

name: Drow
meetText: Meet Drow. He doesn't use his wings much because he's afraid of heights! But what he lacks in flying skills, he makes up for with his funky dance moves. But be warned, if you catch him on the dance floor, he might challenge you to a friendly dance-off!

name: Duane
meetText: Whoosh! That's the sound of Duane cutting through the ice rink with his triple axel. When Duane really wants to dazzle the judges at competitions, he uses his wings to lift over the ice. Duane ice skates year-round and hopes to one day turn it into his full-time career!

name: Duchess
meetText: Duchess loves her "me time". She pampers herself with cucumber cooling eye masks, bubble baths, and of course, soothing temple massages. Despite Duchess' needed alone time, she absolutely loves a Spa Day with her friends. Would you care to join them?

name: Duffy
meetText: When you look into Duffy's big puppy eyes, you can't help but fall in love. He is a snuggly, playful champion, perfect to join any family.  Don't forget to give him a treat every once in a while.

name: Duke
meetText: Duke and his brother Dominic are both fascinated by the ocean! Duke pretends that he is a deep-sea diver and wishes he could swim down to see the creatures who live at the bottom of the ocean.

name: Duma
meetText: Duma loves hanging with besties and is a bigtime fashionista. She also holds a softball record for bases stolen, because she's super-fast!

name: Duna
meetText: Duna collects everything! She especially fond of tiny things like soap bars, seashells, and sticky notes. Her family has asked her to donate some of her extra collections, but she never had a heart to do it. For Duna, everything she collects is important to her. What do you collect?

name: Duncan
meetText: If you've got a problem, Duncan can probably solve it. He's an all-around handy dinosaur who always has his tool belt with him. He's an aspiring architect and loves to map out his own blue prints in his spare time.

name: Dunkie (Wilfred)
meetText: Meet Dunkie. She’s planning her next tropical vacation! She can’t wait to snorkel, try new foods, and hang with her friends. She is loud and boisterous and always orders dessert for the table! Pack your suitcase and come with!

name: Dustin
meetText: Original: Meet Dustin. This active little pup is always ready for adventure. He was once a rescue pup so he knows a thing or two about rescuing others! When he is not training for a frisbee contest he is volunteering at his local fire station. Join Dustin on his next adventure.

name: Easton
meetText: Meet Easton. Scared of the dark? Don't worry, Easton will light your way! This bright 'Mallow always has a smile on his face and something fun and interesting to talk about! He loves deep talks with friends over passion fruit shaved ice. Want to join?

name: Eden
meetText: In the mornings before high tide, Eden climbs the hills and wedges through a cave that opens up to a beautiful secret beach! This is where Eden hosts post-hike bagel picnics for her friends and family that come along on the adventure. Want her to show you the way?

name: Edden
meetText: Edden is quite the little matchmaker. She loves finding a spark that creates long-lasting relationships. Need any advice? Edden is your girl!

name: Edie
meetText: Have you heard the weekly weather report? Make sure you tune in to Edie's Eggcellent Weather Report to find out! Edie loves to talk about the weather and always tries to dress the part. Her favorite ensemble is a jumpsuit with lightning bolts that glow in the dark!

name: Edita
meetText: Meet Edita. She dreams of being a travel blogger. She loves to travel and is always taking photos of her favorite transportation method - the subway. She hopes to make travel safer for 'Mallows like her who want to travel alone, so if you have any advice she's all ears.

name: Edmund
meetText: Though he can easily fly down the mountain, Edmund loves to show off his crunchy moves and feel the fresh snow under his board. This is one pterodactyl who loves cruisin' down the slopes.

name: Eduardo
meetText: Eduardo is a little shy but a loyal friend to have, he is kind to everyone he meets. He enjoys playing video games or even going camping with his brothers, they always have a good time.

name: Edward
meetText: Edward is always ready for the next adventure! This patriotic Squishmallow loves history and shares some of his favorite tales with his Squishmallow pals. Fun fact about Edward: he can remember almost every name in history! And his favorite holiday? You guessed it, the 4th of July! Join this little eagle on his next expedition.

name: Effie
meetText: This is one toy obsessed 'Mallow, she loves to review toys and share them all with her squad. Effie reviews new toys and then donates them for other mini 'mallows to enjoy. Do you have any toys to share with Effie?

name: Efua
meetText: Meet Efua. They are a sleepy owl by day and an exclusive chef by night. If you can score an invite to one of their pop-up eateries, you're in luck! What's on the menu? A yummy sweet and sour soup, just be sure to let it cool first!

name: Egbert
meetText: Egbert manages his college radio station. He has his own show Tuesday and Thursday nights-call in and request a song! Sometimes Egbert interviews students and professors or will update listeners on important school events. Will you tune in to Egbert's radio show?

name: Eiko
meetText: If you like to dress up and have fancy dinners, you'll love hanging out with Eiko. Eiko believes in dressing for a special occasion, but for him, every event is special! His awards season parties are known to be the best among all his friends. Don't worry, your invitation is on its way!

name: Eileen
meetText: Eileen started a community event called Spring Seeds. On the first day of spring, town residents are encouraged to plant a seed of anything they like and share the growth progress throughout the year. Eileen even sends pictures of her sprouting plant to the weekly paper. Imagine all the gorgeous gardens this will create!

name: Elanor
meetText: Meet Elanor. She is one lucky pup because sometimes she gets to go to work with her mom. Elanor loves those days because she has a lot of friends and toys to play with while she's there. She loves having a day for fun, would you like to tag along one day?

name: Elda
meetText: Elda is a dance teacher who also fixes cars. When she was little, she just couldn't decide what she wanted to be when she grew up! Her friends used to laugh when she said she could do both but now they come to her when they need a tune-up or an extra salsa lesson.

name: Eliana
meetText: Do you want to work on a puzzle with Eliana? She can be a tiny bit shy, but when she's working on a puzzle you can bet she gets excited, especially if it's a big one. Right now she's trying to finish one with 1500 pieces!

name: Elida
meetText: Looking for some help on your next big project? Give Elida a call, she is an A+ Project Manager who loves to lend a helping hand! Elida loves organization and keeping everything in check, she says that's her happy place. What keeps her organized you ask, her lucky, pink planner!

name: Elin
meetText: Elin loves math and is the treasurer and founding member of the math club at school. Her mission is to help others understand how math can be fun and a valuable skill for all. One day she wants to be an accountant!

name: Elina
meetText: Elina is a food critic and writes reviews for all the new restaurants in town. Though she can be harsh, she has excellent taste and is very kind with her words. When she's not writing about food, you can find her tending to her garden or gearing up for a hike.

name: Elio
meetText: Meet Elio! Come wintertime he's a total homebody. This 'Mallow is delighted to spend all his free time napping on the sofa or cooking himself a hot and fulfilling meal. Elio keeps his home neat and tidy by cleaning a little bit each day. Grab a blanket and kick back with Elio!

name: Elisa
meetText: Sparkles, sci-fi, and fuzzy slippers are some of Elisa's favorite things. This cheetah-corn is not a morning person but she's always ready for an adventure. On the weekends you can find her doing yoga or snoozing in the sun, with her favorite smoothie on deck!

name: Elizabella
meetText: Helping others is something Elizabella values very much, this year she wants to start volunteering! She has just one problem: she doesn't know what she should do first. Can you help her decide?

name: Ella
meetText: Ella is a talented ballerina who dreams of attending the Squishmallow Consevatory. Just like her older sister Lola, she loves to visit new places. She plans on joining a traveling dance company after the Conservatory in order to see the world!

name: Elle
meetText: Lights, camera action! Looking for Elle? She is the creative eye of the friend group. Elle loves to direct music videos, short films and video tutorials with her favorite Squishmallows cast and crew.

name: Ellen
meetText: Ellen is a barista who does the most amazing latte art! Hearts, paisley patterns, and beautifully detailed leaves are just some of the designs she creates with espresso and foam. Swing by her coffee shop and let her whip you up something tasty and artistic!

name: Ellette
meetText: Meet Ellette! He looks bite sized, but he has a king sized personality! He even hands out king sized candy bars at his castle every Halloween. Ellette brings fun and laughter everywhere he goes. If you catch him at the right time, he'll even sing a song for you! What song would you like to hear Ellette sing?

name: Ellie
meetText: Are you ready to have tons of fun? Meet Ellie the elephant! This elephant is not your average gal, she loves making her friends smile and is quite the comedian. Ellie enjoys spending summers abroad and spends the holidays with her loved ones.

name: Elliene
meetText: Elliene loves spreading the joy of reading so much that she's built a tiny free library in her front yard. She's decorated it with colorful flowers and filled it with all of her favorite books. Anyone can stop by and take one. All are welcome!

name: Elliot
meetText: Elliot is Nick's little helper. He is second in command to make the holidays as sweet as the Squishmallows are. He enjoys eating the cookies that Nick leaves behind on Christmas Day. Shh don't tell Santa!

name: Ellixsa
meetText: Ellixsa knows that you can't rush the good things in life. That's why she takes everything nice and slow. After finishing her homework, she loves doing yoga or reading in her hammock in the backyard. She believes life is about enjoying the moment no matter what you're doing.

name: Elodie
meetText: Are you ready for arts & crafts? Join Elodie for some crafting fun! Her favorite colors are pink and red and she loves to mix and match her DIY home decor. If you need some DIY inspiration or want to spend the day crafting, give Elodie a call!

name: Eloise
meetText: Original: Meet Eloise, the chicest cat in town! This kitty is known for her impeccable taste in style. When she is not on the runway she enjoys crafting with different colors on new creations. Are you ready to see Eloise's next collection?

name: Elsa
meetText: Elsa wants to be a teacher when she grows up. She spends her time helping her friends with their homework and DIY projects when she's not in school.

name: Elton
meetText: Elton is always up to something! Whether he’s tinkering with a watch, a truck or a toy, he’s fascinated by the way things work!

name: Elvio
meetText: Elvio is usually a quiet 'Mallow, but not when it comes to participating in big celebrations with his friends and family! Thats why his favorite holiday is Día de los Muertos. The parade and parties start tonight want to join in the festivities?

name: Elysa
meetText: Introducing... Elysa! This slow slug moves at a leisurely pace.
