Instead of focusing on running quickly through life, Elysa slides down the road, observing and appreciating the complex and beautiful world around her. If you are in need of an intellectual and deep conversation, Elysa is your girl!

name: Liv
meetText: Who loves cheese, space, and nature walks? Liv does! You can find her with a grilled cheese in hand, gazing up at the stars learning about constellations. She wants to build rocket ships when she grows up, do you want to explore space with Liv?

name: Emani
meetText: Emani is Nicole's right-hand elf. She helps keep the North Pole running and makes sure all the elves, reindeer, and even Santa himself are on schedule. What's her secret to success? Naps, cute planners, and being fearless.

name: Emela
meetText: Meet Emela. When she's not in her greenhouse tending to her orchids, you can find her at the farmer's market picking out the perfect peaches to make fresh jam. Emela is the best houes guest because she always brings homemade treats and flowers. Would you like a visit from Emela?

name: Emerald
meetText: Emerald is a talented psychic who enjoys helping meteorologists predict when it's going to rain. When she isn't  at the weather  station you can find Emerald playing Go Fish, a card game she's particulary talented at. Got any 3s?

name: Emery
meetText: Emery is the queen of caffeine! She loves to have friends over for coffee so she can show off her barista skills. She loves to make fancy coffee concoctions with rose petals, lavender, and even gold foil. What can Emery make for you?

name: Emiliano
meetText: Emiliano is a dental assistant by day and a saxophone legend by night. He plays the saxophone with a group of friends at their favorite coffee shop. Do you want to go hear them play?

name: Emily
meetText: Just like her older brother Bart, Emily loves space! Her dream is to become an astronomer so she can help name the new planets and stars that are discovered. Emily also enjoys studying astrology. In her free time, she uses her telescope to study star patterns and creates horoscopes for her friends.

name: Emma
meetText: Emma has a heart of gold, and loves to put that into her artwork. What’s her next arts and crafts project? She is creating friendship bracelets for her best friends Lana and Luke!

name: Emmeline
meetText: Meet Emmeline. She helps Gina and Ruby make the best hot cocoa in the North Pole, just don't ask for her secret recipe! Some of her favorite things are music, art, and gingerbread houses. Emmeline loves to sing while she works. Can you guess her favorite song to sing?

name: Emmi
meetText: Pasta, basketball, and watching funny movies are some of Emmi's favorite things. She also plays guitar and loves to dance - this is one busy sloth! When she grows up, Emmi wants to be a news anchor.

name: Emmie
meetText: Meet Emmie. She's a happy-go-lucky kind of gal. She never wakes up with a plan which allows her endless possibilities of adventure. One of her favorite things to do is hop in her spaceship and set off for a new planet to experience new cultures and foods! Do you want to join her?

name: Emmy
meetText: Meet Emmy. She's in charge of all the toys in Santa's workshop! Emmy has her own list that gets checked twice every day! She is one organized elf. When Emmy's not tracking toys on spreadsheets you can find her at Fiona's, trying her latest ice cream flavor.

name: Enid
meetText: Enid studies folklore and knows hundreds of old tales. Want to here one? Right now, Enid is working on a project about fairies because she wants to prove they're real! Enid is still collecting the data but she knows she'll find a whimsical fairy soon enough.

name: Enos
meetText: Enos is the president of his high school conservation club! Last year he successfully protested the demolition of his favorite oak tree, Roberta. Though some call him a tree hugger. Enos doesn't see why that's a bad thing---after all, trees need hugs too!

name: Enrique
meetText: Enrique loves to play with building blocks, he could spend a weekend building a whole new world! When he grows up he wants to build his own house and he can have a room for all his blocks.

name: Ensley
meetText: Every spring Ensley attends to local Spring Mallow-Maze. This year she'll be racing through the maze to win the giant golden egg! Join Ensley on her next egg hunt!

name: Eric
meetText: Meet Eric. This blobfish is adventurous and lazy at the same time. He loves kayaking, paddle boarding, and a good nap. He's a funky reggae music superfan who loves to jam. Fun fact about Eric: he could eat peanut butter fudge ice cream for breakfast, lunch, and dinner.

name: Erie
meetText: Meet Erie. Catch this thrill-seeker front row on the fastest rollercoaster in the park. Erie loves theme parks and that exhilarating feeling of being at the top of a ride before it drops! Join if you dare!

name: Erika
meetText: This tabby cat tries to stay out of trouble, but she loves to play practical jokes. Her favourite day is April 1st, she plans her jokes months in advance! Do you have any ideas about what she could do next?

name: Erin
meetText: Erin organizes her backpack weeks before the new school year starts and always fills it with fresh supplies. This 'Mallow looks forward to all the subjects she will learn and plans on signing up to be a writing tutor this year. Want Erin to help you with your history essays?

name: Erissa
meetText: Don't touch that dial!—Erissa chooses the radio station around here! Whether it's a talk show or old pop ballads, this 'Mallow is always tuned in. Some of the local stations even know her name since Erissa calls in song requests every Friday! Do you have a song you'd like to hear?

name: Ernest
meetText: Ernest sits outside the dessert shop with a hot chocolate almost every weekend. Sometimes he challenges young 'Mallows to play tic-tac-toe with him. Best out of five! And the winner gets to keep all of Ernest's Halloween Candy. Think you can beat Ernest at tic-tac-toe?

name: Esme
meetText: Have you heard the weather report? Esme can share it with you! She wants to be a storm chaser when she grows up, following storms across the sea and tracking their next moves. She is fascinated by how the weather impacts her world.

name: Esmeralda
meetText: Esmeralda has quite the colorful personality. Her creativity is always shining through, especially in her artwork. Her collections brighten the room and inspire positivity wherever she goes.

name: Esmeralda
meetText: Say hello to Esmeralda the grocery clerk! She loves helping people at her store and knows how important it is to greet them with a smile and some sanitizer to keep them safe. Esmeralda used her love for art to decorate all the signs in the store, including a giant mural reminding the mallows to wear their masks.

name: Esmina
meetText: Movies that make you cry, chocolate ice cream, and pjs is Esmina's perfect night. Instead of going out with friends, she sometimes prefers to stay home. Though she loves the company, sometimes being by herself feels great.

name: Essy
meetText: Essy attends all the punk shows in her area. She makes sure to have a healthy meal before every show so she has lots of energy to dance. You should see her ticket collection—it fills an entire bulletin board! Want to join Essy at her next show?

name: Estrella
meetText: Interested in learning a new hobby? Join Estrella to try something new. She enjoys thinking outside the box, learning as she goes, and making friends along the way.

name: Ethan
meetText: Ethan is one with his community - connecting Squishmallow squads from every age group, size, and location. His passion for unity is highlighted by his work to bring everyone together. He's excited to pass out Valentines to the whole Squishmallow squad.

name: Eunice
meetText: Meet Eunice. She is a DIY diva who loves glitter, glam, and glitz. Eunice loves to add glitter to almost everything, from her notebooks and school supplies to clothes and even her hair! While it sometimes gets messy, she loves to see things sparkle.

name: Eva
meetText: Sweet and tangy treats are Eva's favorite kind, especially blue raspberry cotton candy. Her favorite cousins live by the beach and whenever she visits them, she gets a fresh cone all to herself.

name: Evangelica
meetText: Meet Evangelica. She is a huge animal lover and has a soft spot for animals in need. She works at a rescue farm where she takes care of animals of all kinds. She cooks for them and even reads them stories at night. Would you like to volunteer with her?

name: Evelina
meetText: Meet Evelina, this Evelina wants to save the day. She wants to be an OR nurse when she grows up. As a mini 'Mallow she was hurt and a nurse saved her life. She wants to save lives and inspire future nurses one day at a time.

name: Evelyn
meetText: Video games and slushies are two of Evelyn's favorite things. Her favorite flavor combo is cherry and green apple because they turn her tongue funny colors. She's not allowed to mix them while playing though, in case she accidentally spills on her controller!

name: Ever
meetText: Ever draws her saber with care and grace in every fencing match. She knows being a good sport is more important than winning. It's one reason Ever is so well respected by her peers, and as she grows up, she's considering becoming a fencing instructor. Would you take one of Ever's classes?

name: Everett
meetText: Meet Everett. He has a superpower — he can speed read! On the weekends, he goes to the library to see how many books he can read in a day. Once he read 4 books in only a few hours, so far that's his record! What book should he read next?

name: Evie
meetText: Evie’s favourite questions are ‘did you know?’ And ‘why?’ She loves to learn and share her findings with all her friends. When she’s not busy fact finding, her favourite activities are collecting flowers and twirling! Her favourite foods are marshmallows, chocolate and avocados!

name: Evita
meetText: Grab your snowshoes and join Evita on her next wild, wilderness adventure! But you better bundle up — this 'Mallow never gets cold. She has been known to hike through snowstorms and loves catching snowflakes on her tongue!

name: Eyk
meetText: Meet Eyk. He's a bit of a perfectionist. He will work on something until he thinks it's just right, like his famous strawberry cheesecake recipe or his amazing classical piano skills! Whatever it is Eyk tries his hand at, he always gives it one hundred and ten percent!

name: Ezrah
meetText: Ezrah is one lucky elf, he gets to work with Norma and Norman in the woodshop! When it's time for the elves to start building, he brings new ideas and designs with some help from Santa's wishlist. What can Ezrah build for you?

name: Fabiola
meetText: Meet Fabiola. This fish has a passion for FASHION! She loves to stand out and make the world her runaway. In addition to being a style icon, Fabiola also has a gift of gab. You can ask anyone, she loves some feel-good gossip but she knows when the gossip has gone too far.

name: Faith
meetText: Faith loves playing with toys, and hopes that someday she can make toys! Between styling her toys' hair and changing their outfits, it's not hard to see Faith's creativity. When this smart fox becomes a real toymaker, she'll be able to provide all of her mallow pals with the coolest toys around!

name: Faldette
meetText: Here comes Faldette! Faldette is a bundle of energy, she's one active fox and is always up for some fun or adventure. Faldette has run multiple marathons, one year she broke her PR and came in first! Do you think you could keep up with Faldette?

name: Fancy
meetText: Meet Fancy. This flamingo is known for her beautiful voice and her talented toes - she loves to perform in musicals. She loves to be on stage, dressed in a new costume and dazzling the audience with her routines. Will you watch her in her latest show?

name: Fania
meetText: Do you like hearing stories about castles, kingdoms and queens? So does Fania! She loves to read fairy tales about royalty and even imagines herself as the princess who saves the day!

name: Fanina
meetText: Fanina knows almost everything when it comes to nature. She can name hundreds of different plants and animals, but her favorites are the flowers that grow by the pond in her garden. Fanina wants to go on a camping trip soon, do you want to come along?

name: Farice
meetText: Meet Farice. His kind and generous spirit are truly inspiring. He knits blankets to donate to the local animal shelter and volunteers doing beach clean-ups every Sunday. He never hesitates to help. Need a hand moving or just a nice warm hug? Farice is the 'Mallow for you.

name: Farina
meetText: Meet Farina. She loves lemon bars, hula hoops, and playing pretend. Farina is OBSESSED with fairy tales, and asks her family to call her, "Your Highness". Sometimes she even wears a crown and cape to school! Farina's favorite royal meal is PBJ's cut in the shape of a crown.

name: Fatima
meetText: One 'Mallows trash is another 'Mallows treasure. Just ask Fatima! This inventive multimedia artist loves working with unconventional materials. From sculptures made of scrap metal to stained glass made of soda bottles, Fatima isn't just creating great art—she's helping save the planet!

name: Fariq
meetText: Nights energize Fariq. He does all his best thinking and journaling during those quiet, late-night hours. Sometimes when Fariq's up late, he puts on an western movie and eats a bowl of fruity cereal. But don't worry — he'll keep the volume down.

name: Farrah
meetText: Farrah is the queen of flowers! She owns a flower shop and creates amazing floral arrangements for the Squishmallow Squad. When she's not working with flowers, you can find her daydreaming in her paddle boat.

name: Farryn
meetText: Meet Farryn. She loves to jump in puddles and listen to the rain while she falls asleep. She likes to learn about storms and what the weather can do. Farryn also loves to watch storm chasers and thinks she would make a great storm chaser when she grows up.

name: Fay
meetText: Fay loves to give hand-made gifts to all the people in her life. She decorates cookies with each person in mind, writing their name or a special note in icing. She also makes them hand-written cards with glitter, hearts, and stickers.

name: Faylyn
meetText: Meet Faylyn, this rock and roll 'Mallow loves loud music, motorcycles, and the open road! She believes in safety first, and always wears her helmet, even if it messes her hair up! She's part of a cool motorcycle crew that takes group rides up the coast! Want to join them?

name: Felexine
meetText: Felexine is here to play! This fox is always on the move, whether she's having a spontaneous dance party or going  shopping with her sisters. She loves having fun while staying active, do you want to join in the dance party?

name: Felice
meetText: Meet Felice! This 'Mallow doesn't go anywhere without his camcorder and an extra battery pack. Felice's favorite scary movies inspired him to make his own, and this year he's shooting one about a haunted house! Felice needs your help on his spooky masterpiece. Do you want to be part of his crew?

name: Felicia
meetText: This magical mallow loves to explore the world on hiking trips to some of the most wonderful parts of the planet. If a magical waterfall or icicle fairy kingdom exists, you can be sure that Felicia has seen it! Join her in her next expedition to a mystical land far away!

name: Felix
meetText: Felix loves soccer and, baseball and motorcycles and when he grows up wants to be a scientist. If he's not playing soccer or watching baseball you can find him fixing his motorcycle or getting home from a long ride.

name: Felize
meetText: Every October, Felize throws her annual caramel apple-making party. 'Mallows come from all over, dressed in their spookiest attire to attend. Everyone brings their own apple and Felize supplies all the caramel and yummy candy toppings. This year, she'd love it if you'd join!

name: Felton
meetText: Felton loves everything fruity and sweet. She's studying to become a pastry chef. Her specialty is fruit tarts. She always bakes with organic and seasonal fruits. Mangos in the summer, Mandarins in the winter. No matter the time of year, she's bound to make something delicious.

name: Fenella
meetText: Breakfast is the most important meal of the day for Fenella, she could have breakfast all day! She loves having scrambled eggs for dinner or fresh waffles for lunch. What breakfast food you like the most?

name: Ferdie
meetText: Ferdie loves dressing up, reading, and red licorice, They even host a book club every month. For every book the club reads, Ferdie dresses up like one of the main characters. Now they've inspired other members to dress up as well, would you like to join the book club?

name: Ferko
meetText: Meet Ferko. This shoebill crane loves using his giant beak to munch on pretzels while watching his favorite documentaries. He wants to create his own docu-series one day! He hopes to spread awareness and inspire action to protect the homes and species of endangered animals.

name: Fern
meetText: Fern decorates her house with paper heart chains, confetti and pink balloons for Valentine's Day every year. Join her for the most amazing parties, as she's the best host around.

name: Fiana
meetText: Fiana is not called "Fancy Fiana" for no reason! Fiana is a classically trained ballroom dancer, and turns many mallows' heads with her glittery costumes and her magical moves. Rumor has it, she's thinking about teaching a ballroom dancing class! Are you ready to dance with Fiana?

name: Fidalna
meetText: Fidalna's favorite color is purple and she can't wait to show off her costume at Olena's slumber party. She's bringing her favorite pillow and lots of snacks to share, can you guess what her favorite snack is? Here's a hint, they go best with salsa!

name: Fiemma
meetText: Get ready to snap some pics with Fiemma! Fiemma is a social media influencer who loves to immortalize every moment in photos. She's never without a spare battery pack and portable ring light. Maybe Fiemma will tag you in her next post!

name: Fifi
meetText: Fifi is your girl if you like to go on adventures! She’s traveled to the Arctic, to the mountains, and is ready to go on her next trip with you. Born October 6, Fifi has a vibrant personality and is quite the little firecracker. She channels her energy through yoga flows, and is working on getting her yoga teacher certificate!

name: Fifi
meetText: Three cheers for Fifi the Fire Chief! Fifi’s love for adventure has grown even more since becoming the fire chief. Whether they are putting out fires, rescuing cats from trees, or responding to other emergencies, Fifi and her crew work hard to help their community.

name: Fina
meetText: Meet Fina. She loves the outdoors and goes hiking almost every weekend. Her favorite way to enjoy nature is to bring along her friends Jason and Juniper for a fun adventure. Want to tag along with this hiking squad?

name: Finley
meetText: Finley loves to play pretend! She really gets into whatever character she's playing, dressing up in various costumes and accessories to completely change her look. She played a villain in one of her friend Alex's short action flick — you wouldn't believe it was her!

name: Finn
meetText: All aboard! Finn the conductor is collecting tickets, are you ready for an adventure? Finn loves trains and has a basement full of elaborate train tracks. When he's not building or collecting tickets, you can find him reading more about his current planet and beyond.

name: Fiona
meetText: Fiona lives in an ice castle in the North Pole near her winter squad friends. She has an ice cream shop and can make any flavor you want, don't forget to ask for her famous icicle sprinkles!

name: Fitch
meetText: Fitch makes movies with his camcorder—his goal is to complete one short film a week! But he doesn't do it on his own, his pal Natty gets behind the camera so Fitch can also play the lead role. This week they're shooting a detective movie. Want to help Fitch look for clues?

name: Fitz
meetText: Fitz is one of the fastest corgis you'll ever meet! He loves to show off his skills on the track, and also does the high jump. See if you can catch this track star's eye for Valentine's Day.

name: Fitzy
meetText: Fitzy talks a lot--even during movies! They just can't help but comment on all the exciting stuff happening on screen. Now Fitzy goes to drive-in movies so they can comment all they like, and bring their favorite drinks and snacks to the show!

name: Flannery
meetText: Flannery was feeling a bit blue this morning, when he had a brilliant idea! He decided to combine all the things that bring him joy into one big event and invite his whole squad—including you! There will be disco music, candy peach rings, and lilac scented candles. Join the party!

name: Flaxy
meetText: Meet Flaxy. This playful 'Mallow would play tug of war with you all day long if she could! Flaxy may look small, but she might surprise you with her strength - you could even need another teammate if you want to win a challenge against her! Ready to play?

name: Fletcher
meetText: Who's that mallow behind the drums? It's Fletcher, you can tell by his infamous grin! Once the Fletch-man lays down a groove, you won't be able to sit still. This pterodactyl never misses a beat.

name: Flora
meetText: Flora loves puzzles, board games and movie nights with her family, they have game nights every other week! Her dad recently taught her a few card tricks and now Flora wants to learn cool ways to shuffle and deal cards, can you help her?

name: Florence
meetText: Meet Florence. She wants to be a singer when she grows up, but she hasn't picked her stage name yet. Flo puts on shows for her friends and family in their backyard, her friends Amina and Coco even helped her built it. One day maybe you can see the show!

name: Florent
meetText: Meet Florent. This axolotl is always getting into mischief. He's the class clown and has been known for chatting and telling jokes during class lessons. He can't help it! He's got an extra silly funny bone. He even makes his teachers crack up!

name: Floxie
meetText: Grab your candy bucket and join Floxie, it's almost time for the Halloween parade! Floxie loves seeing all the decorations and the costumes, especially on the haunted house float! They love to collect stickers, bubbles, and of course, yummy candy.

name: Floyd
meetText: Have you ever met a French fry that loved adventure? Meet Floyd! This salty French fry dreams of leaving the kitchen for adventures he’s only heard about! Climbing a mountain, sailing the sea, or even visiting his family in Idaho.

name: Fluxie
meetText: Ready for Fluxie to make your day? This 'Mallow always has a pep in her step and a dash of cocoa powder on her cappuccinos. Fluxie is a barista who loves to work opening shifts so she can spend the rest of her day creating custom designs for her postcard and sticker business

name: Forest
meetText: Meet Forest. He's this year's dentist of the year! He always leaves his patients with big smiles on their faces! When he's not at the office, you can find him hiking upstream through rugged terrain to find his favorite campsite! With Forest, it's always good in the woods!

name: Forina
meetText: Forina is an interpretive dance instructor! The only rule in her dance studio is to be yourself, oh and to have fun! Okay, so maybe there are two rules! Forina believes there is no right or wrong way to move and express yourself in dance! So come join and let the music take control!

name: Foster
meetText: Meet Foster. Foster finds importance even in life’s little moments. He loves to celebrate any achievement, big or small, and made himself a promise to do exactly that in 2022! Even a get-together with his squad is celebration worthy and Foster is so grateful for each and every one of them.

name: Francesca
meetText: Francesca has two jobs on Valentine’s Day. She’ll deliver your special notes to all your friends, but her favorite job is to enjoy heart-shaped lollipops when she gets home.

name: Francis
meetText: A local hero, Francis is a respected firefighter, admired by all the other Squishmallows in his community. He's courageous, sweet and has a soft spot for comic books when he has a moment to relax on the porch after a hard day's work.

name: Francois
meetText: Order up! Francois needs six beef Wellingtons and he needs them now! This culinary cantaloupe is an award-winning chef. Though running a five-star restaurant isn't for everyone, Francois can stand the heat. Bon Appétit!

name: Frank
meetText: Frank enjoys fishing and hanging out at the lake house with his family and friends. He may be a cat but he LOVES the water! Someday he wants to travel the world with his friend Cam – by boat!

name: Frankie
meetText: People may be afraid of Frankie, but there is need to be. He is not the friendly giant you know, who aspires to become a wannabe police officer after Halloween. No haunted house can scare him away

name: Freddie
meetText: Games, guitars, and gumballs are some of Freddie’s favorite things. When he isn’t playing games with his friends you can find him practicing with his band – just don’t step on his lucky guitar pick!

name: Fresa
meetText: Grab a microphone and put on your favorite dance outfit, Fresa is here! This strawberry has dreams of being a pop star, singing and dancing on stage with fans cheering her on. She wants to sing about love, life, and how to stay happy. Do you want to hear her latest song?

name: Freya
meetText: Freya loves being outdoors! She wants to be a marine biologist when she grows up. She loves reading and her favorite books are fantasy; with wizards and dragons. One day she says she’ll be a superhero marine biologist, saving species from extinction!

name: Frieda
meetText: Frieda cuts the prettiest papel picado you've ever seen! Her style is a little less traditional since Frieda cuts with her crab claws. Today she's following a skeleton template for Día de los muertos papel picado. Come see the banner strung all along Frieda's balcony!

name: Fritz
meetText: Fritz pickles all sorts of veggies! After his first bite of pickled cauliflower, Fritz knew pickling would be his new hobby. Now this frog is on the farmer's market circuit selling his own pickled and jarred goods. He's famous for his spicy pickled green beans! Pick some up for your next charcuterie plate.

name: Fuyuki
meetText: Fuyuki plays the triangle for the youth orchestra. She uses two kinds of wands to adjust the volume of the triangle, sometimes even playing with a knitting needle for really quiet notes. Fuyuki loves playing such a complex instrument and is perfecting a triangle roll for the next show!

name: Gabby
meetText: Watch out for Gabby! Her favorite color is silver but don't let that fool you, this figure skating Yeti is going for gold someday! When she's not on the ice you can find her spending time with her friends and family.

name: Ashley
meetText: Ashley loves table tennis, one day she wants to be part of the world’s best table tennis team! For now, she practices with her friends and hosts backyard tournaments. You can help her keep score!

name: Gael
meetText: Don't say Gael's stuck in the 90s, he just knows good music when he hears it! Gael fills his days dusting off his favorite playlists while he spends his time woodworking, cooking, and watching movies with his best friend Nicky. Join them for a 90's holiday singalong!

name: Gaines
meetText: Does Gaines have your phone number? If she does—you're gonna get a joke call! Gaines likes to call her friends and favorite restaurants using silly voices just for fun! One of the restaurant owners in town, Kaia, recognizes Gaines' silly voice, so sometimes they just stay on the phone chatting.

name: Gala
meetText: Meet Gala. They love listening to oldies music on their record player and cooking yummy vegan meals for all of their friends. When they're not perfecting their coconut curry recipe, they love snapping photos with their film camera or taking care of all their house plants!

name: Galci
meetText: Meet Galci. He loves learning about famous unsolved mysteries. When he finds one that interests him, he learns everything about it he possibly can. One day, he wants to host his very own podcast, and in each episode, he'll deep dive into a different mystery!

name: Galia
meetText: Meet Galia. Galia loves being active! They may get a little winded during activities, but as long as they have an inhaler, they will be alright. Nothing can stop Galia from living their best life! Will you join Galia in their next activity?

name: Gallup
meetText: Who's the fastest mallow on the track? If you guessed Gallup, you might be right. He loves to race his friends for fun and is also a star on his cross country team.

name: Gardenia
meetText: Gardenia crafts tasty and colorful stands for lunch every day! You never know what you'll find in one of Gardenia's giant salads, but it's sure to cure your crunch cravings. This 'Mallow is especially fond of edible flowers such as clover, and whips a light, sweet dressing to match. Come join Gardenia for a healthy lunch!

name: Garnet
meetText: Meet Garnet. She and her sisters are very different but they usually get along. While her sisters are more musical, Garnet is all about the glam and glitz of the holiday season. Planning holiday parties and elaborate gift exchanges make her heart happy.

name: Garo
meetText: Being friends with Garo means you've always in close communication. That's because Garo uses a walkie-talkie! His transmitter is always on if you want to chat or have a spur of the moment to hang out. Just make sure you learn the lingo first. Roger that? Over and out!

name: Garret
meetText: Garret cuts his own stencils for stamp art! He rolls ink over the stencil then stamps away, making everything from postcards to posters. You can catch Garret at the monthly art fair selling all his custom stamps and even working on some new ones. Want Garret to make you a custom stamp?

name: Jim
meetText: Pack a bag and get to know Jim! He is the best Squishmallow to hike a mountain with or ski down the slopes on a sunny, winter afternoon. Wouldn’t it be exciting to travel the world with your best friend? Jim gets to do just that with his older brother, Tim. During the day, he backpacks through the woods, and at night, he is at different music venues supporting his brother’s dream.

name: Gary
meetText: Nothing can stop Gary from reaching the finish line! You can't miss his long legs on the track, as he aspires to become a future Olympian. Want to know the best part about Gary? He is fast on his feet and can solve any problem that comes his way!

name: Gasper
meetText: Gasper just got home from an enlightening trip abroad. He was so impressed with the delicious fresh pasta he ate on his trip, he decided to buy a pasta machine! Gasper is going to start by making spaghetti. What sauce should he add to the homemade noodles?

name: Gavi
meetText: Gavi is learning to play the recorder! He and his class are going to have a festive fall recital. He's so excited for his moms to see all the progress he's made! After the show, they're going to go out and celebrate with cinnamon rolls and hot cocoa!

name: Gavyn
meetText: Gavyn is the world's best uncle! His five nieces think Uncle Gavyn makes the best black bean cheeseburgers with sweet potato fries! Gavyn plays guitar in a rock band, and gives his nieces backstage passes to see him in concert all the time. Want to come to tonight's show?

name: Gawa
meetText: Gawa loves to hang out with Caslina, she also like to go on a tea party with friends,Gawa can be a Party Planner when she grew up, and she really wants you to come over!

name: Gelina
meetText: If you're ever in need of a detective, Gelina can help you out! She is an expert at using the smallest clue to find out the whole scoop from her friends. Just don't ask for her source - she protects them at all costs!

name: Gemma
meetText: Photography, museums, and history are some of Gemma's favorite things. She loves to explore museums and take pictures of new and historical buildings wherever she goes.

name: Genesis
meetText: Genesis loves spy movies and is all about the action. She sometimes wishes that she could be a super spy! If she were a spy she'd be stealthy and have the best cover-ups. Sometimes she pretends she's going undercover, what's your code name?

name: George
meetText: George is one energetic mallow, he can talk for hours and sometimes he gets carried away telling stories so his friends have to tell him to slow down. Sometimes he gets so excited he stutters when he talks.

name: Georgia
meetText: Meet Georgia the Peach, her favorite season is Summer! Georgia loves to make her famous iced tea, a family recipe passed down, from peach to peach. She always has some ready when friends come-over, but she'll never tell you what the recipe is!

name: Georgina
meetText: Meet Georgina. Her favorite things are pumpkin pie, poodles, and jumping in the puddles after it rains. Fall is her favorite season because the colors change and she gets to eat pumpkin pie with her friends. Will you jump in the rain with Georgina?

name: Geranium
meetText: Geranium owns the record store in town. It's a small shop, but it's stacked and packed with all kinds of records. In fact, Geranium will tell you that most of the albums are from his own collection! He doesn't have room in his attic anymore, and loves to see his favorite music find a happy home.

name: Geraldine
meetText: Geraldine isn't like most plumbers—she's a bagpipe plumber! Whether the clog is a frog or the jam is some ham, this nimble feline has seen and cleared it all. If you ask nicely, she might even launder your kilt!

name: Gerik
meetText: Do you hear that? Sounds like Gerik's tummy is grumbly! This cat's got one big appetite, especially when the weather turns chilly. Gerik's favorite meal is meat pies and Halloween candy! Grab a plate and nosh with Gerik.

name: Geronimo
meetText: Give Geronimo a head start on any plans, because this bagel is always running behind schedule. He tends to dillydally or get easily distracted, but he always has good intentions! Geronimo has finals this week and he can't be even a minute late. Will you help him get to class?

name: Gertrude
meetText: Gertrude has a reputation for being bossy, but she just likes to help people. She loves group projects and leads study groups for big tests. Want to know a secret about Gertrude? She laughs so hard water sometimes comes out her nose!

name: Gianna
meetText: Gianna knows there is order in chaos. If you need an example, look no further than her room! Sometimes you can barely see the floor because there are clothes and books all over, but Gianna knows exactly where to find everything. Think she has a photogenic memory?

name: Gianni
meetText: Gianni has the most beautiful garden of all the Squishmallows! He grows tomatoes and cucumbers and has lilacs that smell like no other. He's holding an "Open Garden" next week and it's the talk of the town!

name: Gideon
meetText: Meet Gideon. He is the life of the party wherever he goes! He's been all over the world and is full of stories from his travels! He's wrestled giant squid, climbed to the top of 'Mallow Mountain, and eaten with kings and queens! Join him for his next adventure!

name: Gigi
meetText: This 'Mallow moves a mile a minute, thanks to her favourite fuel: apple juice! When Gigi is around, you are sure to smell a hint of apple before you see her. How many is too many? The limit does not exist!

name: Gilbert
meetText: Ready or not, Gilbert is here for spring! Gilbert is a groundhog like no other - he has insomnia but that doesn't keep this Squishmallow down for long! He journals or writes poetry when he can't sleep and shares his poems with his friends. Even though he has trouble sleeping, Gilbert enjoys to get out and smell the magic of spring.

name: Gilbert
meetText: Gilbert always looks forward to the springtime when he can play outside. His family's Easter traditions include decorating eggs, making egg-shaped pancakes and a family baseball game.

name: Gildie
meetText: Meet Gildie! She's a longtime accountant who cleans up at local trivia nights — she's undefeated for the past four years! This spider crunches numbers, hard candy, and the only thing Gildie is faster at than answering questions, is clacking on her calculator!

name: Giles
meetText: Give it up for Giles!  You'll never see this grasshopper without his favortie electric guitar, because he's always working on perfecting tricky riffs. If Giles keeps up this practice routine, he's sure to get into a professional band someday soon.

name: Gina
meetText: Sweet and spicy describes this gingerbread girl! Gina is the head chef for the North Pole and she loves to test new tasty treats for Santa and the elves. But if they don't eat their veggies - she doesn't let them have any cookies!

name: Ginger
meetText: Ginger is a sassy waitress with a dream in her heart—to dance for the Jazzmallows. When she isn't serving breakfast at the local diner, you can find Ginger in dance class. If you ask nicely, she might even show you her signature move—The Ginger Snap!

name: Gio
meetText: Gio fears small places, but when he feels trapped, Gio knows all that he has to do is flap his wings. For Gio, there is nothing more freeing then flying over the tallest buildings and bridges to downtown. Ready to soar with Gio?

name: Giovana
meetText: Giovana and her bestie Wu are ready for spring! They live in a rainy town and when it stops, it's time for fun! They love to splash around in the puddles, smell the flowers, and watch everything change from dull to bright green. Do you want to join them?

name: Gisla
meetText: Meet Gisla. For Gisla each day begins and ends with a mindful meditation. She takes a deep breath, breathing in the future, and lets it go, breathing out the past, knowing in life that not every question needs an answer.

name: Gist
meetText: Kiai! Gist has a blue belt in karate and he would love to show you his favorite moves. When Gist isn't in class, he practices outside in his backyard, or watches karate movies for inspiration. Gist always brings carrot and celery stick snacks to class-he loves the crunch sound they make!

name: Gjemail
meetText: Meet Gjemail. Gjemail and his family come together every year to celebrate Dia de Los Muertos. They create a beautiful altars full of bright, orange marigolds, candied pumpkins, and sugar skulls. What traditions does your family celebrate? Gjemail would love to hear all about it!

name: Glady
meetText: Meet Glady. Her job in construction keeps her busy, but she always finds a way to beat the heat! Glady keeps things sweet, even in her side gig as a poet. Do you want to hear a poem?

name: Glena
meetText: Glena is a water baby and loves all kinds of water activities. Whether it's scuba diving, snorkeling or surfing, you can always find them near the beach. Currently, Glena is working hard and saving up to buy their first sailboat. Sailing lessons, here we come!

name: Glixa
meetText: Glixa is a makeup artist and loves to show off her skills. She especially loves to do calaveras for the celebration of Día de Los Muertos. She adds gems, glitter, and sometimes even feathers to complete her favorite look. Are you ready to become a beautiful Calavera?

name: Gloria
meetText: Meet Gloria. She loves cooking, comic books, and sci-fi movies. She wants to be an archeologist when she grows up. Gloria and her friends play all afternoon in the back yard pretending they're digging for ancient alien artifacts! Want to join?

name: Gobo
meetText: Gobo has won the Vintage Video Game Championship three years in a row! Think he can win again this year? Gobo speed-plays puzzle and block building games and has developed quite a following. This 'Mallow is on his way to become a gaming legend!

name: Goldie
meetText: Goldie is celebrating 150 Years of Cedar Point Fun. Whether walking the sandy beach, staying at Hotel Breakers, watching an amazing show, eating funnel cakes, or riding the best collection of anywhere, Goldie loves nothing more than spending a day at Cedar Point.

name: Gordon
meetText: You don't have to fear, Gordon is one of the friendliest Squishmallows around! He loves helping others so much that one day he wants to start his own nonprofit!

name: Grace
meetText: Grace is quite bootiful and one to fear during a competition. She has participated in pageants all over the area. What's her talent? Ghost bustin' out some of her favourite dance moves.

name: Gracelynn
meetText: Meet Gracelynn the Winter Fox. Snowball fights and building snow forts are two of her favorite things. She loves building a whimsical snow world with her friends, and this year they want to build a snow castle! Do you want to build a snow world with Gracelynn?

name: Gracia
meetText: Meet Gracia. This 'Mallow loves all forms of dance, especially ballet, and dreams of being principal in her favorite ballet. She loves the feeling she gets when she steps on the stage and how the music helps her move. Will you bring her a bouquet for her next performance?

name: Gracie
meetText: Are you ready to meet the queen of the lagoon? Gracie is one of the most glamorous girls you'll meet. Her style is a little retro mixed with old school Mallowood, thanks to her favorite vintage shops.

name: Grady
meetText: Congratulations to Grady This wheelchair-assisted stallion just placed first in a disability-inclusive horse derby. Always one to give back, Grady is super excited to use his winnings to help train the next generation of racehorses on wheels.

name: Grant
meetText: This gutsy goat has one dream: to become a soccer player! He plays soccer with his friends at the park, at school, and at home with his friends. After they win, he celebrates with his favorite, a chocolate swirl ice cream cone.

name: Grayson
meetText: This Squishmallow knows the most important meal of the day is breakfast, and for Grayson that can only mean one thing. Waffles. Waffles with peanut butter, berries, or even chocolate chips. Can you guess his favorite holiday? National Waffle Day of course!

name: Grecia
meetText: Cinnamon rolls and peppermint lattes are the key to Grecia's heart. She loves the festive taste and the feeling of being cozy, even when it's hot outside!

name: Greeley
meetText: Greeley keeps her library card up to date and goes book browsing every weekend. She always returns books on time, no matter how many she borrows, and is careful to keep them clean and intact. Greeley spends so much time at the library, she's thinking about becoming a librarian!

name: Greer
meetText: Greer doesn't just deliver the news—she sings the news! This meteorologist loves to add a musical spin to her daily weather report. Whether yodeling the daily temperatures or rapping about rainfall, her beautiful voice brightens the gloomiest of forecasts!

name: Greggor
meetText: Meet Greggor. He's a modern moose. He lives in a penthouse downtown and loves going to art museums and late-night dinners. He enjoys defying expectations, a lively debate, or diving into a single subject and learning all there is to know about it!

name: Gregory
meetText: Meet Gregory, the go-to photographer for all things nature. Gregory takes amazing photos from all over the world, he just got back from a trip in the Mallow Mountains! He loves sharing the amazing things he sees with other 'mallows. Where should he go on his next photo-adventure?

name: Greta
meetText: Greta has resting bear face - she always looks grumpy but she's a very happy ‘Mallow. Sometimes she's just too busy enjoying life to smile. Greta wants to be a counselor for wilderness camp to teach trail safety, she loves exploring and sharing her mountains with friends.

name: Gretchen
meetText: Gretchen loves hanging out in her treehouse, sipping pineapple juice with her crazy straw, and watching the clouds go by. She loves to daydream about mystical adventures while the world moves around her. Take a seat and daydream with Gretchen!

name: Griella
meetText: Meet Griella, they love lazy Sundays and breakfast in bed. In the afternoon they hit up their favorite sandwich shop and order the number seven with extra pastrami. At night they love concerts, karaoke, or a long car ride with loud music. They know the words so come sing along!

name: Grin
meetText: Grin is a rugged outdoorsman who also enjoys woodworking. When not in his wood shop or hiking mountain trails, he spends his time in flea markets hunting for unique gifts for his friends and family.

name: Griz
meetText: Meet Griz. They love road trips, pineapple ice cream and zoning out to music. Griz has a list of the top 10 best places to drive and they can't wait to get started. The only thing stopping Griz is going by themself, do you want to be their co-pilot?

name: Groovy
meetText: Groovy isn't just groovy--she's way far out! This disco diva shakes her groove thing wherever life takes her. Though her family sometimes get embarrassed when she does 'the wacky parrot at the grocery store, Groovy can't help it. After all, she was born to boogie!

name: Guadalupe
meetText: Guadalupe draws cartoons for her town's local newspaper. You can catch her art weekly in the Sunday edition! Guadalupe comes from a family of artists and has been drawing since she was a little 'Mallow. Does your family have any common traits or skills?

name: Gunther
meetText: Meet Gunther. Don't be fooled by his spikes and scales, this Dino is a big softy! He loves to knit while watching his favorite romantic comedies! He's currently knitting warm and fuzzy blankets for all the dogs and cats at the local animal shelter. Want to help?

name: Guri
meetText: Meet Guri! If you ever need a helping hand, Guri will be there for you! Guri loves to spread kindness and will be there whenever you call. Fun fact about Guri; he gets to help Nick with his nice and naughty lists, which one will you be on?

name: Gustavo
meetText: Gustavo is the life of the party, he loves to have a good time with friends. When he has people over, they grill, have bonfires, and even swim in the pool! All he needs is a DJ, can you help him out?

name: Gustavus
meetText: Gustavus is a popular pup and has a lot of friends but sometimes he prefers to be alone with his thoughts. He used to think he was weird for wanting to be alone sometimes, but now he knows it's good to have his own time too.

name: Gwen
meetText: Meet Gwen! This unicorn is not your average Squishmallow. Gwen loves catching the waves at her favorite beach. She loves the friendly competition of the other surfers and has won many boogie downs by the water. Are you ready for a lesson from your favorite unicorn?

name: Gwendle
meetText: Meet Gwendle. This 'Mallow is an expert bird watcher. He keeps a journal and writes down all the different types of birds he sees on his hikes. He keeps native plants around his house to attract his favorite bird of all, the hummingbird! Grab some binoculars and join him!

name: Gwendolyn
meetText: Congratulations to Gwendolyn! This batty just earned her PhD in Mad Science. While the rest of her class hopes to use their degree to create monsters or travel back in time, Gwendolyn has a different dream in mind—to glow in the dark! Think she can do it?

name: Hadeon
meetText: Who has the prettiest kitchen in all the land? Hadeon does! He knows the heart of every home is the kitchen, so his is spruced up with decorative hanging pots, fruit plates, and a place setting just for you! Pull up a chair and let Hadeon whip up a tasty meal just for you!

name: Hailey
meetText: Meet Hailey. She's a park ranger who loves to educate about the outdoors! She greets visitors at the park entrance and makes sure guests know all the do's and don'ts to staying safe and keeping the park clean. If you're ever in need of a guide, Hailey is the bigfoot for you!

name: Haizley
meetText: Meet Haizley. She's working hard at her swim classes everyday after school. She's already mastered the backstroke and  the butterfly stroke! When she's not practicing her swimming skills she loves helping her dad make dinner and watching nature  documentaries!

name: Hakim
meetText: Meet Hakim. There isn't a sport or activity that he can't do. From the moment he opens his eyes, he's moving around and accomplishing every task on his long to-do list for the day! Don't get in Hakim's way when he is on a mission, but once he's done, you can find Hakim on the couch.

name: Hal
meetText: Say hi to Hal! Hal is a mechanic in training, and loves to learn all about cars and trucks! Hal’s practicing so that he can build a custom car one day and go on a  road trip! He wants to see the ocean, eat new foods, and maybe even make friends along the way.

name: Halima
meetText: The perfect weekend for Halima starts out with a big stack of pancakes at a cozy cabin with friends, to quilt! Last month on their quilting trip, Halima and her friends had so much fun that they almost didn't finish their quilts!

name: Halisa
meetText: You won't be at the park long without a big hello from Halisa. There's always a big commotion when she and her friends skate by. They all met her friends at the skatepark and every summer they say it will be the best one of their lives. Do you want to join in the fun?

name: Hallie the Hamster
meetText: Hallie is a nature girl, and loves to care for the Earth. She scatters seeds around her home to grow yummy vegetables and pretty flowers. Her favorite food is carrots!

name: Halton
meetText: Blink and you might miss Halton. This speedy 'Mallow loves a good underwater race with his friends! He doesn't mind if he wins or loses, he just loves to go fast! The only time Halton slows down is to eat. His favorite food? Super spicy, extra-loaded nachos!

name: Halver
meetText: If you ever need an expert in history, Halver's your 'Mallow. She loves fun facts, trivia and any sentence that starts with "Did you know..?" If you think that you have some interesting knowledge she might not know, she'd love to hear it. Talking about history is Halver's perfect day!

name: Hammie
meetText: Hammie runs an ice hotel! the hospitable mushroom took his love for winter into an icy adventure for all his guests. Everything in Hammie's hotel is made of ice, including the igloo huts and furniture. But don't worry every bed is topped with a super cozy thermal mattress and lots of fluffy quilts!

name: Hanina
meetText: Hanina is one talkative cupcake, her friends joke that she almost never stops! She loves school and learning new things, especially science. She wants to have her own science blog where she shares cool new things she reads about or shows fun experiements she's working on.

name: Hank
meetText: Hank loves mountain biking, roller coasters, and bubble baths. You can find him at the bike shop or trying to plan his next big roller coaster adventure - one day he might even design a bike/roller coaster hybrid ride!

name: Hanna
meetText: Have you met Hanna? This sweet Squishmallow loves writing poetry and every year writes a poem for all of her friends. Maybe one day you will find her poems in the Squishmallow Shop!

name: Hans
meetText: Default Hans: "Hans has seen every movie ever and loves to eat pudding, especially with sprinkles. Actually, when it comes to food, he's willing to try whatever someone puts on his plate, probably because he is so open to change and adventure. He visits his family in Europe every summer where they like to go to museums and explore new countries. Last year on his birthday, August 6, his family surprised him with a special trip to the Alps!"

name: Hara
meetText: Hara dreams of thrilling audiences with her dramatic acting skills. This bunny is so dedicated to her craft, she memorizes all her lines before rehearsal! Hara is ready for the big stage. Want to go to her theatrical debut?

name: Harlan
meetText: Harlan grows beautiful orchids! This gentle gator trims and waters all his orchids so carefully, it's no wonder they bloom into so many pretty colors. Harlan thinks it's time to take his hobby to the next level and open up an orchid shop! Do you want to take homesome orchids for yourself?

name: Harlow
meetText: Harlow loves shaved ice, sushi, and being cozy. She especially enjoys fancy weekend camping trips with friends! Harlow is an expert glamper and is thinking about starting a glamping app. Would you go glamping with Harlow?

name: Harmony
meetText: Hello from Harmony, who teaches music for many of the Squishmallow squad! Her favorite thing to teach is music history, that's how she first fell in love with music. Her first instrument was piano, now she can play 10 different instruments.

name: Harper
meetText: Harper has a love for building cars and airplane models. She is considered the problem solver of the Squishmallows friend group. Harper seeks new and creative ways to connect people and objects together.

name: Harper the Hedgehog
meetText: Harper gives the best "hedgehugs" in the world! Just ask her friends. She is sweet and spunky and always thinks of the best games to play at sleepovers!

name: Harriet
meetText: Harriet whips up amazing concoctions in her kitchen, especially for Valentine's Day. She's actually working on a special Valentine's Day cookbook to share with friends.

name: Harrison
meetText: Have a problem you can't solve? Never fear, here comes helpful Harrison to the rescue! At first, his classmates thought he was being a teachers' pet, but he really just loves to help solve problems.

name: Harrison
meetText: Harrison loves hockey, hiking, and horseback riding. He loves almost anything that involves being outdoors! Once a month Harrison is a counselor for Big/Little Mallows and brings the little Mallows on hikes.

name: Harvey
meetText: Harvey builds big sandwiches that match his appetite. He always uses fresh bread and a variety of fillings, but his favorite by far is tuna salad! The secret ingredient to Harvey's tasty tuna salad is honey mustard if Harvey's extra hungry, he tops off his sandwich with potato chips for a super crunch.

name: Hasani
meetText: Meet Hasani. He may look little, but his personality is larger than life. His silly and lovable demeanor makes him easy to be around, it's hard not to smile when he's around. Hasani has a simple goal for life when he grows up, he wants to be happy!

name: Hautely
meetText: At one point, Hautely was a stressed out stockbroker. These days, she's a long-haul driver! Though sometimes she misses her fancy lunches and fancier business suits, Hautely wouldn't trade the open road for anything. She especially loves honking the horn!

name: Havin
meetText: Meet Havin. They're helpful, handy, and great at thinking outside the box. Havin loves working on maths problems, building birdhouses, and putting together jigsaw puzzles. Havin has a huge sweet tooth, so if you share some sour candy, they'll be your friend forever.

name: Hawley
meetText: Hawley loves haunted houses! Every year, they fly to different Halloween festivals and theme parks just to get a good scare. Hawley doesn't scare easily, so if you see them jump, you can be sure it's a frightening experience!

name: Hayes
meetText: Hayes is an aspiring designer who wants to make suits! These would be no ordinary suits, they would be one-of-a-kind! Hayes learned how to sew and dabbles in fun pajama sets featuring mixed prints and patterns. When you're ready for a cool new look, give Hayes a call!

name: Heath
meetText: Heath is a member of a talented acting troupe-the Wolf Pack! Though Heath was born a husky, he moves, sounds, and acts like a wolf. His fellow actors agree, and are happy to include him where he belongs on stage, front and center.

name: Heather
meetText: True to her species ability to transform, Heather is one of the mightiest mallows around. No matter what obstacles come her way, she doesn't get discouraged. Heather is always able to find a way to solve and overcome any problems with positive solutions.

name: Heather the Husky
meetText: Heather is energetic and adventurous. She loves to challenge herself and set goals to achieve. Her next goal in life is to go to the North Pole!

name: Hectico
meetText: Meet Hectico. This cuddly cobra loves making new friends and greets everyone with a tight hug. When he isn't devouring his first love tacos, Hectico is traveling the world. He loves traveling and making memories to share.

name: Heidi
meetText: Hungry Heidi has one passion: food. After enjoying a long walk outside, Heidi races to the local pizza place and stuffs her face with cheese pizza. Heidi's fellow mallows love to join her, and sometimes, if they're lucky, Heidi will offer them an itsy-bitsy bite of food!

name: Helca
meetText: Helca is one curious penguin, she loves jazz, peanut butter smoothies, and tries not to overthink everything. Helca loves to try new things and hopes to try something new every day. She doesn't know what she wants to be when she grows up, do you have any suggestions?

name: Helena
meetText: If you go to a fair or carnival you had better grab some cotton candy for Helena! This sweet Squishmallow is the first to share hers. When she grows up, she wants to open a dessert bar – just for cotton candy!

name: Helene
meetText: If listening to sad music puts you in a great mood, Helene is the sloth for you! This moody 'Mallow loves to explore the great out doors and laughing at her own jokes. She wants to enjoy her time and never takes herself too seriously. What song should she play next?

name: Helmut
meetText: Meet Helmut. He travels around the galaxy in his out-of-this-world ice cream truck giving out space sundaes! He makes cool creations inspired by flavors across the universe! But be careful, these treats are so delicious you might just get a brain freeze!

name: Henley
meetText: Meet the next popstar, Henley! This Alicorn is not your usual gal, she enjoys performing and singing her very own originals. When she's not in the spotlight she loves baking and eating her favorite, lasagne! Are you ready to boogie down with Henley?

name: Henrietta
meetText: Have you met a narwhal who loves to bake? It's time you met Henrietta! She collects cookie cutters and loves to decorate them special for her friends. This week she's baking sugar cookies, what cookie cutters should she use?

name: Henry
meetText: Known by all the Squishmallows for his fantastic voice, Henry is a famous sports announcer. While he regularly provides commentary on basketball, football, and baseball games, his favorite sport is volleyball.

name: Herb
meetText: Herb is a pitcher and he loves all things baseball, his dad taught him how to play when he was just 4. His current obsession is a collection of trading cards passed down from his grandpa! Wanna play baseball with Herb?

name: Hermine
meetText: Hermine's love for arts and crafts is reaching new heights—literally! This DIY-loving stack of pancakes is using her skills in basket weaving and paper-mache to construct the world's first handmade hot-air balloon. Isn't that crafty?

name: Hernan
meetText: Hernan teaches artistic swimming on weekends and is a lifeguard at the beach for the rest of the week. Artistic swimming is his passion, and he loves the choreography this year's class is developing—they might even make it to regionals!

name: Hettie
meetText: Hettie is a happy little mallow because she was recently adopted! She has always dreamed of finding a family to love and now she even has brothers and sisters. Hettie can't wait for all the adventures she'll go on with her new family.

name: Hetty
meetText: Meet Hetty. This sweet and nurturing 'Mallow is always looking after her friends! Need a warm hug, a stellar pep talk, or just a friend to sit and listen! Hetty is the girl for you! She works hard to make all her friends feel seen and supported! So come hang and be yourself!

name: Hexla
meetText: Halloween is Hexla's favorite holiday; she loves the creepy-crawly deco. Every year she has a dinner party and she decorates the table with spider webs and skeletons, but don't be scared! Do you want an invite?

name: Hila
meetText: Hila is pleased to meet you! He’s always looking for a buddy that’s up for adventure. No matter how hard the quest, Hila always tries his best. That’s his motto, to always keep trying. Hila is a great motivational friend and ‘Mallow.

name: Hilary
meetText: Meet Hilary. She might be the sweetest bear you'll ever meet. As an empath, sometimes she can be too nice but she's learning how to say no. Understanding boundaries and setting them can be hard, but she knows that's important to be kind to herself too!

name: Hobart
meetText: Meet Hobart. This helpful hamster is a never-ending source of information and cool factoids. Hobart is a bookworm and enjoys spending his time reading in the library. You're guaranteed to learn something new or cool whenever Hobart is around! Do you have any fun facts to share?

name: Hodge
meetText: Meet Hodge. This wise and joyful 'Mallow always makes time to stop and smell the flowers. He is kind, lighthearted, and quick with a joke. If you want someone to try something new with, or simply keep you company, Hodge is the 'Mallow for you!

name: Hoknii
meetText: Say hi to Hoknii! Hoknii is a harp playing hippo who loves history. She combines her passions by learning to play songs from historic sheet music that she finds in the library archives. Hoknii performs 100 songs that are more than 100 years old! Which song can she play for you?

name: Holly
meetText: Original: Give a hoot for Holly, the incredibly outgoing owl! Holly’s bright purple feathers make her the belle of the ball. She loves to dance, make new friends, and shop. Holly likes to bake cakes and her favorite color is you guessed it: purple!

name: Honeydew
meetText: Roll up your sleeves, it's time for class, today's assignment is to play in the garden! Honeydew teaches a gardening class; the biggest rule is that you must sing to your plants. What song will you sing?

name: Hoot
meetText: Hoot and his sister Holly are complete opposites. He’s quiet and likes to read and study, sometimes in his tree fort with his friend Cam. But...Hoot is also secretly a wonderful singer, but only when he thinks no one is watching. Catch Hoot and his hoot-iful voice in the shower, and you'll understand what we mean.

name: Dr. Hoot
meetText: Meet Dr. Hoot. He is busy night and day making sure his hospital remains happy, healthy, and safe. He wears a mask with a big smile so his patients and fellow doctors know he is there to help. When he thinks patients might be scared, he starts to sing them a little song to feel better.

name: Horace
meetText: Are you ready for game night? Horace is the yeti you want on your team; he has a whole room dedicated to playing games! With floor-to-ceiling shelves of games and a variety of personalized playing cards, he knows how to have fun. Want to play a game with Horace?

name: Hosha
meetText: Meet Hosha! Hosha is serious about staying hydrated and you'll always see them with their favorite personalized water bottle. They make sure to drink 64 ounces a day! Hosha is on a 150-day hydration streak right now. Can you beat Hosha's hydration record?

name: Huck
meetText: Huck is the sweetest member of the tennis team. He can be found on the courts everyday after school perfecting his serve. A caring friend, he is always a treat to be around. He is constantly spreading love and positivity while keeping things cool in the hot summer sunshine!

name: Hudson
meetText: Have you met Hudson? Hudson is a mushball of love and affection. With their fluffy personality and kind smile, Hudson always knows how to cheer up their 'Mallow pals!

name: Huey
meetText: Roar! Huey’s here! But don’t be frightened, this lovable T-Rex has a heart of gold! Huey loves spending time with his friends and family, especially his twin brother Chuey. Together they want to travel the world and see what adventures they find.

name: Hugh
meetText: Hugh works at a coffee shop next to the college campus and has super busy mornings! He prides himself on making delicious and frothy drinks in a snap. Hugh even knows his regular customers orders by heart and adds beautiful foam art to their lattes!

name: Hugo
meetText: Hugo loves adventure, he always seems to be on an imaginary quest! Whether it's from a movie, a comic book, or hearing a story from a friend, Hugo takes bits of his regular day to create his own cool adventure to save the day.

name: Humphrey
meetText: Humphrey loves writing scripts and plays. When he's finished with his latest work, he'll get together with all his Squishmallow friends and act it out! Join him and see what role you'll land!

name: Hunter
meetText: Hunter is always busy at her dream job as a stage lighting technician. Being a bit too shy for the stage herself, she enjoys helping others shine. She loves being a part of the team and helping others succeed!

name: Ichika
meetText: Ichika doesn't snowboard—she sandboards! This desert-dwelling thrill seeker loves hitting the dunes. Though her crash landings can get pretty gnarly, Ichika always picks herself back up again. Check out the scorpion stickers on her helmet!

name: Icicle
meetText: Icicle loves to bake and make new sweet treats for her friends. Her favorite food is donuts! She is always energetic and hops around her neighborhood finding new adventures.

name: Igor
meetText: Igor's favorite kind of music is heavy metal, and they love dancing to it! Igor finds the drumming patterns so energizing. and loves to bounce back and forth or jump in circles Igor is starting a metal band of their own and wants you to be a part of it. What instrument do you want to play?

name: Iker
meetText: Iker dreams of being a major league baseball pitcher. He plays on a minor league team right now, and threw a no-hitter last season! Iker keeps his energy up during a game with roasted sunflower seeds. Will you cheer on Iker at his game tonight?

name: Ilene
meetText: Meet Ilene, a future Broadway star! This unicorn loves singing, dancing, and being the belle of the ball. Every August she gets to see a new musical on Broadway for her birthday, she doesn’t have a favorite yet because she wants to see them all!

name: Illia
meetText: Illia tends to the bonsai garden at her local plant nursery. She even teaches classes in the evenings on how to clip and care for bonsai, encouraging all 'Mallows to give these beautiful little trees a try. Want to learn about the art of bonsai trees with Illia?

name: Iman
meetText: Iman works at a coffee shop with many of her friends who hope to be actors and actresses. She often works the early morning shift so she has time to rehearse an audition in the afternoon. This week she is auditioning for a role as a zombie princess, can you help her read lines?

name: Imogen
meetText: School may not be her strong suit, but wait until you hear her sing! Imogen thinks school can be a drag but she loves being in the school plays. Her parents say as long as she loves to be on stage she has to go to school. She can't wait to graduate so she can be done with homework and start a new life onstage.

name: Indie
meetText: Need a hand with some home improvements? Indie is at your service! This hermit crab knows a thing or two about fixer-uppers and is just a call away. You'll make Indie's day with some raspberry lemonade and fresh-baked cookies!

name: Inez
meetText: Get out your protractor, a laser pointer, and some marshmallows, class is about to start! Inez believes that math = fun so she uses games, arts and crafts, and even snacks to teach her geometry class. Are you ready for some fun?

name: Ingo
meetText: Look out for googly eyes next time you're walking around town—Ingo sticks them on everything! This prankster thinks googly eyes look funny on lamp posts, fences, and even mailboxes. Watch out, he might stick some on your backpack!

name: Ingred
meetText: Fifteen minutes to curtain! Ingred is an usher at the local theater. When she isn't showing 'mallows to their seats, Ingred likes to stand at the back of the theater and memorize the routines of the dancers. One day, she hopes to make her way from the aisle to the stage!

name: Ingy
meetText: Ingy holds a garage sale every Saturday until sunset. They have bins of old records, kitchen appliances, and souvenirs from faraway places. All of Ingy's neighbors come around to take a peek at what's new, or just to catch up with their pal. Come check out Ingy's record collection!

name: Irina
meetText: Irina is a gymnast and she can’t wait to start competing. She enjoys showing off her skills on the balance beam but her absolute favorite thing to practice is her floor routine. She loves working on a new routine and letting the music fuel her moves.

name: Iris
meetText: This beautiful butterfly is a pageant star, she has won the Miss Squish title 3 years in a row! Her favorite part of the pageants is the talent — she plays the harp!

name: Iris the Husky
meetText: Iris is energetic and unstoppable. She is always planning ground adventures with her friends. She loves the snow and going sledding in the winter.

name: Irving
meetText: Looking for adventure? Give Irving a call. He’s always up for riding ATVs, skydiving or even bungee jumping!

name: Isabella
meetText: Isabella loves to sing, dance, and swim!  She wants be a mermaid someday, and for now her magical mermaid moves on land. She loves spending time with her family and eating cookies!

name: Isis
meetText: Isis/Odile loves the color green, pineapple smoothies, and zoning out to music. She just bought a record player and goes to the record store almost once a week! What album should she get next?

name: Isla
meetText: Ever wonder what it's like flying in space? This unicorn can help you out! Isla is an astronautical engineer and she's working on some very exciting projects. Her favorite type of music to listen to when she's working? Bluegrass!

name: Isolde
meetText: Isolde is a public defense lawyer. She's a tough onion in the courtroom, but once you peel back those layers, you'll find Isolde to be a deeply caring 'Mallow. She fights for all her clients like they're her own family, and wants a fair, just hearing. A friend like Isolde will always have your back!

name: Istvan
meetText: Istvan is a feisty (and hungry!) food critic who loves to try all the culinary options in his town. You can find him dressing up as an anonymous mariachi player, hoping to get the inside scoop on the hottest restaurants. When he's not writing about his foodie experiences, he is practicing guitar and hanging out with his friends! What's your favorite restaurant, and can Istvan come too?

name: Ivanna
meetText: Ivanna's favorite part of springtime is getting ready for softball - she loves picking out new equipment, wearing her lucky cap, and playing with her team-mates! This year Ivanna wants to be a pitcher, she's working on an new pitch called the winding wing, will you watch Ivanna play softball?

name: Ivette
meetText: Ivette teaches art history at the city college. Even though she's on winter break, Ivette has lots of final exams to grade! After grades are in, Ivette can't wait to go to the movies. Holiday films are her favorite and she makes sure to see every new release!

name: Ivy
meetText: Ivy is an avid gardener. She loves to take care of her flowers and succulents, creating beautiful spaces for her friends to play in!

name: Ivy
meetText: There goes Ivy! Ivy's studying for their pilot license so they can travel the world. Trying new foods and meeting new 'Mallows is what Ivy is all about. When they're back on land, Ivy enjoys long naps outside on their hammock. Want to be Ivy's co-pilot?

name: Jacinda
meetText: Frisbee and volleyball are two of Jacinda's favourite sports, especially at the beach. She loves to spend the day playing with friends. Whenever she wants to cool off, she just throws the frisbee towards the water and jumps in.

name: Jack
meetText: Jack is the strong silent type, but he’s always there when you need him. He’s not afraid to speak up for himself or his friends. He can be a little feisty, but he loves to cuddle. Jack loves giving back and thinks we should always lend a helping hand.

name: Jackie
meetText: Jackie and her sisters love to shop vintage, whenever they travel together, they go on a retro hunt. Last month, they found hot pink fuzzy phones that light up when you call. What will they bring home next?!

name: Jacob
meetText: Jacob is the king of the mountain! Spring is his favorite season because it means he can start to climb again, surrounded by beautiful wildflowers. He also likes to make up songs as he hikes up to the summit.

name: Jaelyn
meetText: Do you have anything to throw Jaelyn's way? They're practicing for a juggling competition! Jaelyn loves to juggle and participates in competitions all over the place. This spring they won 1st place for juggling 17 candy bars!

name: Jaime
meetText: Sugar, spice, and everything in between can be found in Jaime's home. She loves to bake goodies for her friends and delivers weekly snacks to the Squishmallows in her squad.

name: Jaina
meetText: Are you ready for an adventure with Jaina? She loves to go for drives to catch the sunrise and could spend the whole day wondering. Whether she's with friends or by herself, she loves to see what's around the corner.

name: Jaiya
meetText: Have you met Jaiya? She is one interesting 'Mallow. While she teaches art, she's also full of fun facts and tidbits about plants, space, and minerals. She likes to talk about the world and start new discussions, just be mindful of time because she could talk all day!

name: Jak
meetText: Jak likes to give hugs with his wings to cheer people up, do you want a wing hug from Jak?

name: Jakarria
meetText: Meet Jakarria. This Mallow has a very big heart and brings joy wherever she goes. Jakarria has a big, beaming smile and whenever you’re hanging out with Jakarria, you can’t help but smile too.

name: Jake
meetText: Jake loves the outdoors! When she is not volunteering her time at the park, she spends her weekend in a cozy cabin in the mountains.

name: Jalisca
meetText: Jalisca is open to talking about her blindness, even sharing her story online and ways she uses her other senses. One of Jalisca's favorite meals is sushi because it has such great texture! This leopard doesn't need utensils and loves to dig in with her paws.

name: Jamal
meetText: If you're interested in geography, Jamal is the cat for you! He wants to start a geography camp, to teach the importance of geography and how it affects our world, do you want to sign up?

name: Jamar
meetText: Jamar loves all things sparkly and bright! When Jamar decorated his home, he mixed glitter in the paint so that every wall would gleam in the sunlight. If you want to visit Jamar's house, he might lend you some of his shiny gold jewelry to wear! Come get glam with Jamar.

name: James
meetText: James is quite the catch. When he’s not studying for his next math test, you can find him in the outfield, becaue he is the captain of the baseball team. He travels all over the country for sports, and is expected to play in the major leagues!

name: Jamir
meetText: Jamir likes to write his ideas in a journal; he starts a new one every year! Sometimes he writes a made-up story that he wants to share with his friends, or its a new invention he wants to see.

name: Jana
meetText: Meet Jana. Every year Jana and her family come together to celebrate their loved ones through vigils, colorful face painting, sharing stories, and eating pan de Muerto. Come join! She'd love to teach you more about her family's traditions!

name: Janet
meetText: Janet has a passion for music, and she views the ocean as a musical playground! After putting on her headphones, Janet strums her tentacles, mimicking the sound of a guitar. Janet's sea squad loves to hear her play and they dance along to her beautiful beat!

name: Jangle
meetText: Meet Jangle. He’s an expert hot cocoa mixologist! He loves experimenting with new and unexpected flavours. Spicy cayenne hot cocoa and lavender dark chocolate hot cocoa were two of his most recent concoctions! He’s always in need of taste testers! So grab a mug and join him!

name: Janna
meetText: Janna just built a skateboard ramp in her backyard! She practices her skateboard skills every day after school and invites her whole squad. Skating helps Janna unwind after a long day and is her favorite way to escape. After that, it's homework time! Come join Janna for a fun skate break.

name: Jans
meetText: Jans is as concentrated as they come. A marine biologist by day, she spends her nights developing the perfect paper straw. Though the hours are long, Jans won't rest until plastic straws are out the ocean and paper straws stop melting in her cup!

name: Janus
meetText: Janus is an active member of the North Pole community! He ,even hosts orientations for new 'Mallows starting at Santa's workshop so they can feel the holiday spirit right away. If you ever have a question about history or traditions Janus probably has the answer.

name: Jarik
meetText: Meet Jarik! Sleepovers with friends are his favorite. They stay up late watching romantic comedies, choreographing funny dances, and making mood boards with pictures they’ve cut from magazines. In the morning they flip fluffy pancakes with extra maple syrup!

name: Jarin
meetText: Have you ever seen a jellyfish juggle? Jarin might be the first with dreams of joining the circus one day Jarin practices his juggling skills with anything he can find.

name: Jarrell
meetText: Meet Jarrell. He is creative and often thinks about the future, dreaming and innovation are his way of life. Music helps foster his creativity, especially a good hip-hop or lo-fi beat. When he needs some downtime, you'll find him watching his favorite anime, do you want to join?

name: Jason
meetText: Early mornings are hard for Jason, especially when he was up late studying! This donkey is studying to become a truck driver - he wants to drive trucks up through the mountains and beyond. Jason grew up loving trucks and can't wait to drive but only after he's had his coffee.

name: Jasper
meetText: Concerts, quesadillas, and collecting posters are some of Jasper's favorite things. He and his friends travel to see their favorite bands and keep all the concert posters in a huge portfolio to keep them safe. Do you want to see all the concerts they've been to?

name: Javari
meetText: Javari works round-the-clock in preparation for the biggest day of the year--Groundhog Day! This marketing guru is responsible for advertising the change in the season. Word in the den? Spring has sprung!

name: Jaxton
meetText: Jaxton believes that you’re never too busy for family time! He is quite the planner and everyone has learned to embrace it. He is coordinating the next big reunion for his entire family who’s scattered throughout the country!

name: Jayda
meetText: Jayda is a medical student who has a passion for helping others. She is also an expert at needlework. When she’s not studying for exams, she’s sketching designs and sewing costumes for her friends! What would you ask Jayda to sew for you?

name: Jaydelle
