meetText: Have you met Miss Jaydelle? Her students seem to love her the most for her fun way of teaching. She knows the answer to just about anything but if she doesn't, the whole class gets to learn something new! Her favorite subject to teach is math because you'll always need it.

name: Jayden
meetText: Meet Jayden. By day he works in a restaurant and by night he is a rock legend. Jayden plays the drums and his skill will blow you out of the water. Once in a while, he'll put on a show for his fellow kitchen staff on the pots and pans. Do you want to hear him play?

name: Jayla
meetText: Jayla organizes events of all kinds! She loves to get involved in fundraisers or charitable events for her community. This generous 'Mallow also hosts free, monthly self-defense classes for anyone curious about learning. There's no doubt Jayla is one tough bird!

name: Jazmanian
meetText: Meet Jazmanian. This cool and compassionate 'Mallow sees a world bursting with possibility! You never know just what fun and creative adventures Jazmanian will get into! But this 'Mallow knows the best things happen when we work together! So come along and see what happens next!

name: Jazzy
meetText: Jazzy loves to enjoy the sun and travel. She can be found laying out by the pool or at the beach with a smile on her face. Her favorite food is cheese and she loves to watch movies with her friends on the weekends.

name: Jean
meetText: Jean watches a lot of French movies- they're her favorite. She loves the old black & white ones the most, and even has posters of them in her room. Jean's learning French at her local community college, and hopes one day watch her favorite movies without subtitles!

name: Jeanne
meetText:
Jeanne is a hyper helper, and the queen of multi-tasking! She uses all 8 tentacles to lend a helping hand, solve problems, and she can still have fun! There's no problem she can't solve.
She is a restrained introvert.

name: Jeannie
meetText: Even though her birthday is in the spring, Jeannie's favorite time of year is Halloween. She loves to dress up in costumes, try new makeup tutorials, and of course give her sisters a little fright. Who should she dress up as this year?

name: Jeff
meetText: Meet Jeff, the park ranger! Because his size can be intimidating to other he is very shy and likes to keep to himself. He prefers a small group of close friends over large crowds. Being a ranger suits him perfectly as he is able to spend long stretches of time on his own in nature.

name: Jeff the Blue Turtle
meetText: Meet Jeff! Jeff hosts a book club for 'Mallows who love reading long, epic novels. This is a breeze for Jeff because he's a trained speed reader! He even keeps track of plots and characters in the books he's reading with colorful highlighters! Want to join Jeff's book club?

name: Jemima
meetText: Meet Jemima, this crooner has a beautiful singing voice. She's also the fastest banjo player ever! Feeling down in the ditch? She'd love to lift you spirits with one of her sweet and catchy songs. When she starts on the banjo, you can't help but smile!

name: Jen
meetText: Jen loves to spend time with her family, listen to music with her friends, and is the queen of naps. When she's not taking care of her family or napping you can find her studying to become a lawyer! Watch out for her purple law school takeover.

name: Jerome
meetText: Jerome doesn't have a 5-year plan or even a 2-day plan! He loves living on the edge. Each morning is a surprise and each day a mystery! On Monday, he's at a silent disco with his friends in the park, and on Tuesday, he's learning how to scuba dive! With Jerome, anything is possible!

name: Jerrika
meetText: Are you ready to take a trip with Jerrika? Jerrika is a journalist who travels the world interviewing those who are changing the world. Before she goes on any adventure, she makes sure to pack her lucky socks, she couldn't travel without them! Could you be her next interview?

name: Jessi
meetText: Meet Jessi. He loves vanilla lattes, hot yoga, and history. When he grows up he wants to be an art history teacher! His favorite way to spend the day is walking the halls of old art museums and grabbing a coffee at the café. Want to join him?

name: Jessica
meetText: Jessica wants to be a doctor when she grows up. You can find her dancing or coloring when she's not studying.

name: Jessie
meetText: Meet Jesse, an aspiring author! Jesse loves scary movies and writes short stories that turn regular mallow life into spooky tales of Mallowville. One day Jesse might write a book of scary stories, would you read it?

name: Jett
meetText: Have you seen Jett? This tricky dragon can really blend in with his surroundings. He got his love for all things camouflage from his dad, he even has a camo-print bed!

name: Jettward
meetText: Jettward is one loveable and playful poodle pup! He will be by your side for any adventure. Some of his favorite activities are playing fetch on the beach, running zoomies at the park and snuggling up on your lap. He wants to be your forever pup.

name: Jeurgen
meetText: Don't be fooled by Jeurgen's appearance. He's a big scaredy-cat! He sleeps with the light on and prefers a silly joke to a ghost story! One thing he does love? Caramel apples! He can't wait to celebrate Halloween and give them out to all the trick-or-treaters!

name: Jezray
meetText: Meet Jezray. This funky frog is a shaker and a groover. They bring music with them wherever they go and is never afraid to bust a move. Jezray loves to stand out by wearing glittery outfits, colorful hair, and showing off their moves.

name: Jim
meetText: Pack a bag and get to know Jim! He is the best Squishmallow to hike a mountain with or ski down the slopes on a sunny, winter afternoon. Wouldn’t it be exciting to travel the world with your best friend? Jim gets to do just that with his older brother, Tim. During the day, he backpacks through the woods, and at night, he is at different music venues supporting his brother’s dream.

name: Jingle
meetText: Did you know that Carol has a twin? Meet Jingle! Jingle may not be as joyful as Carol but still plays along with her holiday shenanigans. Sometimes Jingle downplays the holiday cheer but deep down loves Carol enough to join in on the fun. Do you want to cause some mischief with Jingle?

name: Jingles
meetText: Jingles wants to be a costume designer when they grow up. It's about the tassels, feathers, and glitter that make movies so magical. Last year Jingles helped with the costumes for the school play and can't wait to do it again.

name: Jiovanne
meetText: Hats off to this curious cat, Jiovanne is the adventure cat you’ve been waiting for. Parasailing over dangerous waters, diving deep into the sea for treasure, and even scaling a snow-covered mountain are just some of the things she's done. Where should she go on her next trek?

name: Jivin
meetText: Jivin devours sci-fi novels, homemade mac & cheese, and '90s sitcoms with a bottomless appetite that will make you wonder how they even have time for their day job. Not to worry - somehow Jivin makes it work! Jivin is a youth "Mallow counselor, who also spends their summers mentoring at a wilderness camp! What shows would you watch with Jivin?

name: Joanne
meetText: Joanne is a faithful companion to mermaids on all types of adventures, they’ve even given her the nickname ‘sea pup’! She has a sweet tooth and her favorite treat is honey buns. Her favorite color is emerald green and her birthday is May 14.

name: Joaquin
meetText: En garde! Joaquin is taking fencing lessons this year, he wanted to try something cool and different. At first, there weren't many mallows in his class but now the classes are filling up! He loves cheering on his friends when it's not his turn.

name: Jodie
meetText: Meet Jodie! She collects small objects everywhere she goes and stores them like treasure. It would be impossible to track Jodie's keepsakes — she hides them all over her room! Her favorites are the perfect fall leaves she protects in hardback novels.

name: Joelle
meetText: Joelle wants to be an ambassador when she grows up, she likes to help people. She doesn’t know the first thing about it, so her teacher suggested that she do a report to learn more. Do you want to help her research?

name: Joey
meetText: If it has wheels then Joey is a fan! He loves cars, bikes, tractors and anything else he can speed around in! He regularly gives his friends a ride to the beach where they love to kick around a ball and have fun. When hunger strikes there’s only one snack Joey will reach for and that’s a chocolate brioche.

name: Johan
meetText: Say hello to Johan! Johan has a goofy sense of humor, and sometimes he hides in wacky place so he can jump out and surprise his friends! The only problem is that Johan's friends have caught on to his jokes, so now his pranks aren't quite as surprising. What prank would you play on Johan?

name: Johann
meetText: Do you like to celebrate the season? So does Johann. This super creative pine tree loves dressing up for different holidays. Though most 'Mallows associate him with Christmas, Johann has an outfit for every occassion. His favorite is Halloween!

name: Johanna
meetText: Johanna loves when the air turns crisp and leaves on the trees begin to change. It means all her favorite fall vegetables are in season. She loves to cook hearty soups that keep her and her friends warm during the cool fall nights! So grab a bowl, she'd love to share!

name: Joie
meetText: Joie is an electric unicorn who's always ready for a good time! This unicorn, decked out in neon and giant sunglasses, knows how to make a fashion statement. All of Joie's friends hope to be as stylish as her!

name: Joldy
meetText: Meet Joldy, she's a total trickster who loves playing pranks on her friends. She's been known to hide for up to two hours, waiting for the perfect moment to jump out and scare her friends! So keep an eye out, because you never know when she's planning her next spooky prank!

name: Jolie
meetText: Jolie is a princess in disguise, this Squishmallow gets the royal treatment wherever she goes! Instead of being zebra royalty, she wants to be a detective.

name: Jolly
meetText: Meet Jolly, she loves everything about the snow. Jolly lives in a warm and busy city but dreams of moving far, far away. She wants to live on a snow-covered mountain or maybe a forest where she could ski and enjoy the snow all year long.

name: Jones
meetText: Have you been wronged by cracked gingerbread? Wrinkly wrapping paper? Wilted mistletoe? Call Jones, Attorney at Paw. An expert on holiday law, this persuasive feline doesn't just fight the naughty—he defends the nice!

name: Jonessa
meetText: Jonessa is a great writer and photographer which comes in handy for her growing career as a food critic. Jonessa is happy to give advice on anything from revamping your resume to the perfect pairings for dinner.

name: Jonny
meetText: Have you seen Jonny? This fast-paced mallow is always busy and on-the-move! Even though he has 8 tentacles, Jonny jokes that he could do with 8 more. One thing to know about Jonny, he’ll always speak up for what he believes in.

name: Jordan
meetText: Meet Jordan. This gingerbread boy is ready for action! Jordan went to school to be a firefighter AND an EMT, so he is one of Mrs. Claus’ favorite holiday helpers. Jordan is in charge of keeping the North Pole safe and sound, especially during the busy holiday season.

name: Josa
meetText: Josa loves to make 'Mallows' laugh! She gets voted class clown every year and is known to dress up in silly outfits on school spirit. days Josa even started to wright down some of her favorite jokes. keep your eyes peeled for Josa the next time you see an open mic night!

name: Josephine
meetText: Meet Josephine. She is adventurous and loves to play outside while being creative. Music is her secret weapon. Whether it is swimming, biking, or swinging at the playground, she is always humming or singing along. What's your favorite song to jam along to?

name: Josie
meetText: Josie is a happy-go-lucky type of girl. She has the most positive attitude, and is always ready to cheer up a friend in need!

name: Jova
meetText: Jova invented a new kind of airplane. Her goal is that one day everyone can fly their own little plane—like a car in the sky! Jova pilots this single 'Mallow plane for test runs every morning, then works on improvements the next day. This muffin is sure to be the next best inventor of our time!

name: Joxtine
meetText: This is Joxtine's first slumber party and she's a little nervous. Even though she has fun with her friends, she doesn't know how it might go. She's bringing her favorite blanket to keep her company because it makes her feel safe.

name: Joy the Flying Pig
meetText: Joy loves to fly! Her sparkling wings are always taking her to new heights! Joy is always cheerful and ready to brighten anyone's day.

name: Joy
meetText: Catch her if you can, Joy is a thrill seeker and always on the move! She lives among the treetops and loves to glide like a purple streak through the trees. Once she was gliding so fast that even she didn't think she could stop. Are you ready for adventures with Joy?

name: Joyce
meetText: The only thing Joyce loves more than shopping for herself is shopping for others. A personal stylist at her favorite boutique. Joyce takes joy in helping other 'Mallows decide what to wear and how to wear it!

name: JSK
meetText: Who has a big heart and even bigger dreams? It's JSK! This business casual cat is always on the hunt for innovation, quality, and lattes. When he's not growing his business or networking, you'll find him working out at the gym or playing tennis.

name: Judith
meetText: Judith's favorite season is fall, she loves to jump in the big piles of leaves. When it's time to clean up Judith helps her mom rake and afterward, they make a batch of fresh hot apple cider. Would you like some?

name: Judy
meetText: Judy wants to be a writer when she grows up, she loves to make up fantastical stories based on the people in her town. She shares the stories on her vlog and has her followers help decide which characters to focus on next. What could Judy write about you?

name: Julep
meetText: Are you looking for a party planner? Julep is your girl! She plans elegant galas and loves to entertain guests. She wears a hat to every event she plans; can you guess how many hats she has?

name: Jules
meetText: Meet Jules the mint cat. Jules loves to laugh and play hide and seek with her friends. She also loves to color; she tells stories with her artwork. You’ll know when she’s excited because she gets really loud, she just can’t hide her excitement!

name: Julian
meetText: Drawing and listening to music are two of Julian's favorite things. Though he loves to play with his brothers, he likes to spend time by himself and draw stories about his life. Do you want to draw with Julian?

name: Juliette
meetText: Juliette is a bookworm who loves to get lost in a good story. She has a big imagination, and has a plan one day to go to England and meet the Queen!

name: Junie
meetText: Junie jumped at the opportunity to plan her annual family reunion! Her family gathers once a year connecting from all over, and it's Junie's favorite day. She's planning a delicious barbeque and lots of fun outdoor games. Will you help Junie string the party lights?

name: Juniper
meetText: All rise, the honorable Judge Juniper is here! Being fair is very important to Juniper, and when they grow up, they want to be a judge. For now, Juniper is focused on being fair on the playground and with their friends.

name: Justin
meetText: Meet Justin. This gutsy 'Mallow never says no to a dare! He once painted the neighbor's yard blue! This sometimes gets him in trouble, but all in good fun. Even the neighbors couldn't help but have a chuckle at their bright blue yard. Do you have a dare for Justin?

name: Justine
meetText: Justine loves reading and writing, especially stories about other galaxies! Her favorite time to write is in the spring because everything feels fresh. She hides away in her favorite tree reading or thinking about what stories she might create next. Would you like to read one?

name: Jyri
meetText: Jyri has a serious sweet tooth. He treats himself to cake, tartlets, and cookies all the time. Jyri knows his limit, but sometimes he just can't help himself and he eats too many pastries--the sugar rush really pushes back his bedtime! Wanna split a brownie with Jyri?

name: Kachina
meetText: Meet Kachina. She is lovable and caring spirit who helps people find their healthy paths. She works as a nutritionist, and through she knows different food work for different people, she likes to follow a vegan diet, Do you want to make some vegan cookies with Kachina?

name: Kaelea
meetText: Meet Kaelea. This lovable and huggable koala is all about essential oils, hanging outside, and showing others love. When she's not relaxing in the trees, she is out and about collecting eucalyptus to munch on. And while she's foraging, she will grab some fresh herbs for dinner!

name: Kai
meetText: Kai is the King of the sea! When he's not ruling the sea, you can find him searching for sunken treasure. Kai is also a lover of art and shows his creativity by making elaborate underwater sandcastles with his friends.

name: Kaia
meetText: Meet Kaia. She is the chef and owner of her very own restaurant! She loves making all types of food and is especially good at making handmade pasta. If you are looking for a yummy meal with an amazing friend, reach out to Kaia!

name: Kaitlyn
meetText: Meet Kaitlyn. This loyal and loving lemur is your new best friend and workout buddy! Kaitlyn loves going for runs, swimming in lakes, and hiking. Her latest hobby is mud running! She may get dirty, but she always has her precious pink glow!

name: Kalani
meetText: Meet Kalani! Kalani will do anything for her friends, including waking up early to hang out with her best buddy - Cobie! Kalani loves to do silly sing alongs and play pranks on her friends, but also knows when to lend a helping hand. Want to plan your next prank with Kalani?

name: Kaldette
meetText: Do you hear someone singing? It might be Kaldette! She is bursting with talent and loves to sing throughout her day. Kaldette loves singing along to her favorite tunes while she works, but she doesn't always remember to mute her mic.

name: Kalina
meetText: Ready for some fun? Kalina the cow is at your service. This colorful cow is a party planner turned decorator, and she loves mixing colors, fun shapes, and making magic with retro chic. So grab your go-go boots and get ready for a Mod good time!

name: Kamili
meetText: Here comes Kamili! Kamili wants to be a traffic coordinator one day, helping guide others on the busy streets. Kamili loves to provide direction and be the navigator for friends and family. If you need a co-pilot for your next adventure, you know how to call!

name: Kaprina
meetText: If you think Kaprina looks familiar, you've probably seen one of her commercials. Kaprina's last commercial was for paper towels, and now she has a lifetime supply! Being in commercials is fun for now, but Kaprina has her eyes set on opening her own business. Do you have any ideas for her?

name: Karina
meetText: Original: Karina is a numbers girl. Her favourite subjects have always been maths and science. She plans on using her data expertise as a future computer scientist!

name: Karlie
meetText: Got a glitch? Call Karlie! There's no computer error this techie 'Mallow can't fix and nothing makes her happier than helping her friends. Karlie grew up playing games on her big brother's desktop computer, and now she's developing games on her own! Want to play one of Karlie's computer games?

name: Kate
meetText: Meet Kate. She loves to travel and watch sports, some of her favorite games have been on the road. She enjoys spending time with her family and friends, especially when they're tailgating or watching a championship game. Her favorite game day snack is macaroni and cheese.

name: Katharina
meetText: Meet Katharina. She's a professional gamer and gets to test out new video games all day! She goes on mythical quests and journeys to the end of the planet all from the comfort of her bright pink gamer chair. She's the #1 player! Come join, she'd love to show you the ropes!

name: Kathy
meetText: Meet Kathy. This cozy cat loves to play in the snow. Kathy has a marvelous coat collection; she has a coat for every occasion! When she's not playing in the snow, you'll find her tending to her indoor garden, she loves being a plant mom!

name: Katsla
meetText: Just like her sister Karina, Katsla is all about the numbers. While her sister is about the principles of math and science, Katsla is about the sleep number. She wants to uncover the secrets of sleep, stay tuned for more of her research!

name: Katta
meetText: Katta just got her Pilot's license! Katta is fascinated by all things that fly, which makes aviation the perfect career choice for her. When she's not in the sky, Katta watches water birds in their natural habitat by the seaside.

name: Katya
meetText: Meet Katya. She and her mom moved to a new country recently and sometimes she gets homesick. Her new favorite thing to do is rollerblade by the beach. When she grows up, Katya wants to become a lawyer like her mom and help people.

name: Kavya
meetText: Meet Kavya. This peppy penguin is a team player who is always willing to lend a hand. Kavya believes that being kind and thinking of others are the best ways to live.

name: Kayce
meetText: Have you ever seen a panda pegacorn do Muay Thai? Meet Kayce! She coaches soccer and trains in Muay Thai during the week and on the weekends attends tournaments and cheers on her team.

name: Kayla
meetText: Kayla loves fruit juice, being silly with her friends, and hanging out in her tree house. She helped her dad build it and they even added a projector sheet so her friends can put on puppet shows or watch home movies.

name: Keanu
meetText: Kickball and dodgeball are two of Keanu's favorite games to play at recess. Whenever it's his turn to kick, he pretends he's kicking the ball all the way into space. He hasn't kicked it that far yet, but maybe one day he will!

name: Keely
meetText: Keely is a soon-to-be-mommy, and blogger, who wants to start her own painting business. She paints murals for her friends and family, and dreams of one day painting a mural for her favorite place to visit, the Sydney Opera House!

name: Kei
meetText: Meet Kei! Kei likes to go on long walks when she's feeling stressed, so the park is her favorite place to be. Recently, she's taken a special interest in learning about the names of the cloud formations she sees on her walks! Want to go for a stroll with Kei?

name: Keina
meetText: Never in one place for too long, Keina is a nomad. Keina loves to explore new places, speak new languages, and make new friends! Keina can stay awake all night talking about all the amazing places to visit. Pack your bags if you're ready for a road trip!

name: Keir
meetText: For Keir, fall means all new TV! New seasons of old shows and new original series all start in the fall, and she can't wait to find out what's going on with her favorite characters. Keir looks forward to cozying up with her family for one of their favorite seasonal routines.

name: Keith
meetText: Put on your goggles and grab a tool belt, it's time to step into Keith's woodshop! Keith is a carpenter who builds cozy outdoor furniture. He also teaches a woodworking class. This week his students are helping build a deck, are you signed up?

name: Keith
meetText: Meet Keith. He loves to play sports, make new friends, and go on crazy adventures. One day he wants to travel or coach his own team! One of Keith's favorite things about summer is going to camp. Last year he met two new mallows who go to his school.

name: Kelby
meetText: Meet Kelby. Kelby dramatizes every aspect of his life like he's living in a TV show. So if you see Kelby take a long pause or gasp, don't worry, he's just amplifying the moment. Kelby even gives his houseplants names and narratives!

name: Kelina
meetText: Meet Kelina. She loves painting her nails and handwritten cards. On the weekends you'll find her painting her nails blue and browsing her local stationery store. Send her your address and she'll send you a card!

name: Kellie
meetText: Have you seen Kellie? This 'Mallow is always on vacation! Kellie travels to a different beach every weekend no matter how far. In fact, for Kellie it is all about the journey. Would you like to go with Kellie on her next beach adventure? She can teach you how to build a giant sandcastle!

name: Kelly
meetText: Kelly loves playing his marching drum because he gets to hang it close enough for his arms to reach! This software engineer always keeps up with the latest tech and can't wait to tell his besties, Sager and Cooper, all about it, even when they're busy watching TV. Kelly uses his freshly baked cinnamon rolls to get their attention!

name: Kelsey
meetText: Kelsey loves DIY crafts, gardening, and helping others. She loves to do craft projects and finds inspiration everywhere around her.

name: Kena
meetText: Kena loves coconut shaved ice and watching sunsets by the pool, especially with her friends! They play volleyball and have splash contests to see who has the biggest jump. Grab your swimsuit and join the fun!

name: Kenan
meetText: Kenan has a green thumb! He grows houseplants as low as maintenance as he is and puts them in every windowsill. Kenan loves that the shade they create helps him get his daytime beauty rest, making them the perfect roomies! Want to meet Kenan's plants?

name: Kendla
meetText: Kendla loves everything about being cozy. Whether it’s sitting in front of the fireplace with a good book, or knitting a sweater for her friend Bernice, you can always unwind with her. Her favorite season is fall, what season do you love most?

name: Kendra
meetText: Meet Kendra. She loves to play sports, make new friends, and go on crazy adventures, one day she wants to travel or coach her own team! One of Kendra’s favorite things about summer is going to camp, last year she met two new ‘Mallows who go to her school.

name: Kennedy
meetText: Kennedy loves the outdoors! When she is not volunteering her time at the park, she spends her weekend in a cozy cabin in the mountains.

name: Kenneth
meetText: Hold on to your hat! Kenneth has big dreams to become the next best race car driver! He might not move very fast on his own but as soon as he hits the gas - good luck keeping up!

name: Kenny
meetText: Kenny is not your average dragon – he loves watching movies, going dancing, and learning about the world of finance! When he’s not on the dance floor or catching the latest movie, he’s studying for his Master’s Degree.

name: Kenson
meetText: Kenson is a shy horse, he prefers to be home on a quiet ranch than to be in a crowd. When it's time to get ready for a race, he stays by his fearless friend Chance for motivation.

name: Kent
meetText: Kent is a theatre geek who loves to put on a show. While he's still not quite ready to play the lead, he dedicates a lot of time to the roles he plays and learning how to get into character. This year he's trying out for his first musical, can you help him prepare?

name: Keren
meetText: Keren roams the mall every weekday after school, and all day on weekends. It's her favorite place to be! She's even made friends with 'Mallows at the food court. So next time you and Keren hit the mall, get ready for pizza, hot dogs, and ice cream!

name: Kerry
meetText: Meet Kerry! Kerry is a team player, and is always a good sport - even when their siblings beat them in their daily swim races. Because Kerry is so patient and kind, they make the perfect coach for their family's swim team! Want to be Kerry's assistant coach?

name: Kerstin
meetText: Kerstin looks forward to summer festivals and summer fashion every year! She carefully books weekend passes to all outdoor summer shows, inviting one or two 'Mallow pals along. Kerstin tailors her outfits to be as comfortable as possible in the summer heat. Want to hang with Kerstin?

name: Kervena
meetText: Meet Kervena. He loves spending Saturday afternoons shopping for trendy thrifted threads. He has an eye for all things retro-lava lamps, classic cars, tie-dye, fringed jackets-you name it! He always finds something cool and unique on his excursions. Would you like to join?

name: Kesla
meetText: Springtime means one thing for Kesla - it's time to get outside! She hates being cooped up in the cold, so when springtime arrives, she loves to get outside and smell the fresh air. What is your favorite part of spring?

name: Kevin
meetText: Meet Kevin, this kooky koala loves eating breakfast for dinner. In fact, Kevin could eat breakfast for every meal! Can you guess his favorite breakfast combo? It's cereal and waffles, but he only likes to eat the cereal on top his waffles

name: Keysha
meetText: Keysha is no ordinary Squishmallow - she can read minds! Keysha is a fortune teller and she predicts the future for the Squishmallows Squad. Step into her magical tent and find out your Squish fortune today!

name: Khaled
meetText: You know you're in awe of Khaled's sparkle, smooth appearance! Khaled is one laid back 'Mallow and would spend all day basking in the sun if he could. Say hello, he might just invite you to play frisbee in the park or go for a dip in the pool.

name: Kieli
meetText: Kieli is a talented make-up artist. He uses his face as a canvas to express himself! He loves trying new products and creating new looks, then uploading them to his blog. He draws inspiration from nature and loves warm, earthy colors. He'd love to try his next look on you!

name: Kiki
meetText: Kiki is a medical student who has a passion for helping others. She is also an expert at needle work. When she's not studying for exams, you can find her sewing costumes for her friends! What would you have her make for you?

name: Kiks
meetText: Meet Kiks! Kiks has an unusual, but really fun job - he's a professional gift wrapper! For perfectly curled ribbons, calligraphy name tags and more wrapping paper options than you've ever seen, call Kiks! He'll add his extra loving touch to every present.

name: Kimberly
meetText: Kim is the editor of her school paper; she loves the hustle and bustle of the newsroom and even has a framed picture of her very first edition framed. Kim wants to be an editor at the Squishmallow Times when she grows up!

name: Kimia
meetText: Baking cakes and planning parties are two of Kimia's favorite activities.  She and her best friend Tres'zure plan parties for their friends. Tres'zure works on the decorations while Kimia does the menu, they make quite a team!

name: Kimmie
meetText: Meet Kimmie. This cupcake loves all things cheerful and creative, she loves thinking outside of the box! Kimmie is as bright and colorful as her rosy cheeks snd sprinkles she's always up for a sweet time with a side of giggles. You're in for a lot of fun with Kimmie around.

name: King
meetText: Grab some quarters and get ready for an intense day. King is trying to beat his high score in pinball! Ever since his first game, King has been obsessed with getting the highest score, ever! Do you ever get the end-of-ball bonus?

name: Kinsley
meetText: Looking for some extra help? Kinsley is the Squishmallow for you! Kinsley is a psychologist and volunteers to teach the importance of mental health. Kinsley has a passion for helping people and knows how hard it can be to live without help.

name: Kip
meetText: Kip is a fun-lovin' llama who lives for rock n' roll. You might call Kip an old soul because she prefers tunes from a different time. You can always find her listening to her parents' records and watching legendary performances from the past.

name: Kippie
meetText: Meet Kippie! They love anything and everything collectible, but the pride of their collection is their trading cards! Kippie has over 500 different cards, and each one is special to them. Can you guess which one is rare?

name: Kirk
meetText: You won’t meet anyone as lovable as Kirk! His passion for learning and mentorship makes him the perfect fit for becoming a teacher. What will your first lesson with Kirk be?

name: Detective Kirk
meetText: Meet Detective Kirk! He helps teach other mallows on the force how to help in times of crisis. When mallows have a problem and need a helping hand, Kirk is the koala for the job! He knows that it can be scary to talk to people in uniform so he tries extra hard to be friendly and fair. With Kirk on the case, you don’t have to fear.

name: Kirsten
meetText: If you need a penpal, Kirsten is the panda for you! She loves writing letters to her friends near and far. Her dad built her a cool writing desk, it has compartments for stationery, envelopes, and even a fancy stamp!

name: Kofi
meetText: Meet Kofi. His favorite part of Hanukkah is the food and trying to show off with his siblings. Their family tradition is a fashion show all 8 nights with prizes after the candles are lit. After walking the catwalk he can't wait to dig in!

name: Kristina
meetText: Meet Kristina. She loves to explore and makes the purr-fect travel partner! She's on a mission to visit all the wonders of the world. When she's not traveling around the globe you can find her taking cat naps and hanging out with friends. Where should she go next?

name: Kwame
meetText: Kwame teaches high school history. This is his dream job since it combines talking about 'Mallow history and hanging out with younger  generations. Kwame hosts his classes as interactive discussions and awards a prize to one star student every Friday! Think you can win this week?

name: Kya
meetText: Strawberry cupcakes and blueberry smoothies are two of Kya's favorite things. This koala has quite a sweet tooth and loves all desserts especially with berries: berry cakes, cookies, and even adds frozen berries to her hot cocoa! Fun fact about Kya: she's an expert tree climber even in the snow.

name: Kyla
meetText: Kyla has a memory like no other, and loves to recount stories whenever she meets new friends. She's also got an eye for photography and is great at taking portraits.

name: Kyra
meetText: Kyra knows all about crystals, gems, and minerals! She owns a small shop where she sells these little treasures, as well as books about them. Kyra's passion is helping other 'Mallows find their perfect crystal combo! Come by the shop to chat with Kyra about gems.

name: Lacey
meetText: Lacey loves lollipops, rainboots, and rainy days. She has a new pair of bright blue rain boots that she loves jumping into puddles with. Lacey picks out a new pair every spring and even gives them a name! What should she name her new blue pair?

name: Ladee
meetText: Ladee teaches the first grade. She's a big fan of nap time and reminds her students that every 'Mallow needs a quiet midday break, no matter their age. On Fridays, Ladee walks some of her students to the community pool for a free swim! She thinks there's no better way to end the week.

name: Lake
meetText: Lake writes short magazines and sends them to all of his closest ‘Mallow friends — he’s on issue #109! His dream is to write young adult novels from a little cottage in the woods, and be published under the pen name L.B. Gold. Would you read his stories?

name: Lakely
meetText: Green juice, peanut butter cookies and thunderstorms are some of Lakely’s favorite things. Lakely loves the rain so much that he has a collection of rain boots and matching umbrellas! He loves splashing in the puddles and hearing the crackle of thunder

name: Lala
meetText: Lala is the sweetest lamb you'll ever meet. She makes cards for all her friends and even has a special stamp to seal the envelopes. Lala's favorite thing to do is add just a tiny bit of glitter to the front where she writes her friends names. She hopes the extra sparkle will make them feel special.

name: Lalinda
meetText: Meet Lalinda. Have you heard of Lalinda? This ‘Mallow is taking the music industry by storm with her deep vocals and fun guitar riffs. You’ll catch her strutting down every red carpet this year and headlining all the major music events. Reach out to Lalinda on social media! She loves to hear from her fans.

name: Lamar
meetText: Lamar stars in a food show where he travels Seven Seas searching for the best vegetarian foods! This means he has to eat several meals each day just to get the footage needed for each episode. Not a problem for Lamar! He has limitless appetite for veg-tastic treats.

name: Lamont
meetText: Meet Lamont. This well-traveled ‘Mallow has a unique perspective on the world and a wonderful sense of humor. He brightens up any conversation with laughter and stories from his travels. Lamont seems to have been everywhere and knows just about everyone! Lamont would love to meet you next!

name: Lanai
meetText: Welcome to Lanai's garden! This 'Mallow could spend all day trimming and repotting flower beds, or just sitting on their favorite wicker chair watching everything grow. Lanai is especially proud of their cacti — some are growing taller than the fence!

name: Lance
meetText: Meet Lance. He loves BLTs, cookies and cream milkshakes, and jumping through the sprinkler in the summer. This loveable lemur is the high jump champion and wants to break the record for highest jump ever! Do you think he can do it?

name: Lander
meetText: Who loves animals and working on a farm? Lander does! She wakes up early and talks to them throughout the day, and sometimes, they even help her with silly pranks. Do you want to visit Lander's farm?

name: Lander
meetText: Who loves animals and working on a farm? Lander does! She wakes up early and talks to them throughout the day, and sometimes, they even help her with silly pranks. Do you want to visit Lander's farm?

name: Landon
meetText: If you're ever in need of a helping hand, Landon has a tentacle or two to spare. He works as a project manager and is quite possibly the most organised squid around. How does he unwind after a busy week? Karaoke!

name: Landry
meetText: Stand back and watch Landry work! Landry can fix anything as long as she has her trusty tool belt. Pretty soon Landry will be a licensed contractor fixing homes for all 'Mallows! Do you have a repair Landry can help with?

name: Laslow
meetText: Laslow loves to sing underwater karaoke. He doesn't worry about singing in tune or even singing all the right lyrics. The point is to have fun! He grooves and swims to his own beat. Come join him, he loves singing duets!

name: Laura
meetText: Laura is a creative cat who loves to build and invent things. Her ultimate hobby is gaming and she is always first in queue when a new game hits the market. Laura uses music to inspire her and loves to rock out to her heavy metal collection.

name: Lauren
meetText: Lauren loves to spend time with her sisters Layla and Lucia. She goes to all of Layla's games and all of Lucia's art shows. Layla's favorite part of being a big sister? Being a good role model AND having two best friends.

name: Lavada
meetText: This is one bunny you just have to meet! Lavada loves to live life to the fullest and color outside the lines. She loves jumping on the trampoline with friends during the day and gazing up at the stars at night. Do you know any constellations she can look for?

name: Layla
meetText: Have you ever seen a lemur play basketball? You'll want this leaping lemur on your team! Layla's favorite sport is basketball and she plays on the same team as her friend Wendy!

name: Leah
meetText: Who loves making flower crowns and flying kites? Leah! She makes crown and kite sets for her friends when they come over to play. This year she wants to make a giant kite of crowns, will you help Leah?

name: Leama
meetText: Leama loves glitz and glamour and dresses up any chance she gets. She spends all year looking forward to the time when she can don her tinsel, sparkly lights, golden star, and be the star of the show. Christmas is her time to truly shine!

name: Leanne
meetText: This unicorn loves spending time outside, especially with her family. Leanne comes from a huge family of Unipals and enjoys having pizza Fridays; she always eats the biggest slice! Join her on the next pizza pie night.

name: Leeland
meetText: Looking for a mallow who will always have your back? It's time you met Leeland! Leeland is a team player both on and off the court, especially when it involves his sister. Even though she is older than him and they don't always get along, he has her back.

name: Legacy
meetText: Meet Legacy. She has a beautiful butterfly garden which is perfect for frolicking amongst the flowers and keeping an eye out for new butterflies. Legacy’s favorite past time is laying in the grass and reading a book.

name: Leigh
meetText: Leigh never learned how to swim as a younger 'Mallow, but she just started taking lessons! Leigh practices her breathing technique every day and hopes to swim a full lap soon - all the way to the deep end of the pool. Want to go swimming with Leigh?

name: Lelila
meetText: Meet Lelila. She's a talented ice skater who sews her own outfits! She's currently working on a galaxy costume with extra sequins so she'll look like a dazzling comet soaring across the ice! Want to learn to skate? She teaches lessons too! Lace up your skates and join her!

name: Lemora
meetText: Lemora is everyone's go-to 'Mallow for the best book recommendations. In fact, Lemora extends an open invitation for anyone who wants to borrow from her collection of hundreds of books! Want to see what's on the shelf in Lemora's library?

name: Len
meetText: If ghost encounters and mysteries of the night are your thing, Len is the one for you! He loves to hear all about the unexplained and creates his own theories on what is really going on. Len wants to travel the world to find out more about what goes bump in the night, do you want to join him?

name: Lena
meetText: Lena is a candle queen - she has a candle for every mood! She makes her own soy candles and creates custom scents for all her friends. Just be careful not to eat the candles, she makes them in the shape of food and they look good enough to eat!

name: Lenaya
meetText: Lenaya likes sushi, strawberry shortcake, and reading books by the river. She enjoys traveling to new worlds while dipping her toes in the water. This year she is making all her friends literary Valentine cards, she can't wait to share them with her class.

name: Lenora
meetText: Have you ever met a loon who couldn’t sing? Lenora can’t! She comes from a family of beautiful singers but she is tone-deaf and has a hard time joining in. She wants to start a rock band so she can still sing in a unique way, will you join her band?

name: Leon
meetText: This monster isn't scary! Leon loves to cuddle and play games with his best friends and family. When Leon's having a bad day, he knows loved ones can make him feel better with sing-alongs and lots of sweet snacks! Leon's favorite feel-good snack is chocolate covered pretzels. Want to try one?

name: Leonard
meetText: Have you ever met a lion who didn’t eat meat? Meet Leonard, he’s a vegetarian! He loves lentils, lasagna, and learning how to code. Leonard loves naps like his older brother Richard and is helping create their website – the lion brothers!

name: Leonori
meetText: Leonori is a table tennis champion! He's won 1st place in the 'Mallow tournament 3 years in a row! He practices by wearing a blindfold and sensing where the ball is with only his ears. He also loves going to his friend Doxl's house for a fresh lunch from his garden.

name: Lerna
meetText: Lerna is a powerful, no-nonsense lady. An avid day trader and stock market expert, her independent hedge fund is valued in the billions. When her work is done, she enjoys a robust night life, dining in only the finest restaurants and rubbing elbows with Hollywood elites, earning her the nick name “Five-Star Lerna.”

name: Lesedi
meetText: Do you know any owls obsessed with cinnamon? It's time to meet Lesedi, the cinnamon queen! She loves cinnamon rolls, cinnamon hot chocolate, and even cinnamon lip gloss! When she grows up, maybe she'll start her own cinnamon restaurant, would you eat there?

name: Leslie
meetText: Looking for a Squishmallow to get into some mischief with? Leslie is the 'mallow for you! She loves to set 'traps' for her friends and is a practical joke maven, she is known for her jokes and always has a story to make you laugh.

name: Lester
meetText: Lester dreams a lot. This 'Mallow got so curious about his dreaming, they started a sleep research group in college. Lester is most fascinated by nightmares, and writes down all their dreams so they can learn about what makes them so weird and scary. What do you dream about?

name: Leticia
meetText: Though they have very different personalities, they play tennis like one on the court. Leticia is shyer than her brother Leeland but once she’s got her racket, the game is on. Watch out for her forehand!

name: Levi
meetText: Levi loves marshmallows and jellybeans and every Easter he tries to stack a marshmallow tower to be taller than he is. They usually fall down before he can add the top one, maybe next year he'll run out of marshmallows!

name: Leviathan
meetText: Leviathan is a mythical sea serpent with a need for speed. Across the Seven Seas, this blue beast has a mean reputation, but at the end of the day, Leviathan is just a softie who loves nothing more than a good cuddle.

name: Levinda
meetText: Levinda built an epic treehouse! She even set up a little rope and pulley system to bring supplies up the tree. Levinda laid out a big carpet and some beanbag chairs to create a cozy space for when friends come over to visit. Now the treehouse just needs a name. Do you have any ideas for Levinda?

name: Lexi
meetText: Halloween Edition: Who's that fox? It's your favorite fashionista Lexi and she is ready for Halloween! Lexi designed her costume and she can't wait to show her squad when she gets to Holly's party.

name: Lexie
meetText: Lexie is quite the imaginative Squishmallow. She aspires to become an architect! What’s her next project? She is creating the interior and exterior of her future home with the rest of her cheetah girls.

name: Lexis
meetText: Lexis loves attending hockey games with her sister, Erica. A certified history buff, Lexis enjoys everything she can about the game.  In fact, she knows so much that the local college asked her to teach her a brand-new course—Evolution of the Puck!

name: Liam
meetText: Liam has always dreamt of becoming a teacher. What's his favorite subject? History! He has a love for antique items and fossils, and always has his head in the books.

name: Lianne
meetText: Meet Lianne. She loves dim sum, iced tea, and reading mystery novels. When she’s not drooling over a dim sum feast, you can find her studying to become a lawyer. Lianne comes from a long line of lawyers and wants to continue to help people.

name: Libby
meetText: Lollipops, lacrosse, and lime green are some of Libby's favorite things. This llamacorn doesn't like to share but her friend Lucinda is teaching her why that's important. Will you help Libby learn to like sharing?

name: Liel
meetText: Meet Liel. She loves dancing, dogs, and collecting her favorite toys. Liel is an expert dancer, she and her friends have a blast trying out the latest viral dance trend. Do you want to join them?

name: Lietta
meetText: Lietta can skate fast, but she prefers blades to the board. She skates to the beach every summer with her friend Halisa. They met at the skate park one summer and now they are the best of friends.

name: Lilac
meetText: Hi! My name is Lilac! My mini and I love to hop through meadows and pick flowers.

name: Lilian
meetText: Lilian or as her friends call her ‘Lili’, is kind, loyal and very competitive! She is always up to play a fun activity, especially if it’s a sport. Her favorite sport to play is soccer and her wings help her glide across the field quickly. When she’s not scoring goals, she loves to help her mom cook for their family in the kitchen!

name: Lilibet
meetText: Meet Lilibet. She is bright, bubbly, and just a little gullible. This delightful duck would do anything for you, she's the best kind of friend to have. Lilibet always stands up for what is right.

name: Lilith
meetText: Sparkles and glamour are two things Lilith can't live without. She loves glitter on everything, even her socks! For her birthday brunch, she wants to have glittery waffles and sparkling strawberry sundaes for all her friends.

name: Lilou
meetText: Needlepoint and dodgeball are two things that keep Lilou calm. She likes to focus and get creative when she's working on a new design, she even created personalized canvas for everyone on her dodgeball team!

name: Lily
meetText: Have you heard the phrase 'lillies for fillies'? That's what Lily was named after! Her mom used to help with the fillies' race and one day Lily wants to help too. She loves helping the racers get ready and one year she even gave the winning horse her bouquet!

name: Lily
meetText: Lily and her friend Levi dream of one day opening a candy shop, but they want to specialize in marshmallows, jellybeans, and lollipops! Lily wants to make the candy while Levi stacks it in cool baskets. Would you try Squishmallow candy?

name: Limell
meetText: Meet Limell. He Loves swimming, archery, and hanging with his friends. He's had to take a little break because he just got his tonsils removed. But he gets to eat as many blue raspberry popsicles and he wants! Would you like one? He's always willing to share.

name: Linda
meetText: Linda loves cupcakes, superhero movies, and staying inside on rainy days. Linda is shy at first, but once you get to know her she'll be your best friend!

name: Lindsay
meetText: You've met Regan, the king of hip hop, now is your chance to meet Lindsay, the QUEEN. This spunky leopard has moves and style unlike any other mallow, music is what keeps Lindsay going. Whether she's having a good day or a bad one, she lets the music talk for her and speaks and dances whatever is on her mind.

name: Liv
meetText: Who loves cheese, space, and nature walks? Liv does! You can find her with a grilled cheese in hand, gazing up at the stars learning about constellations. She wants to build rocket ships when she grows up, do you want to explore space with Liv?

name: Livvy
meetText: Meet Livvy. Her favorite color is yellow and she is an amazing photographer. She brings her camera with her everywhere to capture all aspects of life. Her favorite subjects are nature, especially capturing a sunrise or sunset. Maybe one day you'll see her photos published!

name: Liza
meetText: Liza escapes to the spa every Sunday! First Liza goes for a long swim, then it's off to the ice sauna for some cold therapy. This 'Mallow really knows how to treat herself to a relaxing day! Before leaving, Liza grabs a hot cup of jasmine tea and strolls home for a healthy lunch.

name: Lizette
meetText: Gather round, Lizette is about to open a parcel from her grandmother! Her grandmother is a travel guide and sends Lizette a post card and a care package full of treasures from her latest travels. Can you guess where her latest adventure took place?

name: Lizma
meetText: Meet Lizma. She loves writing, playing with her pet dog, and hosting fun, snack-filled parties with her friends! She is an expert at the art of cheeseboards, and makes beautiful spreads! Everyone's invited! So bring your dancing shoes and some songs to add to the party playlist!

name: Lobert
meetText: Lobert travels all over the world helping companies buy and sell their goods. He's on the road this month and will be staying at his sister, Loberta's, bed and breakfast! Lobert always looks forward to catching up with his sis over a tasty brunch. They might even have time for board games!

name: Loberta
meetText: Going out of town? You're welcome to stay at Loberta's bed & breakfast! Loberta hosts 'Mallows from all over and is really starting to gain popularity. You can expect freshly baked muffins every morning, and an extensive board game library.

name: Lobi
meetText: Lobi loves to knit, she has a room full of yarn! Some of her favorites are rainbow yarn, yarn with sparkles, and even bubblegum scented yarn! One day she wants to open a museum for yarn, would you visit?

name: Lockwood
meetText: Lockwood plays professional football! He's living his dream as a kicker playing for his favorite regional team. Lockwood thrives under pressure, and loves having a whole stadium watch him make a winning kick. Want tickets to this Sunday's game?

name: Logan
meetText: If you want someone to keep you safe Logan is the Squishmallow for you! Logan takes his job very seriously!- he's one of Santa's helpers! He helps protect the North Pole making sure that none of Santa's secrets get out. His birthday is December 26th and his favorite drink is hot cocoa with peppermint

name: Lola
meetText: Lola loves the color pink, watching movies with her friends, and wants to be an actress when she grows up. She loves to visit new places and dreams of traveling the world while she makes movies.

name: Lomo
meetText: Lomo is over the moon to meet you! He's a real extrovert and nothing brightens his day more than making a new friend. Once Lomo went on a vacation himself and made so many new friends they all became pen pals! Lomo makes time to respond on each and every letter he receives. Would you like to be pen pals with Lomo?

name: Lonina
meetText: Years of practice make Lonina the yoga queen. She's been stretching since she was a little 'mallow. and now she's a bona fide instructor! Lonina teaches yoga and healing techniques for all ages, and you can find many of her courses on video! Grab your yoga mat and strike a pose with Lonina.

name: Lonnie
meetText: Looking for a Babysitter? Lonnie is the girl for you! She helped watch her siblings so much when she was younger that now she's a babysitting pro. Her best babysitting trick? A DIY popcorn bar for movie night!

name: Loraly
meetText: Need some help with your math homework, or pro tips on space travel? Loraly is the 'Mallow for you! She loves physics, star-hopping with friends, and always has the best restaurant recommendations. Loraly is packing her spaceship now for a weekend getaway. There's room for one more if you want to join!

name: Lorelai
meetText: Meet Lorelai. She's a bit extroverted and a bit introverted, too! She loves a yummy dinner party with friends or a groovy disco party with loud music. She also needs a time alone to recharge with a quiet bath or a book! No matter what, she always finds the right balance for her!

name: Lorenzo the Banana Slug
meetText: Meet Lorenzo. Lorenzo is a TV buff and blogger! He wants to use his knowledge and passion for television to break into showbiz. Lorenzo aspires to build his own TV network so he can schedule all his favorite shows and help create some new ones!

name: Loretta
meetText: Loretta started a chess club at her school so she could meet likeminded 'Mallows who love chess as much as she does. Sometimes Lor brings in chess boards from her collection to show everyone - there are so many different kinds! Her favorite is the mini travel board with itty bitty chess pieces.

name: Lorie
meetText: Lorie is a talented singer and baker. She can make ANY dessert you ask and will even sing your favorite song while she does it. She loves to play in the garden and take care of her friends when they have bad days. When she grows up she wants to work on a farm.

name: Lorita
meetText: Lorita bakes carrot cake so delicious, they only make it once a year! Lorita adds chocolate chips upon request, and will also make a loaf nut-free for some of their 'Mallow pawls. Lorita's super secret recipe makes their carrot cake even more special! Want to order a one-of-a-kind carrot cake from Lorita?

name: Lorono
meetText: Chop Chop! Lorono is the fastest sous chef in the west. He cooks with ease under the pressure! When he's not in the kitchen at his fast-paced restaurant, he's traveling the world to find inspiration and new and delicious flavors to bring back with him. Bon appétit!

name: Louden
meetText: Meet Louden, his birthday is coming up and he's planning the best party ever. There's going to be a peanut butter and jelly sandwich bar, a silly photo booth and a light up dance floor to get groovy on! Everyone is invited, including you! So grab your party hat and come celebrate!

name: Louie
meetText: Are you looking for a racing partner? Louie might be the one for you! Born and raised in Louisville, he grew up racing with his friends and has a special dance when he wins. His favorite part of winning? Celebrating with his friends! Do you want to race with Louie?

name: Louie
meetText: Meet Louie. He has dyslexia and has had to take a few extra lessons to help him learn to read. He's doing really well! He's almost finished with his first chapter book! He's grown to love books and stories and one day wants to be a librarian when he grows up.

name: Louisa
meetText: Get ready to hit the slopes and glide along as Louisa dances across the snow. This penguin princess loves to ski, it's her favorite mode of transportation. You can spot Louisa a mile away in one of her sparkly snowsuits and her hot pink skis.

name: Louise
meetText: When it comes to setting up the table, Louise sets the bar! This hostess with the mostest throws the best dinner parties in town! An ear of corn with an eye for detail, Louise ensures her guests are well fed and even better entertained. Remember to RSVP!

name: Lowell
meetText: Lowell goes out caroling every winter. At first they got nervous singing in public, but now Lowell is as confident as ever! Caroling with friends around town or under the gazebo at the park has become one of Lowell's favorite traditions. Will you join Lowell's caroling group this year?

name: Luanne
meetText: Luanne loves long summer nights on her front porch. She sits in her rocking chair and keeps a wooden folding fan handy in case the air gets too humid. Luanne made a pitcher of iced tea this afternoon. Will you come over and share a glass with Luanne?

name: Lucasta
meetText: Lucasta freaked out last year at the Halloween fair and went home early—but not this year! Lucasta promised herself she would be a brave bat all night, even on the super scary haunted house ride. She brought her pal, Ramably, so they can laugh out loud during all the creepy sound effects!

name: Lucia
meetText: Lucia loves pepperoni pizza, the color yellow, and her sisters (most days). Lucia is a middle child and uses her paintings to show her feelings. Her special skill? She’s ambidextrous! This school year she plans to start an art club, will you join her?

name: Luciano
meetText: Luciano works a 9-to-5, but they also live the caravan lifestyle! They keep all their things in their van and call it home. Every weekend, Luciano drives into the mountains where they find the perfect camping spot right by a lake! By Monday, Luciano returns to their office feeling rested and recharged.

name: Lucille
meetText: Lucille loves living near the water! She always finds new creatures, hidden gems and her favorite, rocks, whenever she goes on a dive. Ask her to see her amazing rock collection.

name: Lucinda
meetText: Meet Lucinda, this sweet Squishmallow LOVES to volunteer at the local animal shelter and dreams of one day running an animal rescue. Her hobbies include taking care of animals, reading, and watching sci-fi with her rescue dog.

name: Lucy-May
meetText:
Lucy-May is all about adventure and doing as much as she can on her roller skates (she has been known to fall asleep in them!). Her favorite drink is boba and on the weekends you can find her with her crew trying new roller derby tricks.
Lucy-May is kind, creative, unique llama!

name: Ludwig
meetText: Log cabins and snowboarding are two of Ludwig's favorite things, he loves being in the great outdoors. He runs a ski lodge that sits at the top of a hill, so every morning when he wakes up, he can see snow-covered trees for miles around. Join him for a sunrise cruise down the slopes.

name: Ludovica
meetText: Ludovica is the electrifying editor-in-chief of a fashion magazine for stylish sea 'Mallows. When she isn't declaring kelp kits out-of-fashion, you can find Ludovica scouring the seafloor for the latest trends. What do you think about barnacles for spring?

name: Luke
meetText: Luke is the king of the playground. He is quite the social butterfly! Luke is always making friends with other Squishmallows on the swings, on the field or on the court.

name: Lula
meetText: Meet Lula. This 'Mallow makes her home in a fixed-up vintage school bus with her parents They travel cross-country to visit National Parks. Lula is working on collecting all of her Junior Ranger badges, When  they're not hiking, she loves roller skating around the bus.

name: Lulu
meetText: Meet Lulu Pineapple, her favorite season is summer. Lulu loves summer cookouts, beach picnics, and going on camping trips. Where should Lulu camp this summer?

name: Lumi
meetText: Who's that panda covered in frosting? It's Lumi! He works at a bakery and creates scrumptious cakes and cupcakes. When he's not decorating cakes or helping pick out a birthday surprise, Lumi loves to relax by playing the cello.

name: Luna
meetText: The cold can't stop Luna's dancing feet. She brings the heat with her smooth moves. Looking for a Squishmallow to lift you up when you're down? Luna is your girl!

name: Lune
meetText: Waiting around is no problem for Lune — she always has a book to read. Lune loves old philosophy books that make her think. Lune wonders who she is and what kind of 'Mallow she wants to be. These are big questions, but for Lune, there's no rush to find the answer.

name: Lupi
meetText: Ready to make a wish? Lupi stays up late looking at constellations and wanting for shooting stars. She never misses a lunar phase or eclipse, and one time she even saw a flying saucer! You never know what you'll see hanging out with Lupi!

name: Luther
meetText: Achooo! Luther is one sneezy shark, his sneeze attacks make him sneeze 6 times in a row. This year at the science fair he's going to do a project on what makes people sneeze. Do you want to help him out?

name: Luvinia
meetText: Meet Luvinia. This daring 'Mallow is a tight rope walker. Would you believe she used to be afraid of heights? Now she walks a rope high up above the mountains! When she's not sky high, Luvinia loves painting, listening to country music, and eating extra spicy food!

name: Luxe
meetText: Sequins, feathers, and a little bit of magic are things you'll find in Luxe's tote. She's a dancer with glitter to spare, just don't get anything on her freshly rhinestoned costume!

name: Luxmen
meetText: Meet Luxmen. He's an entrepreneur! He's working hard to create his own tutoring non-profit to give everyone access to helpful education tools. Luxmen believes knowledge is power and the more we learn, the better the world becomes!

name: Luya
meetText: Luya teaches a life skills math class for high school seniors. She knows teaching personal finance can be challenging, so Luya developed fun group projects for each lesson! This week, Luya's class is covering card responsibility. Ready to give a presentation on interest rates?

name: Luz
meetText: Birthday parties are the best when Luz is around, she loves singing birthday songs for the guests of honor! When it’s time for cake and presents, Luz is first in line.

name: Lyan
meetText: Lyan loves creepy, crawly critters! Lyan has always been curious about insects, and he's thinking about being a scientist when he grows up so he can study them all the time. He even has an ant farm in his room so he can watch them work. Want to see his ant colony?

name: Lydia
meetText: Lydia laughs so loud you can hear her a mile away. The only thing Lydia loves more than big belly laughs is playing the piano! She performs on weekend nights with the local orchestra. It might be the only time Lydia looks serious, but she goes back to chuckling as soon as she takes a bow.

name: Lyla
meetText: Meet Lyla. She loves to cuddle, especially when it means cheering someone up if they are sad. Lyla loves gymnastics and the color blue, she even has a lucky blue leotard. When she grows up, Lyla wants to be a dentist. She can't wait to wear blue scrubs!

name: Lyle
meetText: Do you want to jog with Lyle? Lyle is always on the move and goes for a run at the track every single morning He has so much energy. sometimes he even runs a whole lap before the sun comes up! But if chilling with a cup of tea and a book is more your speed. Lyle is happy to have some calm, quite times with you

name: Lyndon
meetText: Feeling sick? Let Lyndon check it out! She's a medical student curious to learn all she can about curing 'Mallows. Last week, Lyndon learned why her foot falls asleep, and now she takes five minute dance breaks in the middle of a long study session to improve circulation!

name: Mac
meetText: Meet Mac. He's decorating his treehouse for fall and Cornelias is helping him! They have snacks and fabric samples to pick the perfect curtains! He's having trouble deciding on the right shade of orange — pumpkin spice or pumpkin pie? Can you help him decide?

name: Macario
meetText: Meet Macario. He enjoys being in the warm sunshine and exploring the outdoors. His favorite treat is ice cream, he loves all the flavors! Macario loves stopping for ice cream after an adventure, would you take him to your favorite ice cream spot?

name: Mackenzie
meetText: Have you ever seen a more colourful crab than Mackenzie? She is a keen artist and loves to paint abstract portraits of all of her friends. Her two loves are painting of course and hotdogs! It's rare to find her without a paintbrush in one claw and a tasty hotdog in the other.

name: Maddie
meetText: Meet Maddie. She is one of the most passionate and dedicated 'Mallows out there. Maddie's friends are her biggest supporters and always encourage her to reach for the stars. She has big dreams of one day being the president of her very own company!

name: Maddox
meetText: Maddox is a stylist who loves to dance with his friend Poppy. He picks the look to go with Poppy's song choice and designs something new if they can't find the right piece. When they aren't in the studio, you can find Maddox playing video games with friends.

name: Madeleine
meetText: Meet Madeleine, whose friends call her Maddy. Maddy is a girly girl whose favorite pastime is getting a mani-pedi with her mom and her favorite aunt. For Halloween, Maddy chose a purple nail polish and dyed her hair purple to match. Afterwards, she went trick or treating with her big brother!

name: Madven
meetText: Madven attends all the local music shows in her town. She loves collecting the band t-shirts! Madven has almost 100 tees in her collection and she personalizes each of them with different cuts and even little jewels! Do you want Madven to customize a shirt for you?

name: Maeve
meetText: Meet Maeve. Maeve is one of the mellowest 'Mallows you'll meet! They go with the flow, literally! They let the water take them wherever the current goes! They love relaxing with a good book and a snack. Saltwater taffy is their favorite!

name: Magela
meetText: Magela is an activist who works hard for her fellow squad members to be safe and live in harmony. Whenever she hears of a problem, she finds a way to get involved. She knows that when everyone has what they need, the world is a better place.

name: Maggie
meetText: Maggie is no ordinary stingray, she's a stingray with a degree! Maggie just received her Masters in PA and can't wait to start helping people. This helpful stingray loves cooking, volleyball, and of course watching medical shows in her spare time.

name: Magtus
meetText: Magtus collects lots of souvenirs from all over the world! But please ask him before taking one out of the cabinet. Magtus gets protective over these little treasures—even though some are as simple as coins or shells, it's still enough for Magtus to give you some side eye!

name: Magzie
meetText: Meet Magzie. This 'Mallow's mantra is stay calm and dance on! Whenever she's feeling anxious or down, she turns up her favorite music and dances around in her living room. She loves hip-hop and punk rock! Feeling down? Pick a song and dance along!

name: Mahdi
meetText: Mahdi collects seashells on his morning strolls at the beach! He uses simple home goods, like vases and picture frames, to create unique seashell art. Mahdi's most popular pieces are his lamps that are covered in individual shells. Want to see one of his little seashell nightlights?

name: Maisha
meetText: Maisha just started her own business, she makes candles! She handmakes each of the candles she sells and adds a little note to the bottom of each candle. She is always looking for new scent ideas, do you have any suggestions?

name: Major
meetText: Tune in to Major's podcast every Friday night to learn about spooky mysteries and history Major works hard on recording and editing each episode of "Major Mysteries," and he's looking for a co host could it be you?

name: Marjorie
meetText: Marjorie is known as the queen of many things. She is the reigning Miss 'Mallow, was voted as prom queen of her high school and 'most likely to make a difference in the world.' Marjorie stays humble even with all the accolades, and knows being the queen of kindness is what matters the most.

name: Makena
meetText: What's that glistening in the sun? It looks like something made by Makena! She collects jewels, shells, and crystals from the deep sea makes beautiful jewellery. Don't worry about having any copycat designs, she only creates one-of-a-kind pieces.

name: Malcolm
meetText: Have you ever met a soccer-playing Mushroom? Malcolm is the one for you! He's the goalie on his team and they've won the championship three years in a row!

name: Malia
meetText: Meet Malia. Anywhere Malia goes, you're likely to find her sister, Mopey, too! When they were little, Malia and Mopey even made up their own language so that their siblings couldn't listen in on their conversations! Don't worry, Malia and Mopey will always let you in on their secrets!

name: Malik
meetText: Have an equation you just can't solve? Malik is here to help! Malik is great at maths and sees numbers in a totally different way. He love to make numbers make sense for his friends.

name: Maline
meetText: Meet Maline. She has a sweet tooth, but sugar isn't good for her. She recently started baking healthy desserts that taste yummy and make her feel good! Do you want to try a yummy, sugar free cookie?

name: Mallora
meetText: Meet Mallora, one foxy 'Mallow! She is an aspiring fashion designer by and DJs a roller club at night. She sets the mood with her remixes: just keep your hands off her "doo"!

name: Malta
meetText: Malta isn't like most doctors—she's a dessert doctor! From refreezing melted ice cream to reapplying cookie crumbles, this medicinal 'Mallow helps sweet treats reach their full-flavored potential!

name: Malu
meetText: Malu joined her friend Omar's running group! She wants to start practicing for next year's city-wide marathon, and the thought of having a running buddy would be the best way. All this exercise has made Malu hungrier than ever! Want to come over for a big, healthy lunch?

name: Mannon
meetText: Mannon likes order. Just look at her desk—everything is at a 90 degree angle! This comic book artist would never color outside of the lines, and says boundaries help bring out her creativity. It must be working too. Mannon has just been nominated for a well-known animation award!

name: Manny
meetText: Manny is quite the handy man. He enjoys picking up the pieces. He's known for building the most memorable gingerbread houses every year. He hopes to connect creativity and machines as an engineer in the future.

name: Marceline
meetText: Have you met Queen Marceline? This fabulous 'Mallow leads a glamorous life, she lives and breathes old school style. She loves to go thrifting and looking for vintage pieces to add to her new home.

name: Marcellus
meetText: You might think you’re seeing double, but Marcellus is very different than his twin sister. While Maritza is adventurous and active, Marcellus is more soft-spoken and likes to stay inside. He loves to build things like model airplanes, cars, and even little towns.

name: Marcella
meetText: Marcella loves cooking for her friends. This amateur chef is particularly talented at caprese salads, caprese sandwiches, and caprese pasta! Try as she may to move on from basil, tomato, and mozzarella, Marcella can't help it. After all, she's crazy about caprese!

name: Marcita
meetText: Meet Marcita. She loves dressing up and celebrating friends and family just as much as the next 'Mallow, but her favorite way to celebrate is always the food. She wakes up early to prep a feast, would you like to try some?

name: Marco
meetText: Marco loves to play games with his friends like soccer, Go Fish, and his personal favorite, Marco Polo. He likes to spend Valentine's Day with his grandparents who always make him homemade candy.

name: Marcos
meetText: Marcos is writing a song about Vitamin C. The only problem? He can't find a word that rhymes with orange! Though Marcos has looked through every word dictionary in the library, the best he can come up with is 'door hinge.' Can you help him keep looking?

name: Marcus
meetText: You've never met a nicer monster than Marcus! He drives a big yellow bus and makes sure all his passengers get to their destination safe and sound. Marcus loves orange soda and uses black licorice for a straw.

name: Marcy
meetText: Meet Marcy. This snazzy spotted pig can't wait to have her own set of keys because she already owns so many key chains! Marcy is always on the hunt for shiny treasures, and loves everything pretty, plastic, and petite. Next time you see Marcy at school, check out her new collection of backpack pins!

name: Maria
meetText: Need a weather update? Meet Maria, meteorologist at the local news station. She loves her job, rain or shine! But when the sun is out, Maria rides her bright yellow beach cruiser on the boardwalk, and always grabs a passionfruit ice cream after!

name: Mariah
meetText: Have you met Mariah? This little lamb loves horseback riding and horchata and will always have your back. Mariah's favorite place to visit is the stables with her pony named Bernard!

name: Mariam
meetText: Mariam paints an array of self-portraits using watercolors. Each portrait has variations on the other, either with a different color palette or background, but she always keeps the same pose. You can catch her art displayed in galleries downtown. Want to go appreciate Mariam's art?

name: Mariana
meetText: Mariana is a graduate student working on a master's degree in psychology! Mari has always known she wanted to be a therapist, and when she isn't studying at the dinner table, she's practicing her nail art! This week, Mari is painting her talons with green glitter tips.

name: Marianovella
meetText: Meet Marianovella. This nimble narwhal is full of creative ideas thanks to her love of food, fun, and fashion. Sometimes she finds inspiration where she least expects it. If you want someone to get creative with, grab a pizza and give her a call!

name: Maribel
meetText: Original: Maribel has always loved going on trips and exploring new places! Her family has travelled all around the country in their RV, visiting national parks, monuments and historic sites. Join her on an adventure!

name: Marina
meetText: Marina’s favorite color is pink and one day she wants to be a model. She loves playing football, riding dirt bikes, and spending time with her cousin Connor.

name: Mario
meetText: Have you met Mario? His parents want him to be an architect but he wants to be a pastry chef and bake tall, elaborate cakes. Mario has always loved building things so he can't wait to make things out of cake! What kind of cake should he bake first?

name: Mariposa
meetText: When fall rolls around, Mariposa starts brewing her famous hot fruit and spice teas. Today she's making a big batch of cranberry, apple, cinnamon tea, and bringing a thermos to all her neighbors—it's their favorite! What teas do you like to drink in the fall?

name: Marisa
meetText: Meet Marisa. She deals with anxiety and can get a little blue sometimes. Luckily, she has thoughtful friends and family who always stick by her side. When she's feeling down, they hug her and remind her how great she is, and that a new sunny day is just around the corner!

name: Maritza
meetText: Have you ever met a soccer playing cactus? Maritza’s the one for you! She’s the goalie on her team and they’ve won the championship three years in a row!

name: Marius
meetText: Marius takes his time making decisions-they feel so final! He researches about the topic until he's confident about the choice he make. Right now, Marius wants to invest in a new computer. What advice would you give to Marius?

name: Mark
meetText: Motorcycles, milkshakes, and mountains are some of Mark's favorite things. You can catch this 'Mallow getting ready for a road trip or getting ready for another summit!

name: Marla
meetText: How does this ladybug keep up with the hustle and bustle of city life? Marla doesn't even know herself! She lives on the move, flying from one appointment to the next. But Marla always makes time for everything, including herself. Next on today's agenda is a self-care hydrafacial.

name: Marley
meetText: Ready to flip? Marley's French omelettes are as perfect as her somersaults. She's been cooking eggy deligts since she was a young cub — now she has the technique down pat. Omelettes are Marley's favorite meal before gymnastics class and they help her stay strong and energized.

name: Marlowe
meetText: Marlowe is a history buff who loves watching documentaries about ancient civilizations. She dreams of one day climbing the Great Pyramids. Her perfect day is going to a museum and grabbing two scoops of pecan ice cream after. Ask her for a bite, she loves to share!

name: Marshal
meetText: Marshal is the music director and conductor of his city's classical orchestra! Marshal loves composing the music for a concert with the musicians. He's known for getting really into the music and using his whole body when he conducts - even his feathery mane gets messy!

name: Marshina
meetText: Have you met Marshina? This cocoa queen has an imagination that is almost out of this world. From sci-fi heroines to everyday stories, Marshina is full of stories. She dreams of becoming a writer and taking the world she imagined from her head to the big screen.

name: Marta
meetText: Marta decorated her entire bedroom with string lights, puffy clouds, and jewel curtains in every doorway—it's totally dreamy! Marta can't wait to invite her bestie, Maya, to hang out in her posh new bedroom. Ready for fun time with the coolest sundae around?

name: Martina
meetText: Martina is a lipstick artist who shares new makeup designs on her vlog almost daily. She loves to try dramatic or bright looks to stand out. Right now her favorite combo is matte red with gold shimmer gloss, would you try it?

name: Martine
