meetText: If you are looking for a magical meal, Martine is the llama for you! Martine comes from a BIG family and got his love for cooking from his mama. He loves experimenting with old and new recipes and will make you a Llamazing meal any day!

name: Marty
meetText: Have you ever met a dragon who loves to bake? It's time you met Marty! He makes the best chocolate chip cookies thanks to a secret family recipe, one day he wants to open his own bakery. He'll call it Marty's Munchies and make cookies of all kinds.

name: Maruta
meetText: Any dish Maruta makes tastes unexpectedly delicious! Her famous rice with coconut milk and raisins will have you going back for seconds every time. Maruta loves to cook with ingredients that surprise her dinner guests. You're invited to a special Valentine's dinner tonight!

name: Marvin
meetText: Have you met Marvin? This mallow monster is the life of the party when he hears his favorite monster mix! He loves to dance to spooky beats. Marvin's favorite food is spaghetti and meatballs - with pickles!

name: Mary
meetText: Meet Mary. She loves softball, volunteering, and extra cheesy enchiladas. Mary holds the record for the highest number of catches on her team. Her favorite thing to do after games is go to eat with her team, they have a team meal after every game.

name: Marybeth
meetText: Meet MaryBeth! MaryBeth loves to find little spots to make into comfy hidey-holes. She's not particularly shy, but having her own quiet space makes her feel safe and happy! She has one rule -- all of her spots have to have lots of fluffy blankets! Want to hang out in her blanket fort?

name: Massai
meetText: Massai enjoys being active like his cousin, Tristan. He plays basketball, football, and baseball; his lucky sweatband protects his cool 'doo. Can you guess his favorite snack - macaroni and cheese!

name: Mateo
meetText: Mateo gives the best hugs — this 'Mallow is known for spreading smiles wherever he goes. Mateo doesn’t know what he wants to be when he grows up but he knows that he wants to help people.

name: Matias
meetText: Uphill hikes don't scare Matias. Every morning he laces up his boots for a 3-mile hike and watches the sun rise. Once he even hiked 14 miles in one day! Matias eats an avocado to keep his energy up. What snack will you bring to hike with Matias?

name: Matilda
meetText: Meet Matilda. Her favorite food is macaroni and cheese, but she only likes shell noodles. Even though she's picky about noodles, she loves every cheese! Matilda wants to work at a macaroni restaurant where they only serve macaroni and cheese, would you go there with Matilda?

name: Matt
meetText: Did you see those crazy tee-shirt designs? Yes, Matt might have helped inspire the design! He loves graphic design + fashion and aspires to be a fashion designer one day.

name: Maui
meetText: Skateboards and scuba diving are two scary things Maui is determined to conquer her fear of. She already checked roller coasters and rollerblading off her list. Maui doesn’t like to be scared so she tries to conquer her fears by trying new things. Can Maui help you overcome one of your fears?

name: Maura
meetText: Maura has a weak spot for chocolate - she just can't get enough! Whenever her friends travel, they make sure to bring her back some unique chocolate. Maura wants to work in a chocolate shop someday so she can sample all the yummy chocolate.

name: Maurice
meetText: Maurice LOVES chocolate chip pancakes and eats them almost every Saturday. His dad makes a giant stack for Maurice and his sisters to share. One day Maurice wants to be the host for a pancake show so he can try all kinds of pancakes.

name: Mauricio
meetText: Meet Mauricio. This octopus is an optimistic romantic and his love language is food. He finds great joy in cooking for others and finds inspiration when sharing a new recipe. His idea of the perfect meal is an oceanside dinner at sunset. Can he make you something yummy?

name: Mauve
meetText: Mauve is a crochet extraordinaire and is always making new clothes for her friends. She aspires to own a store one day where she can sell all her goods!

name: Mav
meetText: Mav lives for the summer! He hosts water balloon fights and bubble blowing competitions with all his friends. This summer, he's challenging himself to try a new ice cream flavor every day! Think he'll get a brain freeze?

name: Max
meetText: Meet Max the techy! This raccoon loves technology: when he isn't playing his video games or learning about cars he enjoys rocking out to his favorite band. This little raccoon is adventurous and will take long bike rides to his favorite Italian bistro!

name: Maxella
meetText: Maxella challenged herself to make the ultimate party playlist! She's taking her time to carefully select every song, including the order they're played. Once the list in completed, she can't wait to share with her whole squad! Do you have a song to recommend?

name: Maxine
meetText: Click clack, do you hear that? Miss Maxine may have some of the most stylish wings around but she has a fierce walk like you wouldn't believe! When she was a mini mallow, she loved to wear her mom's fancy shoes and now that's all she wears.

name: Maxwell
meetText: Maxwell likes to play hard to get, but he's a real sweetie at heart. He's a poet and has written some great stories. If you're lucky he'll share them with you.

name: Maya
meetText: Meet Maya the mint ice cream! She’s fresh, cool, with a hint of sweet – how all the mallows describe Maya. This marvelous mallow is the best mallow to know if you need a helping hand. She’ll give you a little tough love but always knows the right things to say to turn your frown upside down.

name: Mead
meetText: Mead works from home as a web developer, and loves to create a cozy environment for themselves! For fall, Mead hangs little pumpkin string lights, fills decorative bowls with pinecones, and pours their own cinnamon stick candles. How do you decorate for the fall season?

name: Meadow
meetText: If spring is your favorite season, Meadow is the Squishmallow for you! They love the transition from the dreary winter greys to lush bright colors, especially the smell of blooming flowers. Want to hear their favorite part? Listening to thunderstorms at night.

name: Medea
meetText: Give Medea all your candy wrappers and watch her make a work of art! She knots and glues all kinds of shapes and colors together to create tiny sculptures. Try holding the jack-o'-lantern Medea just made with caramel wrappers—it's so small and light!

name: Medina
meetText: Did you catch that flash of yellow? It's Medina on her longboard! This superfast slushie works at a coffee shop and sometimes she helps with the deliveries. She's an expert at taking orders and juggling coffees.

name: Meemie
meetText: Do you know any good jokes? Make sure to share them with Meemie, this wacky waffle loves to share jokes. Meemie wants to be a comedian one day and help people through hard times.

name: Meg
meetText: If you like camping, Meg is the mallow for you! She knows how to navigate the outdoors and makes the best s'mores you’ll ever try.

name: Megan
meetText: Megan studies chemistry in colorful, cozy outfits! They keep her comfy and focused while she makes her dream of working in a lab come true! Snuggle up and get ready to hit the books with Megan!

name: Meggie
meetText: Meggie edits videos to create little stories. When she times these sequences just right, they make her burst out laughing! Meggie also layers in her friend Sebi's sound effects to add some realism to the finished clip. Want to start some inside jokes with Meggie?

name: Mei Lien
meetText: Mei Lien is the voice of  the subway. Though she hates hearing herself announce delays, she takes pride in reminding passengers to stay safe and 'stand clear of closing doors'. Listen for her on your next ride and remember to mind the gap!

name: Mel
meetText: Mel loves dogs and spending time with her family. She goes camping and hiking on the weekends and makes the best s'mores you've ever had.

name: Melani
meetText: Melani is always on the move, she just can't sit still. Melani goes to school online and hates sitting down so her mom helps to keep her calm. She loves stickers and gets a sticker when she sits for an assignment. Do you want to see her collection?

name: Melania
meetText: Pizza, candy, and hot chips are some of Melania's favorite things. She loves to dance and spend time with her favorite aunt. She's always the first one to sign up for the Squishmallow talent show every year!

name: Melfy
meetText: Melfy's family double checks her Halloween candy so she doesn't eat anything she's allergic to. This little ghost has a tree nut allergy, so she stays away from certain candies, but her favorite sweet is sour chews! As long as Melfy can still enjoy those, she says she doesn't mind her allergies.

name: Melidy
meetText: Melidy just went snowboarding for the first time! She started off kind of nervous, then learned she was a natural. Now Melidy can't wait to keep practicing and even get some more snowboarding apparel. This 'Mallow loves cute winter gear!

name: Melina
meetText: Baking is one of Melina's/Summer’s favorite things to do, her second is eating the sweet treats she bakes. She takes advantage of all eight tentacles in the kitchen and makes some of the best peanut butter cookies you'll ever try.

name: Mellie
meetText: This environmentally conscious Squishmallow believes in looking after both body & mind. Mellie always has a positive outlook and can be found exercising and meditating before the sun has even come up! One day she dreams of owning her very own allotment so she can grow vegetables for Squishmallow friends.

name: Melly
meetText: Meet Melly. She and her best friend Neeona love doing arts and crafts and practicing their martial arts moves together in the park. They're currently making purple and pink best friend necklaces to go with their best friend bracelets and best friend earrings! Want to join?

name: Melrose
meetText: Melrose is the principal of an elementary school! He works to make sure school is a fun and inviting place where all the students feel welcome. Melrose even started a community garden he tends to with students in the afterschool program. They're growing pumpkins!

name: Merritt
meetText: Merritt loves to paint and recently began painting abstract portraits for her friends. She uses many of their favorite colors and adds glitter and feathers for a little pizazz. Would you like to be her next muse?

name: Merry
meetText: Hi! My name is Merry! My mini and I love to play tag and chase our tails in circles.

name: Melzie
meetText: Melzie carves butter sculptures right in her kitchen! She uses a butter knife and fork, or molds with her paws. Want to know what sculpture Melzie is entering in the contest at this year's fall festival? A towering princess castle with a moat!

name: Mia
meetText: Mia is quite the little camper. Who needs an RV when Mia is preparing for a camping trip with her best Squishmallows pals? She will be there to build the tent, make the s’mores, and create the memories.

name: Micah
meetText: Micah's favorite Valentine's Day tradition is skiing! He loves the winter months, and be able to teach all Squishmallow friends how to conquer their fears. Join him this year!

name: Micha
meetText: Meet Micha. He's all about balance. He loves pairing sweet and salty flavors or watching a comedy right after a scary movie! Sometimes he has a lazy day after a long week of busy work or a hike after a relaxing day by the pool! He's super chill and always goes with the flow!

name: Michaela
meetText: Meet Michaela. Thanks to her big heart and how much she cares for others, she is one of the sweetest Squishmallows around. If you're ever in need of a hug or a word of encouragement, she's your gal!

name: Michaela
meetText: Meet Michaela. She loves birds, bubblegum, and baseball. Michaela volunteers at a local shelter once a month and tries to teach the birds 'please', 'thank you' and 'home run!'.

name: Micky
meetText: Micky is full of life! She's a neighborhood coffee shop barista that likes making people laugh and smile. She loves to cook and take her dog Frita for a walk to the doggie park. She's an animal lover for sure and aspires to be a vet some day.

name: Midnight
meetText: Midnight is a tour guide and spends his days showing people around town and giving directions. Since moving out west, he loves to make friends as he shows them around Frontier Town! Midnight loves kicking up his heels with his best friend Stevie the Sheriff.

name: Mieko
meetText: Meet Mieko! Mieko is laid-back, relaxed, and cool as a cucumber! Nothing makes Mieko happier than sitting in the sun, and listening to some of her favorite tunes. When Mieko's in her happy place, she doesn't have a worry in the world! Want to chill with Mieko?

name: Mikah
meetText: Meet Mikah. She loves baseball, red velvet cake, and spending time with her friends. Mikah wants to be an archaeologist when she grows up, and her favorite city to visit is Rome. Fun fact about Mikah: she plays the recorder!

name: Miki
meetText: Miki goes thrifting every weekend—she never knows what she's going to find! Her weakness is jackets and backpacks, especially if they match her warm color profile. The best part is, Miki regularly donates back to thrift stores! For Miki, there's no better way to recycle and reuse.

name: Mila
meetText: Mila is making moves! She has found her healthy fix through creative recipe tips, which she uses to treat her friends and family! Ready to get happy and healthy with Mila?

name: Milaina
meetText: Meet Milaina. Horses and sports are her true loves, and  one day she hopes to open a rescue ranch. She dreams of a beautiful place tucked away in the hills, full of lush green fields, a babbling brook, and even a day spa for the horses and other animals to relax.

name: Milanda
meetText: Meet Milanda. She loves the outdoors and goes hiking almost every weekend. Her favorite way to enjoy nature is to bring along her friends Jason and Juniper for a fun adventure. Want to tag along with this hiking squad?

name: Mildred
meetText: Fish sticks and fudge brownies are two of  Mildred's favorite food. Her grandfather is a fisher man and makes the best fish sticks around. Mildred isn't allowed to use the oven yet, but one day soon she wants to make a brownie bigger then the oven, do you think she can do it?

name: Miles
meetText: Are you ready to meet Miles the computer guru? This dragon loves to learn about the technology world around him. When he is not behind the screen, he enjoys building robots with his friends. One day Miles aspires to be an engineer.

name: Miley
meetText: A friend to all, Miley is one of the sweetest Squishmallows around. Her love language is taking care of others. From a simple cooked meal to a last-minute road trip, Miley is the kind of friend always to ready to be by your side.

name: Millie
meetText: Meet Millie the adventurous astronaut. She shows us how to be brave and try new things, like going sky high on a roller coaster! Millie conquers her fears knowing that she will be stronger and more confident as she reaches for the stars.

name: Mills
meetText: Mills is a professional rock climber! He's been climbing trees and rock faces since he was a little 'Mallow, winning several national championships. Now Mills follows the good weather and focuses on free climbing mountains and boulders. Feeling brave? Join Mills on his next climb!

name: Milly
meetText: Get to know Milly! You can always find her monkeying around on and off the mat! Her family knew that she was destined for gymnastics. She was hanging on everything, of course! Now, she competes all over the world, and is expected to be the next big Olympian. It even lands on her birthday sometimes, which is August 1st! It’s fate, don’t you think?

name: Milo
meetText: Milo is the master of languages and speaks 10 fluently! His favorite pastime is studying extinct languages and teaching them to his friends. He dreams of becoming a linguist for the Smithsonian Institution, so he can combine his love of languages and history!

name: Milto
meetText: Milto dressed up as a jack-o-lantern this year! What do you think of his costume? This 'Mallow is going on a hayride tonight with his pal, and they all decided to dress up in their Halloween costumes to make the night extra special!

name: Mimi
meetText: Mimi loves to go on early morning walks and start the day singing with the birds. She loves starting each day fresh and tries to spread joy. Do you want to know her other favorite morning activity? Making pistachio pancakes and vanilla lattes.

name: Mimi the Strawberry
meetText: Achoo! Mimi sneezes more than your average 'Mallow, but her allergies don't stop her from sniffing flowers, or petting cute puppies! Want to know a secret? This is how Mimi maintains her pinky glow.

name: Mina
meetText: Who's that caticorn with the stethoscope? Mina, or Doctor Mina as she likes to be called. Mina wants to grow up to be a doctor like her mom, she wants to take care of people and teach them to stay healthy. Are you ready for your checkup?

name: Mina-Mae
meetText: Drawing, daydreaming, and standing up for others is the best way to describe this dragon. Mina-Mae is usually quite quiet but when it's time to speak up, her voice stands out from the crowd. Mina-Mae wants to use her artwork for good, do you want to hear her plans so far?

name: Mincha
meetText: Whoops! Mincha forgot where she put her keys - now she's looking everywhere! This 'Mallow uses sticky notes, alarms, anything she can to help jog her memory, but sometimes she still loses things. Micha even tied bells to the keychain. Will you help her find them?

name: Mindy
meetText: Mindy wants a hug when it gets cold outside, will you snuggle with Mindy to keep her warm?

name: Mint
meetText: Have you seen Miss Mint in action? She's a fast horse to beat, and when she wins she loves to parade around and show off her roses.

name: Minya
meetText: Minya travels the country in her camper van with her best friend, Brindall. They love stopping and bathing in natural hot springs, or driving to see super wildflower blooms. She captures everything on her camera and uploads it to her travel blog! Want to tag along?

name: Miper
meetText: Meet Miper. She's studying to become a marine biologist! Did you know 80% of the ocean is unexplored? Not once Miper gets through with it! She can't wait to explore the deep seas and discover all the new and exciting sea creatures waiting down there!

name: Mipsy
meetText: Need to get your life together? Call Mipsy! This detail-oriented axolotl is a professional organizer. Though some think she hates mess. Mipsy and her 16 different label makers can't get enough of it!

name: Miralou
meetText: Meet Miralou. Miralou is an interior designer and makes every room feel calming and perfectly balanced! Even though they're a pro now, they got their start by decorating their own room! How would you decorate your dream room?

name: Miranda
meetText: Miranda loves watermelon, collecting keychains, and making dance videos with her friends. This week she did a video dressed up as a dancing lobster. Miranda loves dressing up in silly costumes for her dance videos, what should she dress up as next?

name: Mireya
meetText: Unlike her cousin Austin, Mireya likes to keep two feet on the ground. She prefers the stage and dreams of starring in plays and maybe even a movie. Do you want to see her costume ideas?

name: Mirren
meetText: Not sure what your dream job is? Mirren can help! She's a career coach who loves to find job matches made in heaven. Mirren counsels 'Mallows at all levels. from seasoned professionals, to first-time job hunters She'll even teach you her fool-proof resume writing system! Ready to get hired?

name: Mischa
meetText: Meet Mischa, she designs roller coasters! Mischa loves adventure and tries to design the biggest (and scariest!) rides. Her favorite coaster design is a twisted triple loop that ends with a waterfall. Will you join her on her next roller coaster?

name: Misko
meetText: Meet Misko. He plays guitar and has toured the world performing with his bands. When he's not writing music, you can find him trading stocks and playing video games. His favorite food on and off the road is pizza, do you want to grab a slice?

name: Miss Vi
meetText: Miss Vi is one adventurous axolotl. She loves to sing, dance, and has a wonderful imagination. She loves snacks, so her nickname is the snackmonster. She might start her own comic adventure book, 'Adventures of the Snackmonster', would you read it?

name: Misty
meetText: Ready to take a ride on the wild side? Misty the mischievous mouse is the gal for you. Misty is not your typical mouse - though she is tiny, she is mighty. She loves hockey, baseball, NASCAR and horses! Her passion for riding aspires her to be an equestrian one day!

name: Mita
meetText: Meet Mita! She's on the shy side, but she loves nothing more than a good rock concert. You can usually spot her wearing a super cool band tee and listening to a new song. Maybe one day she'll start her own band! Want to join?

name: Mitch
meetText: Mitch benefits from all kinds of healing practices. After years on stage as a modern dancer, Mitch relaxes with pressure point massages on his webbed paws, and comforting yoga poses. You should see this platypus in standing tree pose! Want to join Mitch for a guided meditation?

name: Mitchard
meetText: If you're looking for Mitchard, you can find him at the ballpark! This bear loves to sit in the stadium all afternoon with a big of peanuts, muttering jokes and starting the wave. Mitchard comes off as the strong silent type, but once you get to know him, you'll find him cuddly as he is funny.

name: Mitchie
meetText: Say hello to Mitchie! If you're looking for Mitchie, she's probably flying through the air doing one of her famous trapeze tricks! Mitchie is an acrobat, and performs her acts high up in the sky each night. If you want to see the show, you can be Mitchie's guest of honor!

name: Mitzie
meetText: History may seem boring to some, but Mitzie loves it! She enjoys learning about everyday things that may have happened in books or movies and wonders how they might have impacted her life.

name: Mo
meetText: Hop in the car and buckle up, Mo is going to take you on an adventure. He's a tour guide and loves to drive around to show the hidden gems in the neighborhood.

name: Mollie
meetText: Get your stopwatch prepped and have your camera reday, this is going to be a close race! Mollie is a track star and runs almost as fast as a streak of lightning. She sets records at many races and has medals galore.

name: Molly
meetText: Molly loves a hug after she wins in chess! She practices very often because she loves hugs so much, will you celebrate with Molly and give her a hug?

name: Molly the Mushroom
meetText: Molly is the sweetest and most loving 'Mallow you'll ever meet. She has a special sense for knowing when you're feeling anxious, or lonely and is always there to cheer you up. She has a knack for singing bad karaoke and you can't help but crack up when she sings out of key!

name: Momo
meetText: Roses are red, violets are blue, if you like poems, Momo's the monkey for you!

name: Mondy
meetText: Introducing Mondy! If you like sweet treats, Mondy can whip you up a tray of the most delicious cookies ever! Mondy loves to bake, and especially loves decorating her cookies to fit the occasion. Her trademark treat is her "Pool of Peaches" cookie, which combines her siblings' love for both fruit and swimming! Want to try a bite?

name: Monica
meetText: Playing the drums is all Monica dreams about, she just wants to rock! Though she doesn't have a garage to practice in, one day soon she hopes to pick up a pair of sticks and let the music take control.

name: Monty
meetText: Monty loves to work with his paws. He builds his own sets and paints outdoor scenes for all his pals' short films. The painting almost look like real life! Monty even got his bud Mateo to help him make props. Monty can't wait until he's working as a production designer on a professional film set!

name: Mony
meetText: Meet Mony. She loves adventures and fruity drinks! Every year she and her friends migrate south for a tropical vacation to soak up the sun. She always packs extra sunscreen, her favorite striped swimsuit, and an interesting book to read on the beach! Want to join?

name: Moonie
meetText: Moonie is practicing for his scuba diving certification! He has two training dives left before he can scuba dives around coral reefs anytime. Moonie can't wait to see all colorful and beautiful underwater life, and made a driver's promise to interact with it carefully and respectfully.

name: Mopey
meetText: Meet Mopey. Mopey has an imagination like no other! Mopey is always writing down her ideas, so that one day she can make a whole book out of them. Right now, the only 'Mallow she shares her ideas with is her sister, Malia, but she'll tell you all about them too, if you'd like!

name: Morgan
meetText: Morgan may be a monster, but underneath that steely exterior lies a heart of gold! Charity work is his favorite pastime. Morgan is also an avid swimmer and hot air balloon enthusiast.

name: Morrison
meetText: Once the leaves change color in the fall, Morrison goes out leaf-peeping! He loves leisurely hiking a path near his house and taking in all  the beautiful colors. Sometimes Morrison picks up fallen leaves and presses them in one of his big books of cauldron spells.

name: Morty
meetText: Meet Morty, he might look a little strange on the outside, but on the inside he’s just like you. Morty loves talking to his friends about his home, outer space. His favorite earth food is birthday cake ice cream.

name: Mr. Orlen
meetText: Mr. Orlen leads a jazz parade through his town every Halloween! All musicians are invited to come and join in. Mr. Orlen's parades always end with a big outdoor party in front of the town cemetery and the music and dancing go on all night!

name: Mully
meetText: Say hi to Mully! Mully is a folk-music-loving mushroom. If you're ever feeling low, Mully will make you smile by strumming you a song on his banjo. If you're lucky, he might play you a tune on his harmonica too!

name: Murray
meetText: Have you met Murray? He dreams of being a master chef and is a bit of a mischief-maker. When Murray isn't assisting Gina or making his famous charcuterie boards, he's probably starting snowball fights with his cousin Misty.

name: Myrna
meetText: Meet Myrna. Myrna is an ambitious go-getter who tends to take on more than she can handle. She will say yes to any plan and any friend in need, but sometimes all she really needs is boundaries and a nice nap. Can you help Myrna set some boundaries and take a relaxing nap?

name: Myrtle
meetText: Myrtle likes pumpkin spice sorbet and caramel apple ice cream; she loves when fall flavors hit the store! When she was just a mini-monster Myrtle wanted to be a hair dresser and now she owns her own salon. Be sure to stop in for a fresh monster 'do.

name: Nabila
meetText: Have you met Nabila? This narwhal loves a good bargain and making someone's day. She is an expert when it comes to knitting and crocheting. Nabila uses her talent to make beautiful blankets, she donates many around the holidays for those in need.

name: Naddie
meetText: Meet Naddie. This thoughtful turtle is a team player and wants to be known for his collaboration and kindness. His love language, is "acts of service" so he is always willing to lend a helping hand. Do you have anything, Naddie can help with?

name: Nadine
meetText: Meet Nadine. This fabulous fox is the knitting queen! Nadine loves knitting and watching movies when it gets cold outside because she enjoys feeling cozy. She also loves scary movies, but she doesn't like to watch them at night. Whenever she gets scared she hides under one of the blankets she made, they help her feel safe. Would you like Nadine to knit you something?

name: Nafese
meetText: Nafese is an animal lover who couldn't hurt a fly, this is one 'Mallow who will stand up for everyone. Besides his kind and caring nature, Nafese is known for his super-speed. He might be one of the fastest 'Mallows around!

name: Nakia
meetText: Meet Nakia. This sleepy 'Mallow loves to nap in the long, soft grass of her favorite meadow. The sunshine keeps her nice and warm. When she's having a particularly good dream, her belly turns rainbow! She'll tell you all about it when she wakes up!

name: Nancy
meetText: Nancy is a busybody and always on the move. If you took a look at her calendar, you'd see she's booked for weeks in advance! She loves to organize clubs, group meetups, and other fun events with her friends. Nancy tries to make every second count, what should she plan next?

name: Naomi
meetText: Naomi lives deep in the sea and travels very far to see her friends. While she resides in the deep dark ocean, she loves jumping out of the water to catch some rays! Her friends love her for her positive attitude, and sparkly horn. Are you ready to catch some waves with Naomi?

name: Nash
meetText: Nash thinks about life's big and puzzling questions. Like, if a tree falls in the woods when no one is around, does it make a sound? When Nash and his buddy, Orin, get together, they talk for hours, and sometimes they only end up with more questions! What do you wonder about?

name: Nassim
meetText: Meet Nassim. This mellow 'Mallow spends mornings drinking chamomile tea and meditating to the sounds and nature in the garden. Nassim is an amazing listener and gives great advice. Just say the word and Nassim will put the kettle on!

name: Natalie
meetText: Natalie loves listening and dancing to music. Natalie has a record player that is very special to her, a gift from her dad! She loves having people over to listen to records and dance. What record do you want to hear next?

name: Nathan
meetText: Who loves oranges and tacos and is ready to keep you company? Nathan! This Squishmallow may be an introvert but he's always ready to curl up for a movie or have an adventure in the latest video game (as long as there are tacos nearby)!

name: Natty
meetText: Natty enjoys finding new ways of filming a scene. Last week, Natty rigged her camera to the front of her bike and peddled towards her friend Fitch while he was making a scary face. Natty thought this gave the scene a really cool effect!

name: Navina
meetText: Painting is one of Navina's favourite forms of self-care. She likes to use beautiful, bright colours that look almost life-like. She loves creating art that almost comes alive when you look at it! What should Navina paint next?

name: Navina
meetText: Painting is one of Navina's favourite forms of self-care. She likes to use beautiful, bright colours that look almost life-like. She loves creating art that almost comes alive when you look at it! What should Navina paint next?

name: Naya
meetText: Saxophones and seahorses are two things Naya loves. She just started playing the saxophone after begging her mom for weeks! Some of Naya's family play together in her garage so she wants to join the band.

name: Nebula
meetText: Meet Nebula. She loves painting and learning about microorganisms. Nebula's parents are scientists and they gave her a microscope kit to learn more about the tiny organisms in her world. Sometimes she paints the cool things she sees and shares them with her friends. Can you name a microorganism she should paint?

name: Nedison
meetText: Nedison builds houses! He believes every 'Mallow deserves to live in the house of their dreams, so Nedison and his team work hard to make sure that happens, Want Nedison to give you a tour of the latest house he helped build?

name: Neeona
meetText: Meet Neeona. She and her best friend Melly have known each other since they were little 'Mallows. They do just about everything together! Neeona loves making homemade pizza and always lets Melly sprinkle on the cheese and veggie toppings! Want a bite? They'd love to share!

name: Neely
meetText: Neely really lives her dreams. Sometimes a dream moment will actually happen to her in real life! Neely even started writing a dream journal so she could keep up. Her favorite dream-turned-into reality moment was winning first prize at her school's science fair!

name: Nefen
meetText: Meet Nefen. He loves climbing and doing stunts, one day he hopes to win an award for best stunt coordination! This year on Valentine's Day Nefen wants to go climbing and then get chocolate strawberry milkshakes. Would you like to join him?

name: Neha
meetText: Neha loves astrology—in fact, she runs an official Leo fan club! This dodo bird might be a proud Pisces herself, but she admires how bold and creative her favorite sign can be. Though she has plenty of Leo friends already, her horoscope predicts many more to come!

name: Nell
meetText: Nell is shy but bold! Her creativity shines through in everything she does in her graphic design work. When she isn’t behind her computer you can find Nell practicing her  DJ skills with her friend Suneetha, although if she is hungry she will drop everything for a huge bowl of pasta!

name: Nellie
meetText: Nellie is a sweet but strong little parakeet, who loves being with her 'Mallow family and friends. Nellie keeps in touch with faraway loved ones with handwritten letters, detailing all she sees from her favorite window perch. When she's not enjoying her perch, Nellie tends to her veggie garden!

name: Nessie
meetText: Meet Nessie. She is a 'Mallow Scout and is currently working toward her wilderness survival badge. Whenever she camps, she makes her special s'mores. Her secret recipe uses bananas and peanut butter instead of chocolate! She also loves telling campfire stories, so come, sit, and listen along!

name: Nestor
meetText: Nestor don't need solo time. This chicken nugget is his best self when he's surrounded by all his nugget pals. They even started a friendship group called the Bar-B-Crew! Nestor's squad even speaks in code, and everyone has a nickname. What do you want your nickname be?

name: Nia
meetText: Nia is an excellent cook and specialises in vegan cuisine. She loves to sing whilst cooking and thinks her wonderful voice adds to the flavour of her dishes. When she’s not in the kitchen Nia enjoys swimming with her friends and making a splash!

name: Niala
meetText: Niala is going to her bestie Coralie's birthday party, but she's feeling really shy and nervous. Big, loud gatherings are not Niala's cup of tea, but she wants to be there and show Coralie her love and support. Plus, Niala got the perfect present and she can't wait to watch Coralie open it!

name: Niamh
meetText: Niamh reads celebrity magazines every chance she gets. Sometimes it's in line at the grocery store, or waiting for a beauty appointment. They're a little bit of a guilty pleasure for Niamh, but that doesn't make it any less fun!

name: Nic
meetText: Nic is a night owl who loves to listen to music and see the latest pop-up events with his friends. He goes hiking every weekend and shares his new music with his friends.

name: Nichelle
meetText: Here comes Nichelle with fresh fruit and veggies for her daily juice. This 'Mallowe fresh presses a kale, mango, ginger juice first thing in the morning to keep her energized for spin class. Nichelle started juicing some time ago and still loves all the health benefits.

name: Nick
meetText: Nick is the volunteer of the century. He travels all over the world and donates time and money to make the world a better place. He works around the clock day and night to bring you the jolliest day of the year.

name: Nicky
meetText: Nothing makes Nicky's heart smile like watching a holiday movie with friends and family! She doesn't like cooking, but she LOVES to bake! When she's not rewatching movies or baking you can find her daydreaming and staying up late drinking chocolate peppermint milkshakes!

name: Nico
meetText: Food, art and dinosaurs are some of Nico's favorite things. He loves art class because he gets to be crafty and creative. When he's not working on a new art project, you can find him learning a new recipe in the kitchen or sharing some cool dino facts with his friends.

name: Nicole
meetText: Meet Nicole. She loves the color purple and laughing in the sun. Nicole is a fashionista and always looks very put together. She's a hard worker at a wholesale company and supports her team 100%.

name: Nicolita
meetText: Meet Nicolita! This charismatic unicorn is a total social butterfly. Whether playing softball with friends, helping patients at the local hospital, or entertaining guests with her world-famous charcuterie board, you can be sure where Nicolita goes, other 'Mallows follow.

name: Nightingale
meetText: If you're looking for a best friend, you're going to love Nightingale. While he seems cool on the outside, he's kind and funny and can always make you laugh. One thing you can always count on is that Nightingale will always share the snacks.

name: Nikita
meetText: Looking for some new music? Nikita is the owl for you! Discovering new music and sharing it with friends is Nikita's thing. She loves to go to live shows and wants to work in music when she grows up.

name: Nissa
meetText: Nissa prepares for the holidays far in advance! She always keeps an eye out for thoughtful gifts and spends time carefully wrapping each present. When this 'Mallow isn't out spreading joy, you can find her a boxing practice. Sit ringside for Nissa's evening class to watch her bob and weave!

name: Nitch
meetText: Nitch sings baritone in the North Pole choir, and just landed his first solo! Now he's extra excited for the annual holiday concert. Nitch keeps himself performance ready with daily power naps and spicy hot chocolate before rehearsal to warm up his vocal cords.

name: Nitro
meetText: Meet Nitro. This hammerhead loves to tell stories and wants to be a director one day. He is most excited about filming a documentary and helping bring awareness to stores you might now know. Give him a camera and watch him go!

name: Nixie
meetText: Energetic Nixie loves some friendly competition! Nixie's favorite activity is playing sky-tag with her friend Desmund. With the help of her incredible agility and small size, she is known as the best sky-tag player around!

name: Nixy
meetText: Meet Nixy. She's part of a rollerblade dance group with her friends! Every week they go to their favorite roller rink and practice their moves under the spinning disco ball. After, they order cheesy mozzarella sticks and hit the arcade! They have room for one more! Want to join?

name: Noah
meetText: Noah may be shy but there’s one thing he loves to talk about – baking cupcakes! Baking yummy cupcakes and giving them to his neighbors helps him feel less shy. Now Noah loves to share his cupcakes, would you like to try one?

name: Noe
meetText: Noe glows with quiet confidence. They're a 'Mallow of few words who hopes you won't mind saving conversation until it's really necessary. Noe writes in a daily journal to keep all their thoughts organized, and otherwise enjoys taking long naps and listening to talk radio.

name: Noelani
meetText: Every time Noelani enters a room, she lights it up with laughter! This 'Mallow knows that even her messy eating habits can garner some giggles, and there's nothing she loves more than making her friends and family smile. Well, except for pickles—pickles are a close second!

name: Noodles
meetText: Noodles can't wait for the slumber party! Noodles loves staying up late to watch movies and is bringing board games and cupcakes. Noodles loves playing board games and could play them all night! Do you want to join?

name: Nora
meetText: Meet Nora the Fairy! This magical mallow loves to write poems and notes to all of her pals. She leaves them in tiny message bottles around Squishville! So, if you’re having a bad day, a note from Nora and some magic pixie dust are sure to cheer you up!

name: Norbu
meetText: Have you met Norbu? This octopus is a ham, just wait until you hear their jokes! Norbu says the funniest things that would make you laugh even if you're in a bad mood. Norbu is thinking about taking improv classes, would you like to join?

name: Norma
meetText: Meet Norma. Norma loves eggnog ice cream and happens to be the best carpenter in the North Pole! Norma helps build everything from toys to furniture, she once made a sled that looked like a mini version of Santa's sleigh.

name: Norman
meetText: Glass blowing can be difficult in the North Pole, but this Squishmallow makes it look easy. Norman is the best glassblower around! When he’s not working, Norman’s favorite thing to do is snowboard with his friends.

name: Noro
meetText: Do you like scary movies? Noro sure does! From ghosts in the closet to monsters on the roof, this boo-happy cthulhu has seen it all. He hopes to direct a frightening feature of his own one day and can't wait to hear the screams in the theater!

name: Nova
meetText: Nova's favorite part of Spring is how beautiful the world looks. She loves the dreary, rainy days that bloom into a beautiful bursts of sunshine and color. Nova paints with watercolors and the colors of the spring inspires her work. Do you want to help Nova paint this spring?

name: Novi
meetText: Novi is a pizza lover, her nickname is Margherita and nothing makes her happier than extra cheese. She loves discovering new ways to make delicious, cheesy pizza inventions. Her latest obsession is pizza muffins. She could eat 12 at a time!

name: Nya
meetText: Need a good skincare routine? Nya is here for you! After struggling to find something that works, she created her own products for a healthy routine. She'll help your skin grow with her collections of creams, lotions, masks, & serums.

name: Nyla
meetText: Meet Nyla the book worm! This unicorn loves curling up with a good book. She loves popcorn and popsicles with a little spice! Nyla loves exploring around her and this year will take a hot air balloon ride for her birthday in June. Will you join the fun with Nyla?

name: Oakley
meetText: Bring your tools to hang out with Oakley! She's a do-it-yourself master and total crafting pro. Last week, she made a coffee table, and this week, she finished a new kitchen table! Oakley is always looking for her next project - maybe you could make something together?

name: Obu
meetText: This energetic frog loves everybody and everything, except loud noises. Obu gets startled and scared when she hears loud noises, so her job at the library is the perfect place for her. If Obu hears a loud noise, will you comfort her?

name: Oceana
meetText: Oceana gets ready for Día de los Muertos by preparing a bright and colorful altar! She makes sugar skulls, picks marigolds, and her bestie, Frieda bring stacks of papel picado to hang. Oceana invites you to help too—don't forget to bring the salt!

name: Octave
meetText: Octave spends most of his lounge time in the hot springs near his forest home. There, he gathers with friends and neighbors to talk or take naps. When the winter gets very cold, Octave rolls in the snow, then jumps into the hot spring. What an exhilarating experience!

name: Octavia
meetText: Meet Octavia. She has a helpful pep in her step just like her sister Jeanne! Octavia loves to paint nails and wants to open a nail salon that helps people. She wants to help people who cannot visit salons but doesn't know where to start. Will you help her?

name: Oden
meetText: You can spot one of Oden's giant sandcastles from way down the shoreline! They recently perfected their sandcastle technique by adding tiny shells and stones to hold towers in place. Today, Oden is working on a bridge and moat with twigs and seaweed. Want to see their latest creation?

name: Odessa
meetText: Do you love glittery lights and cocoa nights? It's time you met Odessa! She lives on a farm and every winter she transforms it into a glistening winter wonderland. She hosts skating parties, hot cocoa tastings, and even a sugar cookie decorating contest. Grab your scarf and join the festivities!

name: Isis
meetText: Isis/Odile loves the color green, pineapple smoothies, and zoning out to music. She just bought a record player and goes to the record store almost once a week! What album should she get next?

name: Odion
meetText: Please welcome Odion. Odion just transferred to a new school and is feeling a little shy, but he'd love to meet you! He's taking advanced computer science this year because it's his favorite subject. He even used to tutor computer science at his old school. Can you help find his next class?

name: Olalla
meetText: Olalla enjoys reading and writing. She is very good at writing history books and cares deeply about teaching and comic books. She also loves sports and is a hockey fanatic. Her perfect day would include reading and a tie-breaking hockey game, would you like to join her?

name: Olana
meetText: Olana works as a pediatric nurse! She loves practicing medicine, and her sweet nature makes her perfect for treating little 'Mallows. Olana even has a technique for delivering a painless vaccine. What's her trick? Olana numbs her patient's arm with an ice wrap then finishes with a super fun bandage!

name: Olav
meetText: Olav takes spring cleaning seriously. He turns over his home dusting and mopping, and donating old belongings. You've never seen a more productive blobfish! Olav loves fresh starts, and the beginning of a new season really motivates him. How does spring make you feel?

name: Oldin
meetText: Oldin's got eight arms, perfect for playing the xylophone! He loves fashion, travelling, and rocking out with his friends in their underwater punk band! Tickets are free and everyone's invited, so come out and rock on!

name: Olena
meetText: Olena is hosting a slumber party and invited her friends! There is just one rule: you have to wear a costume. Olena is wearing her favorite dinosaur ensemble! She has movies, popcorn, and even a facemask station set up, do you want to join?

name: Oleta
meetText: Meet Oleta. She photographs food for commercials and is the best in the industry. Oleta's compositions are always colorful, balanced, and perfectly in focus. The next time you see a food ad, take a closer look — it could be Oleta's work!

name: Olexa
meetText: Meet Olexa. Rainy days suit this introvert just fine. Olexa loves bundling up on cold blustery days and reading books, watching an old black and white film, or just listening to some relaxing lo-fi hip hop while the rain pitter-patters on the rooftop. Would you like to join them?

name: Olga
meetText: Original: Are you looking for a trivia partner? Olga is a history buff like you wouldn't believe. Olga comes from a family of librarians and learning new historical trivia happened almost daily. Can Olga join your team?

name: Olina
meetText: Meet Olina. This outoging octopus loves to bake cookies for Valentine's day, especially chocolate chip. This year she wants to bake a giant cookie in the shape of a heart! Do you think she can do it?

name: Olive
meetText: Olive doesn’t forget anything! How? She is constantly creating scrapbooks for every holiday, birthday party, and travel adventure with her friends and family! She is the first to capture every special moment with her favorite Squishmallows.

name: Oliver
meetText: Oliver likes to make handmade Valentines for his friends with glitter and his paws. Spend some time with him and make your own Valentines together.

name: Olivia
meetText: Meet Olivia. She is a talented photographer and has been known to spend hours in the darkroom developing film. She loves taking portraits of her friends and their pets. When she grows up, she wants to travel the world as a photojournalist!

name: Oliviana
meetText: A superstar is born! Meet the queen of rock Oliviana. She loves to jam with her band, and shreds her electric guitar at big venue concerts Oliviana blings out her costumes with eye-catching studs, so she shines during her performance. You can't miss her on stage

name: Ollie
meetText: Meet Ollie. She loves fairy tales, naps, and road trips with her family. Every year they pick a new destination by drawing names out of a hat. This year Ollie hopes she'll pick someplace magical and far away, maybe even a castle!

name: Olma
meetText: Can you guess how Olma makes her signature art prints? With fruit and veggies stamps! Cut apples, lemon slices, and celery ends are just the a few of Olma's stamping tools. She's working on a colorful collage right now. What fresh produce should Olma use for her latest work of art?

name: Omar
meetText: Original: Omar loves crystals, gems and jewelry and has an eye for finding the beauty in everything he does. He hopes to be a jeweler one day!

name: Omari
meetText: Omari loves to play games; card games, board games, video games, you name it! He just got a new set of playing cards, with cool holographic prints, he can't wait to try them out. Do you want to play a game with Omari?

name: Omri
meetText: Meet Omri. This amazing ornament loves to skate! Omri lives near a pond and when it gets cold enough they turn it into a skating rink. This year, Omri wants to add a fire pit to warm up and make s'mores. Do you want to join in the fun?

name: Onel
meetText: Congrats to Onel on his new job as a paralegal. It's going to take some time before Onel introduces himself to everyone in the office, but once he's comfortable, this 'Mallow isn't as shy as he seems. Onel's always the first to sign up for karaoke!

name: Onica
meetText: Meet Onica. Her favorite time of year is summer. She loves the warm weather and going to her local state fair to load up on all of the wacky food with her dads! This year, she wants to try the hamburger with jelly-filled donuts for buns!

name: Opal
meetText: Meet Opal. She's the only girl in a family with 4 older brothers who love her dearly. Last year they gave her a pink sparkly dirt bike! She especially loves to ride after the rain so she can splash around in the really big puddles.

name: Ophelia
meetText: Meet Ophelia. This sweet Squishmallow loves everything theatre, one day she wants to be an actress and direct her own plays. Ophelia loves being on stage and she knows that she would be a great director. She helps with the pageants her school puts on every spring.

name: Orazlo
meetText: Orazlo works as a vet tech in the North Pole, He's responsible for keeping the reindeer fit and healthy all year round so they can be ready for the holiday season. With all his animal knowledge. Orazlo started invemting new sleigh gear for the reindeer. Think Santa will approve his designs?

name: Oriam
meetText: Meet Oriam. For this 'Mallow nothing beats the quiet stillness of nature. Oriam loves going off the grid, hiking deep into the forest, and setting up camp beneath the forest canopy. Her favorite campground snack is peanut butter, banana, and toasted sandwiches.

name: Orin
meetText: Orin is a silly orange; he responds to questions with more questions and on Fridays, he tries to do everything backwards. Thankfully his friends like his silliness and play along with his jokes.

name: Orphie
meetText: Meet Orphie. He's going to sleep away camp for the very first time! He's excited but a little nervous. He's never been away from his mom's this long, so he'll miss them a lot. But Orphie knows he'll make new friends and memories that will last for a lifetime.

name: Orzella
meetText: Meet Orzella. She loves to quilt and spend time with her friend Grant. They have quilting parties and catch up on their favorite nostalgic cartoons. On the weekends Orzella loves to bake, if you're lucky you might get to try one of her famous blueberry Danishes!

name: Oshun
meetText: Meet Oshun. This flexible 'Mallow is a talented gymnast. You can catch her bouncing around the reef doing somersaults and cartwheels! She may not always stick the landing but she always has fun! For her next move, she wants to master the balance beam!

name: Ottie
meetText: Ottie works at Peety's clothing boutique. She closes the shop nightly and leaves everything in tip-top shape for the morning. Ottie loves to help every customer and is skilled at creating outfits for every 'Mallow. Come by the shop and Ottie will put together some looks just for you!

name: Otto
meetText: Are you ready to pick out the perfect pumpkin? Make sure you visit Otto's farm — he grows the best pumpkins around! Otto wins the contest for the largest pumpkin almost every year. Last year his prize-winning pumpkin was bigger than a house!

name: Ova
meetText: Meet Ova. She loves movie marathons, slumber parties, and roller coasters. She's scared of heights, so she might take some time to get on the ride! Will you help her get over her fear?

name: Owen
meetText: Owen is a gift of a friend. He has a heart of gold and hopes to positively affect others as a therapist in the future. He was adopted into the wonderful family of Hoot and Holly; the three ‘Mallows in a pod.

name: Oz
meetText: Lights, camera, action, Oz is ready to take center stage! This succulent can't wait to show off his stuff. With his powerful voice and dance moves, this 'Mallow' is sure to keep you grooving to music all day!

name: Pace
meetText: Pace entered a talent show at school! She's going to perform a scene from one of her favorite musicals and is rehearsing the dance moves every day with her best pals. Pace and her friends are going to lip sync the lyrics and wear matching outfits! Will Pace see you at the talent show?

name: Paco
meetText: Paco is quite the entertainer among his friends. He loves to be up to date on current events and loves sports. His favorite sport is soccer and he hopes to become a sports broadcaster when he grows up.

name: Paddock
meetText: If you're in need of luck, Paddock could be the mallow for you. Though he doesn't call himself, good things tend to happen when he's around.

name: Paden
meetText: Paden lives for Saturday morning cartoons. He wakes up extra early so he doesn't miss a single one! For Paden, watching cartoons is more than just fun, as he's also learning valuable storytelling skills for when he starts creating his own animated shows. Want to see Paden's story ideas?

name: Paedra
meetText: Paedra is a beautiful panda-corn who also happens to be the best big sister. She almost always has a solution to any problem. Though she isn't much older, she is very wise and helps her siblings learn through stories.

name: Paige the Owl
meetText: Unknown

name: Paige
meetText: Many are sweet, but Paige is quite spicy. She is the little firecracker of her friend group, and loves to show it. Paige always takes the spotlight with her supportive Squishmallows pals front and center.

name: Paisley
meetText: Paisley loves makeovers, this year she had a spooky slumber party for her birthday. Can you guess what they did? Movie marathon and makeovers of course! One day maybe Paisley will get to do makeovers for the movies.

name: Paislynn
meetText: Meet Paislynn. It may seem basic to some, but she really loves fall. Hearing the crunch of leaves under her feet, wearing warm cozy sweaters, and the feeling that comes from being with friends are just a few of her favorite things.

name: Palmer
meetText: Have you seen the latest Mallow sculpture? It was designed by your guy, Palmer! He's an eclectic kind of goat, creating amazing statues and sculptures. When he's looking for some inspiration, he heads to the beach at sunrise to surf and meditate.

name: Paloma
meetText: This pegasus loves to create art by welding! She works with her brothers in their family welding business, and although she is still learning how to use the big lasers, she loves to weld together scraps and make beautiful art from nothing.

name: Pam
meetText: An aspiring florist, Pam is a natural at creating the most beautiful bouquets. Make sure to place an order with her before Valentine's Day!

name: Pama
meetText: Pama reads so many books that there are stacks of them everywhere in her home! Pama prefers classic novels and short stories, but she will read anything if you recommend it. This 'Mallow even has a collection of encyclopedias she will sometimes open up and read just for fun!

name: Pammy
meetText: Pammy is a small town pig who recently moved to a new city, but she's still a little nervous to venture out. She's thinking about learning pottery to meet new 'Mallows or maybe a dance class. Could you show her around?

name: Pandora
meetText: Ever since Pandora’s parents invited a magician to perform at her last birthday party, she’s dreamed of nothing other than learning how to do magic. When Pandora grows up, she plans on performing in front of large crowds and dazzling them with her slight of hand!

name: Pania
meetText: Meet Pania. She likes to run and do obstacle courses, she is all about testing her limits as an athlete. Pania wants to be a track coach when she grows up so she can inspire others to work hard and set goals.

name: Panja
meetText: Meet Panja. She helps her besties, Gina and Ruby, whip up the best hot cocoa in the North Pole. Panja and her squad sing holiday tunes while they make tasty treats and pick out gifts for friends, they may not always be in tune but they sure have a great time.

name: Patrick
meetText: Meet Patrick, this Squishmallow is one happiest you'll ever meet. He gets a little grumpy when his belly isn't full but once he eats he's back to his happy Squishmallow self.

name: Patricia
meetText: Patricia is trying on new outfits for a big event next weekend! What do you think of this blue and purple jumper? Nothing energizes Patricia like a shopping spree with her 'Mallow pals. Her bestie, Cristina, is picking out some jewelry to complete Patricia's look!

name: Patty
meetText: Patty's family has the most popular booth at the springtime farmer's market. She loves to help them out, but when the work is done, she loves to stomp in puddles.

name: Patterson
meetText: Patterson tried out for his school's football team today! He fumbled the ball once during tryouts, but otherwise did a good job. Patterson hopes to start playing now as a freshman so he can make the varsity team. Can you imagine Patterson sporting one of those leather jackets?

name: Paul
meetText: Paul loves to play ball! Since bellyball is his favorite sport, Paul is very excited to be starting an official Bellyball League. Hopefully, his friends will join so that they can see Paul's incredible curveball!

name: Paulie
meetText: Who is creative, loves to dance and while he DJs, and tries to make a difference in the world? Paulie! This Philanthropic pup hopes to make the world a better place through music and being kind. Maybe one day he'll start a nonprofit that focuses on music and giving back

name: Paulita
meetText: Paulita is the nap queen. She loves to take naps almost all day and then spends her free time singing, painting, or eating her favorite food: chicken nuggets.

name: Paulton
meetText: Meet Paulton. This chocolate bar is the perfect mix of sweet and spicy. Paulton is a digital diva who brings joy to his friends, especially at work. When he's not putting out fires you can find him unwinding with his plant haven or on his way to brunch.

name: Pavlo
meetText: Meet the great and powerful Pavlo! The most powerful thing about Pavlo is his stomach! He can eat anything and everything even when he's full he goes back for seconds. It's no wonder his favorite restaurants are buffet style!

name: Pax
meetText: Pax spends hours in the studio working on his music. His dreamy soundscapes will transport you out of this world with soothing synths that he mixes with nature sounds that he records on his hikes. So relax, put your headphones on, and your mind at ease!

name: Paxton
meetText: Meet Paxton. He loves Malloween but this perky pumpkin is afraid of the dark! Paxton has a pirate ship night light that makes spooky pirate ships sounds. One day he hopes to overcome his fear of the dark, would you help him conquer his fear?

name: Pearl
meetText: Pearl loves strawberry milkshakes and watching the sunset. She sings her favorite songs in the shower and dreams of one day performing on stage.

name: Pearson
meetText: Meet Pearson! Pearson lives with his grandparents and loves mac n cheese, motorbikes, and fly fishing. Even though he doesn't like fish, Pearson loves to spend time with his grandma because she taught him how to fish! He's not old enough to ride motorcycles yet but one day he will!

name: Pedi
meetText: Meet Pedi. This octopus’s has a taste for food and adventure. Pedi hopes to travel the world as a chef someday. She wants to learn how to cook with new or different ingredients and seeing exciting things along the way. Do you have a recipe to share with Pedi?

name: Peety
meetText: Watch Peety strut on by wearing her own unique designs! This pretty pig owns a boutique in town lined with all her stylish creations. Peety's style is whimsical, timeless, and flattering on all 'Mallow shapes and sizes. Let Peety show you around her store!

name: Pei
meetText: Pei is an amazing navigator and understands the world unlike any other. Their sense of direction and advice is almost mystical. With a map in hand and a mind full of ideas, Pei leads all of their friends in the right direction.

name: Pell
meetText: Pell loves to shop and he's a serious impulse buyer! This 'Mallow can't help but pick up an item or two at the register, or dig through the crates at the front of the store for any fun-looking knick-knacks. Check out his collection of trading cards!

name: Penelope
meetText: Loveable, cuddly and oh so cute, Penelope is the perfect Valentine. She loves to share her sweets with those around her, and is great at making them herself.

name: Penny
meetText: Penny is the total opposite of her brother, Scout. Her paintings are pure perfection and she never colors outside of the lines. Last year her painting won first place at her school's Easter Art competition. She's ready to win again!

name: Pep
meetText: Meet Pep. He's a delivery driver who loves to sing while he's working. He may be tone deaf but that doesn't stop him! Pep loves blasting music so he can sing and dance along on his route. Next time you see him, give him a wave.

name: Pepper
meetText: Pepper loves waltzing in the ballrooms of sunken cruise ships. Sometimes, she even imagines she was a glamorous passenger on board—Princess Flipperina of Whales! Can you help her practice her box step?

name: Percy
meetText: Ready, set, action! Percy loves to come up with extreme storylines for his action figures. He's also interested in robotics, and is learning how to code!

name: Perkin
meetText: Everyone in town knows Perkin! He lives a quiet life, but you can usually find him out in the evenings after the sun has set. Don't be alarmed by his glowing red eyes, because Perkin is as pleasant as any 'Mallow you'll meet. So if you see him around, go ahead and say 'hello'!

name: Perni
meetText: Meet Perni. This 'Mallow is an expert bird watcher. He keeps a journal and writes down all the different types of birds he sees on his hikes. He keeps native plants around his house to attract his favorite bird of all, the humming bird! Grab some binoculars and join him!

name: Perry
meetText: Hang 10 with Perry for the day and you’re sure to become an avid surfer! When he’s not surfing you can find him relaxing near the beach enjoying frozen yogurt and waxing his board for the next wave.

name: Persefanie
meetText: Meet Persefanie. She loves bubbles, bicycles, and beach volleyball. Persefanie spends her summers at the beach perfecting her serve and playing in the sand, she just added streamers to her bike and has a little bell to let others know she's passing by. Will you play volleyball with Persefanie?

name: Peter
meetText: Yes, you guessed it! Peter is quite the cuddly pig. He loves the winter time, and cuddling up with other pigs in a blanket. When he’s not getting cozy, you can find him at a wrestling match or giving piggy back rides to his friends. Peter loves making new friends and is very good at keeping the old ones, too.

name: Peterson
meetText: Peterson drives a big pickup truck—the same one he's been driving for years. Sometimes it goes on the fritz and Peterson has to make repairs, but this cookie doesn't mind one bit. His truck helps everyone around town with moves of all sizes, making Peterson's pickup truck as beloved as he is.

name: Petey
meetText: Meet Petey. This playful pirate is always ready for fun. He tends to get distracted very easily but he makes an excellent first mate! His favorite kind of adventure? Sharing the code for the latest scary movie with his friends.

name: Petina the Polar Bear
meetText: Petina plays the trumpet and loves baseball. When she grows up, she hopes to be a team manager one day! Her favorite stadium snack is caramel popcorn with chocolate drizzle, do you want to go to a baseball game with Petina?

name: Petina
meetText: Lasagna and painting are two of Petina's favorite things. She started painting as a mini 'Mallow to map out her feelings and discovered how good it made her feel. She looks forward to sharing art and lasagna with her foster family whenever Terry comes to town.

name: Petra
meetText: Petra loves gel pens, striped socks, and scary movies. She has movie marathons with her friends and even started a movie club at school. Maybe one day she can direct her own scary films.

name: Petrina
meetText: Meet Petrina. Lasagna and painting are two of her favorite things, Petrina says good food and art are necessary for her self-care routine. Her dream is to travel and paint after a leisurely lunch, where should she go first?

name: Petula
meetText: Petula's personality is just as beautiful and bold as she is! She's the perfect 'Mallow to ask for fashion or makeup advice because she's always on top of the latest trends. She loves bringing out the beauty from within, do you want to get glam with this unicorn?

name: Peyton
meetText: Peyton is an environmental advocate who wants to help the world go green! She dreams of becoming an environmental lawyer who will protect endangered animals, combat pollution and save the worlds coral reefs. She's a great friend to take on your next beach cleanup!

name: Philip
meetText: Philip is an artist at heart who draws his inspiration from everyday life - from photography to watercolors to pottery. He has been known to feature his friends in his artwork, so put on your best smirk and prepare to become the next Mona Lisa!

name: Philipe
meetText: Meet Philipe. He loves taking long road trips up the coast with his friends in his bright blue convertible! They have perfected their road trip playlist and always playing funky tunes! Come join! They make tons of pit stops load up on yummy saltwater taffy and fun souvenirs!

name: Philippe
meetText: Philippe enjoys a good game of hopscotch with his friends, especially Marco. He also enjoys taking pictures of his family and friends, which he will be doing this Valentine’s Day. Join him!

name: Philomena
meetText: Philomena believes everyone deserves more sleep—that's why she's running for mayor! This siesta-loving politician hopes her platform of guaranteed nap time and memory foam for all strikes a chord with voters. If elected, Philomena promises to put tiredness to rest!

name: Phoebe
meetText: Phoebe is the fraternal twin sister of Fifi. While her sister likes to travel the world, Phoebe prefers discovering the world through the books she reads. She read over 1,000 and is the perfect buddy for story time!

name: Phoenix
meetText: Phoenix is a kind-hearted and clever unicorn. When she's not spending time with her unigals, she volunteers her at the hospital. She loves playing boardgames with patients and is always up for a challenge. Are you ready to get your game on with Phoenix?

name: Phyllis
meetText: Have you met Phyllis? She is captain of the swimming team and can't wait to get back in the pool. If she could, she would turn into a mermaid!

name: Phylo
meetText: Phylo is an amazing painter. He spends hours in his studio painting abstract shapes and landscapes, He loves to create vibrant colors and textures! When he's not painting, you can find him out dancing with his friends or ordering yummy take-out.

name: Piaxa
meetText: Meet Piaxa. She may be out of this world but she is one curious creature. Piaxa loves to spend hours reading in her blanket forts. She loves to read mysteries, adventure books, and even comics, do you have any recommendations to share?

name: Pierogi
meetText: Pierogi is not only a plumber—he's also an amateur magician! This wannabe wizard loves performing tricks for his customers. Though they don't always go according to plan, Pierogi the Magnificent never fails with his signature spell: Abracaday, leak go away!

name: Pierre
meetText: Mozart, Beethoven, and Bach are some of Pierre's favorite composers.  One day he hopes to have one of his own compositions played at the Sydney Opera House.

name: Pierre
meetText: Meet Pierre. They love slithering along the paths by their house looking for rare flowers, plants, and trees! One time they even found a carnivorous plants. Want to tag along with Pierre?

name: Pilar
meetText: Ready for a relaxing afternoon with your friend Pilar? Lace-up your shoes and off you go! Pilar likes to start off with a little hacky sack or disc golf followed by a snack, what do you want to do first?

name: Pinxelle
meetText: Pinxelle is a bit shy, she enjoys keeping to herself. She has a small group of friends, they've known each other since they were mini 'Mallows. Even if they become busy, they make time for each other and always have each other's backs.

name: Piper
meetText: Are you ready to meet hyper Piper? Piper is the queen of ice skating, and known for her fun dance moves and outrageous outfits! She especially likes to dress up for her birthday on December 15. She flies down the hills on her fluffy belly and holds the world record for creating the best igloo in all the world. If she’s not playing in the snow, you can find her having cocoa with her friend Puff or scoping out new books to read in the local library.

name: Pippie
meetText: Meet Pippie! If you're ever feeling low, Pippie's warm and kind personality is sure to turn your day around! Do you want to know what secret ingredient makes Pippie so sweet? Smiles!

name: PJ
meetText: Look out world, because PJ is about to put his name on buildings near and far! An aspiring architect, PJ has a knack for creative design, organization, and knowing how to add a special touch to just about everything he does.

name: Pleyton
meetText: Meet Pleyton! Even though this 'Mallow is cold-blooded, his favorite places are cold and snowy. While all his friends are heading to the beach, he headed to the mountains with a warm jacket and lots of layers! No matter where he goes, Pleyton make sure to bring his bestie — Amalie! Want to come on a chilly adventure with Pleyton?

name: Poleena
meetText: Have you ever walked into a room and forgotten why? This happens to Poleena all the time. She's constantly forgetting where she put her keys or where she last saw her eyeglasses, (they're on her head). She may be forgetful, but she always remembers to have fun!

name: Polly
meetText: Polly likes pancakes, strawberry ice cream, and going to the amusement park. When they go, her whole family wears matching t-shirts and they pack a huge picnic lunch. Polly wants to visit amusement parks all over the world, where should she go next?

name: Pommie
meetText: Grab your tiara and get ready for awards season! Pommie hosts unforgettable award show parties all winter, and while getting dressed up isn't required, it is encouraged! You can except bite-sized appetizers, nomination ballots, and cheerful shouts during the ceremony. Will you RSVP?

name: Ponderosa
meetText: Have you ever met a seafaring unicorn? Now you have! Ponderosa flies ahead of her ship to watch for land, bad weather, and scout for danger. On her down time, she enjoys rootbeer floats and sharing stories with the crew.

name: Poplina
meetText: Poplina is super sweet and just a little shy. Although it may take her a minute to open up to new 'Mallows, once she does, you'll get to know her very quickly. Poplina has all sorts of stories, did you know she's been to eight countries?

name: Poppy
meetText: Put on your dancing shoes because Poppy is here to show off some moves. Poppy and her dance partner Maddox are the king and queen of the dance floor. Gliding and grooving around, they are a sight to see. Poppy chooses the music based on her mood.

name: Posey
meetText: Mini-golf and frisbee are two of Posey's favorite games, she could play for hours! Last year she had a mini-golf birthday party, they played mini-golf until it was almost dark. That was the best birthday ever.

name: Poxiana
meetText: Poxiana is all ready for the slumber party. She has her toothbrush, a sleeping bag, and a sleeping mask that all match her costume. She loves all things unicorn! She can't wait to see her friends and all their costumes. What costume will you be wearing?

name: Preeti
meetText: Look—no bones! When it comes to bending over backwards, Preeti is a total pro. In fact, this super flexible slug is a limbo world champion. With no knees or vertebrae holding her back, it's easy to see why! How low can you go?

name: Prescott
meetText: This panda loves to show her love by giving thoughtful. handmade gifts! Every Valentine's Day. Prescott gives her family themed presents that she's been working on for months. Last year, everyone got hand-knit socks and an invitation to a family ice skating party! Would you hit the ice with Prescott?

name: Prescott the Penguin
meetText: Come chill with Prescott! Prescott loves the cold, so winter is her favorite season. She and her friends Piper and Puff all like to wear their matching parkas and have photoshoots together in the snow!

name: Prim
meetText: Prim loves looking at the sky, she is fascinated by life above her head! Each dawn, Prim wakes up early so she can watch the little bit of night sky turn into the next beautiful day. At night-time, it's almost impossible to get Prim to go to sleep because she's obsessed with the stars!

name: Prince
meetText: Original: Prince is considered royalty on the playground. You can’t miss him doing flips and tricks across the monkey bars with his adventurous Squishmallows pals. Want to join in on the fun?

name: Priscilla
meetText: Have you met Priscilla? This perky peacock is always ready to lend a helping hand, there’s not much she can’t do! Priscilla loves to spend time with her friends and finds many new activities for them to try.

name: Prital
meetText: Meet Prital! Prital owns a small business specializing in organic, loose leaf teas, and she creates unique blends with herbs picked fresh from her garden! Her favorite fusions include lavender and sage. Get ready for afternoon tea with Prital!

name: Priya
meetText: Ready for a fun adventure in the clouds? Join Priya and Corinna their next quest! Priya's dad built them a clubhouse that looks out to the stars, so by day they watch for monsters in the clouds and by night, they go on space adventures with their telescopes.

name: Puff
meetText: It's time to meet Puff, the tech-fanatic penguin! He is the internet's number one fan and is always searching for the newest thing. He's also into robotics, and has the most fun when he's either building or coding.

name: Pyle
meetText: When the sun goes down. Pyle, the tax accountant becomes DJ Pyle Remix, the hottest record-spinner in town. From disco to dubstep this far-out fungus loves helping 'Mallows dance the night away, In fact they sometimes boogie 'til breakfast! Got any requests?

name: Quartz
meetText: Are you ready for a gouly adventure? Grab a flashlight and pack a bag, it's time to join Quartz on a ghost hunt! Quartz wants to befriend a ghost and hopes one day soon she can meet one.

name: Quest
meetText: Quest isn't a know-it-all—she just knows it all! Legend has it this owl has been giving advice for centuries. From princesses unsure of frogs and chefs unsure of ingredients, her ancient wisdom has led few astray. Need help? Just ask!

name: Quigley
meetText: You're invited to Quigley's farm! Quigley's days are spent outside tending his vegetable patch and fruit orchard — he eats right off the land! This 'Mallow works hard but always finds the time to enjoy the sunset from his back porch.

name: Quincy
meetText: Known by his friends as "Question King Quincy", Quincy is one of the most inquisitive mallows around. Quincy asks some of the hardest questions and hopes that one day, he'll be able to answer them!

name: Quinick
meetText: Quinick makes jewelry for fun, but his sibling, Nassim, is encouraging him to start a website for all of his shiny creations. Now Quinick is starting this little side business! All of his designs are minimal, dainty, and only use the best metal and stones. Would you like to request a custom piece made by Quinick?

name: Quinn the Fox
meetText: Quinn loves to play hide and seek! She is fun and mischievous, and loves to skip through warm sunny meadows with her friends.

name: Quinn
meetText: Quinn loves iced tea with lemon, sugar cookies, and making eggplant parm. She is an introvert and a foodie who loves to read about food from all over the world. Do you have any good food stories to share?

name: Rachel
meetText: Meet Rachel. She's outgoing, sweet, and here for fun. Rachel loves hanging with friends, getting lost in a good show, and spending the weekend on the water. Catch this mushroom on the boat jamming and surrounded by friends or curled up on the couch watching TV.

name: Rada
meetText: Meet Rada. Rada is passionate and driven, and one day wants to be the CEO of her own company. She has everything ready, except a business idea. Have any suggestions?

name: Rahima
meetText: You've probably never met a 'Mallow as strong as Rahima. She's training for the biggest competition around, where she hopes to compete in the weightlifting category. Even though her muscles might intimidate you, she's as sweet as she is strong.

name: Raina
meetText: Meet Raina. She enjoys working with numbers and solving puzzles. She creates a plan of action and uses that to get things done. Even her garden was designed with a beautiful blueprint in mind! If you need a plan, she's you gal!

name: Raisy
meetText: Meet Raisy. Last week, she dozed off and had a crazy dream, she dreamt that she discovered a new galaxy and that 'Mallows could fly around in space! She flew off into the stars and then she woke up. Maybe one day it can come true!

name: Rambly
meetText: Rambly is a crafty cat and her medium of choice is paper! This Halloween, she's folding up a whole bunch of paper lanterns with spooky cutouts in seasonal colors. But year-round, Rambly's favorite paper craft is origami—check out the peace sign she just made!

name: Ramon
meetText: How do you like your eggs, Ramon's making breakfast! Ramon has a big family who loves to eat and even though he's the youngest, he is an excellent cook.

name: Ramona
meetText: Meet Ramona, the hopscotch queen! She loves milkshakes (of every flavor) and wants to be a bus driver like her dad when she grows up.

name: Ramsey
