meetText: Firetrucks, lemonade and video games are some of Ramsey's favorite things. Though he's not allowed, he could play video games all day! Ramsey wants to be a firefighter when he grows up, he lives near a fire station and loves to wave when the trucks drive by.

name: Randall
meetText: Geology student Randall was a little confused when he went to a heavy metal show and saw a rock band playing. Though he was disappointed they never talked about iron or copper, Randall loved the music— in fact, he just bought their CD! Rock out with Randall!

name: Randy
meetText: If you can't find Randy, look up! Randy is a rock climbing expert, capturing scenic beauty from elevations above. But if you're lucky he'll invite you to be his next adventure buddy!

name: Raquel
meetText: Raquel is a dreamer. She dreams of a colorful world full of happiness and peace! Some may say her head is in the clouds, but this pegacorn promises her dream will become reality with extra hard work, patience and acceptance.

name: Rashad
meetText: Rashad loves basketball, music, and taking midday naps. Rashad is the founding member of the music club at school and wants to own his own record label one day. They meet on Saturdays, do you want to join?

name: Rattles
meetText: Rattles loves being a dance instructor. He is great at helping others to feel confident as he teaches them how to twist and turn on the dance floor! When not dancing, Rattles can be a bit clumsy. He's had to replace his cell phone three time already this year! Will you attend Rattles' next class?

name: Rayen
meetText: Rayen has an eye for design. Many other 'Mallows try to keep up with her latest fashion trends. She hopes to use her sketches and designs on the runway one day! Can she design something for you?

name: Rayford
meetText: Who loves ska music? Rayford does! Turn the volume to 11 and join him in his second favorite pastime: cooking! There's nothing he loves more than making a 5-course meal for others with his very best friend, Corlita!

name: Raylor
meetText: Meet Raylor. This perky pup loves hiking in the mountains, going on camping trips, and playing in the snow. Raylor recently moved from the city to a mountain town and can't wait to live his new life.

name: Ravalia
meetText: Ravalia is the life of the party - just like her famous fruit punch! She loves to add fresh fruit, tiny umbrellas and serves with the funkiest straw she can find. Try a batch at the next game night and get ready for charades and a good time!

name: Reese
meetText: Reese loves ants on a log with crunchy peanut butter and playing in the mud. Spring is her favorite season; it rains and provides plenty of mud puddles for her to jump in.

name: Refalo
meetText: Refalo forgets how he started restoring vintage lunch boxes, he just knows he hasn't stopped working on them for decades! There's a whole community of collectors who need help refreshing chipped paint or rusty handles. Refalo owns a few vintage lunch boxes himself, but he prefers repairing them for others.

name: Regan
meetText: Regan is the king of hip hop, aspiring to one day make it as a producer in the music business. He's made a few albums at home with his friends, and hopes they'll be out on the airwaves soon!

name: Reggie
meetText: There goes Reggie! He's a world-class figure skater all over the world. Reggie performs freestyle movements of jumps, spins, and flips. His dream is to one day compete in the global figure skating competition. Will you be there to cheer on Reggie?

name: Regina
meetText: Meet Regina. She loves the world of theatre and wants to be a set designer when she grows up. She enjoys working on the set and making sure everything looks perfect. One time, this silly Squishmallow build a castle out of soda cans!

name: Reginald
meetText: Captain of the lacrosse team, Reginald is a fearless leader. He loves to spend time with his teammates on and off the field, especially when it involves watching one of his favorite movies!

name: Regz
meetText: Meet Regz. He loves loading up on art supplies and green tea mochi and drawing colorful, kooky characters in his sketchbook! When he grows up he wants to animate his very own cartoon show about an alien rock band from outer space! With Regz, you never know what he'll draw next!

name: Reid
meetText: Some days you just need a little advice, and that is Reid's secret weapon. They're a guidance counselor! Reid helps their students with challenges both at school and at home even if they all need is a friendly listener. Rumor has it, Reid might even give you a sticker or two

name: Reina
meetText: Meet Reina, this fabulous butterfly loves fashion, fun and drawing. Her love for fashion inspires many of her beautiful creations. She is outgoing and loves to spend time with friends, maybe one day you will see her artwork on the cover of a magazine.

name: Remmy
meetText: Remmy has the reputation of being a "Gnome-It-All." She is an expert in trivia and quiz games, but Remmy really shines in the Squishmallows Spelling Bee. She's won 6 years in a row and nobody has even come close to beating her!

name: Renard
meetText: Renard is a natural-born leader who has a knack for bringing others together. They love planning summer picnics and organizing freeze tag games in the park. Everyone is invited and encouraged to bring a friend. Renard always brings plenty of food for everyone so come join!

name: Renata
meetText: Renata is a ballet dancer who  loves to show off her skills. She's been dancing since she was just a mini mallow. Her favorite snack after a weekend performance is a big plate of cheesy ravioli and chocolate milk.

name: Renate
meetText: Meet Renate. She wants to be a surgeon when she grows up. Even though being in the hospital can be scary sometimes, she wants to be a superhero to some lives. Who knows, maybe she can make medical history? Paging Doctor Renate!

name: Renee
meetText: Renee is one fun 'Mallow. She loves calligraphy, drawing, and playing lacrosse! Her favorite colors are purple and blue and she loves a good movie night. What can Renee draw for you?

name: Reshma
meetText: Grab a helmet and grab a basket, it's time for a ride with Reshma. This motorcycle 'Mallow loves long rides to the forest, beach, or mountains. Her favorite place to ride is to the strawberry fields. She picks a few baskets for her favorite treat: strawberry shortcake.

name: Ressie
meetText: Meet Ressie. She spends most of her time reading books, from ancient history to chemistry, she just loves to learn! Recently, Ressie read a book about dinosaurs and now she likes to look for fossils at the beach. What's your favorite kind of book to read?

name: Resul
meetText: Resul runs his own hot dog truck! He drives to busy beach spots and performs some of his clown tricks while waiting for hungry 'Mallows to gather. Resul's truck is known for all of its exciting topping options, like grilled pineapple, coleslaw, and super spicy sliced peppers! What hot dog toppings do you like?

name: Reva
meetText: Reva is a great athlete and is almost always outside. You can usually find her playing soccer with friends. While she's great at soccer and hopes to be a professional player one day, Reva is also great at tennis! She enjoys having one sport for fun and one for focus.

name: Revna
meetText: Watch your words with Revna! She's a debate team champ, two years in a row, and is serious about speech. Revna loves structuring her arguments, creating a standout thesis statement, and sprinkling in a few jokes to keep the audience engaged. Will you watch Revna at her next debate?

name: Rey
meetText: Meet Rey. This shy shark has an eye for fashion, fun, and capturing the "perfect moment" for all of his friends. Rey loves to take pictures and add funky filters before sending the photos to his friends. One day he will have a gallery full of colorful snapshots to explore!

name: Reza
meetText: Nobody loves animals more than Reza. From earthworms to elephants, she is a tender and caring 'Mallow who believes every creature has something wonderful to offer. One day she wants to run her very own wildlife sanctuary just like her parents.

name: Rhett
meetText: Rhett has a nose for breaking news and investigating reporting. He's always the first 'Mallow on the scene of an important story! Rhett relies on verified facts and well-crafted soy lattes to keep him going for another 24-hour news cycle.

name: Rheya
meetText: Want to play a game of tennis or a game of catch? Rheya is your girl!  She's sporty, fun, and always on the go.  Last year, Rheya was voted "Most Athletic" by her entire class! Playing ball helps her de-stress and feel like her best self. Come along and join the game!

name: Rheys
meetText: Rheys may have a blind spot directly to the front, but his peripheral vision is fantastic! His sense of hearing is also so sharp, he could probably hear you from a mile away! Rheys travels all the time with his best buddies searching for warm ocean water and tropical fruits. Mangos are his favorite!

name: Rhiannon
meetText: If it’s holidays, beaches and great food you’re looking for then Rhiannon is your girl! This travelling mallow is at her happiest when she is laying on a sun lounger, relaxing in the heat. Her Squishmallow friends miss her when she’s away and love to hear her tales when she returns.

name: Riah
meetText: Have you met Riah? This little mallow is like a ray of sunshine - she makes mallows smike wherever she goes! Riah is kind, considerate, and loves to give hugs to all her friends and family. Her favorite food is peaches and her favorite sport is Taekwondo.

name: Richard
meetText: Richard spends his days napping and his nights working as a security guard. His favorite color is orange and even though he looks tough, this lion is a big softy.

name: Ricky
meetText: Living up to his species, Ricky knows how to make all the other Squishmallows laugh! Catch him at his next open mic night and see for yourself!

name: Rida
meetText: Meet Rida. She plays the mandolin in a folk band with her friends. They travel cross-country on their tour bus and  perform their songs for retirement communities. Rida always loads the bus up with snacks, drinks, and movies for the long ride. Do you want to join the tour?

name: Ridelle
meetText: Got a big event coming up? Let Ridelle roll out the red carpet for you! She's a special events planner who always goes the extra mile for her clients-- no detail is ever too small for Ridelle the most memorable events are personalized and fun!

name: Rider
meetText: Cedar Point is home for Rider, where enjoying rides all day is just another perk. Whether taking it easy on the train, spinning on a flat ride, or being thrilled on the biggest and best roller coasters, Rider still races to get back in line to ride again and again.

name: Rie
meetText: Meet Rie! Rie has a big family with 4 siblings, and more than 12 cousins! She loves spending time with her family and playing hide-and-seek with her younger brothers. Want to join the game?

name: Rienne
meetText: Hosting a game night? Don't forget to invite Rienne! She loves games of all kinds, her favorites are trivia and charades. Rienne knows how to keep game nights fun and make sure everyone feels included.

name: Riley
meetText: Big hello from Riley the dragon! Riley enjoys the finer things in life. He loves visiting art museums with colorful paintings. When he isn't admiring the art world around him, he enjoys travelling to new places that inspire him. Are you ready to get artsy with Riley?!

name: Rinz
meetText: Rinz is a real foodie who loves traveling to new places in search of delicious dishes. This 'Mallow will lace up his sneakers and go exploring for days! Next, this entrepreneur is getting ready to launch a new business. Want to pitch Rinz some ideas?

name: Ripply
meetText: Ripply's outlook is as bright as he is! Where ever he goes, good things just seem to happen. He loves the simple thing in life like tacos, long talks with friends, and sunny days at the beach. You can't help but smile when hanging with Ripply!

name: Risa
meetText: Say hello to Risa, she's new in town and wants to make friends. Before her first day of school, she plans to bake chocolate chip banana bread for her new class. Do you want to bake yummy treats with Risa?

name: Rita
meetText: Rita is one of the sleepiest mallows around, she just loves to take naps! What's her favorite part about naps? Her favorite fuzzy slippers and matching eye mask because they smell like lavender.

name: Rito
meetText: Rito loves to cook and helps his mom cook for his family. He has fun trying new recipes and testing out new flavors.

name: Ritter
meetText: Ritter just got back from a trip in the rainforest! He was filming a documentary on various 'Mallow communities and their way of life. Ritter loves to travel and learn about the world, so being a documentary filmmaker is his absolute dream! Want to join Ritter at his next movie premiere?

name: River
meetText: Meet River. River is nervous about a family trip coming up. She's going to visit her extended 'Mallow family, far away from where she lives. River really doesn't like to travel and fears new places because she doesn't know what to expect. How does traveling somewhere new make you feel?

name: River the Narwhal
meetText: Hi! My name is River! My mini and I love to swim in the ocean and surf the waves.

name: Rivka
meetText: Rivka makes her own fortune telling cards! She cuts the cards from super-cute craft paper, then designs them. What do you think about a celestial theme? Rivka loves doodling stars and planets, but her favorite part is sprinkling lots of glitter! Your future is looking artsy with Rivka.

name: Robb
meetText: Ready to meet Robb? This orangutan's love for cleaning means his house is always picture-perfect. When he's not vacuuming or keeping the house tidy for his family, he's getting wild with his friends. In fact, he's known as 'Local Robb' around town because he's never met a stranger.

name: Robbie
meetText: Robbie loves to play soccer, card games and cross-country ski. You can usually find him spending time with his cousins Puff and Piper on the soccer field. When he grows up, he wants to be a geologist or a professional soccer player.

name: Robert
meetText: Meet Robert. He loves basketball and trampolines. Robert may not be the best basketball player on the court but his passion for the game keeps him going. Robert hopes that with practice one day he can change his luck. Do you want to play a pick-up game sometime?

name: Roberto
meetText: Somersaults and crazy cool stunts are Roberto's hopes and dreams for the future, he wants to be a stuntman! He practices stunts and tumbling with his brothers. Roberto can't wait until the day he gets to do real stunts!

name: Robyne
meetText: Meet Robyne - this bubbly bunny loves grape juice, chocolate cake, and traveling the world. Robyne has a map of the world and all the places she wants to go, every time she goes to a new city, she adds a pin to the poster. Can you guess how many pins she added this year?

name: Rocio
meetText: Have you ever met a triceratops who can speak 7 different languages? When she was a mini mallow Rocio’s family moved a lot so she learned a new language for every new home. Now she loves to help others learn them too!

name: Rocket
meetText: Watch out for Rocket as he zooms by! Rocket is on the swim team, can you guess his events? He's great at open swim but his favorite event is the freestyle relay, he takes off like a rocket and that's how he earned his nickname.

name: Rocky
meetText: Don’t stop Rocky! He is on a roll. Rocky has been an adventure seeker since he was little and plans on climbing his first summit this year. Grab a hiking stick and bring the fun!

name: Rodina
meetText: Meet Rodina. Fun facts, cute cats, and the perfect panini are some of her favorite things. This laid-back 'Mallow loves any occasion where she can pet pets and discuss foods from distant lands - or better yet, try them with friends!

name: Rodry
meetText: Rodry sits in his favorite tree at night to watch the fireflies. It's like having a personal light show in his backyard! Even when Rodry has company over, he only lights candles to keep the space mostly dim so the fireflies can shine bright. Join Rodry for a twinkling summer night!

name: Rolland
meetText: Meet Rolland. He loves art history and can spend all afternoon with his head buried in an art book. He's taking a still life drawing class and is getting pretty good! When he paints he sometimes gets color everywhere, so make sure you're wearing apron before you join him!

name: Roman
meetText: Need some help making the right decision? Roman is here to help! Roman wants to be a leader when they grow up and knows it's important to take care of the world we live in. They like to play fair, eat clean, stay green, and think about others.

name: Romina
meetText: She's loud, loveable, and knows how to have fun, Romina is one mallow you just have to meet. Her passion is life and trying to figure it all out, so if you're ready for a cool adventure, give Romina a call!

name: Romano
meetText: You can't help but look at Romano when he enters a room. This 'Mallow has some serious screen-stealing presence! Different casting directors have approached Romano in the past, but he's never been interested in acting or modeling. Romano prefers a super chill life he has as a seaweed farmer!

name: Romy
meetText: Romy has a fashion sense that is always outside the box but perfectly on trend. She even designs and tailors some of her clothes herself for a unique fit. Next time you have an event to get dressed for, give Romy a call she'll know just how to style you!

name: Ronalda
meetText: Don't let her horn fool you—Ronalda plays the strings! This musically-gifted 'Mallow is the principal violinist for the Yeti Philharmonic. Though some call her elusive, Ronalda is just busy. Between leading symphonies and writing symphonies, who could blame her?

name: Ronan
meetText: Meet Ronan. This fiery fellow knows a thing or two about campfires, he keeps the flames at the perfect height when he goes camping with his friends. They roast lots of yummy things over his perfect fire, including s'mores!

name: Rondah
meetText: Meet Rondah. She's an astrologist! She writes amazing horoscopes, that is unless Mercury is in retrograde! Then she gets totally turned around! When she's not reading the moon, sun, and stars, she likes making homemade candles or getting tacos from her favorite taco truck!

name: Ronello
meetText: Watch out for Ronello on lane 10! He's on a bowling winning streak and has been known to swipe his tail in celebration. Ronello only plays with his own personalized blue bowling ball that has the perfect weight and fit for his hand. Want to play on Ronello's winning team?

name: Ronisia
meetText: Ronisia lives her dream of being an astronaut! She focuses all her time and energy collecting data, learning about the universe, and sharing that knowledge with other 'Mallows. Would you want to explore space with Ronisia?

name: Ronnie
meetText: Ronnie loves building birdhouses, last week he made a purple two-story birdhouse with green shutters. His sister Belana helps him paint and make sure they are ready to move in. Do you want to buy a birdhouse from Ronnie?

name: Morty
meetText: Meet Morty, he might look a little strange on the outside, but on the inside he’s just like you. Morty loves talking to his friends about his home, outer space. His favorite earth food is birthday cake ice cream.

name: Rory
meetText: Meet Rory the unicorn. Rory loves having slumber parties with her pals. They love watching comedies and breaking out the karaoke machine. Can you guess Rory's favorite slumber party game? Hide and seek!

name: Merry
meetText: Hi! My name is Merry! My mini and I love to play tag and chase our tails in circles.

name: Rosa
meetText: Fresh from the beach, Rosa is one of the chillest Squishmallows around. She swims, surfs, and sunbathes all day and doesn't get very far without her favorite snack, you guessed it, pineapple!

name: Rose
meetText: Do you need a florist? Rose is the one for you! She creates bouquets and arrangements of all shapes and sizes. She started by making flower crowns for all her friends and now runs one of her family's floral shops. What kind of bouquet do you want Rose to make for you?

name: Roseanne
meetText: Roseanne started her own toy unboxing show! Check out her online channel for new videos posted every Friday. Roseanne loves unwrapping mystery toys, so she can decided to share the surprise for everyone!

name: Rosemary
meetText: Rosemary takes popping popcorn to another level. You will never catch this 'Mallow using a microwave! Rosemary only pops whole kernels in her best iron skillet and finishes it with a secret blend of spices. Rosemary loves all kinds of popcorn flavors, but if you ask her, caramel corn is her favorite!

name: Rosemund
meetText: Rosemund is a hard-of-hearing librarian. Though mischievous 'Mallows sometimes think that means they can chit-chat. Rosemund has a trick up her ear—her hearing aid! With its volume on high, Rosemund is able to hear the faintest turn of a page (the only noise she allows).

name: Rosie
meetText: Meet Rosie, she’s visiting her family from the other side of the pond! Rosie loves crunchy biscuits, going to concerts with her friends, and spending time with her nanna. Rosie’s nanna makes the best tea and always has yummy treats ready when she comes over.

name: Rossi
meetText: Is your closet a mess? Rossi will handle it from here! She's a professional organizer who loves to teach clients all her tips and tricks. Rossi's goal is to create a system that lasts, keeping every closet and room in order. Can Rossi help you get organized?

name: Roslyn
meetText: Roslyn collects spiders just for fun! She thinks they make beautiful, low-maintenance pets. So far Roslyn owns five different arachnids. but Teri the tarantula is her prized spider. Sometimes Roslyn even lets Teri sit on her shoulder so they can watch TV together!

name: Roth
meetText: Have you seen Roth's house keys? He lost them again. Roth clipped a bell to them, but that hasn't helped. Even for such a thoughtful 'Mallow, Roth gets easily distracted and misplaces things. But eventually, he finds what he was looking for!

name: Rou
meetText: Meet Rou. She loves staying up late with friends and singing karaoke to their heart's content. They always order lots of sushi. Tuna is her favorite and she gets it extra spicy! Want to join them? Grab the mic!

name: Roven
meetText: Say hi to Roven! Roven loves to play sports like kickball, dodgeball, and disc golf. Days in the park are so much fun for Roven, but sometimes they leave her a little breathless and she needs to use her inhaler. After a quick rest, Roven is ready to get back in the game!

name: Roxy
meetText: Roxy loves to play in the dirt, sneak up on her friends, and plant flowers to make the world a prettier place. Join her to plant some pink tulips on February 14 and you’ll make her day.

name: Roz
meetText: Roz is as sweet as they come, but her feelings tend to get a little sour when she bottles them up. That's why she's super excited to start therapy this year! Though it might take a while for this jar of jam to open up, Roz can't wait to get started.

name: Rozen
meetText: Rozen is an entomologist—that means she studies insects! Her specialty is in spiders and hopes to one day meet the elusive eight-foot tarantula. Rozen heard it has a web the size of a football field and she can't wait to check it out!

name: Ruby
meetText: Ruby enjoys long walks on the ice with her occasional hot cocoa beverage. Ruby is the North Pole’s Christmas coordinator. She plans all of the reindeer events leading up to the grand finale on Christmas day.

name: Rudy
meetText: Ready for takeoff with Rudy the rocket? He and his best friend Daxxon are explorers on a mission to defend the universe, or so they tell their friends. They share a love for adventure and being helpful, would you like to join them?

name: Rufus
meetText: Rufus recently had a growth spurt and now he is very tall. Sometimes his friends tease him about being bigger than a moose! At first, he was worried, but now he knows his height can come in handy, especially reaching the snacks at the top shelf.

name: Brielle
meetText: Brielle and her friend Prince are getting ready to go to space! At least that's what they're telling her mom, they've built a space station out of pillows in the living room! They might have to save the planet before dinner time, do you think they can do it?

name: Rupert
meetText: High up in the treetops, Rupert celebrates Valentine's Day in his own unique way by decorating his tree with red lights and pink hearts.

name: Rutabaga
meetText: Have you ever met a caterpillar who can't live without chocolate? Peanut butter cups and chocolate chip cookies are two of Rutabaga's favorite treats. And if you're making cookies Rutabaga has just one rule to follow: always add more chocolate chips!

name: Ruth
meetText: Ruth loves the beach and exploring the ocean. She knows how to sail and takes her family sailing during the summer. In the winter you can find her dreaming of her next tropical sailing trip.

name: Ruthie
meetText: Ready to go dancing with Ruthie? Ruthie has been a dancer practically since she was born, her family jokes she was dancing as soon as her feet touched the ground! She knows dance of all types, her favorites are salsa and jazz.

name: Rutie
meetText: Do you know how Rutie conquers his fear of rollercoasters? By riding them! He's a brave rooster with a strong stomach, and no matter how scary a roller coaster looks you can be sure Rutie is ready for the experience. Look out for Rutie next time your at an amusement park!

name: Ryan
meetText: Original: Ryan is not your average husky, while he enjoys playing sports and spending time with friends, he also loves to spend time learning about robots and technology. One day he hopes to be a famous inventor, so watch out!

name: Ryan
meetText: Original: Ryan is not your average husky, while he enjoys playing sports and spending time with friends, he also loves to spend time learning about robots and technology. One day he hopes to be a famous inventor, so watch out!

name: Ryder
meetText: Ryder loves marshmallow eggs as much as his sister Candy loves jellybeans - and that's a lot! While his sister loves to compete, Ryder prefers to be behind the scenes, He helps the younger bunnies find eggs and even shares his basket with anyone who hasn't found many.

name: Sabine
meetText: Sabine has a huge jewelry collection, you'd think she was royalty with all that sparkle! Are you ready for her secret? She makes it all herself! Sabine enjoys arts and crafts, and she loves making custom accessories for her friends. What can Sabine make for you?

name: Sabino
meetText: Peach pie with ice cream and pecans is Sabino’s favorite treat. He learned how to bake just so he could eat pie whenever he wants. Sabino is a doorman and if he works late, coming home to bake a pie helps him relax. Would you like to try a slice?

name: Sabrina
meetText: Sabrina is one of a kind! This caticorn has travelled the globe and seen amazing things. She wants to travel to every single country and she will even send you a postcard!

name: Sachie
meetText: Meet Sachie. When he isn't taking piano lessons or perfecting his smoked salsa recipe, you can find him hanging with his family. They've got a super fun vacation planned. Sachie can't wait to bring his camera to document the whole thing!

name: Sadie
meetText: Sadie is a great swimmer and loves climbing trees, too. Her favorite way to spend weekends is sleepovers with friends.

name: Safa
meetText: Safa is the ultimate fan 'Mallow. She once got so excited about meeting her favorite author at a book signing, she puffed up and had to get out of the line! It was pretty embarrassing. But after Safa collected herself, she got the autograph and even a picture. Who do you stan?

name: Safiyah
meetText: Do you know Safiyah? She loves everything bright and colorful! Safiyah is going to school to be a hair and make-up artist, but when she’s not studying or practicing you can find her making colorful tie-dye clothing creations. What colors should Safiyah tie-dye for you?

name: Sager
meetText: If you're looking for Sager, you can probably find her curled up on the couch with her best friend, Cooper! Sager waits all week for her favorite show, so that she can turn down the lights, grab some ice cream and a cozy blanket, and catch up with all her favorite characters. Wanna tune in and chill out with Sager?

name: Sakina
meetText: Sakina loves daydreaming and waiting to see what the universe will bring. Last week, she dozed off and had the craziest dream, she dreamt that she discovered a new galaxy where all the ‘Mallows could fly! She flew off into the stars and suddenly woke up. Have you had any crazy dreams?

name: Salita
meetText: If you're a fan of hugs, snuggles and cuddles then Salita is the 'Mallow for you! For her, a big ol' hug is a perfect way to greet your friends. If hugs aren't your thing, Salita has a pretty good elbow tap on deck. Though she loves hugs, she respects her friends' space first!

name: Salvador
meetText: Jump in line and get ready for some fun, Salvador is here to play! Salvador lives for speed and spins, especially when it comes to games. The faster he spins, the more fun he has, are you ready to give it a try?

name: Sam
meetText:
Sam is the friend for you, but only if you can keep up! He is a runner, and can race circles around his friends at the park. He absolutely loves the outdoors and is always on the move. His birthday is June 19th, a wonderful time for a camping trip. You can find him snowboarding in the winter and on jet skis in the summer time. 
You can't say no to his puppy eyes! He brings out the best in everyone he meets, and is quite the companion. He is fast and furious, which makes sense. He hopes to be a race car driver when he grows up!

name: Samanthé
meetText: Samanthé is smart, diplomatic - but can sting you with her sass! She loves music, especially soca music so she can snap her pinchers! She travels the world and speaks 6 languages. While she doesn't love crowds of people, she will always be there when you need her the most.

name: Samir
meetText: Who's that 'Mallow leading the pack? It's Samir! This wonderful whale never planned on being in charge but his kindness and consideration have helped him become an excellent leader. If you need some advice on making the best choice, give Samir a call!

name: Sammy
meetText: Hopscotch and hula hoops are some of Sammy's favorite things - every spring Sammy hopes to host the largest hopscotch contest! One day Sammy wants to turn their hopscotch dream into a game show, who do you think will be the champion?

name: Samuel
meetText: Samuel is quite musically talented. He can pick up any instrument, and make you want to move your feet and dance within three seconds! He loves performing for others, and his favorite instrument to play for everyone is the guitar!

name: Sandra
meetText: Sandra can say "hi" in three languages! This multilingual 'Mallow teaches at the local university and would love for you to drop in to one of her classes. Sandra knows the best way the learn new language is by having fun. That's why she incorporates jokes into every lesson!

name: Sandro
meetText: Smells like a summer barbeque! That means Sandro is grilling up some kebabs, tomatoes, and even pineapple! Everything tastes better fresh off the grill. Do you know Sandro's secret to the perfect barbeque? Home-dried wood chips!

name: Sandy
meetText: Sandy spends the day watching people have fun and walking on the beach. Sometimes she likes being surrounded by her flock of friends, other times she prefers to be on her own. One thing to know about Sandy, this hungry bird never gets tired of looking for French fries!

name: Santiago
meetText: Santiago is a very special squirrel - he loves deep sea diving! Even though he's not the fastest creature in the ocean. He's also really great at card games, so have your poker face ready!

name: Santino
meetText: Santino makes the best blueberry pancakes, his dad taught him how to add the blueberries just right. When he’s not making pancakes for all his friends, you can find Santino playing soccer, he wants to be a professional goalie someday. Santino is also known to like surprises and often plans surprise parties for his friends. He catches his targets off guard by jumping through the air and giving them a hug in the face.

name: Santos
meetText: Santos wants to be an opera singer when he grows up. He enjoys wearing costumes and singing loudly, he knows how good his voice sounds with the right acoustics.

name: Sarah
meetText: It’s squirrel time! Sarah is one of the finest stand-up comedians in the entire Squishmallow squad. Her laughter can be heard from miles away! Be sure to check out her special Valentine’s Day routine.

name: Satine
meetText: Satine is a total brunch bun! She orders way too much food and packs whatever is left over to save for later. Satine hands out all morning with her orange juice and coffee, either reading the morning paper or chatting with a buddy. Join Satine and don't forget to bring your appetite!

name: Saul
meetText: Saul wants to light up your day! He's a busy electrician helping every 'Mallow shine. You can find Saul running tech at the local theater hanging lamps and managing  the switchboard! Want to help Saul at his show tonight?

name: Sawtelle
meetText: Sawtelle guides her clients through both big and small challenges as a life coach. She's always been the best advice giver, just ask her brother Paden. Sawtelle reminds everyone to listen to their heart and take deep breaths every day. She is one sweet 'Mallow!

name: Sawyer
meetText: Find a penny, pick it up, and all day long you’ll have good luck! Sawyer loves to collect pennies, beads, and shiny knick-knacks he finds in the forest during the day. Join him on a treasure-hunting expedition!

name: Saxa
meetText: Have you seen Saxa? This is one fancy pants 'Mallow! Saxa is expressive in both attire and attitude and always shows her true colors. She is honest but fair with her friends and family and gives great advice. Saxa is one iconic 'Mallow you won't want to miss.

name: Sayed
meetText: Springtime for Sayed is a lot of fun and a lot of hard work. This brisk bunny is training for track! Sayed wants to be the fastest sprinter around and practices running up the hills near their home. Rain or shine, you'll find Sayed putting in the work!

name: Scarlet
meetText: Meet Scarlet. This sweet Squishmallow loves all things theatre and dance – she wants to be a costume designer AND a performer on Broadway. Her father taught her how to sew and every year she makes the costumes for her school plays. One day he’ll be front row for one of her shows!

name: Scarlito
meetText: Most owls are afraid to leave the nest—not Scarlito! This courageous young daredevil was born to soar. Though Scarlito has a lot left to learn, this natural flier is already reaching new heights!

name: Schifra
meetText: Meet Schifra. Schifra is an art critic who calls herself a critic of the world. This squirrel has a opinion on everything and she loves to share it! She uses an old-school typewriter she found at a swap meet for her weekly column. Would you like to read it?

name: Scout
meetText: Scout loves to paint, but he's a bit messy. By the end of the day, all of the colors get on his white fur so that he looks like a painting himself!

name: Scrapper
meetText: Scrapper is known as a daredevil; he creates the fireworks and lightshow for the Skeleton Squad and rides a motorcycle on stage. Scrapper also makes a mean devil's food cake and bakes one for the band at the start of every tour.

name: Seamus
meetText: Bring your binoculars and go bird watching with Seamus! He keeps a bird encyclopedia with him at all times and would love to tell you all about the birds you spot. Bird watching requires lots of patience and silence, and best of all, making bird calls! Want Seamus to show you how to whistle one?

name: Seanster
meetText: Seanster is always in the mood for a snack! Even when he's in the middle of playing videogames, you can bet there's a bag of chips nearby. Seanster and his bestie, Steph, are getting ready to go to a movie tonight! Want them to save you a seat?

name: Sebastian
meetText: Sebastian loves to spend his time playing basketball and one day wants to go pro in the NBL (National Bunny League). You can find him in the kitchen - eating or helping his mom.

name: Sebi
meetText: Sebi never leaves the house without his microphone. He keeps his ears perked for any new or interesting sounds, then records them. Sebi saves all these clips on his computer so he can easily share them with his bud Meggie for one of her movies!

name: Sel
meetText: Introducing Sel! Sel has a lot of interests, which makes having to choose which one to study in school even more difficult! To help her decide, Sel's plan is to pick one topic a week to learn about, and after a month, she'll pick her favorite! Which subject should she try out first?

name: Selassi
meetText: Selassi plays fiddle for a bluegrass band. It took her many years to get the hang of such a difficult instrument, not to mention the challenge of Selassi's web paws! But this 'Mallow never gave up, and now she's one of the fastest fiddle players around. Come see Selassi at a show this weekend!

name: Selema
meetText: Selema studies French at the community center in town. She's swimming abroad next year with some of her 'Mallow pals and decided to learn the language for her trip. Selema practices vocabulary every day and even tests herself on flashcards. Join Selema tonight for a classic French movie!

name: Selene
meetText: Selene dreams of being a marine biologist, she loves to learn more about her home and how to keep it clean. She spends her free time sun bathing and learning new languages. What should she learn next?

name: Selly
meetText: Meet Selly! Some might like gardening but Selly LOVES it! She even built a greenhouse in her backyard so that her hibiscus can stay warm all year. When she's not watering her plants, she's taking pictures of them! Want to see some photos of her camellias?

name: Selma
meetText: Meet Selma! Just like her brother Skyler, this sweet skunk helps out in the garden but truly enjoys building mini towns with objects from the wild. When she grows up she wants to build her very own cottage with a garden filled with roses. Come help Selma on her next building project!

name: Sena
meetText: Have a produce question? Sena is here to help! She just opened a general store and gets her fruits and veggies fresh and local every day. She loves to support her community in any way that she can.

name: Seraphina
meetText: What is Seraphina’s favorite Valentine’s Day candy? Definitely sour gummies! If you give her some she’ll be sure to share with you, and also tell you a joke.

name: Serena
meetText: Have you ever seen a swan play hockey? You better catch a game soon; you might even see Serena score a goal! Serena and her friends love to glide across the ice, this year they hope to win the Squishmallow tournament.

name: Serene
meetText: Meet Serene, the calmest squirrel you'll meet! Just like her name, she is cool, collected and the perfect 'Mallow to help you take a deep breath. She meditates every day and loves to give her friends advice.

name: Serge
meetText: Serge plays keyboard and adds all kinds of spooky sounds to tracks for his band. His favorite part of being in a band is playing with his friends and telling his mom about the crazy costumes he gets to wear.

name: Sertina
meetText: Sertina plays the trumpet and loves baseball. When she grows up, she hopes to be a team manager one day! Her favorite stadium snack is caramel popcorn with chocolate drizzle, do you want to go to a baseball game with Sertina?

name: Seth
meetText: Seth loves the outdoors. He lives for swimming, hiking, and spending time in his tree house practicing yoga. He is the first to try a new sport or play a new instrument, and although he may not be the best everything he tries, he doesn't let that stop him from having a good time!

name: Sevda
meetText: Follow Sevda to the ice! Sevda dreams of becoming a world-class skater and is almost always at the rink, perfecting her routine. Sevda loves to help others learn her sport, so grab your skates and take a whirl!

name: Seymour
meetText: Seymour writes for a food magazine! This month's issue features lots of fun Halloween recipes, so Seymour has been tasting and writing about all the different festive dishes. Seymour's favorite dish so far is the pumpkin cheesecake. He loved the little whipped cream ghosts topping!

name: Shabnam
meetText: Shabnam is a civil engineer who loves to travel! She's always planning the next adventure for her family. For Shabnam, nothing is more important than her loved ones, so it's no wonder she's known for being on of the sea's sweetest 'Mallows.

name: Shadi
meetText: Shadi might look intimidating, but she's super sweet! She started a nonprofit when she was in school and is constantly proving her generosity through random acts of kindness. Just the other day, Shadi held a donation drive for her local animal shelter.

name: Shane
meetText: Once the weather warms up, Shane runs to the nearest lake to go paddle boarding! They love to feel the sun warm them up as they gently drift out. If it gets too hot, Shane jumps in for a quick rinse in the clear, fresh water, then gets back on their board! Wanna go paddle boarding with Shane this summer?

name: Shannon
meetText: Order up! Shannon is a barista who loves to have fun at work, she specializes in moody drinks. She'll ask how your day is going and then if you want to order from the regular menu or if you want a moody drink. What kind of drink are you in the mood for?

name: Shantira
meetText: Shantira loves to knit, and has enough yarn to build a house! She makes sweaters, hats, blankets, and more. Last year she knit her two best friends a matching dinosaur footed pajama set.

name: Shany
meetText: This sparkly Squishmallow loves everything pink and Valentine's day is one of her favorite holidays! She loves to pamper herself with pink sparkly bath bombs and heart shaped glitter cookies.

name: Sharde
meetText: Sharde is the sweetest Squishmallow with the biggest heart! She's the kind of friend you can count on. Sharde loves to dance at sunset and when she's with her Squishmallow friends she always has her camera on hand to capture the special moments. Fun fact about Sharde: when it comes to cheese, she loves it on everything!

name: Sharie
meetText: Tap, tap, tap goes Sharie in her shiny tap shoes! One of the best in her dance class, Sharie loves to put on a good show and make the audience smile as she performs on stage.

name: Sharon
meetText: Looking for a photographer? Sharon is the shark for you! She travels the globe taking photos for Squishmallows of all kinds but her favorite place to be is usually at home with her family or playing her brand new guitar!

name: Shaun
meetText: Original: Shaun is a high-spirited fitness fanatic who loves to stay active. Whether it's hiking, biking or rollerblading. You will always find him outdoors. He's the perfect friend to break a sweat and soak up the sunshine with!

name: Shauna
meetText: Shauna and her friend Landon rule the stage, they've been dubbed the king and queen of karaoke amongst their friends. Shauna is a crowd pleaser and warms the crowd up with a new ballad every week. Can you guess her next song?

name: Shay
meetText: Need a spot at the gym? Shay has limbs and jokes to go around! Lifting weights, reading plays, and a good joke are Shay's way of life. He loves to recite his favorite monologues and with some added humor for his friends.

name: Shelby
meetText: Shelby loves to hang out with friends and family. She loves going to the park to climb around but when she is not playing, she loves to take naps!

name: Sheldon
meetText: Sheldon enjoys spending time by himself and learning more about the ocean he lives in! He loves learning about all the plants, other sea creatures, and making friends with the people he meets along the way. Fun fact about Sheldon: he wanted to be a jellyfish when he grew up!

name: Shellie
meetText: Meet Shellie. This silly skeleton plays the drums and loves to make noise. She used to bang on pots and pans as a mini-mallow and now tours all over. Her favorite thing about touring with the Skeleton Squad? Seeing new mallow fans everywhere she tours.

name: Shena
meetText: Shena is looking for someone to play catch with so grab a glove! She's working on her curve ball because she wants to try out for the softball team this spring. Though she's great at bat, she wants to become the best pitcher around. Will you help her?

name: Shep
meetText: Shep drives a long-haul truck for a delivery company. He maintains his truck himself, including always rotating his tires! Shep loves his life on the road and is looking for a like-minded 'Mallow to join him on his far-off adventures. Do you enjoy long-distance road trips?

name: Shevra
meetText: Do you know any good jokes? Shevra is one Squishmallow who loves to laugh. She's always kind and has a smile that will cheer you up. Give her the gift of a laugh and she'll light up the room!

name: Shondie
meetText: Meet Shondie. She is always trying out new hobbies. First it was baking sourdough bread, then it was tie-dying all the clothes in her closet. Now she's trying her hand at beekeeping. So far she's doing pretty good! Do you have a hobby she should try out next?

name: Shoni
meetText: Meet Shoni. Don't be surprised if he asks you for directions. This 'Mallow is always getting lost and turned around! But Shoni doesn't mind. He loves all the new places he gets to see and the new friends he meets on the way! Who knows where he'll go next!

name: Shoshana
meetText: Shoshana has a beautiful voice and dreams of being a superstar. She is learning how to dance so she can sing and dance her way to the stage, do you want to practice with her!

name: Shozo
meetText: Meet Shozo. Shozo is a planner who helps 'Mallow everywhere feel safe. He works in logistics and planning to make sure fire drills, tornado drills, and other weather emergencies are handled. Snowstorms or flash floods? Shozo's got it handled!

name: Sid
meetText: Meet Sid. He adds chocolate milk to his marshmallow cereal and hot sauce on his omelets. Sid listens to opera to entertain himself and make time go faster while sitting in traffic. What song would you like Sid to sing?

name: Sienna
meetText: Sienna hosts the best dance parties around! This caring caticorn invites her whole Squishmallows Squad for a night of sweet dance moves in snazzy outfits. The decorations are always extra sparkly--her favorite color is rainbow! Will you join Sienna for her next bash?

name: Sigrid
meetText: Congrats to Sigrid! She just became her airline's first female airline pilot. Sigrid flies all around the world but most of her routes are to mountainous northern regions. When Sigrid's not working her dream job, she rounds up her best buddies for an island getaway!

name: Sigzby
meetText: Meet Sigzby. This super special ‘Mallow is rarely seen in the wild, that’s because she’s nocturnal! When everyone else is sleeping, she’s up rock climbing, making origami, or practicing her ballet moves! When the sun comes up, you can find her snoozing in her favorite tree!

name: Silky
meetText: Have you ever met a lucky filly? Silky might be your first! She loves having her mane braided and her favorite food is biscuits with strawberry jam. Silky dreams of winning the Kentucky Derby one day, maybe her lucky name can help! Will you cheer her on?

name: Silver
meetText: Silver specializes in horoscopes and has their own weekly column in the local paper. They reference a huge astrology book with all the planetary meanings and explanations to help them write the weekly horoscopes. Will you let Silver read your birth chart?

name: Silvia
meetText: Silvia may look like a sleepy Squishmallow but that’s because she works late at night! Silvia is an orthopedic surgeon and works nights at the hospital. She loves helping people as long as she’s had enough sleep!

name: Silvina
meetText: Silvina is a writer and loves the finer things in life like designer shells and tropical trips. She loves basking in the shade with a cool breeze to help her get started on a new book. Whenever she travels it gives her inspiration to write a new book.

name: Simon
meetText: Want a buddy to just relax with? Simon is your perfect match. If you can’t find him, he is probably at the store buying another video game! In fact, he is the greatest gamer on the block. Fun fact about Simon? He loves virtual reality. If it were up to him, he would teleport in a second!

name: Simone
meetText: Grab your spectacles and get ready for a musical journey, Simone is about to go on stage! Simone is an opera singer with a magical voice. You're always in for a treat if you can catch her while she's in town.

name: Sinclair
meetText: Sinclair and his cousin Austin love to talk about outer space, but they always disagree on whether aliens exist. Austin thinks they do but Sinclair needs more proof. He wants to join Austin on a space adventure to find out, are you ready for liftoff?

name: Sinead
meetText: Sinead loves the ocean and dreams of exploring the sea. There's just one problem, Sinead doesn't know how to swim! Maybe one day Sinead will explore the ocean, for now, it's time for swimming lessons!

name: Siobhan
meetText: Meet Siobhan. Did you know he used to be afraid of water? Now he loves going on night swims with his friends. His favorite part is how the stars in the sky makes the water sparkle all around him! Want to join him? Dive in!

name: Sissy
meetText: Grab some flour and put on your apron, Sissy could use some help in the kitchen. Sissy loves to try new things, this week she's baking brownies for a school project. Can you help her gather all the ingredients?

name: Sivi
meetText: Meet Sivi. She is sweet, warm, and generous. Her favorite part of the holidays is seeing the smiles on her friends' faces when they unwrap something special she's made for them. She crafts handmade cards and necklaces. She'd love to make you something special, too!

name: Skeeter
meetText: Have you seen Skeeter? This super-fast skeleton runs around like a flash of lightening at all the Skeleton Squad shows! Skeeter is friends with the Squad and makes sure all their favorite snacks are backstage: caramel apples, apple cider witches brew, and sour gummy candy.

name: Sketlana
meetText: Watch out for Sketlana! This queen of the bass knows a thing or two about bringing the house down. Sketlana plays bass and ukelele and is known for her spooky scream in Skeleton Squad. Fun fact about Sketlana: she designs all the costumes for the band!

name: Skully
meetText: Star gazing, salami and sci-fi movies are some of Skully's favorite things. This creepy cat loves to think about what other living things could exist in space, they are positive that there's more life out there!

name: Sky
meetText: Sky shreds on the tennis court. Her backhand is almost stronger than her forehand! Sky is ready to make tennis her career, but first she has to graduate high school. There's only one semester left before Sky graduates—she's thinking about going to prom in a neon tennis outfit!

name: Skyler
meetText: Skyler is obsessed with gardening - he helps his grandmother and has developed quite the green thumb! He may give you a fright when you first meet him, but this skunk is a softie at heart.

name: Sloan
meetText: Sloan is a private chef--- she's also a private investigator! This sneaky skunk works night and day learning what customers like to eat. Through in-depth interviews and the occasional dumpster dive, Sloan is able to create the most of custom cuisines. Bon appetit!

name: Snell
meetText: Welcome to Snell's jewelry store! She buys and trades jewelry from all over the globe to have perfectly crafted accessories in her shop. Snell even wears some of the unique item, like a glazed kiwi barrette and strawberry brooch pin. Want Snell to make a little gift bag  just for you?

name: Sofia
meetText: You’ve never met a unicorn who loves dogs more than Sofia. This artist loves to paint and draw dogs of all shapes and sizes. Maybe one day you’ll see her work in a gallery or in a museum!

name: Solina
meetText: Meet Solina. She's naturally charming. Maybe it's the sparkle in her eye, or that she's great at keeping secrets! Whatever it is, she's the type of 'Mallow you just want to be around. She's always doing something fun, like salsa dancing lessons. Want to join?

name: Sophie
meetText: Inspired by the flowers near her home, Sophie is an aspiring fashion designer. She loves creating new looks and staging fashion shows with her friends.

name: Soraya
meetText: Meet Soraya. Her laugh is so contagious so you can't help but join in when you hear it. Soraya has a care-free attitude, and that's what makes her so easy to love. She rarely gets upset and can help calm anyone down.

name: Spencer
meetText: Looking for a happy helper? Add Spencer to your squad! Spencer is a greeter at the store and LOVES his job. He is always willing to lend a paw or make someone smile! To let go and have fun, Spencer loves to shop for toys at Five Below!

name: Spice
meetText: Spice loves everything pink—like strawberry cupcakes and sparkly rhinestones! When she isn't writing in her diary or dancing to pop music, you can find her at the mall. She loves meeting up with her best friend, Sugar, to get extra-large cinnamon buns from the food court!

name: Squaz
meetText: Meet Squaz. He loves toy cars, biking, and cheese! Sometimes Squaz gets angry or sad and doesn't know what to do. But if he has his cheese, and a good friend, he will make it through anything.

name: Stacy
meetText: Stacy is a shy squid, she prefers to be home with her friends or even by herself. Big groups of Squishmallows make her a little nervous, so she loves to learn and explore through books. She's quiet at first but all her friends know she can be very silly.

name: Stahl
meetText: Stahl blows bubbles so artfully, he turned it into a live show. He uses dish soap and thick rope to lasso the biggest bubbles you've ever seen! You can watch Stahl's soapy creations hover over an audience--- but be careful don't sit under a bubble before it pops!

name: Staley
meetText: Gather 'round! Staley lights up any campfire with his howling harmonica — you can't help but sing along! After s'mores, Staley and his squad make up scary stories until everyone is so nervous that they burst out laughing. Do you have a scary story to share?

name: Stanley
meetText: Need a friend who will support and protect you? Well, then you’ve got a friend in Stanley. He has been practicing karate since he was small. He even has his black belt test next month! When he’s not kicking a punching bag, he is writing poetry.

name: Star
meetText: Star braves the unknown every day when exploring outer space! This galaxy adventurer stays optimistic and hopeful no matter what each daily mission brings. Being a space explorer isn't always easy, but Star has the strength and true superhero qualities to succeed at anything!

name: Starla
meetText: Meet Starla. She loves iced tea, board games, and exploring. Starla is an ocean studies major and wants to keep the ocean clean and safe for everyone. Starla’s parents taught her to care about environmental issues and to keep it safe for all creatures.

name: Starry
meetText: Starry's motto is honesty is the best policy. She loves astrology and stargazing, and is always looking for new ways to reach her dreams.

name: Stasia
meetText: Every team needs a cheerleader! Stasia is the cheerleader for her family's swim team and always motivates them to do their best! Stasia does all kinds of impressive routines on the sidelines while she cheers. You can join the cheer team, too - if you want!

name: Steele
meetText: Meet Steele! This whale shark is happiest when in motion. He was born deaf and loves to dance and feel the vibrations of the drums and bass. You can catch Steele and friends at a heavy metal show or dancing beneath the strobe light to their favorite DJ. Make sure to wave hello!

name: Stefana
meetText: Stefana is a playful, curious Squishmallow who loves flying and meeting new people. She always looks forward to her next trip around the globe, and makes a unique cross-stitch after each adventure as a way to capture her favorite memories.

name: Stella
meetText: Stella’s a good friend because she’s always honest and super adventurous. Stella and her family hike in the forest all the time.

name: Steph
meetText: Steph gets extra accordion air thanks to her little parachute arms! She loves playing an instrument almost as fun as she is. After a long work week, you can find Steph spreading her laughter and making everyone around her smiler. How does she her energy up? Rocking out to industrial music!

name: Steve
meetText: Steve is working hard towards getting a black belt in karate! When this determined 'Mallow isn't practicing his fierce martial arts moves, he's powering up with yummy snacks! His favorite? French fries and cinnamon sugar soft pretzels dipped in ice cream!

name: Stevie
meetText: Stevie is the sheriff of Frontier Town. He can be tough to get close to and can have a mean streak, but don't let his gruff demeanor fool you. He watches out for everybody and makes a great friend. He can usually be found helping others with his best buddy Midnight.

name: Stevon
meetText: Meet Stevon, he's a certified scuba instructor. He loves how quiet the world becomes when he's swimming under water and the way kelp beds sway softly with the current. It's truly a magical experience he loves to share with other people. Want to learn? He'd love to teach you!

name: Stix
meetText: Meet Stix. This mischievous mallow lives to keep the spirit of Malloween alive. 365 days a year, Stix maintains a costume and mischief shop filled with goblins, goons, and games for the perfect fright night.

name: Stokely
meetText: Unlike most bears, Stokely doesn't hunt for salmon in freezing rivers—he sips espresso in cozy cafés! An artisan craftsman, Stokely loves the finer things in life. Though some think him ferocious, Stokely is as refined as they come. Just look at his music library!

name: Stu
meetText: Meet Stu. He might look prickly but he's actually a big softy! He loves giving back during the holidays. Every year , he holds a toy drive at his local fire station and makes stockings filled with peppermints and chocolate for friends in need. Want to lend a helping hand?

name: Stump
meetText: Stump is the main bouncer for the Skeleton Squad and knows a thing or two about keeping the squad safe. When the band isn't touring Stump teaches a spooky self-defense class, costumes are encouraged!

name: Sugar
meetText: Sugar enjoys slam poetry, bitter black coffee, and her favorite heavy metal bands. Though her bestie Spice doesn’t fully understand her hobbies—like shredding on the electric guitar or tending to her menagerie of crows—she supports her, nonetheless. One thing they can always agree on? Cinnamon buns!

name: Suneetha
meetText: Meet Suneetha, the burrito loving bird with a passion for hip hop music! She loves nothing more than to practice her DJ skills with her friend Nell, but sometimes the Squishmallows neighbours aren't too keen! When she's relaxing Suneetha loves to watch Squish 1 racing and imagines playing a gig at a race one day!

name: Sunny
meetText: Need to know if it's going to be raining next week or if you should pack a jacket? Ask Sunny! She's always had a knack for knowing just what's going to happen next when it comes to the weather, and looks forward to becoming a weather reporter when she's older.

name: Sunshine
meetText: At the end of a storm, there is always a rainbow. Sunshine tends to show up just when things are looking the darkest and brightens up your day with all the colors of her rainbow.

name: Susie
meetText: Susie might be small, but she's got a big voice! Susie is a talented singer, who spends her days singing with the choir team and practicing for the school's talent show. If you need a friend to rock out with, Susie is the perfect buddy to provide backup vocals!

name: Suzy
meetText: Meet Suzy Strawberry, her favorite season is spring. Suzy loves to garden and shows off her beautiful flowers in her flower shop. What should she grow this spring?

name: Svetlana
meetText: Boogie boarding and sunbathing in her hammock are Svetlana's idea of a good time, especially with a good book. She loves a laid back afternoon with an adventure book and a smoothie to keep cool. What should she read next?

name: Swerl
meetText: Swerl has more fun watching basketball then playing it. She's such a loyal fan of her local basketball team. they made Swerl her own jersey! Swerl wears it proudly to all the home games, and even though she isn't the fastest to jump and cheer, she the loudest!

name: Swish
meetText: Swish is a swordfish but don't let that scare you! He's friendly and laid back. He only ever uses his sword to stir sugar into his coffee! He goes to his local bakery every morning for his favorite blueberry scone and coffee and works on his daily crossword puzzles!

name: Syana
meetText: Syana is a talented DJ known for creating the best mashups to move and groove to, especially the throwback classics. They love throwing pool parties and cookouts and make sure to turn the speakers all the way up. Grab your swimsuit and dancing shoes because everyone is invited!

name: Sydnee
meetText: Meet Sydnee. This squirrel wants to be a super-spy when she grows up! Sydnee loves to watch spy and undercover agent movies with her dad, they even have their own secret code words. Sydnee wants her dad to build a super-secret tree house, would you like to help?

name: Sydney
meetText: Meet Sydney. From solving crimes to swimming with manatees, this mushroom really does it all! You can usually find her at concerts, vibing to her favorite music with friends. So if you need a concert buddy, you know who to call!

name: Tabitha
meetText: Early mornings and asking "why" fuel this tabby cat! Tabitha is a curious cat who loves to write and one day wants to be a journalist. She prefers behind the scenes to the spotlight, and is always thinking of her next story angle.

name: Tadita
meetText: Meet Tadita. Tadita is a Talk Show Host who loves to spice things up! Call in your question, and Tadita will give you the sassy truth! She might call you out if you are doing something wrong, but she will always do it with love.

name: Tahoe
meetText: No hill is too steep for Tahoe! In fact, this cat prefers to bike on an incline. She leaves home every morning to go on a hilly 5-mile bike ride and can see the whole neighborhood from the top! Think you can pedal it out with Tahoe?

name: Tajo
meetText: This fuzzy 'Mallow may be a Tasmanian devil, but don't let his name fool you! He's one of the sweetest guys around. Tajo is very active and loves to hike, climb and swim. He's studying to become a conservation scientist so that he can help protect forests and national parks!

name: Talford
meetText: Talford is an expert at playing hide and seek. When he's not hiding in the branches of a tree or a shrub, he loves to do arts and crafts with his friends. Making friendship bracelets is his favorite! Do you want to make some?

name: Talia
meetText: Talia loves to garden, she even tries to teach her cousins Bop and Buttons when they visit. Talia has one of the prettiest gardens around.

name: Talib
meetText: Meet Talib. This pizza-loving pterodactyl is cooking up something special. He combined his love for woodwork and food and built his own pizza oven! Now Talib can make specialty pizzas for all of his friends and other pizza enthusiasts. Would you like a slice?

name: Talisa
meetText: Looking for some help with your website? Talisa is the caticorn for you! As a web developer, she can create the perfect website for your needs. Last week she finished working on a video gaming website for one of her friends, do you want to check it out?

name: Tallulah
meetText: Tallulah is a rare find, and has magical powers because of the horn on her head. She's a great magician and loves to show off her tricks. P.S. You can rub her tummy for good luck on February 14th!

name: Tally
meetText: You won’t be able to contain your excitement when Tally walks into the room. She continues to lift the other Squishmallows up with her role as a health and fitness coach. Need some motivation? Schedule a one-on-one with your favorite pal.

name: Tangerine
meetText: Tangerine and her best friend Posey love to play mini-golf. Their favourite restaurant has mini-golf, horseshoes, and a Ferris wheel! After a day of putting, Tangerine loves to watch the sunset on the Ferris wheel, maybe you can join them one day.

name: Tangie
meetText: Grab your wings and get ready for flight school, the bat class is all here! Tangie is learning how to fly, she can't wait to soar through the night sky. She hopes to be the fastest bat in the class, do you want to race?

name: Tanja
meetText: Meet Tanja. She is always laughing at the most inopportune moments. She can't help it! Something about a quite room tickles her silly bone! But her laughter is contagious and even gets Santa and his elver cracking up! Think you can keep a straight face around Tanja? Good luck!

name: Tank
meetText: Because of his size, Tank may look like a menacing mallow, but he lives by the motto: "peace, love, and minding my own business". This hammerhead hippie wants to live in harmony and just enjoy life.

name: Tanner
meetText: Tanner is a concert fanatic! What’s his favorite music style? Jazz! Come be front and center at Tanner’s next gig on trumpet. Don’t miss him and his band perform and travel through the world of music.

name: Tansy
meetText: Tansy visits every art gallery in his city---even the artists know him by name! This 'Mallow counts down the days to new exhibits, and the multimedia and installations are his favorite! Will you join Tansy for a gallery tour?

name: Tara
meetText: Shh! Tara is librarian in training thanks to her favorite childhood series, 'The Boxcar Children'. She loves volunteering on the weekend to read books at her local library.

name: Taryn
meetText: Taryn loves Valentine's Day; the cards, the hugs, and getting her favorite candies! Each year she gives out hand-made cards to all her friends, this time she made a few extra (just in case!). Do you have a valentine for Taryn?

name: Tasha
meetText: Tasha loves hot pink with sparkles and goes bowling with her dad every weekend. She even has hot pink shoes and a sparkly bowling ball that match! For good luck she rubs the bottom of her shoes three times and then blows a kiss while her ball rolls down the lane. Believe it or not, that gives her good luck!

name: Tatiana
meetText: Tati loves dancing, baking, and exploring with her friends. She wants to save the world one day at a time. Catch her with her friends out in the wild or in the library reading up on her next big adventure!

name: Tavio
meetText: Tavio loves magic tricks and scary movies, this year he wants to have a scary magic birthday party. He wants a hypnotist or a scary magic show, and a giant magician hat pinata

name: Taylor
meetText: Looking for someone to design your next red carpet outfit? Taylor is the Squishmallow for you! This seamstress has a passion for fashion and can create your dream outfit for any occasion.

name: Tazik
meetText: Here's comes Tazik! This magnificent 'Mallow loves going to the skate park with friends. Last week he got a cool new skateboard to match his rainbow 'doo!

name: Teddy
meetText: Teddy is a basketball coach and his favorite color is orange. After championship games he takes the team out for orange cream soda floats . Teddy has a lucky bandana that he wears all season, can you guess what color it is?

name: Tegan
meetText: Introducing... Tegan! Start following this 'Mallow now before she becomes a big dance star. Tegan started the latest glow-in-the-dark dance craze after sharing her dance routines online. Tegan wears twinkling shoes and holds glowsticks, but her signature move is spinning a light-up hoop!

name: Tenise
meetText: Meet Tenise, he just moved to the big city from the jungle! Change can be scary, but he's already made so many new friends! He works at a bakery and brought a little of the jungle with him! He makes the best banana coconut cakes in town. Try one, he's got extra!

name: Tenzing
meetText: If you love to climb rocks then Tenzing is the one for you! Tenzing loves to scale the seawalls whenever she goes, her most recent adventure was climbing a sunken ship. Go ahead and ask her about all the cool things she's seen, Tenzing is full of stories.

name: Ter
meetText: Nothing spells happiness for Ter like rest and relaxation. She's one busy 'Mallow, but she makes sure to put a spa day on her calendar. With her favorite aromatherapy candles and cucumber slices on her eyes, she can truly feel at peace. What's your favorite way to relax?

name: Terell
meetText: Meet Terell. Ever since Terell found his lucky clover, good things seem to happen wherever he goes! Maybe it’s the clover and maybe it’s his optimistic outlook. He sees the bright side of life and is great at helping others see it too! It’s hard not to feel lucky when hanging with Terell!

name: Teresa
meetText: Who loves the color purple, eating delicious food, and helping people? Teresa! This busy unicorn is studying to be a doctor by day and a foodie by night.

name: Terry
meetText: Gobble gobble, it's time for Terry's famous garlic mashed potatoes! Every year Terry visits his old foster family to meet the current foster mallows. He knows it's not always easy growing up that way but he tries to show the mini mallows that one day they'll be okay!

name: Tetero
meetText: Tetero molds sugar skulls at home with sugar and meringue powder. He has a knack for painting them in bright and shiny colors, and loves to gift them to friends during Dia de los Muertos celebrations. Tetero is reminded of his mother this time of year, since they used to always paint sugar skulls together.

name: Tex
meetText: Introducing Tex the taco! Cheese, onions, and a little extra spice are some of Tex’s favorite things. Tex is a chef and loves to use new ingredients to mix things up. This tasty taco knows how to throw a party, especially when his favorite toppings are in town!

name: Thayer
meetText: Are you ready for Thayer, this mischievous mallow has some tricks up his sleeves! Thayer loves pranks, scary movies, and anything blue-raspberry. One day he wants to host a prank channel where the contestants dress up as giant blue-raspberries and play games. TBD if his mom will let him!

name: Theo
meetText: Theo loves cars, trucks, and anything that can move fast. He spends his time fixing cars and dreams of racing them someday!

name: Theotto
meetText: Theotto lives out in the marshes! He spends most of the year in hibernation, waiting for the perfect weather. With his large size and quiet demeanor, Theotto is one of the most beloved neighbors in the community. This charming 'Mallow invites you to his yearly autumn equinox party!

name: Thomas
meetText: Thomas wants to be just like his big brother Nic when he gets older, this year he gets to help DJ the Squishmallow Valentine Dance Will you be his valentine?

name: Thompson
meetText: Thompson is one cheerful armadillo. He always has a smile on his face. He's a night owl who loves listening to music, especially punk rock! Thanks to his older brother, that's his favorite style of music. He cherishes his older brother and learns everything from him!

name: Tia
meetText: Say hello to Tia! Tia is always on top of the latest streetwear and fashion trends, and even learned how to sew so she could make her own clothing line! She loves using recycled fabric to make unique clothes that are comfy too. What should Tia call her fashion line?

name: Tibby
meetText: Tibby loves tree climbing and playing sports outside. She has a curious personality and loves to try new things. Her friends say the best thing about Tibby is her big heart.

name: Tiff
meetText: Tiff has dreams of being an actress, she loves playing new characters and being part of a new story. When it's time to get into a new role, she sits at her vanity to read her lines in a mirror. What's her next role? Helping her family with the chores.

name: Tiffany
meetText: Tiffany's favorite Valentine's drink is chocolate milk with red heart sprinkles. She loves to play tennis and is looking for a doubles partner. Could it be you?

name: Tilly
meetText: Tilly never misses a local baseball game and loves to watch them from high in the sky--- it's the best view! Since baseball is her favorite sport to watch she's learning how to play and someday hopes to be a pitcher. Could you help Tilly throw her first pitch?

name: Tilman
meetText: Tilman loves to race his friends through the snow during the day and loves curling up by the fire at night with frozen treats. He's fiercely loyal to his squad and wants to be a lawyer one day!

name: Tim
meetText: Ever seen Tim before? You might not recognize him now, but you will!  He is one of the greatest leading guitarists of today. Want to join Tim on his next tour bus? He gets to travel all over the world alongside his younger brother, Jim! What’s his favorite kind of music to perform? Alternative rock! He loves celebrating birthdays, which is why his January 1st birthday is always poppin'.

name: Tim
meetText: Ever seen Tim before? You might not recognize him now, but you will!  He is one of the greatest leading guitarists of today. Want to join Tim on his next tour bus? He gets to travel all over the world alongside his younger brother, Jim! What’s his favorite kind of music to perform? Alternative rock! He loves celebrating birthdays, which is why his January 1st birthday is always poppin'.

name: Timmy
meetText: Who's there? It's Timmy! He hosts the most entertaining pumpkin patch parties every Halloween. The only thing Timmy enjoys more than hosting parties is telling knock-knock jokes! In fact, Timmy asks that you tell him your funniest knock-knock joke to RSVP. Do you have a joke for Timmy's party?

name: Tina
meetText: Tina’s style is one for the books. Her patterned clothing isn’t the only thing that stands out about this spunky Squishmallow. She is known for her unforgettable hair styles that leave every Squishmallows excited for their next hairdo!

name: Tinley
meetText: Hats off to the chef, Tinley is in the building! Tinley loves to cook and just became the head chef at a new restaurant. She dedicated her first dish to her noni, she calls it Noni's Pasta, you should try it!

name: Tinsel
meetText: Have you ever wondered why winter cheer is so important? The long dark nights and dreary days  can makes some 'Mallows blue, and Tinsel is here to help. Even if the holidays are hard to handle, Tinsel wants to be the reason that other 'Mallows smile.

name: Tito
meetText: Tito is known for being quiet but when he has something funny to say, all his friends crack up. Tito wants to be a counselor when he grows up to help kids who are quiet like him.

name: TJ
meetText: Want to know a secret? TJ is a spy! From holiday caroler Trina Jinglebell to mad scientist Tammy Jurassic. TJ has a disguise for every occasion. Later this week, she's even going undercover at a supervillain convention—as The Jitterbug, of course!

name: Tobey
meetText: Do you want to go on a berry-picking adventure? Tobey is the ‘Mallow for you! Tobey loves all berries but his favorite is the blueberry. He loves fresh blueberries to make muffins, pancakes, and even blueberry cookies!

name: Tobias
meetText: Tobias signed up to be on the school's cheer team, but he's nervous about tomorrow's audition. He's hoping years of dance practice will make him in the squad! Tobias shines with school spirit and his strong tail can help with cheer pyramids. Think Tobias will make the team?

name: Todd
meetText: Have you ever wondered how to play the harmonica? Todd is a harmonica hero - he can play almost any song he hears! Watch for him on the newest game show 'Play That Tune' to see if he's the next big harmonica sensation!

name: Tom
meetText: Tom really knows how to light up a room! He spends all year looking forward to whipping out his Christmas decorations! He loves matching his tinsel to his ornaments and dawning the perfect sparkling star and lights! Want to borrow some of his decorations? He'd love to share!

name: Tomar
meetText: Square dancing and sugar cookies are two of Tomar's favorite things. Her perfect day would be a huge square dance with all her friends, followed by baking cookies. Do want to come along?

name: Tomara
meetText: Blackberry jam on peanut butter toast is Tomara's favorite breakfast food, she could eat it every day! Tomara can't wait until the school trip to a blackberry farm, she hopes they'll even get to pick some! Do you want to pick blackberries with Tomara?

name: Tommy
meetText: Tommy loves to play pool and card games, someday he wants to open up an arcade! Tommy wants to add his favorite food to the menu: loaded baked potatoes with cheese, sour cream and extra bacon. Would you visit his arcade?

name: Tomos
meetText: Rainy days makes Tomos jump for joy! This frog never minds getting caught without an umbrella—he always has his hat on! There's nothing cozier than a rainy night in autumn with a hot cup of tea. Will you stay in with Tomos?

name: Toni
meetText: Meet Toni. She is an amazing gardener and loves to spend her time in the fresh air and playing in the dirt. When she grows up, Toni wants to study plant medicine. Do you want to garden with Toni?

name: Tonya
meetText: Tonya practices internal medicine for 'Mallows of all ages—it's a dream come true! When Tonya was a little piglet, she got sick for a whole month. But instead of letting that bring her down, she was inspired to be a doctor! Will you let Tonya check your vitals?

name: Tori
meetText: Tori is known for being a multitasker. She can do algebra homework, clean her room, and talk on the phone with a friend all at the same time! How does Tori accomplish so much? Her eight tentacles, of course! When Tori needs a break, she loves to lay out and soak up some vitamin D by the store.

name: Torrence
meetText: Wanna to take a trip with Torrence? Torrence's goal is to tour all the parks on her map, and she's looking for a travel buddy! This dragon can hike her way to a high peck and then safely flying back down. Come adventuring with Torrence!

name: Tortuga
meetText: Tortuga is a cruise director! When he isn't leading a conga line on the lido deck, you can find him working on his debut novel. It's about a haunted cruise ship that is definitely not inspired by the one Tortuga works on. At least, that's what he tells passengers...

name: Tracey
meetText: 3-2-1-Drive! Tracey spends her time racing cars, trucks, and one day wants to be a professional monster truck driver! Her birthday is September 17 and this year she wants to have a monster truck themed party.
