name: Tres'zure
meetText: Tres'zure loves to plan events for her friends, especially for their birthdays. She and her friend Kimia plan a wonderful birthday experience for all their friends. Tres'zure's favorite part is creating the vision board and making memories with her friends.

name: Trey
meetText: 'Home run hitter' is this Squishmallow's nickname, Trey is a baseball superstar. He plays every chance he can, and one day hopes to be in the big leagues!

name: Treyton
meetText: Jazz music, prank videos, and grilled cheese sandwiches are some of Treyton's favorite things. One day he accidentally called his saxophone a grilled cheese sandwich, and then he decided to keep the name. What would you name an instrument?

name: Bertwin
meetText: Meet Bertwin. He loves coffee, reading, and combing his beard. He loves to read books about magic and mystery and is even working on his own novel. Bertwin gets pretty distracted so he needs a study buddy to help him stay focused on his writing; will you help him write?

name: Trilly
meetText: Trilly splurged on a big makeup kit! She loves the color palette and can't wait to play around with different looks. Trilly doesn't need a special occasion to get dressed up she has fun expressing herself though makeup every day! Will you let Trilly give you a makeover?

name: Trina
meetText: Trina loves to color and go on adventures with her brother Triston and their friends. She wants to be a deep sea diver someday and tries to help her brother get over his fear of swimming.

name: Trinity
meetText: Meet Trinity, she loves tapioca pudding, tortellini, and tamales. Trinity loves baseball even more than her brother Trey and wants to be a team manager when she grows up.

name: Trish
meetText: Trish wants a hug when she's having a bad day. Will you help cheer Trish up?

name: Tristan
meetText: Want to get in shape? Schedule a session with Tristan, an amazing personal trainer! He’s training for a bodybuilding competition right now, and after that, a marathon!

name: Triston
meetText: Triston is rarely seen without his twin sister Trina. They join the same clubs at school and even have the same class schedule. One place you won't find him - the pool (he is afraid of swimming).

name: Troy
meetText: Grab your clubs and get ready to hit the green with Troy! He spends his free time perfecting his swing and improving his putting game. One day he hopes to win the tournament!

name: Trudy
meetText: Trudy is always up on the latest trends, which is why her friends love when she does their hair! When she’s not in the salon, you can catch her reading a magazine, shopping or enjoying a beautiful walk in the park.

name: Truman
meetText: Truman is a dentist who loves to travel. This turtle swims around the world offering dental care to all 'Mallows in need. Truman knows having teeth cleaned isn't easy for everyone, so he makes sure every cleaning is quick even fun! Want to hear one of his classic knock-knock jokes?

name: Tuck
meetText: Are you ready to meet the best dressed horse at the Kentucky Derby? Tuck is one stylish pony! He loves to dress up and his motto is 'dress to impress'. Tuck matches funky patterns with florals, stripes with gingham, and almost always has a fresh red rose on hand.

name: Tucker
meetText: Tucker hurt his friend Medina's feelings yesterday, but that wasn't his intention. Now he wants to make it up to her by preparing her favorite food - tacos! Tucker thinks a big hug and homemade meal are the perfect apology. How do you make up with your friends?

name: Tula
meetText: Tula loves rock climbing and reading, but not at the same time. She and her best friend Vanessa go climbing on the weekends, they have matching helmets and support each other as they climb. After a long day, she can't wait to curl up and read her latest book.

name: Tulio
meetText: Tulio has a big goal, to go to every baseball stadium ever! He’s not sure yet how many he can get to, but so far he’s visited 4. Do you want to go with him to a game soon?

name: Tuluck
meetText: Tuluck volunteers at his local elementary afterschool program. He's known as a homework wizard! No other 'Mallow can solve homework problems like Tuluck. This keeps him super busy, bouncing around and helping all the students. Tuluck wouldn't have it any other way!

name: Turk
meetText: Turk wants a hug after winning his cross-country races! He tries to run faster each time to beat his own records. Will you give him a hug after his next race?

name: Twyla
meetText: Twyla is a tooth fairy in training, and wants to be the best one ever! She is still learning how to collect teeth with her magic tooth wand but one day she'll get to leave behind all kinds of wonderful prizes for the teeth she collects.

name: Tycho
meetText: Tycho is a sustainability engineer, creating products, buildings, and systems to meet a set of sustainability standards. Even her fun hobby is good for the earth! She makes eco-friendly soaps for her friends and family that have zero waste, are non-toxic, and smell like vanilla lavender. What scent should Tycho make next?

name: Tyler
meetText: Meet Tyler. He loves playing in the dirt, soccer, and eating cold pizza for breakfast. Tyler wants to be like his dad and study plants when he grows up. He loves learning about plants and how they can survive in so many different climates.

name: Tyree
meetText: Have you met Tyree? This perky pup works at a hair salon and plans to do hair for the movies one day! After a long day he loves to curl up with pizza and a good book, do you want to join him?

name: TyRee
meetText: Who loves animals and working on the farm? TyRee does! She wakes up early and talks to them throughout the day, sometimes they even help her with silly pranks. Do you want to visit TyRee's farm?

name: Ulana
meetText: Ulana dealt with a lot of life changes last year that left her feeling tired and a bit down. So, she started a positivity routine! Ulana writes a daily gratitude list and lights wishing candles. Today, Ulana is grateful for her 'Mallow pals and wishes for her basil plant to grow big and strong!

name: Ulga
meetText: Meet Ulga! This magical ‘Mallow is a magician’s assistant! You can catch her on stage taming fierce tigers then making them disappear in a puff of sparkles and smoke! With Ulga, you never know what magical tricks and surprises lay in store!

name: Uma
meetText: If you're in need of a card for someone special, you have to go to Uma's shop. She makes the most beautiful cards! Uma has cards for everything; from birthdays to bad days and everything in between. What kind of card should Uma make for you?

name: Umberto
meetText: Umberto teaches "Advanced Clownery" at the local college. This semester, his students are learning how to ride a unicycle and juggle bowling pins— at the same time! Umberto promises that if everyone passes their final exam, they can pie him in the face!

name: Uri
meetText: Uri loves peppermint mocha drinks and cinnamon sugar cookies, especially when it's hot out! Winter flavours are their favourite. Uri makes extra dough and strores the finished cookies in the freezer for an extra yummy treat.

name: Ursula
meetText: Are you ready to make an investment? Ursula is the cat for you! She helps the Squishmallows with a lot of their investing and performing questions - by day she manages investment portfolios and by night she is working on her karaoke career!

name: Unai
meetText: Unai teaches meditation and is known for their cozy techniques. A fluffy cushion and warm shawl helps them feel the most recharged after each practice. Unai also believes in the healing power of naps, and even wrote a book about it! Where's your fave spot for a quick nap?

name: Valentina
meetText: Valentina lives with her cousin Bubbles and helps manage the family business, the Hippity Hop Hat store. Valentina loves styling her squad with hats of all shapes, sizes, and colors. Her specialty? Designing giant Easter egg hats! Would you let Valentina design a hat for you?

name: Valentine
meetText: Valentine believes breakfast is the most important meal of the day. Thats why she starts every morning with 3 chocolate chip pancakes, 2 plates of scrambled eggs, and 1 big glass of orange juice! Valentine calls it her '3,2,1 Special' and can't get enough of it Maybe that's why she's such a morning 'Mallow.

name: Valerie
meetText: Valerie is dressed like a royal performer in her crown and robe. She swoops in to help other performers get ready for the show. Valerie knows the first rule in the show biz, that the show must go on. She's willing to pitch in and do what she can to help others.

name: Vanessa
meetText: When she's not climbing with her friend Tula, you can find Vanessa practicing for her latest choir concert. She loves to sing and has a new solo to practice, her first one this year! Will you help her practice?

name: Varity
meetText: Who loves pink, playing tag, and learning from podcasts? It must be Varity! This husky loves pink, from her backpack to her breakfast. She also loves to play games and learn. Each week Varity sends cards to her friends with some of the fun facts from her favorite podcasts.

name: Vas
meetText: Meet Vas. They express themselves through fashion and art! Whether its a sequin jacket or a disco ball earrings, everything Vas wears make them shine inside and out! Vas loves their LGBTQ family because there is space for everyone! How do you express yourself?

name: Vee
meetText: Meet your new magical friend, Vee! Whether it's curled up with a good book or cheering on her favorite team, Vee ALWAYS dresses to impress.  Vee loves fashion and lollipops. However, her true passion is for sports and hopes to one day be a fantasy sports telecaster!

name: Vera
meetText: If you're in need of some good news, Vera has got your back! Vera wants to be a reporter and looks for one good thing to report each day. Some days it can be hard, but Vera loves to deliver good news. Do you have any to share?

name: Vermicelli
meetText: Are you superstitious? Vermicelli sure is. This bundle of nerves forgoes umbrellas, avoids ladders, and skips right over every sidewalk crack. Though he sometimes feels silly being so cautious, Vermicelli isn't taking any chances. He even dyed his black cat white!

name: Veronica
meetText: If you like adventure, pretzels, and crossing books off your reading list, Veronica is the Octopus for you! With a book or two in each tentacle, you can be sure she’s on some amazing adventures.

name: Vickie
meetText: If you love decorating cupcakes and watching cheesy TV shows, Vickie is the Squishmallow for you! She loves to wear her cupcake apron and talk to the TV while she's baking - she LOVES the drama of her favorite shows.

name: Vie
meetText: If there's a photo booth nearby, you can bet Vie is already in front of the camera! She is a big photo booth enthusiast, and don't even ask her how many photo strips she has collected already-because it's a lot! Ready to capture the moment with Vie?

name: Vig
meetText: Little Vig can’t wait to grow their froggy legs! They know there’s so much to explore on land, but for now, Vig loves spending time with their siblings and finding sunny spots in the lake to swim. Will you visit Vig after they hop out of the water?

name: Viggy
meetText: Viggy just got his braces removed! Now he's going to devour all the crunchy, chewy foods he wasn't able to eat for a few years—starting with popcorn! Viggy's favorite flavor is caramel with peanuts. This Halloween is going to be the best yet. Want to snack on sweets with Viggy?

name: Vince
meetText: Vince is no ordinary vampire, this goofy guy is full of jokes and considers himself a scholarly creature. He tries to apply his favorite subject, history, to the jokes he tells and if his jokes don't impress you then his latest research on historical mallow mysteries will!

name: Vinny
meetText: Did you see a flash of green go by? It was probably Vinny! This terrific turtle practically lives in his roller blades, he skates everywhere he goes. Vinny loves maths and science because they help him calculate how fast he's going. Do you think you can skate faster than Vinny?

name: Violet
meetText: Violet is the bright, spirited queen of the sea who has a passion for adventure and exploration! She loves to join Kai on his quest for sunken treasure and uses her degree in archaeology to identify where the treasure originated!

name: Vivie
meetText: Vivie loves salt, sand, and sunny days. She's been known to spend all day at the beach eating tacos, building sandcastles, and playing in the waves. Sometimes she covers herself in kelp and pretends she's a sea monster to make her friends laugh. Grab a bathing suit and come swim!

name: Vlad
meetText: Vlad is a home-body during the day but at night he’s the lead singer in a mallow metal band, the Skeleton Squad. When he’s not on tour or in practice you can find him napping the day away. Wanna know his guilty pleasure? Spaghetti and meatballs, but hold off on the garlic bread!

name: Wade
meetText: Original: Wade is a pretty big guy, and at first glance gives many 'Mallows a fright! He tries not to take it personally but one day Wade hopes his looks won't make other 'Mallows so scared of him. Fun fact about Wade: he plays the violin.

name: Walker
meetText: Have you ever seen a goat play the banjo? Walker can't, but he's learning how! He wants to start a Squishmallow jam band, do you want to join?

name: Wallis
meetText: Wallis spends his summer afternoons at the park! This mallow loves to fly a kite, or lie on his favorite woven blanket watching birds and devouring potato salad. Wallis even sticks around after the sun sets and waits for the stars to come out—he can name all the constellations!

name: Wally
meetText: Wally may seem rough on the edges, but he's really sweet once you get to know him! His adventurous spirit can't be matched by anything else on the planet. He loves exploring and his favorite quests to go on always include his best friends!

name: Wamina
meetText: Meet Wamina. She is a special education teacher who loves teaching her students new ways to express themselves. On the weekends she likes to explore the mountains, hiking with friends, and enjoying the fresh air. Will you go on an outdoor adventure with Wamina?

name: Wanda
meetText: Wanda loves all things strategy - chess, dominoes, and making the perfect sandwich. When she visits her grandparents they take her to play games in the park and afterwards, she makes them her famous sandwiches.

name: Warner
meetText: Who can't sit still and loves to try new things? It's Warner! This elephant loves to use his imagination and do things differently with the games, foods, and even the toys he plays with. He wants to be an inventor when he grows up.

name: Warren
meetText: If you're always in a mood for a laugh, Warren is the 'Mallow for you! This boar tests all his jokes on his buddies before performing his stand-up act at a comedy club. Warren jokes a lot about himself and his wacky childhood. Did you know he has 10 siblings?

name: Waverly
meetText: Grab your boots and basket, it's time to visit Waverly's garden! She grows fruit and veggies for her own backyard. Fill your basket with yummy produce, just be careful not to step on anything in the garden.

name: Waymond
meetText: You can usually find Waymond at the beach! They love the ocean more than any place in the world - even the sound of crashing waves brings Waymond joy. If they could have any superpower, it would be to breathe underwater, so they could swim all day long! Want to join Waymond at the beach?

name: Webb
meetText: Wondering how to spend your weekly allowance! Call Webb! They understand all the business trends and make sure to keep up to date with the latest news. It's no wonder Webb's been so successful advising 'Mallows on what to do with their money!

name: Wellesley
meetText: Wellesley is the editor-in-chief of a magazine—a magazine about Wellesley! Featuring such columns as 'What Wellesley Wears' and 'What Wellesley Eats.' Wellesley loves keeping his readers up-to-date on the wonderful world of Wellesley. Not enough Wellesley? Check out the podcast!

name: Wen
meetText: Wen loves roller skating, shopping, and hiking. Her favorite color is pink so she wears her pink hiking boots on all her hiking adventures. Wen likes to treat herself with Italian food and garlic bread after a long hike. Are you ready for a hike day with Wen?

name: Wendy
meetText: Welcome Wendy! Wendy's birthday is May 10, meaning her SquishScope sign is a Taurus. You can always find her out on the basketball court (she won the MVP award last year) or in the science lab, since chemistry is her favorite subject. She wants to be a famous scientist when she grows up and likes to paint pictures of her inventions.

name: Wesley
meetText: Wesley grew up with his aunt, and loves making paper airplanes. His aunt is a musician and he gets to travel the world for her tours. Wesley makes each of the band members a good luck airplane to throw at the start of all their shows.

name: Wexla
meetText: Have you met Wexla? This wonderful witch wants to be an engineer when she grows up. She plans to design tall, spooky buildings that are also eco-friendly.

name: Whitney
meetText: Whitney is no ordinary witch - she lives for the virtual world! Whitney designs video games and while her sisters are a little girly, she considers herself a little more warlock at heart. Her latest creation takes you on an adventure of zombies, gremlins and danger, with a big boss fight at the end! Would you play her game?

name: Wilbie
meetText: Wilbie loves to make interesting sandwich combinations and then sharing a picnic feast when he's done! One of his favorite sandwich creations includes brie cheese, apples, and spicy pepper jam. What ingredients can Wilbie add to your sandwich?

name: Wilde
meetText: Wilde sleeps soundly even after the sun rises. They love dreaming through early daylight hours and say that's when they get their best ideas for a song. Sometimes Wilde records a song they heard in their dream as soon as they wake up, which could be late afternoon. But a good song can happen at any moment!

name: Wilfred
meetText: Meet Wilfred. His energy, joy, and smile can be quite contagious, so get ready for some fun! Wilfred loves playing catch, quality time with his friends, and late night snacks. Want to make his day? Ask him for a big bear hug!

name: Will
meetText: Will's favorite thing to do is play in the snow; building snow forts, decorating snow dragons, and especially snowball fights. He builds a huge snow castle to play in, it even has a moat!

name: Waverly
meetText: Grab your boots and basket, it's time to visit Waverly's garden! She grows fruit and veggies for her own backyard. Fill your basket with yummy produce, just be careful not to step on anything in the garden.

name: Willis
meetText: Willis is the ultimate comic book fan! He has an impressive collection of hardcover editions and single issues decorating the bookshelves in his home. When Willis isn’t catching up on his reading, you can find him exploring a new fantasy video game. He loves those epic soundtracks!

name: Willow
meetText: Willow the Pegasus is a flying ball of energy! She's ready to get up early for her favorite fitness class and spend the rest of her day helping her friends and finding adventures all over town. You can find her lending a helping hand to all her neighbors on the weekend.

name: Willoughby
meetText: Want to know why Willoughby is so good at dodgeball? He's scared of getting hit! Whether dipping, diving, or flying through the air, Willoughby will do anything to avoid the ball. Though some call him dodgy, that's the name of the game!

name: Willy
meetText: Willy was the runt of the litter-but that doesn’t hold this mallow back! He is fascinated by storms and wants to be a weatherman when he grows up! He loves bow-ties and he has a weather bow-tie collection he can’t wait to show off!

name: Wilma
meetText: Wilma is an excellent mixologist – she makes the best apple cider around! She makes big batches every year starting in September for her apple cider stand. Would you try Wilma’s apple cider?

name: Winger
meetText: Winger is a powerful griffon whose job is a flight instructor. He teaches others to look out for one another and to be aware of obstacles that could get in the way. He glides effortlessly in the sky while keeping an eye out to make sure you're safe and secure.

name: Winifred
meetText: Winifred is a jeweler and creates stunning one-of-a-kind pieces that sparkle and glow. She gets to know her customer before designing something special for them and loves to see their reaction. Would you like her to make something for you?

name: Winnie
meetText: Winnie is not your ordinary walrus, she loves making ice cream sundaes and sand castles (not at the same time). When she's not making her specialty gummy bear sundae you can find her creating her next sand castle masterpiece!

name: Winnie
meetText: Winnie is a baker, and loves to decorate cookies with her sisters. Her favorite way to decorate is using purple, green, and orange sprinkles. She once tried to bake a GIANT jack 'o lantern cookie but her oven was too small. One day she wants to bake the biggest cookie in the world.

name: Winona
meetText: This is one excited Squishmallow, she's learning a new language AND getting a sister! Winona's new sister is deaf, so their whole family is learning how to sign. Will you help her practice?

name: Winsey
meetText: Meet Winsey. His love language is cooking! It's how he shows he cares! Come check out one of his famous, backyard cookouts jam-packed with funky music, dancing, delicious food, and great company! Everyone's invited so grab a plate!

name: Winston
meetText: Winston is an aspiring chef who takes his cooking creativity to the next level. His friends inspire his latest culinary delights and he is always ready to whip up his famous mac and cheese.

name: Witt
meetText: Witt hosts games night every Friday in their tabletop game store. New players are always welcome since it's a great way to meet 'Mallows and make new friends. Witt even has seaweed soda on tap free for all players! Come join Witt this Friday for lively game play and community vibes!

name: Wren
meetText: Who's that butterfly covered in flour? It's Wren! She works at a bakery and gets up very early to bake yummy bread, rolls, and croissants for breakfast.

name: Wyatt
meetText: Meet Wyatt. Wyatt loves shooting hoops at home with his big sister, Wendy! These two ‘Mallows play pickup basketball all the way until dinner time. This year, Wyatt became a mathlete, so playing a fun game is just what he needs to stay sharp in between competitions.

name: Wanda
meetText: Wanda loves all things strategy - chess, dominoes, and making the perfect sandwich. When she visits her grandparents they take her to play games in the park and afterwards, she makes them her famous sandwiches.

name: Xam
meetText: Welcome to Xam's nature center! Let this gentle 'Mallow teach you all about caring for the local ecosystem, while you also make new friends from the community. Xam tends to his melon trees most, and loves to have dishes of fresh sliced muskmelon for visitors.

name: Xandra
meetText: There's no Squishmallow more well traveled than Xandra! She used to be a professional scuba diver and traveled to over 50 countries before she hung up her snorkel to work in the city. Unlike her hermit neighbors, Xandra is an outgoing and friendly crab who loves to party with her friend Carlos.

name: Xavier
meetText: Meet Xavier. He loves rock climbing, board games, and desert. He knows the best spot in town for tiramisu! He's always game for a late-night snack run or staying up to tell funny stories under the stars. Just be sure to bring a flashlight, he's a little scared of the dark.

name: Xenia
meetText: Roller skates and basketball are two of Xenia's favorite things. She may not be the best player on the team but she does her best to have fun. When she's not on the court you can find her at the skate park with her friend Angelie.

name: Ximena
meetText: Scrapbooking is how Ximena likes to spend her time. She loves to celebrate her family by creating beautiful scrapbooks for each of them. Last week she started one for her quince, one of her favorite days ever. Do you want to scrapbook with Ximena?

name: Xin
meetText: Xin collects cuckoo clocks from all over the world! He hangs them on the walls of his office and kitchen - he's close to having 200 clocks. Wait until it's the next hour because you'll hear all of Xin's clocks ring and sing at the same time!

name: Xiomara
meetText: Grab your goggles and a notebook, it's time for Xiomara's class! Xiomara is a chemistry teacher and loves to have fun in class. Last week she made bath bombs and slime, what will she do next?!

name: Yancy
meetText: Meet Yancy. This 'Mallow is a firecracker on the roller rink. She and her friends created a skating team and they meet every week to practice their moves. After practice, they order the team favorite: an extra-large pineapple and cheese pizza. Would you like a slice?

name: Yara
meetText: Yara is an avid hiker. She loves discovering new places off the beaten path. For every place she goes, she collects a wildflower and keeps it dried and pressed in her journal! Daisies, poppies, and bellflowers, just to name a few! Grab your journal and join her on your next adventure!

name: Yasmin
meetText: Yasmin has always enjoyed lending a helping hand, even as a mini mallow she would volunteer to pass out the snacks in school. Now that she's older, she started a club that volunteers every month, do you want to join?

name: Yekaterina
meetText: Yekaterina works as a tax accountant for the local insurance company. After a long day in the office, she enjoys unwinding at home with a bowl of tuna salad and her beloved cat, Ms. Floof. These besties don't need much, as long as they have each other!

name: Yesenia
meetText: Yesenia loves to spend her day by the pool. She loves to play water games like volleyball and dive for rings and things at the bottom of the pool. When she needs a break she has a cooler full of smoothies and snacks, do you want to join?

name: Yollie
meetText: Yollie is the sweetest Yeti around! This gal loves going to the cabin with her best friends Riah and Gabby. She loves snow cones and making snowmallows in the winter. Join Yollie on her next trip to the cabin!

name: Yukon Striker
meetText: Meet Yukon Striker! Yukon has a fondness for gold, enjoys soaring over the wilderness of Frontier Canada and taking dives at 90 degrees. He's a rugged bird but a true and loyal companion. SCI 12 #25 / Squishdate 10.28.2021

name: Yuri
meetText: Meet Yuri. Yuri loves plants and has a growing collection of indoor plants including a cactus named Fred. Yuri lives in a city where there aren't a lot of trees so Yuri tries very hard to keep the plants alive and happy. What plant should Yuri get next?

name: Yus
meetText: Who is that lamb waiting for an adventure? It's Yus! She lives in the mountains and when she hears the sounds of spring, she loves to join in. Yus loves to sing and hear her songs echo through the mountains. She's looking for a partner to harmonize with, is it you?

name: Zachary
meetText: Zac is a biology enthusiast with a brilliant mind. He is currently a medical student who dreams of becoming a heart surgeon. When he's not studying for exams, he likes to stay active and play flag football with his friends!

name: Zan
meetText: If you need a little magic, Zan is the mallow for you! This whimsical wizard knows a thing or two about magic and loves to help out his friends. The best way to repay him for his time? Walking his broom when he's out of town!

name: Zap
meetText: All aboard for Albacore! Zap is the conductor of a high-speed locomotive that brings handcrafted sushi rolls to rural communities. Make sure to try her sashimi—it's off-the-rails!

name: Zarina
meetText: Zarina has memberships to all the museums in her city! Whenever she has a free day to herself, she swings by to check out the new exhibits. The natural history museum is her favorite, and she almost has all the collector pins! Would you like to join Zarina on her next museum visit?

name: Zaya
meetText: Meet Zaya. She loves traveling and photography. Her dream is to be a model and travel the world with her best friends! She works at a clothing store right now and takes photography classes at night so she can one day achieve her goal.

name: Zaylee
meetText: Zany Zaylee is here, are you ready for some fun? Zaylee loves to do silly things like speak in her own language with her friends, walk sideways on the playground, and drink milkshakes through a crazy straw. What should she do next?

name: Zeena
meetText: Zeena is a true story-teller. She loves to share tales with her friends and family, and has even won a few prizes at school for her work. Look out for her books in the future!

name: Zeke
meetText: Zeke is in charge of the special pit crew that keeps Tracey's race car maintained and running smooth. He absolutely loves noodles, nachos and watching the cars he works on zoom past him on the race track!

name: Zelia
meetText: Meet Zelia, she's got a huge sweet tooth. Lucky for her, her friend Tenise is a baker! Zelia is a talented soccer player and plays every Sunday in the park. After she treats her and her teammates to one of Tenise's delicious coconut cakes made special with extra icing!

name: Zelina
meetText: Día de Los Muertos is one of Zelina's favorite days of the year. Besides the yummy food and wearing makeup, it's a special time to remember and celebrate the lives of family members who passed. This year, she's adding a candle for her mom, would you like to learn more?

name: Zelma
meetText: Meet Zelma. She's a quintessential extrovert. Anytime she's out and about, she runs into someone she knows. Last week she saw a teacher from nursery school! She loves salsa dancing, vintage clothes, and taking care of all her plants at home.

name: Zerdan
meetText: Meet Zerdan. This methodical mutt loves to play games, especially chess! Zerdan wants to be a chess champion and plays whenever they can, one day Zerdan hopes to become a Grandmaster! Zerdan is hoping to play their first match soon, would you like to play?

name: Zhen
meetText: Zhen collects vintage toys. He loves anything made from wood or metal and is extra interested if it has some wear and tear. Today Zhen picked up a large top with a pull string to make it spin! He could spin this top all day. It might be his new favorite in the whole collection!

name: Zinabell
meetText: Meet Zinabell. Catch this 'Mallow rocking the newest and hippest fashion trends! Every week she dyes her hair a new color of the rainbow! When she grows up she wants to style for high fashion runway shows and photoshoots!

name: Zinx
meetText: Have you met Zinx? Zinx has a hilarious sense of humor and is always cracking jokes, they love making their friends laugh. Zinx is the kind of ‘Mallow to be voted the most loveable class clown. Get ready for some jokes that are out of this world.

name: Zipp
meetText: Meet Zipp. He's training for an endurance race that will take him all the way through the jungle! When he's not training, he's loading up on nutritious snacks! Jicama and mango with spicy chili pepper are his favorites! Can you keep up with Zipp? He'd love a training partner!

name: Ziv
meetText: Meet Ziv. He loves gardening and forest conservation! Everyday, he plants a tree to give the forest a little extra help to grow. He's planted 400 trees already! When he grows up, he wants to be a climate scientist and help protect the whole world! Grab a seed and join him!

name: Zobey
meetText: Zobey is great company to be around (even if he doesn't look like it at first!). He can be a sarcastic little fella, but you can count on him when you need to. He's very laid back and always loves to share a few chill jokes with everyone around him.

name: Zoe
meetText: Zoe lives and breathes food. It makes perfect sense since her family owns multiple restaurant businesses in the area. She aspires to become a restaurant owner one day with her cousins, Astrid and Ace.

name: Zoeyana
meetText: This unicorn loves Halloween, from the costumes and the decorations to the treats. She is so excited to go to Holly's Halloween party! Last year, she had a costume contest, party favors, and even a piñata!

name: Zosia
meetText: Zosia started with just one caravan, and loved it so much, she bought another! Now she owns a whole campsite of caravans that travelers can book a stay in. Best part is, each caravan has its own unique theme and design Zosia decorated herself. Call Zosia to reserve a cute caravan for your next trip!

name: Zozo
meetText: Meet Zozo. She loves art and filmmaking and is really quite silly. Zozo loves to have fun with her friends and use her imagination. She loves creative and makes her own videos, drawings, and even toy designs. Do you want to see her portfolio?

name: Zumir
meetText: Zumir makes sweets at a busy candy shop just outside town. He starts early in the morning and lets all those sugary smells flow into the neighborhoods close by. Wouldn't that give you a candy craving? Zumir makes all kinds of treats, but mint chocolate truffles are his specialty!

name: Zumirez
meetText: Stand back—Zumirez baked a big batch of nachos and he just pulled them out of the oven! This 'Mallow is a lifelong vegetarian so his nachos are loaded with three bean chili, fresh avocado chunks, and lots of gooey cheese. Grab a napkin and dig in with Zumirez!

name: Zuzana
meetText: Zuzana plays the guitar and has a big tour coming up. She can't leave without extra rhinestones and a big box of her mom's chocolate chip cookies, she can't go without them!

name: Zyan
meetText: Meet Zyan! This charistmatic 'Mallow makes everyone she talks to feel special. That's because they are! Zyan knows that everyone has something unique and important to offer. Whether it's a silly joke, a random fact, or a new perspective. Zyan wants to hear all about it!

name: Zyta
meetText: Time for Zyta takeover! This 'Mallow hosts the liveliest party and is always the center of attention! Zyta strikes up conversation easily and is always looking for more friends to add to her squad. Stick with Zyta for fun times!

name: Pink Caticorn
meetText: This adorable caticorn is covered in soft fuzz, featuring both the ears of a cat and the horn of a unicorn.

name: Rainbow Llama
meetText: Made just for The Paper Store, this adorable llama pal is covered in rainbow-colored fuzz.

name: Cam
meetText: Original: If you’re looking for a feline friend, Cameron’s your cat. He loves to jump in and out of boxes, build forts with his friends Hoot and Wendy and use his skateboard to get around town. Cam also loves going to the beach to take cat naps with his friends, but is always up for an adventure!
